            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 58,
            "text": "Mi Nga lemâahda i Musa, kuéet wavan; sinna, deffir es, teddam d uâajmi. Kunwi d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 8,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 59,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir waya, Nsemmeê awen, amar a ppesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 8,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 60,
            "text": "Mi Nefka, i Musa, Tazmamt akked ufraz, amar a ppeppwanhum.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 8,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 61,
            "text": "Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: 'a yagdud iw! Kunwi, s tidep, tdensem iman nnwen, mi teddam d uâajmi. Ssutret ssmaê i Uxellaq nnwen; mminet, ppif i kunwi ar Uxellaq nnwen. Issuref awen. Neppa, s tidep, Issuruf, Ipêunu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 8,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 62,
            "text": "Mi tennam: 'a Musa! Ur neppamen yisek, d awezi, alamma nwala Öebbi, âinani'. Tewwet ikwen id ssiâqa, kunwi tepwalim.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 8,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 63,
            "text": "Sinna, Nerra kwen id, deffir tmeppant nnwen, amar a ppesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 8,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 64,
            "text": "S usigna, Nerra yawen tili. Nessers awen d lmenna, ifeôôuoen: 'eççet si téidanin is ikwen Nat'. Ur a£ dnisen, maca densen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 8,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 65,
            "text": "Mi Nenna: 'kecmet tamdint agi, eççet degs, s tawant, ayen i wen ihwan; kecmet si tebburt, s lekni; init: nendem. Ad awen Nsemmeê tuccva nnwen, a Nernu i iâaôviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 9,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 66,
            "text": "Wid idensen bedlen awal, ur d win i sen nnan. Nessers ed, i wid idensen, tawait seg igenni, ilmend n tucmitin nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 9,
            "ruku": 7,
            "hizbQuarter": 3,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 67,
            "text": "Mi issuter Musa aman i ugdud is, Nenna: 'ewwet aéôu, s uâkkwaz ik'. Feggvent ed, segs, mrawsnat tliwa. Yal wa iéôa anda ara issew. 'Eççet, esswet, si ôôeéq n Öebbi. Ur ssefsadet di tmurt am imjaêen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 9,
            "ruku": 8,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 68,
            "text": "Mi tennam: 'a Musa! Ur nesteqnaâ bippa s yiwen n lqut. Nuj a Mass ik, ad a d Issuffe ayen d teggar tmurt: tizzegzewt is, axyaô is, ticcert is, laâds is, lebûel is'. Inna: 'tebam a pbedlem ayen ilhan s wayen ixuûen? Üûubbet ar Maûeô, a n tafem, war ccekk, ayen tessutrem'. Ili d fellasen ddell akked ééelt. Sebbeben d urrif n Öebbi. Ayagi, acku llan ugin issekniyen n Öebbi, neqqen lambiyya, war ssebba. Ayagi, imi âuûan, u zgaren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 9,
            "ruku": 8,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 69,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen, udayen, imasiêiyen, iûabiyen, kra iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ad sâun arraz ar Mass nnsen, ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 70,
            "text": "Mi Nga laâqed yidwen, Nessuli adrar sennig wen: 'eîîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, mmektit ed i illan degs, amar a pêezzbem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 71,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir waya, twexxôem. Lemmer maççi d lfevl n Öebbi fellawen, akked uêunu S, a ppilim seg imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 72,
            "text": "Ni tessnem wid, segwen, iccven di Ssebt. Nenna yasen: 'ilit d iddawen imaâfan'!",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 73,
            "text": "Nerra p d amedya i imuddiren akked wid i ten id ineûfen, u d aâggen i wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 74,
            "text": "Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: 'Öebbi, s tidep, Iumeô awen d a ppezlum tafunast'. Nnan: 'day a tettihiv fella'? Inna: 'ad iyi Isseô Öebbi! Ur ppili seg at war tussna'.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 75,
            "text": "Nnan: 'nuj a ar Mass ik, ad a d Ibeggen anta p'. Inna: 'Neppa, s tidep, la Iqqaô: tafunast ur wessret, ur meééiyet, garasen. Xedmet i wen d ippumôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 76,
            "text": "Nnan: 'nuj ar Mass ik, ad a d Ibeggen ini s'. Inna: 'Neppa, s tidep, la Iqqaô: d tafunast tawôat, ini imfeooeo, ad iaâoeb w ip iwalan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 10,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 77,
            "text": "Nnan: 'nuj ar Mass ik, ad a d Ibeggen anta p. £uône, s tidep, tistan ppemcabint. Ih, ma Iba Öebbi, a nepwanhu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 11,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 78,
            "text": "Inna: 'Neppa, s tidep, la Iqqaô: d tafunast ur taâtib si tyerza n tmurt, ne si tissit n yigran, tûeêêa, ur tepwacôev'. Nnan as: 'tura, tebbwiv d tidep'. Zlan p. Qôib ur ewqimen.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 11,
            "ruku": 9,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 79,
            "text": "Mi tenam yiwen, wa irra p id ef wa. Öebbi Issuffe ed ayen teppeffrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 11,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 80,
            "text": "Nenna: 'ewwtet ep s kra ines'. Akka i Issidir Öebbi lmeggtin. Issenâat awen issekniyen iS, amar a pfehmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 11,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 81,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir waya, qquôen wulawen nnwen; cuban aéôu, ne kteô, di taeôt. Ih, llan iéôa iseg d pfeggiven isaffen. Llan, s tidep, wid ipceqqiqen, teffen d waman segsen. S tidep, llan wid iellin si tugwdi n Öebbi. Ur Ifil Öebbi ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 11,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 4,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 82,
            "text": "Day tôebem a kwen amnen? Ni arbaâ, segsen, ssemêasen i wawal n Öebbi, sinna, mi t fehmen, ad as bedlen udem, u nitni éôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 11,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 83,
            "text": "Mi mmugren wid iumnen, ad inin: 'numen'. Mi qqimen garasen, qqaôen: 'day ad asen tinim ayen i wen Imla Öebbi, a kwen nnaen yis, ar Mass nnwen? Day ur tepmeyyizem ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 11,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 84,
            "text": "Ne ur éôin ara, Öebbi Issen ayen teffren, akked wayen qqaôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 12,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 85,
            "text": "Garasen, at war tauôi, ur nessin Tazmamt, siwa ayen nnwan. Nitni ilen kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 12,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 86,
            "text": "A tawait n wid ipparun Tazmamt s ifassen nnsen, sinna, qqaôen: 'ayagi suô Öebbi', iwakken ad aen, yis, ayen ôxisen! A tawait nnsen, ilmend n wayen uran ifassen nnsen! A tawait nnsen, ef wayen keppben!",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 12,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 87,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ur a tepnal tmes, d awezi, siwa kra n wussan'. Ini: 'day teîîfem lemâahda suô Öebbi? Öebbi, d awezi, ur Izeggil lemâahda S. Ne teqqaôem, ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 12,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 88,
            "text": "Xaîi, win ikesben tucmip, u tennev as tuccva s…, widak, d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 12,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 89,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, widak, d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 12,
            "ruku": 10,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 90,
            "text": "Mi Nga laâqed i At Isôail: 'ur âabdet siwa Öebbi. Elhut ar imawlan, ar llzem nnwen, ar igujilen, ar igellilen. Init i medden, awal imaânen. èéÈallet, zekkit'. Sinna, twexxôem, siwa kra segwen, u, kunwi, tnumrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 12,
            "ruku": 11,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 91,
            "text": "Mi wen Nga laâqed nnwen: 'ur zzazalet idim nnwen, ur pemssuffuet seg ixxamen nnwen'. Da twefqem, kunwi d inagan.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 13,
            "ruku": 11,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 92,
            "text": "Sinna, kunwi d wid imminen, tessuffem arbaâ segwen, seg ixxamen nnsen. Tezzim asen s ibekkaven akked taâdawt. Ma usan kwen id, d imeêbas, tfeddum ten. Irna, ipwagdel awen usuffe nnsen. Day tumnem deg uêric n Tezmamt, tnekôem wayev? Anwa ay d arraz n wid, segwen, ixedmen aya, ma maççi d ddell, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u, ass n tnekra, ad ppunefken i uâaqeb uqsiê mavi? Ur Ifil Öebbi ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 13,
            "ruku": 11,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 93,
            "text": "Widak d wid iuen tudert n ddunit s laxeôt, ur ippifsus fellasen uâaqeb, ur ppusellken.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 13,
            "ruku": 11,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 94,
            "text": "Ni Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Nuzen ed imazanen, deffir es. Nefka abeggen i Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Null it s ôôuê iqedsen. Yal tikelt ideg ara kwen id ias umazan, s wayen ur awen nehwi, tesmewôem iman nnwen. Kra teskaddbem ten, kra tenam ten.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 13,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 95,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ulawen nne qquôen'. Xaîi, Ixza ten Öebbi, ilmend n tijehli nnsen. Drus iten wid iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 13,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 96,
            "text": "Mi ten id tusa Tezmamt, suô Öebbi, d atebbet n wayen illan uôsen, - u llan, iu lêal, ssuturen ad elben wid ijehlen - mi ten id iusa wayen ssnen, ugin t. Ad Inâal Öebbi ijehliyen!",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 14,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 97,
            "text": "I icmet wayen ief zzenzen iman nnsen! Ugin ayen id Issers Öebbi. Ëesden mi id Issers Öebbi, si lfevl iS, i win i S ihwan n yimdanen iS. Sebbeben urrif ar wayev. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb isdullun.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 14,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 98,
            "text": "Ma nnan asen: 'amnet s wayen id Issers Öebbi'! A d inin: 'numen s wayen id irsen uône'. Nekôen ayen i t id itebâan, u neppa d tidep, d atebbet n wayen illan uôsen. Ini: 'acimi tneqqem lambiyya n Öebbi, zik, ma d lmumnin ay tellam'?",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 14,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 5,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 99,
            "text": "Ni iusa kwen id Musa, s ubeggen. Sinna, deffir es, teddam akked uâajmi. Kunwi d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 14,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 100,
            "text": "Mi Nga laâqed yidwen, Nessuli adrar sennig wen: 'eîîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, u ssemêesset'. Nnan d: 'nesla u nâuûa'. Ikecm asen uâajmi ar wul, si tjehli nnsen. Ini: 'dir it wayen i wen iumeô liman nnwen, ma d lmumnin ay tellam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 14,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 101,
            "text": "Ini: 'maday, ar Öebbi, axxam aneggaru i kunwi kan, ur pkkan ara imdanen, mennit tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep'!",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 102,
            "text": "D awezi, ur p pmennin, ilmend n wayen xedmen ifassen nnsen. Öebbi Issen imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 103,
            "text": "A ten tafev, war ccekk, êemmlen tameddurt sennig medden, sennig imcurak. Atan yiwen segsen, issaram ad idder agim iseggwasen. Tewzi n laâmeô is, ur as tessifrir aâaqeb. Öebbi Ipwali ayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 12,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 104,
            "text": "Ini: 'anwa illan d acengu n Jebrayen'? D neppa, s tidep, it id issersen ef wul ik, s lebi n Öebbi. D atebbet n wayen it id izwaren, d nnhaya u d abecceô n lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 13,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 105,
            "text": "Win illan d acengu n Öebbi, lmalayek iS, imazanen iS, Jebrayen, Mikail…, ihi, Öebbi d acengu ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 13,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 106,
            "text": "Ni Nessers ak d issekniyen iberrzen. I ten inekôen, siwa iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 13,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 107,
            "text": "Day yal tikelt ideg ara gen laâqed, a t ixdaâ urbaâ segsen? Ih, tegwti segsen, ur uminen.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 13,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 108,
            "text": "Mi ten id iusa umazan suô Öebbi, itebbet ayen illan uôsen, arbaâ n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, rran Tazmamt n Öebbi s azagur nnsen, amzun ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 15,
            "ruku": 13,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 109,
            "text": "Ddan akked wayen xedmen ccwaîen mgal tagelda n Sliman. Sliman ur ijhil. Maca ccwaîen jehlen. Sseêfaven i medden ssêur, akked wayen id irsen, di Babil, ar lmalayek Harut akked Marut. Ur sselmaden yiwen, mebla ma nnan: 'nekwni newwu kan, ur jehhel'! ÊÊÊËefven, uôsen, amek ara ssemfaôaqen argaz akked tmeîîut is. Ur îîurun yiwen syis, siwa ma Iba Öebbi. ÊÊÊËefven ara ten ivuôôen, ur ten ineffaâ. Ni éôan ar win i p iuen, ur as illi umur di laxeôt. War ccekk, ard ucmit wayen is zzenzen leôwaê nnsen, lemmer éôin!",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 16,
            "ruku": 13,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 110,
            "text": "Lemmer, s tidep, uminen u êezzben, ad ifrir warraz suô Öebbi, lemmer ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 16,
            "ruku": 13,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 111,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur qqaret: 'Âass a d', init: 'Wali a d', u ssemêesset. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 16,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 112,
            "text": "Ur bin ara ijehliyen, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, akked imcurak, ad awen d irs kra n lxiô, suô Mass nnwen. Öebbi Ismenyaf, s uêunu S, win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 16,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 6,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 113,
            "text": "Ur Nessemsay assekni, ne ur t Nesseppu, mebla ma Nebbwi d win it yifen, ne i t icban. Day ur teéôiv ara Öebbi Izmer i yal cci?",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 17,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 114,
            "text": "Day ur teéôiv ara, ar n Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan? Ur tesâim, war Öebbi, bab, ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 17,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 115,
            "text": "Ne tebam a ppesteqsim Amazan nnwen, akken ippusteqsa, zik, Musa? Win ibeddlen liman s tijehli, innetlaf ar yir abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 17,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 116,
            "text": "Si leêsed nnsen, aîas seg wAt Tezmamt, mi sen d tban tidep, budden awen tijehli, mbaâd liman nnwen. Ssemêet, ssemsut, ar d Ias Öebbi s lameô iS. Ni Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 17,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 117,
            "text": "èéallet, zekkit. Ayen ara tezzewrem n lxiô i iman nnwen, a t tafem ar Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipwali ayen akw txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 17,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 118,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ur ikeççem Loennet, siwa win illan d uday, ne d amasiêi'. D wagi ay d asirem nnsen. Ini: 'awit ed atebbet nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 17,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 119,
            "text": "Xaîi, win iunzen i Öebbi, u d aâôvi, ad isâu arraz is, ar Mass is. Ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 17,
            "ruku": 14,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 120,
            "text": "Nnan wudayen: 'imasiêiyen ur sennden s acemma'. Nnan imasiêiyen: 'udayen ur sennden s acemma'. U nitni la qqaôen Tazmamt. Akka, wid ur nessin ara, nnan am nitni. Ad Iêudd Öebbi, garasen, ass n tnekra, ef wayen ief mgarraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 18,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 121,
            "text": "Anwa idensen sennig wid igedlen, di leowamaâ n Öebbi, asmekti n yisem iS, u lhan d deg ussexôeb nnsen? Widak, ur iwata ara a ten kecmen, siwa ma s tugwdi. I nitni, ddell di ddunit, u aâaqeb abarar di laxeôt.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 18,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 122,
            "text": "N Öebbi agmuv akked utaram. Ar wanda tezzim, din Udem n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 18,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 123,
            "text": "Nnan: 'Öebbi Isâa mmi S'. Gedha s yiS! Ni ineS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Akw, péallan i Neppa,",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 18,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 124,
            "text": "Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan. Ma Iseyya lameô, ad as Yini kan: 'ili'! Ad yili.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 18,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 125,
            "text": "Nnan wid ur nessin: 'a lemmer ad a d Immeslay Öebbi, ne ad a d ias ussekni'! Akka ay nnan wid i ten id izwaren, am awalen nnsen. Ppemcabin wulawen nnsen. Ni Nbeggen ed issekniyen i ugdud ipputebbten.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 18,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 126,
            "text": "Ih, Nuzen ik id, s tidep, d abcir, u d aneddaô. Ur ippili fellak usteqsi ef at wuud.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 18,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 127,
            "text": "Ur k pôavin wudayen ne imasiêiyen, alamma teddiv d ddin nnsen. Ini: 'd nehhu n Öebbi ay d nehhu'. Ma teddiv akked usirem nnsen, deffir wayen ik ed iusan n tmusni, ur k ipfukku, si Öebbi, bab, ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 19,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 128,
            "text": "Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, qqaôen p leqôaya iwatan. Widak umnen yis. Wid i p iugin, widak d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 121,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 19,
            "ruku": 15,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 129,
            "text": "A yAt Isôail! Mmektit ed lit iW, is i kwen £ate. Nek, Smenyafe kwen i imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 122,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 19,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 130,
            "text": "Ëezzbet i wass ideg ur ippuqeîîi yiwen, deg umkan n wayev, s wacemma; ur tepwaqbal leôama segs, ur t tenfaâ ccafuâa, ur ppusellken.",
            "numberInSurah": 123,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 19,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 7,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 131,
            "text": "Ibôahim, mi t Ijeôôeb Mass is, s wawalen, iu awal. Inna: 'Nek, a k Rre d win ara inehhun medden'. Inna: 'u si tarwa w'? Inna: 'lemâahda W ur taâna ara imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 124,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 19,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 132,
            "text": "Mi Nerra Axxam d lemqam i yimdanen, u d amkan n laman: 'erret lemqam n Ibôahim d loamaâ'! Nâuhed i Ibôahim akked Ismaâil: 'zzizdget Axxam iW, i wid idewwiôen, wid ipimin, wid iîîinizen, wid ikennun'.",
            "numberInSurah": 125,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 19,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 133,
            "text": "Mi inna Ibôahim: 'a Mass iw! Err wagi d tamdint n laman, £it imezda is s ppemôat; wid, segsen, iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru'. Inna: 'win ijehlen, a t Ooe ad izhu cwiî, sinna, a t Nehôe ar uâaqeb n tmes. A tualin tucmip'!",
            "numberInSurah": 126,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 19,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 134,
            "text": "Ibôahim akked Ismaâil, mi ssalayen leêyuv n Uxxam: 'a Mass nne! Eqbel suône, Keçç, s tidep, d Win Isellen, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 127,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 135,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Err ane d imvuâen iK, u, si dderya nne, lois ar aK ianzen. Mel a isekkiren nne, Ssuref a. Keçç, s tidep, Tessurufev, Tepêunuv.",
            "numberInSurah": 128,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 136,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Azen asen d amazan segsen, ad asen iqqaô issekniyen iK, ad asen isseêfev Tazmamt akked ûûwab, a ten izzizdeg. Keçç, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab'.",
            "numberInSurah": 129,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 16,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 137,
            "text": "Anwa iugin ddin n Ibôahim, siwa win iccemten iman is? Ni Nefren it di ddunit. Di laxeôt, neppa, war ccekk, seg iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 130,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 138,
            "text": "Mi s Inna Mass is: 'anez'! Inna: 'unze aS i Mass imavalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 131,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 139,
            "text": "Iweûûa yis Ibôahim arraw is - akken Iaâqub -: 'a yarraw iw, Öebbi, s tidep, Ifren awen ddin, ur ppemmtet siwa ma tunzem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 132,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 140,
            "text": "Ne tellam d inagan mi d ters tmeppant ar Yaâqub, mi inna i tarwa s: 'anwa ara tâabdem deffir i'? Nnan: 'a naâbed Öebbi k, u Öebbi n lejdud ik: Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq. Öebbi Yiwen. Nekwni nunez aS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 133,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 141,
            "text": "Wigi d lois i iâaddan. Ines ayen ikseb, nnwen ayen tkesbem. Ur kwen steqsayen ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 134,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 20,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 142,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ilit d udayen ne d imasiêiyen, a ppepwanhum'. Ini: 'Xaîi, maca ddin n Ibôahim, imalen ar tidep. Ur illi seg imcurak'.",
            "numberInSurah": 135,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 21,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 143,
            "text": "Init: 'numen s Öebbi akked wayen id irsen uône, wayen id irsen ar Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq, Iaâqub, laâôac, ayen ippunefken i Musa, Âisa, ayen ippunefken i lambiyya, suô Mass nnsen. Ur nessemgarrad yiwen segsen, nekwni nunez aS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 136,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 21,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 144,
            "text": "Ma umnen ayen icuban ayen tumnem, atnan pwanhan. Ma wexxôen, haaten kan di lefôaq. Iqadd ik Öebbi, segsen. Neppa Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 137,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 21,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 145,
            "text": "Ssbia, n Öebbi. Anwa yifen Öebbi i ssbia? Nekwni d iâabbaden iS.",
            "numberInSurah": 138,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 21,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 146,
            "text": "Ini: 'day ad a tnamrem ef Öebbi, u Neppa d Mass nne, u d Mass nnwen? I nekwni igiten nne, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Nekwni d izedganen iS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 139,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 21,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 147,
            "text": "Ne a d tinim: 's tidep, Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq, Iaâqub, laâôac, llan d udayen, ne d imasiêiyen'? Ini: 'Anwa i isnen sennig akw, d kunwi ne d Öebbi'? Anwa i idensen sennig win iffren ccada, i isâa suô Öebbi? Ur Ifil Öebbi ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 140,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 21,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 148,
            "text": "Asatu agi iâadda. Ines ayen ikseb, nnwen ayen tkesbem. Ur fellawen asteqsi ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 141,
            "juz": 1,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 21,
            "ruku": 17,
            "hizbQuarter": 8,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 149,
            "text": "Ad inin ijelufen, ger medden: 'acu iten iswexxôen si lqibla nnsen, uuô llan péallan'? Ini: 'N Öebbi agmuv akked utaram. Inehhu win i S ihwan, s abrid uwqim'.",
            "numberInSurah": 142,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 22,
            "ruku": 18,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 150,
            "text": "Akka ay kwen Nerra d lois alemmas, iwakken a ppilim d inagan n medden, ad yili Umazan d anagi nnwen. Nerra lqibla uuô teppezziv, iwakken kan a Néeô anwa iddan d Umazan, anwa iualen ar deffir. D lhejna, siwa i wid Inha Öebbi. Ur Iveggiâ Öebbi liman nnwen. Ih, Öebbi, i yimdanen, d Umâin, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 143,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 22,
            "ruku": 18,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 151,
            "text": "Ni Nwala, tezziv udem ik ar igenni. A k Nawi ar lqibla ara tôaviv. Ezzi udem ik ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam. Anida tellam, zzit udmawen uôes. Ih, wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, éôan p d tidep suô Mass nnsen. Ur Ifil Öebbi ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 144,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 22,
            "ruku": 18,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 152,
            "text": "Xas a d tawiv, i wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, yal assekni, ur tezzin ar lqibla k. Keçç, ur tezzi ar lqibla nnsen. Kra segsen, ur tezzin ar lqibla n wiyav. Ma teddiv akked usirem nnsen, mbaâd ma tusa k id, suône£, tussna, a ppiliv, imiren, seg imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 145,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 22,
            "ruku": 18,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 153,
            "text": "Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt ssnen p, akken ssnen arraw nnsen. War ccekk, arbaâ segsen teffren tidep, u nitni éôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 146,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 18,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 154,
            "text": "Tidep suô Mass ik, ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun.",
            "numberInSurah": 147,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 18,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 155,
            "text": "I yal yiwen, loiha uuô izzi. Sâut timenyugert ar lxiô. Anda teddam, ad Yili Öebbi yidwen akw. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 148,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 19,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 156,
            "text": "Ansi d tusiv, ezzi udem ik ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam. Neppat, ih, d tidep suô Mass ik. Ur Ifil Öebbi ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 149,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 19,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 157,
            "text": "Ansi d tefev, zzi udem ik ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam. Anida tellam, zzit udmawen nnwen uôes, iwakken ur kwen pnamaren imdanen, siwa wid idensen, segsen. Ur ten ppagwadet, agwadet iyI. Ad awen Time lit iW, amar a ppepwanhum.",
            "numberInSurah": 150,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 19,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 158,
            "text": "Akken i wen Nuzen Amazan segwen, immal awen issekniyen nne£, izzizdig ikwen, isselmad awen Tazmamt, akked ûûwab; isselmad awen ayen ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 151,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 19,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 159,
            "text": "Mmektit iyI d, a kwen id Mmekti. Snemmret iyI, ur jehlet.",
            "numberInSurah": 152,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 19,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 160,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ssutret tallalt, s ûûbeô akked téallit. Ih, Öebbi ar iûebôiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 153,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 23,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 161,
            "text": "Ur qqaôet mmuten wid ipwanan deg ubrid n Öebbi. Xaîi d imuddiren, maca ur teêûim ara.",
            "numberInSurah": 154,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 162,
            "text": "War ccekk, a kwen Njeôôeb s kra usigwed, n llaé, n nneqs n wayla, n leôwaê, n lellat. Ssefreê iûebôiyen;",
            "numberInSurah": 155,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 163,
            "text": "Wid, ma uen tawait, qqaôen: 'nekwni n Öebbi, nekwni, a nual uôeS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 156,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 164,
            "text": "Widak, fellasen téilla suô Mass nnsen, akked uêunu. Widak d wid ipwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 157,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 9,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 165,
            "text": "Ih, ÛÜafa akked Meôwa, seg isekkiren n Öebbi. Win iêuoen s Axxam, ne iéuô it, ulac uilif fellas, ma izzi yasent. Yif it win izzin, s lebi s. Ih, Öebbi Ippara tajmilt, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 158,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 166,
            "text": "Ih, wid iteffren ayen id Nessers ubeggen akked nnhaya, mbaâd ma Nbeggen it i yimdanen, di Tezmamt, widak, Ixza iten Öebbi, xzan ten wid ixezzun.",
            "numberInSurah": 159,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 167,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid inedmen u xedmen ayen ilhan, u beggnen d. Widak, ad asen Ssurfe. Nek Ssurufe, Pêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 160,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 168,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen u mmuten d ijehliyen, widak, fellasen xezzu n Öebbi, lmalayek, akked yimdanen, meôôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 161,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 169,
            "text": "Degs ad wekkôen. Ur ippifsus fellasen uâaqeb, ur illi w ara ten id iwalin.",
            "numberInSurah": 162,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 170,
            "text": "Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Aênin Ipêunun.",
            "numberInSurah": 163,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 24,
            "ruku": 20,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 171,
            "text": "Ih, di lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan: afraz ger yiv akked wass, lbabuô ippazalen di yill, s wayen infâan medden, ayen id Issers Öebbi n waman, seg igenni - Issidir yissen tamurt, deffir tmeppant is, Issenkar, degs, yal lweêc -, abeddel n wavu akked usigna i imuêepmen ad yili ger igenni akked tmurt. War cekk, ard issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen.",
            "numberInSurah": 164,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 25,
            "ruku": 21,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 172,
            "text": "Ger yimdanen, llan wid ippadamen tanudda, war Öebbi. Ëemmlen ten akken Ippuêemmel Öebbi. Wid iumnen zaden akken êemmlen Öebbi. Awufan wid idensen, mi walan aâaqeb, ad éôen ar tazmert akw n Öebbi, u Öebbi Iqseê deg uâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 165,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 25,
            "ruku": 21,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 173,
            "text": "Mara zekkôen uvfiôen nnsen, wid ipwatebâan, u walan aâaqeb, u tfukk yidsen lemxalîa,",
            "numberInSurah": 166,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 25,
            "ruku": 21,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 174,
            "text": "ad inin uvfiôen: 'a lemmer a nual, a ten nzekkeô akken i  zekkôen'! Akka ay sen Issken Öebbi igiten nnsen. A yamxix nnsen, ur d teffen si tmes!",
            "numberInSurah": 167,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 25,
            "ruku": 21,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 175,
            "text": "A yimdanen! Eççet seg wayen iêellen, imaânen, di tmurt. Ur teddut di lateô n Cciîan. Neppa, s tidep, d acengu nnwen n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 168,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 25,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 176,
            "text": "Ippameô awen kan tuccva, lâaô; a ppinim, ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 169,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 25,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 177,
            "text": "Ma nnan asen: 'ddut akked wayen id Issers Öebbi', a d inin: 'xaîi, a neddu akked wayen id nufa ar imezwura nne'. I ma llan imezwura nnsen ur meyyzen acemma, ur pwanhan?",
            "numberInSurah": 170,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 26,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 178,
            "text": "Amedya n wid ijehlen, d amedya n win uuô ppuun, seg akken ur issel, siwa i usuu akked uberreê. D iâeééugen, d igugam, d ideralen, nitni ur pmeyyizen.",
            "numberInSurah": 171,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 26,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 179,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Eççet si téidanin ikwen Nat. Snemmret Öebbi, ma d Neppa ay tâabdem.",
            "numberInSurah": 172,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 26,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 180,
            "text": "I awen Igdel Öebbi, siwa loifa, idamen, aksum n yilef, akked îêegga i war Öebbi. Win terra tmara, ur ibi, ur izgir tilas, ur illi d abekkav is. Ih, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 173,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 26,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 181,
            "text": "Ih, wid iteffren ayen id Issers Öebbi, si Tezmamt, ppaen yis ayen ôxisen, widak, siwa times ara ççen, deg iâabbav nnsen. Ur asen Ipmeslay Öebbi, ass n tnekra, ur ten Izzizdig. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 174,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 26,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 182,
            "text": "Widak, d wid iuen ttelfan s nnhaya, aâaqeb s ssmaê. Acu ara ten iûebbôen si tmes?",
            "numberInSurah": 175,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 26,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 183,
            "text": "Akka, acku Issers ed Öebbi Tazmamt, s tidep. Ih, wid imgarraden ef Tezmamt, haaten di lfiôaq umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 176,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 26,
            "ruku": 22,
            "hizbQuarter": 10,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 184,
            "text": "Ise, maççi ma tezzim udmawen nnwen, ar ugmuv akked utaram. Maca, ise d wid iumnen s Öebbi, s wass aneggaru, s lmalayek, s Tazmamt, s lambiyya. U ppaken ayla, ef lemêibba S, i llzem, igujilen, igellilen, win d ibbwi ubrid, imapparen, akw i uberru n waklan. D wid ipéallan, ipzekkin, ippaîîafen di lemâahda nnsen, ma âahden, iûebôiyen di lmeêna akked twait, di tegwnip n ccqa. D wigi i illan di tidep, d wigi i ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 177,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 27,
            "ruku": 23,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 185,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Iura fellawen ppaô n tmegrav. Lêeôô s lêeôô, akli s wakli, nnta s nnta. Win iwumi isemmeê gma s kra: îlaba s lewqama, feddu s lewqama. Ayagi, d sshala suô Mass nnwen, akked uêunu. Win iffen abrid, deffir waya, ad isâaddi aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 178,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 27,
            "ruku": 23,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 186,
            "text": "I kunwi, ppaô d tameddurt, a yuâqilen. Amar a pêezzbem.",
            "numberInSurah": 179,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 27,
            "ruku": 23,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 187,
            "text": "Iura fellawen: ma tusa d tmeppant, ar yiwen degwen, ma iooa d lxiô, a t ifk i imawlan is, akked llzem, s lqanun. D ayen ilezmen i wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 180,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 27,
            "ruku": 23,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 188,
            "text": "Win it ibeddlen mbaâd ma isla yas, abekkav is siwa ef wid it ipbeddilen. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 181,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 27,
            "ruku": 23,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 189,
            "text": "Ur idnib win iten issemûalaêen acku iugad rrya, ne abekkav, suô win ippuweûûan. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 182,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 28,
            "ruku": 23,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 190,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Iura fellawen uéummu, akken iura ef imezwura nnwen, amar a pêezzbem.",
            "numberInSurah": 183,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 28,
            "ruku": 24,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 191,
            "text": "Ussan ipwaêesben. Win iuvnen segwen ne illan ippinig, annect n wussan nniven. Wid i s izemren, feddu ad cceççen igellil. Win izaden lxiô, ilha yas. Ma tuéamem, ppif i kunwi, lemmer teéôim.",
            "numberInSurah": 184,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 28,
            "ruku": 24,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 192,
            "text": "Aggur n ÔÖemvan, ideg d irs Leqwôan, d nnhaya i medden, d abeggen n nnhaya akked ufraz. Win segwen iwalan illul ed waggur, a t iuzum. Win iuvnen ne illan ippinig, annect n wussan nniven. Öebbi Iba yawen sshala, ur awen Iba ara cedda. A pfukem tallit, a pkabrem Öebbi imi kwen Inha, amar a ppesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 185,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 28,
            "ruku": 24,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 193,
            "text": "Ma steqsan k, imdanen iW, fellI, Nek Qeôbe. Pjawabe i unuju n yimsuter, ma ipper iyI. Ihi, ad iyI d jawben, ad amnen yissI, amar ad pwanhun.",
            "numberInSurah": 186,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 28,
            "ruku": 24,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 194,
            "text": "Iêell awen, deg iv uéummu, a pqeôôbem ar tlawin nnwen. Nitenti d lebsa nnwen, kunwi d lebsa nnsent. Iéôa Öebbi ar tellam tepkellixem iman nnwen. Issuref awen, Isemmeê awen. Tura qeôôbet uôsent, nadit ayen i wen Iura Öebbi. Eççet, esswet, ar pferzem lxiv amellal, si lxiv aberkan, di tafrara. Sinna, uéummet ar yiv. Ur pqeôôibet uôsent, ma tâazlem iman nnwen di lowamaâ. D tigi ay d tilas n Öebbi. Ur pqeôôibet uôsent! Akka i Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen iS i yimdanen, amar ad êezzben.",
            "numberInSurah": 187,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 29,
            "ruku": 24,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 195,
            "text": "Ur ppemyeççat ayla nnwen, garawen, d aêerfi, ur t ppaket i yimêaddan, iwakken a ppeççem amur, seg wayla n medden, di lmenkweô, u kunwi teéôam.",
            "numberInSurah": 188,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 29,
            "ruku": 24,
            "hizbQuarter": 11,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 196,
            "text": "La k steqsayen ef tlalit n waggur. Ini: 'd lewqat i medden, u i lêio'. Ise, maççi d anekcum ar ixxamen si zdeffir nnsent. Maca, ise d aêezzeb i Öebbi. Kecmet ixxamen si tebbura nnsen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 189,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 29,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 197,
            "text": "Nnaet deg ubrid n Öebbi wid i kwen ipnaen. Ur zegret tilas. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid izegren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 190,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 29,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 198,
            "text": "Nnaet pen anda ten tufam, ssuffet pen seg wanda i kwen ssuffen. Ahewwel iwâaô kteô umennu. Ur ten nepnaet ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam, siwa ma nnuen kwen degs. Ma nnuen kwen, nnaet pen. Akka aqeîîi ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 191,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 30,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 199,
            "text": "Ma fukken, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 192,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 30,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 200,
            "text": "Nnaet pen alamma tfukk lfetna, u iual ddin i Öebbi. Ma fukken, ur pnaet, siwa imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 193,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 30,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 201,
            "text": "Aggur iôqan s waggur iôqan. Tiririt n ppaô ef wayen ippugedlen. Win ikwen id ibbwven, awvet ep, akken ikwen id ibbwev. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Cfut ar Öebbi ar wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 194,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 30,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 202,
            "text": "Ssedqet deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ur d ppawit tawait, s ifassen nnwen. Maânet. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 195,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 30,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 203,
            "text": "Öuêet ar lêio akked lâumôa, i Öebbi. Ma têeûlem, ssadaqa tushilt. Ur pseîîilet iqweôôa nnwen, ar ppawev tikci s amkan is. Win iuvnen, segwen, ne ihlek aqeôôu s, ad ifdu s uéummu, ne ssadaqa, ne iseflan. Mi tellam di laman, win izuôen ur iêuo, ad iseddeq ayen i s isehlen. Win ur nufa ara, ad iuéum krav wussan di lêio, ûa wussan ar tualin, akken ad awven mraw. Ayagi i win ur nesâi tawacult illan ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, cfut ar Öebbi Iwâaô deg uâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 196,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 30,
            "ruku": 25,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 204,
            "text": "Lêio deg wagguren ipwassnen. Win iâazmen, degsen, ad iêuo, ihi, di lêio ur telli tuzzuft, ne ayen n dir, ne nnmara. Ayen txedmem n lxiô, Iéôa t Öebbi. Awit aâwin, maca aâwin amxallef d aêezzeb. Ëezzbet iyI a yuâqilen!",
            "numberInSurah": 197,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 31,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 205,
            "text": "Uu ili uilif fellawen ma tessarmem lfevl suô Mass nnwen. Mi d tûubbem si Aâôafat, mmektit ed Öebbi, ppama n lemqam iôqan. Mmektit eP id, akken i kwen Inha, wanag tellam, uqbel, seg imeôôqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 198,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 31,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 206,
            "text": "Sinna, ddut anda ddan medden, ssutret ssmaê i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 199,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 31,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 207,
            "text": "Mi tfukkem isekkiren nnwen, mmektit ed Öebbi, akken d tesmektayem imezwura nnwen, ne kteô. Ger imdanen, wid iqqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Efk a di ddunit'. Ur ppawin amur di laxeôt.",
            "numberInSurah": 200,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 31,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 208,
            "text": "Llan, garasen, wid iqqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Efk a di ddunit, ise, di laxeôt, ise. Esseô a seg uâaqeb n tmes'.",
            "numberInSurah": 201,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 31,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 209,
            "text": "Widak, ad awin amur seg wayen kesben. Öebbi Ipawal deg uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 202,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 31,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 12,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 210,
            "text": "Mmektit ed Öebbi, deg ussan iâuden. Win iawlen di sin wussan, ur icciv ara; win iâaîlen, ur icciv ara, ma illa d win ipêezziben. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Cfut, ar uôeS ara tepwafesrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 203,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 211,
            "text": "Yiwen ger imdanen, iâoeb ik umeslay is, ef tmeddurt n ddunit. Irra Öebbi d Anagi, ef wayen illan deg ul is. U neppa iqseê i tilla.",
            "numberInSurah": 204,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 212,
            "text": "Mi izzi, ad ikkat di tmurt, iwakken ad issefsed degs, ad isqucc igran akked lmal. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara asefsed.",
            "numberInSurah": 205,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 213,
            "text": "Ma nnan as: 'êezzeb i Öebbi'! A t tekcem lqwedôa ubekkav. Ad isteqnaâ s Loahennama. A yir usu!",
            "numberInSurah": 206,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 214,
            "text": "Ger imdanen, win izzenzen iman is, issaram llza n Öebbi. Öebbi d Umâin ar imdanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 207,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 215,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Kecmet di tifrat s lekmal is, ur teddut d lateô n Cciîan. Neppa, s tidep, d acengu nnwen n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 208,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 216,
            "text": "Ma teccvem, deffir n tisin ubeggen uôwen, cfut Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 209,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 217,
            "text": "Day a pôaoun kan, ad asen d Ias Öebbi, akked lmalayek, di tili usigna? Ad iûaô lameô. Ar Öebbi ara ualen lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 210,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 32,
            "ruku": 26,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 218,
            "text": "Steqsi At Isôail, acêal issekniyen iberrzen i sen Nefka. I win ipbeddilen tikci n Öebbi, deffir tisin is uôes, ihi, Öebbi Iqseê deg uâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 211,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 33,
            "ruku": 27,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 219,
            "text": "Wid ijehlen, ccebêen asen tameddurt n ddunit. Ttihin ef wid iumnen. Wid ipêezziben ad ilin sennig sen, ass n tnekra. Öebbi Ipiti win i S ihwan, s lufa.",
            "numberInSurah": 212,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 33,
            "ruku": 27,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 220,
            "text": "Llan imdanen d yiwen n lois. Iuzen ed Öebbi lambiyya ad beccôen, ad nabin. Issers ed, yidsen, Tazmamt s tidep, iwakken ad Iêudd ger medden, ef wayen ief mgarraden. I imgarraden fellas, siwa wid iwumi teppunefk, mbaâd ma iusa ten id ubeggen. Ppemyasamen. Inha Öebbi wid iumnen deg wayen n tidep, ief mgarraden, s tsriê iS. Öebbi Inehhu win i S ihwan, s abrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 213,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 33,
            "ruku": 27,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 221,
            "text": "Day tilem a pkecmem Loennet, wanag ur kwen id iusi wayen id iusan ar wid i kwen id izwaren? Mmugren d lmeêna, ccqa, zzelzla, armi inna umazan akked wid iumnen yides: 'melmi laânaya n Öebbi'? Day, s tidep, ur d teqôib ara laânaya n Öebbi?",
            "numberInSurah": 214,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 33,
            "ruku": 27,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 222,
            "text": "Steqsan k ef wayen ara fken. Ini: 'ayen ara tefkem n lxiô, i imawlan, i llzem, i igujilen, i igellilen, i w ar d iawi ubrid'. Ayen ara txedmem n lxiô, war ccekk, Iéôa t Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 215,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 33,
            "ruku": 27,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 223,
            "text": "Iura fellawen umennu, u neppa d ayen tkeôhem. Ahat tkeôhem ayen ilhan i kunwi, ahat têemmlem ayen n dir i kunwi. Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 216,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 34,
            "ruku": 27,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 224,
            "text": "La k steqsayen ma ad yili umennu deg waggur iôqan. Ini: 'amennu degs, d abekkav. Abekkav it ielben, ar Öebbi, d assefôe ef ubrid n Öebbi, d ankaô is, u d ankaô n Loamaâ n Lêaôam; d assuffe, segs, imezda is'. Ahewwel ileb amennu. Zgan a kwen pnaen, alamma swexxôen kwen, ma zemren, si ddin nnwen. Win, segwen, iffen i ddin is, ad immet d ajehli. Widak, mêan igiten nnsen di ddunit, di laxeôt. Widak, d at tmes, degs, nitni, ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 217,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 34,
            "ruku": 28,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 225,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen, win iunagen u juhden deg ubrid n Öebbi, widak ggunin aêunu n Öebbi. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 218,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 34,
            "ruku": 28,
            "hizbQuarter": 13,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 226,
            "text": "La k steqsayen ef ccôab akked leqwmeô. Ini: 'degsen abekkav meqqwôen, akked ibuar i medden. Abekkav nnsen ileb ibuar nsen'. La k steqsayen, acu ara seddqen. Ini: 'ayen iugaren'. Akka i wen Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen, amar a pmeyyzem",
            "numberInSurah": 219,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 34,
            "ruku": 28,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 227,
            "text": "af ddunit akked laxeôt. La k steqsayen ef igujilen. Ini: 'ppif ma txedmem asen lxiô. Ma txulvem ten, d atmaten nnwen'. Öebbi Ifrez ger ufessad akked uâaôvi. Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, a kwen Icebbwel. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 220,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 35,
            "ruku": 28,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 228,
            "text": "Ur ppaet timcurak alamma umnent. Taklit iumnen tif tamcarekt, xas taâoeb ikwen. Ur pnasabet imcurak alamma umnen. Akli iumnen yif amcarek, xas iaâoeb ikwen. Widak, neccden ar tmes. Öebbi Inecced ar Loennet akked ssmaê, ma Irad. Ipbeggin issekniyen iS i medden, amar a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 221,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 35,
            "ruku": 28,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 229,
            "text": "La k steqsayen ef tarda. Ini: 'd aîan. Âazlet tilawin di tarda, ur pqeôôibet uôsent alamma ûfant. Mi ûfant, qeôôbet uôsent, akken i wen Iumeô Öebbi'. Ih, Öebbi Iêemmel wid iutuben, Iêemmel wid izzizdigen.",
            "numberInSurah": 222,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 35,
            "ruku": 29,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 230,
            "text": "Tilawin nnwen d aêôiq n tyerza nnwen. Melmi tebam, aset s aêôiq nnwen. Zzewret lxiô i yiman nnwen, êezzbet i Öebbi. Cfut ar kunwi a T temmagrem. Becceô lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 223,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 35,
            "ruku": 29,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 231,
            "text": "Ur ssekcamet Öebbi mara teggallem a ppizdigem, a pêezzbem, a ppessemûalêem medden. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 224,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 35,
            "ruku": 29,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 232,
            "text": "Ur kwen Ipqissi ara Öebbi ef tgallit ef awal. Maca, a kwen Iqiss ef wayen kesben wulawen nnwen. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 225,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 36,
            "ruku": 29,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 233,
            "text": "Wid iggullen ur pqeôôiben ar tlawin nnsen, ad gganin kué wagguren. Ma bedlen ôôay, ihi, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 226,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 36,
            "ruku": 29,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 234,
            "text": "Ma âazmen berru, ihi, Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 227,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 36,
            "ruku": 29,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 235,
            "text": "Timnufaq ad aôount krav tardiwin. Ur asent iêell ara ad ffrent ayen Ixleq Öebbi, di tâabbav nnsent, ma umnent s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Ma ban irgazen nnsent ad mûalaêen, izzewr iten lêal a tent id rren, di lmudda nni. Akken pwalasent ay ppalasent, s lqanun. I yirgazen, asurif er loiha nnsent. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 228,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 36,
            "ruku": 29,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 236,
            "text": "Berru, sin iberdan; tiririt, s lqanun; aserreê s lewqama. Ur awen iêell ara a ppedmem kra, seg wayen i sent tefkam - siwa ma ugaden ur pqadaôen ara tilas n Öebbi. Ma tugadem ur pqadaôen ara tilas n Öebbi, ulac uilif fellasen ef wayen is ara d tefdu iman is. D tigi ay d tilas n Öebbi, ur tent zegret. Wid izegren tilas n Öebbi, widak, d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 229,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 36,
            "ruku": 30,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 237,
            "text": "Ma ibra yas, ur as têell, imiren, alamma tu argaz nniven. Ma ibra yas, ulac uilif fellasen ma ualen ar din, ma walan qudôen tilas n Öebbi. D tigi ay d tilas n Öebbi. Ibeggen itent i ugdud issnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 230,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 36,
            "ruku": 30,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 238,
            "text": "Ma tebram i tlawin, u sâaddant tallit nnsent, erret pent id, s lqanun, ne serrêet asent, s lqanun. Ur tent pparat s uêeppem, a ppeccvem. Win ixedmen akka, idens iman is. Ur ppuraret s issekniyen n Öebbi. Mmektit ed ayen i kwen Iat Öebbi, akked wayen i wen d Issers si Tezmamt, akw si ûûwab. Ipnabi kwen yis. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Cfut ar Öebbi Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 231,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 37,
            "ruku": 30,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 239,
            "text": "Ma tebram i tlawin, u sâaddant tallit nnsent, ur asent tekset ad aent irgazen nnsent, ma mwafaqen s lqanun. Ar waya ay pwanecden wid, segwen, iumnen s Öebbi, akked wass aneggaru. Ppif akka, i tezdeg akked ûûfawa nnwen. Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 232,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 37,
            "ruku": 31,
            "hizbQuarter": 14,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 240,
            "text": "Tiyimmatin ad ssuîvent arraw nnsent, sin iseggwasen mden, i win iban ad itim ussuîev. £ef ubabat, lmakla akked lebsa nnsent, s lqanun. Ur ipwakellaf yiman siwa ar wayen iwumi izmer. Tarwa ur teîîuôôu imma s, ur teîîuôôu baba s. I uweôôat, am akka. Ma ban ad kksen tuîîva, mcawaôen, ulac uilif fellasen. Ma tebam tamôebbit, a ppessuîîev tarwa nnwen, ulac uilif fellawen, ma txelûem ayen i wen ilaqen, s lqanun. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Cfut ar Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 233,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 37,
            "ruku": 31,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 241,
            "text": "Wid, segwen, issuffen taôwiêt, u ooan d tilawin, ad aôount kué wagguren akked mraw wussan. Mi sâaddant tallit nnsent, ulac uilif fellawen deg wayen xedment deg iman nnsent, di lqanun. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 234,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 38,
            "ruku": 31,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 242,
            "text": "Ulac uilif fellawen, ma tennam d a pxevbem tilawin, ne ma teffrem. Iéôa Öebbi, ar tesmektayem tent id. Maca, ur asent âahdet, di tbavnit, siwa ma tennam awal uwqim. Ur ferrut ef lemlak, alamma ibbwev lajel iuran. Cfut ar Öebbi Iéôa i illan degwen. Ëadret iman nnwen segS. Cfut ar Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 235,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 38,
            "ruku": 31,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 243,
            "text": "Ulac uilif fellawen ma tebram i tlawin ur tennulem, ne iwumi ur tefkim lwajeb. Efket asent tikci iweqmen. Asâay s tezmert is, igellil s tezmert is. D lwajeb i iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 236,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 38,
            "ruku": 32,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 244,
            "text": "Ma tebram asent, uqbel a tent tennalem, u, iu lêal, tefkam asent lwajeb, ihi, azgen n wayen i sent tefkam, siwa ma semêent, ne isemmeê usemsaô n jjwao. Ssmaê iqôeb nezzeh ar uêezzeb. Ur tepput lfevl garawen. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 237,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 38,
            "ruku": 32,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 245,
            "text": "Ëarbet ef téilla, u taéallit talemmast. Beddet i Öebbi, s wannuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 238,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 32,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 246,
            "text": "Ma tugadem, s ibeddi, ne di rrekba. Ma tellam di laman, mmektit ed Öebbi, akken i wen Isselmed ayen ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 239,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 32,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 247,
            "text": "Wid segwen issuffen taôwiêt, u ooan d tilawin, ad asent vemnen aseggwas n wuççi, ur tent ssuffuen. Ma ffent, ulac uilif fellawen, deg wayen xedment, deg iman nnsent, di lqanun. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 240,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 32,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 248,
            "text": "I tembwurab taqviât, s lqanun. D lwajeb ef wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 241,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 32,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 249,
            "text": "Akka i wen Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen iS, amar a pêemûem.",
            "numberInSurah": 242,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 32,
            "hizbQuarter": 15,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 250,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid iffen, seg ixxamen nnsen, d igima, ugaden tameppant. Inna yasen Öebbi: 'emmtet'! Sinna, Issader ten id. S tidep, Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ef yimdanen, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur snemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 243,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 33,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 251,
            "text": "Nnaet deg ubrid n Öebbi. Cfut ar Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 244,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 33,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 252,
            "text": "Win iôevlen aôeîîal umâin i Öebbi, ad as t id Irr s lufa. Öebbi Ippaîaf, Ismiri. £uôeS a ppualem.",
            "numberInSurah": 245,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 39,
            "ruku": 33,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 253,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara imvebbôen seg wAt Isôail, deffir Musa? Mi nnan i nnbi nnsen: 'azen a d agellid, a nenna deg ubrid n Öebbi'. Inna: 'ma iura fellawen umennu, day a ppagim a ppennaem'? Nnan: 'ur a issefk ara a neqqim ur nepna ara, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ni ssuffen a d, nekwni akked tarwa nne, seg ixxamen nne'. Mi iura fellasen umennu, wexxôen, siwa drus segsen. Öebbi Issen imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 246,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 40,
            "ruku": 33,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 254,
            "text": "Inna yasen nnbi nnsen: 'Ni Öebbi, s tidep, Iuzen awen d Ïalut, d agellid'. Nnan: 'amek ara yili d agellid nne? Nezwar it akken neklal tagelda. Ur as ippunefk wayla'. Inna: 'Öebbi, s tidep, Ifren it garawen, u Irna yas aîas n tmusni akked loeppa'. Ippak Öebbi tagelda S i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 247,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 40,
            "ruku": 33,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 255,
            "text": "Inna yasen, nnbi nnsen: 's tidep, assekni n tgelda s, d tisin uôwen usenduq. Degs talwit suô Mass nnwen, akked wayen id igwran, seg wayen id teooa twacult n Musa, akked tin n Haôun. A t id awint lmalayek. Ih, deg waya, d assekni i kunwi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 248,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 40,
            "ruku": 33,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 256,
            "text": "Mi iffe Ïalut, s lâaskeô, inna: 'Öebbi, s tidep, a kwen Ijeôôeb s wasif. Win iswan segs, ur illi yidi. Win ur neswi, neppa, s tidep, yidi. Kkes ed win iswan cwiî, deg ufus is'. Swan segs, siwa ixeîîayen segsen. Mi zegren, neppa akked wid iumnen yides, nnan: 'ur nezmir assa, i Oalut akked lâaskeô is'. Nnan wid issarmen ar nitni ad mlilen d Öebbi: 'acêal d abrid, îayfa tameééyant teleb îayfa tameqwôant, ma Irad Öebbi'. Öebbi ar iûebôiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 249,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 41,
            "ruku": 34,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 257,
            "text": "Mi qublen Oalut akked lâaskeô is, nnan: 'a Mass nne! Azen a d ûûbeô, Tebbet isurifen nne, Awes a mgal agdud ijehliyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 250,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 41,
            "ruku": 34,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 258,
            "text": "Irad Öebbi, rebêen ten. Dawed ina Oalut. Ifka yas Öebbi tagelda akked ûûwab. Isselmed as seg wayen i S ihwan. Lemmer ur Issemnamar ara Öebbi, imdanen, a ppefsed tmurt. Maca, Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ef imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 251,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 41,
            "ruku": 34,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 259,
            "text": "Atnan issekniyen n Öebbi; Nemmal ak ten, s tidep. Keçç, war ccekk, seg imazanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 252,
            "juz": 2,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 41,
            "ruku": 34,
            "hizbQuarter": 16,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 260,
            "text": "Imazanen agi, Nesmenyaf kra i wiyav. Garasen, wid iwumi Immeslay Öebbi. Issuli kra segsen, tiseddaôin. Nefka abeggen i Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, u Nekfa t s ôôuê iôqan. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur ppemyenan wid i ten id ivefôen, deffir n tisin ubeggen uôsen. Maca, mgarraden. Segsen wid iumnen, segsen wid ijehlen. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur ppemyenan, maca Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan.",
            "numberInSurah": 253,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 42,
            "ruku": 34,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 261,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Seddqet seg wayen ikwen Nat, uqbel tisin n wass ideg ur telli ttjara, ne tiddukla, ne ccafuâa. Ijehliyen, d nitni ay d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 254,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 42,
            "ruku": 35,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 262,
            "text": "Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Amuddir, Imezgi. Ur Ipnuddum, ur Iggan. IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Anwa akka ara icufâan uôeS, siwa ma s tsriê iS? Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ur êemûen kra, si tmusni S, siwa ayen i S ihwan. Lewsaâ usgeld iS, d tamurt akked igenwan. Ur T issaâtab uêareb fellasen. Neppa, d Aâlayan, d Ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 255,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 42,
            "ruku": 35,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 263,
            "text": "Ddin maççi s yiil. Ni tepwafôez lewqama si lwelîa. Win iugin iôebbiten n tkerkas u iumen s Öebbi, ihi, iîîef afus ioehden, ur nceqqeq. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 256,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 42,
            "ruku": 35,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 264,
            "text": "Öebbi d Bab n wid iumnen. Issuffe iten id si tillas ar tafat. Imawlan n wid ijehlen, d iôebbiten n tkerkas. Ssuffen ten id si tafat ar tillas. Widak, d at tmes, nitni, degs ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 257,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 43,
            "ruku": 35,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 265,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara win inumren Ibôahim ef Mass is, acku Ifka yas Öebbi tagelda? Mi inna Ibôahim: 'Mass iw d win Issidiren, Ineqqen', inna d: 'nek ssidire, neqqe'. Inna Ibôahim: 'ihi, Öebbi Issenqaô ed iîij seg ugmuv; keçç, ssenqeô it id seg utaram'! Inneêcam win ijehlen. Öebbi ur Inehhu yara agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 258,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 43,
            "ruku": 36,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 266,
            "text": "Ne am win iâaddan di temdint tilemt, thudd wakali. Inna: «amek ara d Issider Öebbi tagi, deffir tmeppant is?» Ina t Öebbi twinas iseggwasen, sinna, Issenker it, Inna: «acêal teqqimev?» Inna d: «qqime ibwass, ne ur ibbwiv wass». Inna: «xaîi, teqqimev twinas iseggwasen. Muqel lqut ik akked tissit ik, ur xûiôen. Muqel ayul ik. A k Nerr d assekni i medden. Muqel isan amek ara ten Nessemlil, sinna, ad asen Nessels aksum». Mi ipputebbet, inna: «éôi Öebbi Izmer i yal cci».",
            "numberInSurah": 259,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 43,
            "ruku": 36,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 267,
            "text": "U mi inna Ibôahim: «a Mass iw! Ssenâat iyi amek tessidirev lmeggtin». Inna: «day ur tuminev ara?» Inna: «xaîi, maca iwakken ad ithedden wul iw». Inna: «ihi, îîef kué igvav, awi ten id uôek, sinna, err, di yal iil, amur segsen. Sinna, siwel asen, a d asen dumatu. Cfu ar Öebbi d Uohid, d Uûwib».",
            "numberInSurah": 260,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 44,
            "ruku": 36,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 268,
            "text": "Wid ipseddiqen ayla nnsen deg ubrid n Öebbi, cuban aâqqa id igren sa tyedrin. Di yal taydrep, twinas iâqqayen. Öebbi Issugut i win i S Ihwan. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 261,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 44,
            "ruku": 37,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 269,
            "text": "Wid ipseddiqen ayla nnsen deg ubrid n Öebbi, ur seddan, i wayen ssedqen, tiyta ne rregmat, ad awin arraz nnsen suô Mass nnsen; ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 262,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 44,
            "ruku": 37,
            "hizbQuarter": 17,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 270,
            "text": "Awal imaânen akked ssmaê, ifen aseddeq i vefôent rregmat. Öebbi d Asâay, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 263,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 44,
            "ruku": 37,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 271,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur ssemsayet ssadaqa nnwen, s tiyta akked rregmat. Am win iseddqen ayla s, iwakken a t walin medden, ur iumin s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Icuba taéôut i iumm wakal. Iwwet fellas uzayev, iooa p d asuki. Ur sfaydin acemma seg wayen bbwin. Öebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 264,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 44,
            "ruku": 37,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 272,
            "text": "Wid ipseddiqen ayla nnsen, ssaramen ad Iôavi Öebbi, u tebbten iman nnsen, cuban leonan di tiilt. Iwwet fellas ugeffur, ifka d sin imuren n lella s. Ma ur iwwit fellas ugeffur, d nnda. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 265,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 45,
            "ruku": 37,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 273,
            "text": "Yiwen degwen, ma tusa t id tewser, u uôes tarwa tuôhift, day ad issirem ad isâu leonan n tezdayin akked tfeôôant, isaffen ppazzalen ddaw as, degs, i neppa, yal ppemôa? Têuza t tnifift degs times, iôa. Akka i wen Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen, amar a pmeyyzem.",
            "numberInSurah": 266,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 45,
            "ruku": 37,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 274,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Seddqet seg wayen imaânen i teîfem, seg wayen i wen d Nessuffe si tmurt. Ur fernet ucmit, segs, ayen ur teppadamem siwa ma s tuqna n wallen, a t tseddqem. Cfut ar Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 267,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 45,
            "ruku": 38,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 275,
            "text": "Cciîan iâahed awen tiggulelt, iumeô awen lâaô. Öebbi Iâahed awen ssmaê suôeS akked lfevl. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 268,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 45,
            "ruku": 38,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 276,
            "text": "Ippak ûûwab i win i S Ihwan. Win iwumi ippunefk ûûwab, ni ippunefk as aîas n lxiô. Siwa uâqilen i ismektayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 269,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 45,
            "ruku": 38,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 277,
            "text": "Ayen tefkam useddeq, ne teqqnem n tuqqna, Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa t. Ur llin imâiwnen i imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 270,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 46,
            "ruku": 38,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 278,
            "text": "Ma tefkam ssadaqat âinani, ilha. Yif it ma s tuffra, u ma tefkam tent i imeban. Ad pwakksent kra si tucmitin nnwen. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 271,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 46,
            "ruku": 38,
            "hizbQuarter": 18,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 279,
            "text": "Ur fellak a ten tenhuv. Maca Öebbi Inehhu win i S Ihwan. Ayen tefkam n lxiô, i iman nnwen. Ur tefkim siwa ef udem n Öebbi. Ayen tefkam n lxiô, a kwen id iual, u kunwi ur kwen dennisen.",
            "numberInSurah": 272,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 46,
            "ruku": 38,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 280,
            "text": "I imeban ifelsen deg ubrid n Öebbi, ur nezmir ad inigen di tmurt; wur nessin, inwa ten d imeôkantiyen, seg wakken êekmen. A ten tâaqlev ar tiddi nnsen: ur ssuturen imdanen s nnbec. Ayen tefkam n lxiô, s tidep, Öebbi Iéôa t.",
            "numberInSurah": 273,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 46,
            "ruku": 38,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 281,
            "text": "Wid ifkan ayla nnsen deg iv, deg wass, s tuffra u âinani, ad awin arraz nnsen ar Mass nnsen; ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 274,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 46,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 282,
            "text": "Wid iteppen rrba, ur d pnekkaren siwa am ara d kren win issexbibev Cciîan, mi t innul. Ayagi, acku nnan: «ttjara am rrba kan». Öebbi Iêell ttjara, Igdel rrba. Win n tusa lewûaya suô Mass is, da ixva, ines ayen iâaddan. Lameô is ar Öebbi. Wid iualen, widak d at tmes, nitni, degs, ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 275,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 47,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 283,
            "text": "Ad Imêu Öebbi rrba, ad Isbuôket ssadaqa. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara yal ajehli amednub.",
            "numberInSurah": 276,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 47,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 284,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, u péallan, u pzekkin, ad awin arraz nnsen ar Mass nnsen; ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 277,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 47,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 285,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Eooet ayen d igwran si rrba, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.",
            "numberInSurah": 278,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 47,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 286,
            "text": "Ma ur tewqimem ara, êûut ara kwen Inna Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma tnedmem, nnwen ôaselmal. Ur denniset, ur pwadenset.",
            "numberInSurah": 279,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 47,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 287,
            "text": "I win illan di lhejna, aôout liser. Ma tseddqem, yif it i kunwi, lemmer teéôim.",
            "numberInSurah": 280,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 47,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 288,
            "text": "Ëezzbet i wass n tualin nnwen ar Öebbi. Imiren, yal yiwen ad as ippunefk wayen ikseb; nitni ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 281,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 47,
            "ruku": 39,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 289,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma tesâam îlaba ar lajel ipwassnen, arut ep. A p iaru umaru segwen, s ûûfawa. Ur ippagwi umaru a p iaru, akken i s Isselmed Öebbi. Ad iaru ayen ar as yini umeîîalbu. Ad iêezzeb i Öebbi, Mass is. Ur issenqas acemma segs. Ma illa umeîîalbu d abuhal, ne d uôhif, ne ur izmir ad yini neppa, ihi, ad yini umeddakwel is s ûûfawa. Sbeddet sin inagan seg irgazen nnwen. Ma ur llin ara sin irgazen, argaz akked snat n tlawin, seg wid tôuvam ad cehhden. Ma telev yiwet segsent, tayev a d temmekti. Ur ppagwin inagan, ma pwanecden. Ur stehzayet a p tarum, meééiyet ne meqqwôet, ar lajel is. Ayagi iwzen kteô ar Öebbi, iwata kteô i ccada, iwulem kteô ad awen ikkes ccekk. Kkes ed ssuq i tefram imiren garawen; ulac uilif fellawen, ma ur t turim ara. Awit inagan deg uzenzi nnwen. Ur ippili ujuôu ef umaru ne ef unagi. Ma tjuôem, ihi, dir ikwen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi Isselmad ikwen. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 282,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 48,
            "ruku": 40,
            "hizbQuarter": 19,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 290,
            "text": "Ma d iminigen ay tellam, ur tufim amaru, a ppeppunefk ôôhina. Ma ifka yiwen segwen lamana i wayev, win iwumi teppunefk, a p irr i win i s ifkan lamana s. Ad iêezzeb i Öebbi, Mass is. Ur ppeffret ccada. Win ip iffren, ihi, neppa, idneb wul is. Öebbi Iéôa ay txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 283,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 49,
            "ruku": 40,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 291,
            "text": "N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ama tesseknem i illan deg iman nnwen, ne tebam t, a kwen Iêaseb Öebbi fellas. Ad Isemmeê i win i S Ihwan, ad Iâaqeb win i S Ihwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 284,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 49,
            "ruku": 41,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 292,
            "text": "Iumen Umazan s wayen id iusan, uôes, suô Mass is. Lmumnin, akw, umnen s Öebbi akked lmalayek iS, Tizmamin iS, imazanen iS. Ur nesemgirrid yiwen ger imazanen iS. Nnan: «nesla, nunez. Ssmaê iK a Mass nne! £uôeK tualin.",
            "numberInSurah": 285,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 49,
            "ruku": 41,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 293,
            "text": "Ur Ipkellif Öebbi yiman, siwa ar wayen iwumi izmer. Ines wayen ikseb, mgal is wayen iddem. A Mass nne! Ur a Pqassa ma neppu, ne neccev. A Mass nne! Ur a Sbibbi taâkkwemt akken ip Tesbabbev i wid i  d izwaren. A Mass nne! Ur a Sbibbi ayen iwumi ur nezmir. Semmeê ane, Suref a, Ëun fellane. Keçç d Bab nne, Srebê a ef ugdud ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 286,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 49,
            "ruku": 41,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
