            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 295,
            "text": "Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Amuddir, Imezgi.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 296,
            "text": "Issers ak d Tazmamt s tidep, d atebbet n wayen ip id izwaren. Issers ed Tuôa akked Linoil,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 297,
            "text": "uqbel, d nnhaya i medden. Issers ed Leqwôan. Ih, wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, fellasen aâaqeb uqûiê. Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 298,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi ur aS iffir wacemma di tmurt, ne deg igenni.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 299,
            "text": "D Neppa i wen Ippaken udem, di tâabbav, akken i S ihwa. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 300,
            "text": "Neppa i k ed Issersen Tazmamt, degs issekniyen uvhiôen, nitni d tayimmap n Tezmamt. Wiyav d licwaô. Da, wid iwumi mmalen wulawen, teddun akked wayen illan d licwaô, ssaramen ahewwel, ssaramen asefhem is. I Issnen asefhem is, siwa Öebbi. Qqaôen imawlan n tmusni: 'numen yis. Suô Mass nne akw'. Id ismektayen, siwa uâqilen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 301,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Ur Smili ulawen nne, mbaâd ma Tenhiv a. Efk a d, suôeK, aêunu. Ih, Keçç, ard Amit.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 302,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Keçç, s tidep, ara Ijemmlen medden, ass ief ur illi ccekk. S tidep, Öebbi ur Izeggel lemâahda.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 50,
            "ruku": 42,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 303,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen, ur sen d ippawi acemma, ar Öebbi, wayla nnsen, ne tarwa nnsen. Widak, d nitni ay d isufa n tmes.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 51,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 304,
            "text": "D tin n ugdud n Ferâun akked wid i ten id izwaren. Skaddben issekniyen nne£. Iwwet iten Öebbi, ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Öebbi Iwâaô i uâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 51,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 305,
            "text": "Ini i wid ijehlen: 'a ppepwaelbem, a ppepwafesrem di Loahennama'. A yir usu!",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 51,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 306,
            "text": "Ni d assekni, i kunwi, mi mlalent snat trebbuyaâ. Yiwet tepna deg ubrid n Öebbi; tayev d tajehlit, twala d snat, s yiéôi s. Öebbi Ippak afus, s tallalt iS, i win i S ihwan. Deg wayagi, s tidep, aselmed i wid ipwalin.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 51,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 307,
            "text": "D tucbiêt ay d tedheô i yimdanen leêmala n ccehwiyyat: tilawin, tarwa, iâammuôen ibararen n ddheb akked lfeîîa, iâawdiwen n ccetla, lmal, akal. Ayagi, d zzhu n tmeddurt n ddunit. Öebbi, uôeS amkan lâali, n tualin.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 51,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 20,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 308,
            "text": "Ini: 'ad awen mle i yifen aya? I wid ipêezziben, ar Mass nnsen, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen, tilawin iûfan, akked llza suô Öebbi'. Öebbi Ipwali imdanen;",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 51,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 309,
            "text": "wid iqqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Nekwni, s tidep, numen. Ihi, Semmeê a ibekkaven nne, Sellek a seg uâaqeb n tmes'.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 52,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 310,
            "text": "Iûebôiyen, imawlan n tidep, imvuâen, wid ipseddiqen, wid istefiôen di tafrara.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 52,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 311,
            "text": "Icuhhed Öebbi ar ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa. Akken lmalayek, akked imawlan n tmusni. Ibedd i lmizan. Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 52,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 312,
            "text": "Ih, ddin ar Öebbi d annuz. Ur mgarraden wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, armi deffir n tisin n tussna uôsen, wa iqheô wa. Wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, ihi, Öebbi Ipawal deg uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 52,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 313,
            "text": "Ma nuqmen k, ini: 'unze aS i Öebbi. Akken, wid iddan yidi. Ini i wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, akked at war tussna: 'ma tunzem'? Ma unzen, ihi, pwanhan. Ma wexxôen, ay fellak siwa anabi. Öebbi Ipwali imdanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 52,
            "ruku": 43,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 314,
            "text": "Ih, wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, u pnaen lambiyya, war ssebba, u pnaen wid seg yimdanen ippamôen lmizan, becceô iten s uâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 52,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 315,
            "text": "Widak, d wid iwumi mêan igiten nnsen di ddunit, di laxert. Ur sâin isellaken.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 52,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 316,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid iwumi ippunefk kra si Tezmamt, la ssuturen, i Tezmamt n Öebbi, aêuddu garasen? Sinna, ad iwexxeô urbaâ segsen, u nitni pnamaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 53,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 317,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku nnan: 'ur a teppep tmes, siwa kra n wussan'. Iuôô iten, di ddin nnsen, wayen id snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 53,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 318,
            "text": "Amek ihi, ma Njemmel iten, ass ideg, ur degs ccekk, yal yiwen ad iellet ayen ikseb, nitni ur ppudensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 53,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 319,
            "text": "Ini: 'a Öebbi, Agellid n tgelda, Teppakev tagelda i win i K ihwan, Teppeksev tagelda i win i K ihwan, Tepâuzzuv win i K ihwan, Tesdulluv win i K ihwan. Lxiô deg ufus i K. Ih, Keçç, Tzemrev i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 53,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 320,
            "text": "Tessekcamev iv deg wass. Tessekcamev ass deg iv. Tessuffuev amuddir si lmegget. Tessuffuev lmegget seg umuddir. Tepitiv win i K ihwan, war aktili'.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 53,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 321,
            "text": "Lmumnin ur pparan ijehliyen d iêbiben nnsen, war lmumnin. Win ixedmen aya, ur illi, s wacemma, ar Öebbi. Kkes ed aêezzeb i têezzbem iman nnwen segsen. Iâaggen awen Öebbi s yiman iS. Tualin ar Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 53,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 322,
            "text": "Ini: 'ama teffrem i illan deg idmaren nnwen, ne tessnaâtem t, Öebbi Iéôa t'. Iéôa i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 53,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 323,
            "text": "Ass ideg yal iman ad iaf irs ed, wayen ixdem n lxiô, akked wayen ixdem n cceôô, ad issirem a ppili, garas yides, tallit ezzifen! Iâaggen awen Öebbi, af yiman iS. Öebbi d Umâin ar imdanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 44,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 324,
            "text": "Ini: 'ma têemmlem Öebbi, ddut yidi. A kwen Iâuzz Öebbi, ad awen Isemmeê ibekkaven nnwen. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 325,
            "text": "Ini: 'ssemêesset i Öebbi akked Umazan'. Ma wexxôen, ihi Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 21,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 326,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi Ismenyaf, i imavalen, Adem, Nuê, tawacult n Ibôahim, tawacult n Âimôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 327,
            "text": "Wa iurew wa. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 328,
            "text": "Mi tenna tmeîîut n Âimôan: 'a Mass iw! Wekkle aK ayen illan di tâabbuî iw, d lewkala, Eqbel suôi. Keçç, ih, d win Isellen, d Amusnaw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 329,
            "text": "Mi p id turew, tenna: 'a Mass iw! Urwe p id d nnta'. - Öebbi Iéôa, sennig akw, d acu d turew. Ddkeô, maççi am nnta. - 'Nek semma as Meryem, rri p seddaw tecvaî iK, neppat akked tarwa s, mgal Cciîan imenfi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 330,
            "text": "Iôêeb yis Mass is, asteôêeb ilhan; Isgem ip, tigmi ilhan; Ikwellef ip i Zakariyya. Yal tikelt ara iôuê uôes Zakariyya ar lmiêreb, a n iaf tesâa ôôeéq. Inna: 'a Meryem! Ansi i m d ikka waya'? Tenna: 'suô Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Iôeééeq win i S ihwan, war aktili'.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 54,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 331,
            "text": "Da Zakariyya inuj uô Mass is, inna: 'a Mass iw! Efk iyi d, suôeK, tarwa ifazen. Keçç, s tidep, Tsellev i unuju'.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 332,
            "text": "Mi ibedd, ipéalla di lmeêreb, ssawlent as d lmalayek: 'Ibecceô ik Öebbi s Yaêia, d atebbet n wawal n Öebbi, d ssid, d azedgan, d nnbi, seg iâaôviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 333,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Amek ara sâu aqcic? Ni wessre, tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt'. Inna: 'akka, Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 334,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Efk iyi d assekni'. Inna: 'assekni ik, ur tepmeslayev i medden krav wussan. Asal kan. Mmekti d aîas Mass ik, sbuccaâ iT tameddit, tafrara'.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 45,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 335,
            "text": "Mi s nnant lmalayek: 'a Meryem! Öebbi, s tidep, Ifren ikem, Izzazdeg ikem, Ismenyaf ikem i tlawin imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 336,
            "text": "A Meryem! Anez i Mass im, knu yaS, îîinez akked wid iîîinizen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 337,
            "text": "Ayagi si tmucuha i iffren, Nweêêa yak t. Ur telliv yidsen, mi jebden taseqqaôt, anwa segsen ara itkelfen ef Meryem. Ur telliv yidsen mi mqellaâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 338,
            "text": "Mi s nnant lmalayek: 'a Meryem! Öebbi, s tidep, Ibecceô ikem s wawal suôeS, ism is: lmasiê Âisa, mmi s n Meryem; mucaâ di ddunit akked laxert; seg iqôiben.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 55,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 339,
            "text": "A d ipmeslay i medden, si dduê, am unqaqôi, ad yili seg iâaôviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 56,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 340,
            "text": "Tenna: 'a Mass iw! Amek ara sâu aqcic, ur iyi innul urgaz'? Inna: 'akka. Öebbi Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Ma Iseyya lameô, ad as Yini kan: 'ili'! Ad yili'.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 56,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 341,
            "text": "Ad as Isselmed Tazmamt, ûûwab, Tuôa, Linoil.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 56,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 342,
            "text": "D amazan ar At Isôail: 'ni nek usi d, uôwen, s issekniyen suô Mass nnwen. Nek ad awen d xelqe, s talaxt, ayen icban afôux, ad ûuve degs, ad iual d afôux, ma Iba Öebbi. Ad sseêlu aderal, amuvin n lbeôû, a d ssidre lmeggtin, ma Iba Öebbi. Ad awen ini d acu teppeppem, akked wayen txezznem deg ixxamen nnwen. Deg waya, s tidep, d assekni i kunwi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 56,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 343,
            "text": "A d tebbte iyi d izwaren di Tuôa, ad awen êelle kra n wayen illan ipwagdel awen. Usi d, uôwen, s ussekni, suô Mass nnwen. Ëezbet i Öebbi, aet iyi awal.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 56,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 344,
            "text": "Öebbi, s tidep, d Mass iw, u d Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eP, d wagi ay d abrid uwqim'.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 56,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 22,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 345,
            "text": "Mi israê Âisa tijehli suôsen, inna: 'anwi ay d imâiwnen iw ar Öebbi'? Nnan as d lexwan: 'nekwni d imâiwnen n Öebbi. Numen s Öebbi, eched ar nekwni d imvuâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 56,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 346,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Numen s wayen id Tessersev, nedda d umazan, Aru ya seg inagan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 347,
            "text": "Undin. Iundi Öebbi. Öebbi Yif akw imendayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 46,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 348,
            "text": "Mi s Inna Öebbi: 'a Âisa! Nek ad Ddme ôôuê ik, a k id Ssali uôI, a k id Ssiferre seg wid ijehlen, ad Rre, wid iddan yidek, sennig wid ijehlen, ar ass n tnekra'. Sinna, tualin nnwen uôI, ad Ëudde, garawen, ef wayen ief teppemgarradem.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 349,
            "text": "Ma d wid ijehlen, a ten Âaqbe di ddunit, di laxert, aâaqeb aqeûêan. Ur asen ppilin isellaken.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 350,
            "text": "Wanag wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ad asen Ifk arrazen nnsen. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 351,
            "text": "Ayagi i ak Nemmal seg issekniyen, akked usmekti uûwib.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 352,
            "text": "Ih, amedya n Âisa, ar Öebbi, am umedya n Adem. Ixelq it seg wakal, sinna, Inna yas: 'ili'! Illa.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 353,
            "text": "Tidep, suô Mass ik. Ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 354,
            "text": "I win i k inumren fellas, deffir wayen i k id iusan n tussna, ini: 'yyaw a nenced tarwa nne, tarwa nnwen, tilawin nne, tilawin nnwen, iman nne, iman nnwen. Sinna, a nemmesgill, a nd²âu ad Ixzu Öebbi ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 57,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 355,
            "text": "Ih, tagi d tamacahup n tidep, ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi, Neppa, war ccekk, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 356,
            "text": "Ma wexxren, ihi Öebbi Issen ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 47,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 357,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yAt Tezmamt! Yyaw ar wawal azduklan garane yidwen. A naâbed siwa Öebbi, ur aS nepcarak acemma; ur pparan, kra segne kra, d iôebbiten, war Öebbi'. Ma wexxôen, init: 'cehhdet ar nekwni d imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 358,
            "text": "A yAt Tezmamt! Acimi temnamarem ef Ibôahim? Ur n risent Tuôa akked Linoil, armi deffir es, day ur tmeyyzem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 359,
            "text": "Kunwi, atan temnamarem ef wayen tessnem. Ihi, acimi temnamarem ef wayen ur tessinem? Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 360,
            "text": "Ur illi Ibôahim d uday ne d amasiêi, maca illa d amvuâ imalen ar tidep. Ur illi seg imcurak.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 361,
            "text": "Ih, imdanen iqeôben nezzeh ar Ibôahim, war ccekk, d wid i t ivefôen, akked Nnbi agi, akked wid iumnen. Öebbi d Bab n lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 362,
            "text": "Arbaâ, seg At Tezmamt, iba a kwen itlef. Ara telfen siwa iman nnsen, ur éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 363,
            "text": "A yAt Tezmamt! Acimi tugim issekniyen n Öebbi, u kunwi tepwalim?",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 58,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 364,
            "text": "A yAt Tezmamt! Acimi teslusum, i tidep, ayen idensen, u teppeffrem tidep, kunwi teêûam?",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 59,
            "ruku": 48,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 365,
            "text": "Arbaâ, seg At Tezmamt, inna: 'amnet mi iuli wass, s wayen id irsen ar wid iumnen, nekôet tameddit'. Amendeô ma a d ualen.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 59,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 366,
            "text": "Ppamnet kan win ivefôen ddin nnwen. Ini: 'ih, nnhaya d nnhaya n Öebbi. A ppeppunefk i yiwen am wayen i wen ippunefken'. Ne a kwen namren af Mass nnwen. Ini: 'lfevl, s tidep, deg ufus n Öebbi, Ippak it i win i S ihwan'. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 59,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 367,
            "text": "Iâateq aêunu S i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 59,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 23,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 368,
            "text": "Seg wAt Tezmamt, illa win, xas teooiv as adrim aîas, ad ak t id irr. Illa wayev segsen, ma teooiv as adinar, ur ak t id ippara, alamma tezgiv uôes. Akka, acku nitni nnan: 'ur a d ppawven at war tussna'. U ggaren d tikerkas ef Öebbi, u nitni éôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 59,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 369,
            "text": "Xaîi! Win iîîfen di lemâahda s, u iêezzeb…ihi, Öebbi Iêemmel wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 59,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 370,
            "text": "Ih, wid ippaen s lemâahda n Öebbi akked tgallit nnsen, ayen ôxisen, widak, ur ppawin amur di laxert, ur asen Ipmeslay Öebbi, ur ten id Ipmuqul, ass n tnekra, ur ten Izzizdig. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 59,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 371,
            "text": "Ih, arbaâ segsen ssexsaôen Tazmamt s yilsawen nnsen, iwakken a pilem n Tezmamt, ayen ur nelli n Tezmamt. Qqaôen: 'aya suô Öebbi', u neppa ur illi suô Öebbi. U qqaren tikerkas ef Öebbi, u nitni éôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 60,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 372,
            "text": "Ur ippunefk ara i umdan iwumi Ifka Öebbi Tazmamt, ûûwab, u Irra t d nnbi, ad iual ad yini i medden: 'ilit d imdanen iw, war Öebbi'. Maca: 'ilit d iselmaden, imi tesselmadem Tazmamt, u tlemdem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 60,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 373,
            "text": "Ur awen Iumeô ara a pperrem lmalayek akked lambiyya, d imawlan. Day awen Iameô tijehli, mbaâd ma tellam d imvuâen?",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 60,
            "ruku": 49,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 374,
            "text": "Mi Iîîef Öebbi laâqed n lambiyya: 's tidep, Fki awen si Tezmamt akw si ûûwab, sinna, iusa kwen id umazan, i itebbten ayen illan uôwen. Amnet yis, âiwnet ep'. Inna: 'tâazmem u tqeblem, f waya, laâqed iW'? Nnan as: 'naâzem'. Inna: 'ihi, cehhdet, Nek, yidwen, seg inagan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 60,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 375,
            "text": "Wid iwexxôen, deffir waya, nitni d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 60,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 376,
            "text": "Day ban ddin ur nelli n Öebbi? U Neppa, unzen aS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan, ban ne ugin. £uôeS, tualin nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 60,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 377,
            "text": "Ini: 'numen s Öebbi, akked wayen id irsen uône, akked wayen id irsen ar Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq, Iaâqub, laâôac, ayen ippunefken i Musa, Âisa, akked lambiyya, suô Mass nnsen. Ur nesmenyaf yiwen degsen. Nekwni nunez aS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 378,
            "text": "Win iban ddin, war annuz, ur ipwaqbal suôes. U neppa, di laxert, seg imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 379,
            "text": "Amek ara Inhu Öebbi agdud inekôen deffir liman is, u cehhden ar Amazan d tidep, u iusa ten id ubeggen? Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 380,
            "text": "Widak, aqeîîi nnsen d ddell suô Öebbi, d lmalayek, akked imdanen meôôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 381,
            "text": "Degs ad wekkôen; ur ippifsus fellasen uâaqeb, ur stiseren.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 382,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid iualen nedmen, deffir waya, u xedmen ayen ilhan. Ih, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 383,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen, deffir liman nnsen, sinna, rnan di tijehli, ur tepwaqbal nndama nnsen. Widak d imeôôqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 384,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen, u mmuten d ijehliyen, ur ipwaqbal suô yiwen degsen, azal n tmurt n ddheb, a t id ifdu. I widak, aâaqeb aqeôêan, ur sâin amâiwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 61,
            "ruku": 50,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 385,
            "text": "Ur teppawvem ar ppuba, d awezi, alamma tseddqem seg wayen têemmlem. Kra n wayen tseddqem n cci, ihi, Öebbi Iéôa t.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 3,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 24,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 386,
            "text": "Yal lqut illa iêell i At Isôail, siwa ayen igdel Isôail i iman is, uqbel a d ters Tuôa. Ini: 'awit ed Tuôa, eôt ep, ma tessawalem tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 387,
            "text": "Wid id igren tikerkas ef Öebbi, deffir waya, nitni d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 388,
            "text": "Ini: 'Inna d Öebbi tidep; ddut d ddin n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep, ur nelli seg imcurak'.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 389,
            "text": "Ih, axxam amezwaru, i irsen i medden, war ccekk, d win n Bekka. Iôqa, d nnhaya i imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 390,
            "text": "Degs issekniyen iberrzen; d axxam n Ibôahim. Win it ikecmen, atan di laman. I Öebbi, iwata ad êuoen medden s Axxam, ma zemren a t awven. Win iugin, ihi, Rebbi ur Iêwao ara imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 391,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yAt Tezmamt! Acimi tnekôem issekniyen n Öebbi'? Öebbi d Anagi n wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 392,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yAt Tezmamt! Acimi teîîeôôifem, wid iumnen, seg ubrid n Öebbi? Tessaramem t iaâwej, u kunwi d inagan'. Ur Ifil Öebbi ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 393,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma tuem awal i urbaâ, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, a kwen rren d ijehliyen, deffir liman nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 62,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 394,
            "text": "Amek tnekôem, u kunwi ôan awen d issekniyen n Öebbi, u, garawen, Amazan iS? Win iîîfen di Öebbi, ni ipwanha s abrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 51,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 395,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, akken Iklal aêezzeb. Ur ppemmtet alamma tunzem.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 396,
            "text": "Eîfet akw di teêmilt n Öebbi, ur ppemfaôaqet. Mmektit ed ayen ikwen Iat Öebbi. Mi tellam d icenga, Issemlal ulawen nnwen. S lit iS, tualem d atmaten. Tellam ef rrif n maylellif n tmes, Isellek ikwen segs. Akka i wen Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen iS, amendeô ma a ppepwanhum.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 397,
            "text": "Amar ad yili, segwen, lois i ineccden ar lxiô, ippamôen lqanun, itekksen ayen n dir. Widak d imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 398,
            "text": "Ur ppilit am wid imfaôaqen, u mgarraden, deffir n tisin ubeggen uôsen. I widak, aâaqeb aqeôêan,",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 399,
            "text": "ass ideg ara imlulen wudmawen, ara ibriken wudmawen. Wanag wid iwumi ara ibriken wudmawen nnsen: 'tnekôem, deffir liman nnwen? Jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tnekôem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 400,
            "text": "Wanag wid iwumi ara a imlulen wudmawen nnsen, ad ilin deg uêunu n Öebbi. Nitni, degs, ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 401,
            "text": "D wigi ay d issekniyen n Öebbi. Neqqaô ak ten id, s tidep. Ur Ibi Öebbi ddens i imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 63,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 402,
            "text": "N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ar Öebbi tualin n lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 64,
            "ruku": 52,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 403,
            "text": "Tifem akw leoyus id iffen i medden. Teppamôem lqanun, teppekksem ayen n dir, tumnem s Öebbi. Ppif, i At Tezmamt, lemmer uminen. Garasen lmumnin; tegwti degsen d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 64,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 404,
            "text": "Cwiî kan ara kwen vuôôen. Ma nnuen kwen, ad rewlen, sinna, ur sâun amâiwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 64,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 405,
            "text": "Iwwet iten ddell anda ma llan, siwa wid iîîfen di teêmilt n Öebbi, u di teêmilt n medden. Lqan urrif n Öebbi, u teli d tiggulelt fellasen. Ayagi, acku llan nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, la neqqen lambiyya, war ssebba. Ayagi, imi âuûan u zgaren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 64,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 25,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 406,
            "text": "Ur aâdilen. Illa lois, seg At Tezmamt, i iqqaôen issekniyen n Öebbi deg iv, u nitni kennun.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 64,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 407,
            "text": "Umnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, ppamôen lqanun, tekksen ayen n dir, pêirin ar lxiô. Widak seg iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 64,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 408,
            "text": "Ayen xedmen n lxiô, ur asen ipwankaô. Öebbi Issen wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 64,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 409,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen, ur asen d ippawi acemma, ar Öebbi, wayla nnsen, ne tarwa nnsen. Widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 65,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 410,
            "text": "Amedya n wayen pseôôifen di tmeddurt n ddunit agi, am umedya n wavu, degs abruri. Iêuza iger n ugdud idensen iman is. Isnegr it. Ur ten Idnis Öebbi; d iman nnsen ay dennisen.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 65,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 411,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pparat d iêbiben, wur nelli segwen. Ur zgalen a kwen hewwlen. Ban a kwen hejjnen. Ni ibda d lbwev seg imawen nnsen. Ayen iffren deg ulawen nnsen, ielb it. Ni Nbeggen awen ed issekniyen, ma tepmeyyizem.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 65,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 412,
            "text": "Atan kunwi d wid i ten iêemmlen, ur kwen êemmlen. Tumnem di Tezmamt, s lekmal is. Ma mmugren kwen, ad inin: 'numen'. Mi aben, ad eééen ivudan nnsen si zzâaf fellawen. Ini: 'emmtet si zzâaf nnwen'! Ih, Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 65,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 413,
            "text": "Ma iusa kwen id ise, a ten isnuben. Ma tevôa yidwen tucmip, ad feôêen yis. Ma tûebôem, u têezbem, ur kwen teîîuôôu s wacemma, tandit nnsen. Ni Izzi Öebbi i wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 65,
            "ruku": 53,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 414,
            "text": "Mi teffev, ûûbeê zik, si twacult ik, temmalev i lmumnin imukan umennu, Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 121,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 65,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 415,
            "text": "Mi qôib feclent snat n trebbuyaâ nnwen, u Öebbi d Bab nnsent. Iwata i yal lmumen, ad ippkel ef Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 122,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 416,
            "text": "Ni Iâiwen ikwen Öebbi di Badô, mi tellam tendellem. Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, amar a ppesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 123,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 417,
            "text": "Mi tenniv i lmumnin: 'day ur testeqnaâm ara, mi kwen Iâiwen Öebbi s krav igima n lmalayek, id irsen'?",
            "numberInSurah": 124,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 418,
            "text": "Xaîi, ma tûebôem u têezzbem, ma ewwsen d fellawen, a kwen Iâiwen Mass nnwen, s smus igima n lmalayek ikkaten.",
            "numberInSurah": 125,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 419,
            "text": "Ur Iga akka Öebbi, siwa i ubecceô nnwen, ad rtiêen yis wulawen nnwen. Rrbeê suô Öebbi kan, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 126,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 420,
            "text": "Iwakken ad Iôé arbaâ n wid ijehlen, ne a ten Iééaâ, ad ualen nnewnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 127,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 421,
            "text": "Ur k iaâna lameô s wacemma. Ad asen Issuref, ne a ten Iâaqeb, nitni d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 128,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 422,
            "text": "N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ipsemmiê i win i S ihwan. Ipâaqab win i S ihwan. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 129,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 54,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 423,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur teppet rrba ipzeggiden, tepzeggid. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 130,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 424,
            "text": "Ëezzbet ilmend n tmes i ippuheggan i ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 131,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 425,
            "text": "Aet awal i Öebbi akked Umazan, amar ad yili uêunu fellawen.",
            "numberInSurah": 132,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 66,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 26,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 426,
            "text": "£iwlet ar ssmaê suô Mass nnwen, akked Loennet iwsâan am tmurt akked igenwan. Teppuhegga d i wid ipêezziben,",
            "numberInSurah": 133,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 427,
            "text": "wid ipseddiqen - sâan ne xuûûen -, wid isnusun reffu, wid ipsemmiêen i medden - Öebbi Iêemmel lâuûam -,",
            "numberInSurah": 134,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 428,
            "text": "wid, ma xedmen tucmip, ne densen iman nnsen, a d mmektin Öebbi, ad stefôen ef ibekkaven nnsen. Anwa Ipsemmiêen ibekkaven siwa Öebbi? Ur pgerninen deg wayen xedmen, u nitni éôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 135,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 429,
            "text": "Widak, akafi nnsen d ssmaê n Mass nnsen, akked leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. D arraz igerzen i wid issewqamen.",
            "numberInSurah": 136,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 430,
            "text": "Âaddant tedyanin uqbel nnwen. Iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevôa d wid id iggaren tikerkas.",
            "numberInSurah": 137,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 431,
            "text": "Wagi d abeggen i medden, d nnhaya akked unecced i wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 138,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 432,
            "text": "Ur ppifcilet, ur webnet, d kunwi i iaâlayen, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.",
            "numberInSurah": 139,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 433,
            "text": "Ma iêuza kwen lada, ni lada i t icban iêuza agdud. Ussan agi Nerra ten, ger medden, d tidwal, iwakken ad Yissin Öebbi wid iumnen, ad Iddem segwen inagan. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 140,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 67,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 434,
            "text": "Iwakken ad Ijeôôeb Öebbi wid iumnen, u ad Isqucc ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 141,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 435,
            "text": "Day tilem a pkecmem Loennet, wanag ur Iéôi ara Öebbi wid ijuhden segwen, ur Issin ara iûebôiyen?",
            "numberInSurah": 142,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 436,
            "text": "Ni tepmennim tameppant, uqbel a p id temmagrem. Ni twalam p, kunwi tepmuqulem.",
            "numberInSurah": 143,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 55,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 437,
            "text": "Muêemmed d Amazan kan. Ni âaddan imazanen, uqbel is. Ma immut ne ipwana, day a ppualem ar deffir? Win ara iualen ar deffir, ur iîîuôôu Öebbi s wacemma. Öebbi ad Ikafi wid isnemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 144,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 56,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 438,
            "text": "Ur ipmeppat umdan siwa ma Irad Öebbi, di lajel iuran. Win iban akafi n ddunit, ad as t Nefk. Win iban akafi n laxeôt, ad as t Nefk. A Nkafi wid isnemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 145,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 56,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 439,
            "text": "Acêal n lambiyya i innuen, idda yidsen urbaâ iqwan, ur fcilen seg wayen iten issaâtben, deg ubrid n Öebbi, ur xuzen, ur fkin mayna. Öebbi Iêemmel iûebôiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 146,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 56,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 440,
            "text": "Awal nnsen, siwa mi nnan: 'a Mass nne! Semmeê a ibekkaven nne, akked tugut nne di lameô nne. Tebbet isurifen nne, Sserbeê ane ef ugdud ijehliyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 147,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 56,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 441,
            "text": "Ifka yasen Öebbi akafi n ddunit, akked ukafi lâali n laxert. Öebbi Iêemmel lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 148,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 68,
            "ruku": 56,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 442,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma tuem awal i wid ijehlen, a kwen rren ar deffir, a ppualem txesôem.",
            "numberInSurah": 149,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 69,
            "ruku": 57,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 443,
            "text": "Xaîi! Öebbi d Bab nnwen. Neppa, Yif akw imâiwnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 150,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 69,
            "ruku": 57,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 444,
            "text": "A Nessekcem tugdi deg ulawen n wid ijehlen, imi curken i Öebbi, ayen iwumi ur d irs ara udabu. Axxam nnsen d times. A yir tanezdut i imednas!",
            "numberInSurah": 151,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 69,
            "ruku": 57,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 445,
            "text": "Ni Issawel awen Öebbi tidep, di lemâahda S, mi ten tesnegrem, s tsriê iS. Armi, mi tfeclem, temnamarem f lameô, taâûam mbaâd ma Issken awen d ayen têemmlem. Garawen wid iban ddunit, garawen wid iban laxert. Sinna, Issebâad ikwen fellasen, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb. Ni Isemmeê awen. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 152,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 69,
            "ruku": 57,
            "hizbQuarter": 27,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 446,
            "text": "Mi tulim ur d tezzim, u Nnbi inecced ikwen ar ineggura nnwen. Ineûûef awen ailif s wayev, iwakken ur twebnem ef wayen i wen iôuêen, akked wayen ikwen iuen. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 153,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 69,
            "ruku": 57,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 447,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir uilif, Issers awen d laman, ives id ilin ef urbaâ segwen. Ni arbaâ pêebbiôen ef yiman nnsen, nnwan, ef Öebbi, ayen ur nelli d tidep, nnwaya n at war tussna. Qqaôen: 'day illa wayen i  iaânan, di lameô'? Ini: 's tidep, lameô akw i Öebbi'. Teffren, deg iman nnsen, ayen ur ak mmalen. Qqaôen: 'lemmer illi wayen i  iaânan, di lameô, ur nepwana dagi'. Ini: 'xas ma tellam deg ixxamen nnwen, wid ief tura tmeniwt, a ten tawev s imîeôêen nnsen. Iwakken ad Ijeôôeb Öebbi i illan deg idmaren nnwen, ad Izzizdeg i illan deg ulawen nnwen. Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 154,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 70,
            "ruku": 57,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 448,
            "text": "Ih, wid segwen iwexxôen asmi mlalent trebbuyaâ, d Cciîan kan iten iccacven, ilmend n kra n wayen kesben. Ni Isemmeê asen Öebbi. Akka, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 155,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 70,
            "ruku": 57,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 449,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur ppilit am wid ijehlen. Nnan i watmaten nnsen iunagen di tmurt, ne ipnaen: 'lemmer llin uône, ur mmuten, ur twanan'. Ad Irr Öebbi, ayagi, d aneggaf deg ulawen nnsen! Öebbi Issidir, Ineqq. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 156,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 70,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 450,
            "text": "Ma tepwanam deg ubrid n Öebbi, ne temmutem, ssmaê n Öebbi akked uêunu, war ccekk, ifen ayen la jemâan.",
            "numberInSurah": 157,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 70,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 451,
            "text": "Ma temmutem ne tepwanam, war ccekk, ar Öebbi ara tepwafesrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 158,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 71,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 452,
            "text": "S uêunu n Öebbi, têelmev uôsen. Lemmer tqeûêev, tesaôev ul ik, ad baâden fellak. Semmeê asen, ssuter ad ppusemmêen, ciweô iten ef lameô. Mi tseyyiv, ppkel ef Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Iêemmel wid ippkalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 159,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 71,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 453,
            "text": "Ma Iâiwen ikwen Öebbi, ur kwen irennu yiwen. Ma Iooa kwen, anwa illan a kwen iâiwen, deffir eS? £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 160,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 71,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 454,
            "text": "Ur issefk ara i nnbi ad idnes. Win idensen, a d ias s wayen idnes, ass n tnekra. Sinna, yal wa, ad as ippunefk wayen ikseb. Nitni, ur ten pmeôôiôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 161,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 71,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 455,
            "text": "Day win iddan d llza n Öebbi am win isebebben urrif n Öebbi, u tanezdut is d Loahennama? A taggara tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 162,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 71,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 456,
            "text": "Ur aâdilen ar Öebbi. Öebbi Ipwali acu xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 163,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 71,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 457,
            "text": "Ni Öebbi Iat lmumnin, mi sen d Iuzen Amazan segsen, immal asen issekniyen iS, izzizdig iten, isseêfav asen Tazmamt akked ûûwab, ulamma llan, zik, di ttelfan n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 164,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 71,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 458,
            "text": "Ma tuem tiyta, ni terram p berdayen. Tennam: 'ansi waya'? Ini: 'aya seg iman nnwen'. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 165,
            "juz": 4,
