            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 459,
            "text": "Ayen ikwen iwwten, ass n temlilit n trebbuyaâ, s tsriê n Öebbi. Iwakken ad Iéeô anwi ay d lmumnin,",
