            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 461,
            "text": "Wid innan i watmaten nnsen, u nitni qqimen: 'lemmer i  ssemêessen, ur pwanen'. Ini: 'sdarit iman nnwen si tmeppant, ma tessawalem tidep '.",
