            "page": 72,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 462,
            "text": "Ur pili mmuten wid ipwanan deg ubrid n Öebbi. Xaîi, d imuddiren. Ad ppuôeéqen ar Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 169,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 72,
            "ruku": 58,
            "hizbQuarter": 28,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 463,
            "text": "Ad feôêen s wayen i sen Ifka Öebbi, si lfevl iS. Zhan, imi wid deffir sen, mazal ur ten id nelêiq, ur ppagawaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 170,
