          },
          {
            "number": 467,
            "text": "Ualen d s lit n Öebbi akked lfevl, ur ten innul cceôô; ddan d llza n Öebbi. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 174,
