            "page": 74,
            "ruku": 60,
            "hizbQuarter": 29,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 478,
            "text": "Yal iman ad ijeôôeb tameppant. Ass n tnekra, ad awen ippunefk, kan, warraz nnwen. Win isellken si tmes, ikecmen Loennet, ni irbeê. Tameddurt, di ddunit, d zzhu kan ipuôôun.",
            "numberInSurah": 185,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 74,
            "ruku": 60,
            "hizbQuarter": 29,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 479,
            "text": "A ppeppujeôôbem deg wayla nnwen akked yiman nnwen. Ad wwten aîas degwen, wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, akked imcurak. Ma tûebôem u têezzbem, ayagi, s tidep, d ayen isselêayen lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 186,
