            "page": 74,
            "ruku": 60,
            "hizbQuarter": 30,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 480,
            "text": "Mi Iîîef Öebbi laâqed n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt: 'a p tbeggnem i medden, ur p teppeffrem'. Rran p deffir izugar nnsen, uen yis, ayen irxisen. I icmet wayen uen!",
            "numberInSurah": 187,
