            "hizbQuarter": 30,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 481,
            "text": "Ur pili ad sellken, seg uâaqeb, wid ifeôêen s wayen fkan, u ban a ten ccekôen ef wayen ur xdimen. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
