            "hizbQuarter": 30,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 484,
            "text": "Wid id ismektayen Öebbi s ibeddi, s iimi, s tuééla. Pmeyyizen lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan. A Mass nne! Ur Texliqev aya d aêerfi. Gedha s yiseK! Sellek a seg uâaqeb n tmes.",
