            "ruku": 61,
            "hizbQuarter": 30,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 485,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Ni, s tidep, Keçç, Texziv win Teskecmev ar tmes. Ur llin wid ara isellken imednas.",
