            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 76,
            "ruku": 61,
            "hizbQuarter": 30,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 491,
            "text": "Maca, i wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen: leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen, d inebgawen n Öebbi. U d wayen illan ar Öebbi, d amxallef i izedganen.",
