            "page": 77,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 496,
            "text": "Ma tugadem ur tweznem ara ar igujilen, aet ayen i wen ihwan n tlawin: snat, kravt, kuét. Ma tugadem ur tessaâdalem ara, yiwet kan, ne taklatin nnwen. Akka i iwulem, ur ppakwret.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
