            "page": 77,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 497,
            "text": "Efket tuççit nnsent i tlawin, d tikci. Ma rrant awen d kra segs, s lebi nnsent, ççet ep, s lfeôê akked llza.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 77,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 498,
            "text": "Ur ppaket i ijelufen ayla nnwen, win i wen Ifka Öebbi i tmeddurt. Öeéqet pen segs, sselset pen, ééiédet awal nnwen uôsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 77,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 499,
            "text": "Jeôôbet igujilen, alamma bbwven i jjwao. Ma tufam ten éewôen, efket asen ayla nnsen. Ur ten teppet s uveggaâ d usexseô, uqbel ad imuôen. Ameôkanti ad iêezzeb, amebun ad içç s lekyasa. Mara sen tefkem ayla nnsen, s inagan fellas. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi i leêsab.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 77,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 500,
            "text": "I yirgazen, amur seg wayen d ooan imawlan akked llzem. I tlawin amur seg wayen d ooan imawlan akked llzem. Ama cwiî, ne aîas, d amur ilezmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 78,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 501,
            "text": "Ma êedôen, i ufôaq, llzem, igujilen, igellilen, ôeéqet pen segs, tinem asen awal uûwib.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 78,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 502,
            "text": "Ad agwaden wid id iooan, deffir sen, tarwa tagellilt. Ad agwaden fellasen. Ad êezzben i Öebbi, s wawal iweznen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 78,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 503,
            "text": "Ih, wid iteppen, s ddens, ayla igujilen, la teppen kan times deg iâabbav nnsen, ad pwagren deg ujajiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 78,
            "ruku": 62,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 504,
            "text": "£ef tarwa nnwen, Iweûûa kwen Öebbi: i uqcic amur n snat tullas. Ma llant sennig snat n tullas, nnsent amur wis kué n lweôt. Ma yiwet i illan, ines uzgen. I imawlan is, i yal wa, amur wis sdis n wayen id iooa, ma isâa mmi s. Ma ur isâa ara mmi s, u weôten t imawlan is, amur wis kué i immas. Ma isâa atmaten, i immas amur wis sdis, kkes ed ayen ippuseôfen ne îlabat. Imawlan nnwen, arraw nnwen, ur teéôim ara menyif iten, akken i kwen nefâan. D aêeppem n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 78,
            "ruku": 63,
            "hizbQuarter": 31,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 505,
            "text": "Nnwen uzgen n wayen id ooant tlawin nnwen, ma ur sâint ara tarwa. Ma sâant mmit sent, i kunwi amur wis kué n wayen id ooant, kkes ed ayen ippuseôfen ne îlabat. I nitenti, amur wis kué n wayen id teooam, ma ur tesâim ara mmit wen. Ma tesâam mmit wen, i nitenti amur wis îam n wayen id teooam, kkes ed ayen ippuseôfen ne îlabat. Ma d argaz awêid ne d tameîîut tawêiî, ma isâa agmat ne taultmap, i yal wa segsen, amur wis sdis. Ma deg waîas ay llan, ad feôqen amur wis krav, war ccqa, kkes ed ayen ippuseôfen ne îlabat. D aweûûi n Öebbi. Öebbi Iéôa, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 79,
            "ruku": 63,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 506,
            "text": "D tigi ay d tilisa n Öebbi. Win issemêessen i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, a t Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
