            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 507,
            "text": "Win iâuûan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, izegren tilas iS, a t Issekcem ar tmes, degs ad iwekkeô, ad isâaddi aâaqeb isdullun.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 79,
            "ruku": 63,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 508,
            "text": "I tid ixedmen lâaô di tlawin nnwen, awit ed, fellasent, kué inagan nnwen. Ma cehhden d, kemnet pent di texxamin, alamma teddem itent tmeppant, ne Iga yasent Öebbi abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 80,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 509,
            "text": "Wid segwen it ixedmen, âaqbet pen. Ma nedmen, u xedmen ayen ilhan, anfet asen. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Issuruf, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 80,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 510,
            "text": "Issuruf kan Öebbi i wid ixedmen cceôô ur éôin, sinna, steôoâen, war laâvil. Widak, ad asen Issuref Öebbi. Öebbi Izga d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 80,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 511,
            "text": "Ur illi usuref i wid ixedmen tucmitin. Alamma, mi d tusa yiwen tmeppant, a d yini: 'nek steôoâe tura'. Akken, wid immuten u nitni d ijehliyen. Widak, Nhegga yasen d aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 80,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 512,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur awen iêell ara a pweôten tilawin, ur qbilent, ne ad asent tekksem jjwao, iwakken a ppawim amur seg wayen i sent tefkam, siwa ma xedment lâaô ibanen. Illit yidsent, s lqanun. Ma tkeôhem tent, ahat tkeôhem ayen ideg Irra Öebbi lxiô meqqwôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 80,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 513,
            "text": "Ma tebam a pbedlem tameîîut s tayev, u tefkam tuççit i yiwet, ur as tekkset acemma. Ma tekksem, d ayen n dir u d abekkav n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 81,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 514,
            "text": "Amek ara tekksem imi temyekcamem, u bbwint suôwen laâqed meqqwôen?",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 81,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 515,
            "text": "Ur ppaet tilawin i uen ibabaten nnwen, kkes ed ayen iâaddan. Ayagi, s tidep, d lâaô, d dduni, d yir brid.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 81,
            "ruku": 64,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 516,
            "text": "Pwadeglent awen tyimmatin nnwen, issit nnwen, tissetmatin nnwen, tiâamtiwin nnwen, tixaltitin nnwen, issit n ugmat, issit n tweltmap, tiyimmatin nnwen i kwen issuîîven, tissetmatin nnwen ukud teîîvem, tivegwalin nnwen, issit id tessekrem n tlawin nnwen ukud tcerkem usu - ma ur tecrikem ara usu, ulac uilif -, tilawin n warraw id turwem. Ur zdukulet snat tsetmatin, kkes ed ayen iâaddan, - Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu -,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 4,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 81,
            "ruku": 65,
            "hizbQuarter": 32,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 517,
            "text": "tilawin ijewoen, kkes ed taklatin nnwen. D Öebbi i wen Iuran. Iêell awen, deffir waya, a ppezhum s wayla nnwen, s lewqama, maççi s lemveôôa. Tid, segsent, ukud tezham, fket asent arrazen nnsent, d aêeppem. Ur illi uilif fellawen deg wayen ief temwafaqem, deffir uêeppem. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 82,
            "ruku": 65,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 518,
            "text": "Wid, segwen, ur nezmir ara ad aen tiêuôiyn iumnen, ad aen si teklatin nnwen, tid iumnen. Öebbi Yif akw akken Iéôa liman nnwen. Wa seg wa. Aet pent, s tsriê n twacult nnsent, fket asent arrazen nnsent, s lqanun. D tizedganin, maççi d tucmitin, ne d tid iffen abrid. ÛMa ualent d tiêuôiyn, sinna xedment lâaô, aâaqeb nnsent azgen n win n tiêuôiyn. Akka i win, segwen, ippagwaden abekkav. Ma tûebôem, ppif i kunwi. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 82,
            "ruku": 65,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 519,
            "text": "Iba Öebbi ad awen Ibeggen, a kwen Iawi d wansayen n wid i kwen id izwaren, a d Iual uôwen. Öebbi d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 82,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 520,
            "text": "Iba Öebbi ad awen Issuref. Ban wid iteddun d lemcihwat, a pmalem lmil abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 83,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 521,
            "text": "Iba Öebbi ad Issifes fellawen. Ipwaxleq umdan d uôhif.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 83,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 522,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur ppemyeççat ayla garawen, d aêerfi, kkes ed ma d ssuq ief temwafaqem. Ur neqqet iman nnwen. Ih, Öebbi Izga Ipêunu fellawen.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 83,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 523,
            "text": "Win ixedmen akka, s zzkaôa akked ddens, deqqal a t Nger ar tmes. Ayagi, izga d ayen isehlen i Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 83,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 524,
            "text": "Ma tjunbem ayen meqqwôen, seg wayen i wen ipwakksen, a Nessuref i tucmitin nnwen, a kwen Nessekcem anekcum ukyis.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 83,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 525,
            "text": "Ur ppasmet, ma Ismenyaf Öebbi kra i wiyav. I yirgazen, amur seg wayen kesben; i tlawin, amur seg wayen kesbent. Ssutret i Öebbi, si lfevl iS. Ih, Öebbi Izga Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 83,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 526,
            "text": "Nerra, i yal wa, iweôôaten n wayen d ooan imawlan, llzem, akked wid ukud tâaqqdem. Efket asen amur nnsen. Öebbi Izga Ipwali yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 83,
            "ruku": 66,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 527,
            "text": "Irgazen ad ûunen tilawin, imi Ismenyafa Öebbi kra ef kra, ilmend n wayen pseôôifen seg wayla nnsen. Tilawin imaânen, iunzen, ipêaraben ef sser n wayen Iêureb Öebbi. Tid suô tugadem tuêsift, nnaet pent, âazlet pent deg imîeôêen, ôebbit pent. Ma uent awen awal, ur tent ppawvet. Ih, Öebbi Izga Âalay, Meqqweô.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 84,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 528,
            "text": "Ma tugadem ad mfaôaqen, aznet amêaddi n twacult n neppa, wayev n twacult n neppat. Ma ban ad mûalaêen, a ten Issemâaceô Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Âalay, Iéôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 84,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 33,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 529,
            "text": "Âabdet Öebbi, ur aS pcaraket acemma. Elhut ar lwaldin, ar llzem, ar igujilen, ar imeban, ar loaô i wen ippilin akked win ur awen neppili, ar umeddakwel ar yidis, ar iminig, ar waklan nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara amzuxi, imnefxi,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 84,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 530,
            "text": "wid ipcuêêun u ppamôen i medden ccêa, iteffren ayen i sen Ifka Öebbi, si lfevl iS - Nhegga d, i ijehliyen, aâaqeb isdullun -;",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 84,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 531,
            "text": "wid ipûeôôifen ayla nnsen, iwakken a ten id walin medden, ur uminen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru; wid isâan Cciîan d amsaâaf. A yir amsaâaf!",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 85,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 532,
            "text": "Acu ar asen iôuêen, lemmer uminen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, u ûeôôfen seg wayen is iten Iôéeq Öebbi? Öebbi Izga Issen iten.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 85,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 533,
            "text": "Öebbi, s tidep, ur Idennes s wayen iwzen ubelkim. Ma tebbwiv d ise, a t Irr d sin, a d Ifk, suôeS, arraz ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 85,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 534,
            "text": "Amek, ihi, ma Nusa, si yal lois, s unagi; ma Nusa, yissek, d anagi ef wigi?",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 85,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 535,
            "text": "Assen, wid ijehlen u âuûan Nnbi, ad ssirmen a ten tesseblaâ tmurt. Ur teffren awal i Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 85,
            "ruku": 67,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 536,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pqeôôibet ar téallit ma tsekôem, alamma teéôam acu d teqqaôem. Ne ma tellam s loanaba - siwa ma la teppinigem -, alamma tessardem. Ma tuvnem ne tunagem, ne iusa d yiwen segwen si ccicma, ne tennulem tilawin, ur tufim aman, ddmet akal zeddigen, sâaddit ep ef udmawen nnwen d ifassen nnwen. Ih, Öebbi Izga Ipqili, Ipsemmiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 85,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 537,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid iwumi ippunefk kra si Tezmamt? Ppaen d ttelfan, ban a ppennetlafem seg ubrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 85,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 538,
            "text": "Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen icenga nnwen. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Bab. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Amâiwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 86,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 539,
            "text": "Seg udayen, wid iîîeôôifen awalen seg inumak nnsen. Qqaôen: 'nesla, naâûa, ssemêes i wayen ur d nnin, muqel a d'. Ssaâwjen ilsawen nnsen, kkaten di ddin. Lemmer, s tidep, qqaôen: 'nesla, nunez, ssel, muqel a d', war ccekk, yif it i nitni, u iwqem kteô. Maca, Ixza ten Öebbi, ilmend n tijehli nnsen. Ur ppamnen, siwa ixeîîayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 86,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 540,
            "text": "A wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt! Amnet s wayen id Nessers, d atebbet n wayen illan uôwen, uqbel a Nesab udmawen, a ten Nerr ar deffir, ne a ten Nexzu, akken Nexza at Ssebt. Lameô n Öebbi ad iâaddi.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 86,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 541,
            "text": "Öebbi, s tidep, ur Ipsemmiê mara S carken. Ipsemmiê ayen nniven, i win i S ihwan. Win icurken i Öebbi, ni ibbwi abekkav abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 86,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 542,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid iran iman nnsen zeddigit? Maca, Öebbi Izzizdig win i S ihwan. Ur pwadensen ula s uclem utemôiw.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 86,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 543,
            "text": "Wali amek id gren tikerkas ef Öebbi. Ayagi kan, d abekkav n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 86,
            "ruku": 68,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 544,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid iwumi ippunefk kra si Tezmamt? Umnen s iôebbiten n tkerkas, u qqaôen, i wid ijehlen, ar widak pwanhan sennig wid iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 86,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 545,
            "text": "Widak d wid Ixza Öebbi. Wid ara Ixzu Öebbi, ur asen teppafev amâiwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 546,
            "text": "Ne sâan kra si tgelda, da ur ppaken i medden ula d atemôiw.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 547,
            "text": "Ne êesden medden, deg wayen i sen Ifka Öebbi, si lfevl iS. Ni Nefka, i twacult n Ibôahim, Tazmamt, ûûwab. Nefka yasen tagelda tameqwôaêant.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 548,
            "text": "Segsen wid iumnen yis, segsen wid i p iugin. Beôka ten ajajiê n Loahennama.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 549,
            "text": "Ih, wid inekôen issekniyen nne£, deqqal a ten Nerr ar tmes. Mi ôan igwelman nnsen, ad asen d Nenûef s igwelman nniven, ad jeôôben aâaqeb. Ih, Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 550,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Nessekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, din ad wekkôen, i lebda. I nitni, degsen, tilawin zeddigen; a ten Nawi ar tili isburrun.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 34,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 551,
            "text": "S tidep, Iumeô awen Öebbi a pperrem lamanat i imawlan nnsent, a pêuddem s lmizan, ma têuddem ger medden. Ih, ilha wayen uuô i kwen Ipnabi Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Issel, Ipwali.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 552,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Aet awal i Öebbi. Aet awal i Umazan akked imawlan n lameô segwen. Ma temgarradem ef lêaoa, erret ep ar Öebbi akked Umazan, ma tumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Ppif akka, d ppawil amxallef.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 87,
            "ruku": 69,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 553,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid iumnen, ziemma, s wayen ik ed irsen, d wayen id irsen, uqbel ik? Ban aêuddu iôebbiten n tkerkas, ulamma pwamôen a ten nekôen. Iba Cciîan a ten itlef ttelfan umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 88,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 554,
            "text": "Ma nnan asen: 'aset ed ar wayen id Issers Öebbi, akw ar Umazan', a pwaliv ixabiten wexxôen ak, ugin.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 88,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 555,
            "text": "Amek ihi, ma uen tiyta, ilmend n wayen xedmen ifassen nnsen, sinna, a d asen uôek, ad ggalen s Öebbi: 'neba kan lewqama akked lembwafqa'.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 88,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 556,
            "text": "Widak, Iéôa Öebbi i illan deg ulawen nnsen. Ihi, îîixeô asen, nabi iten, meslay iten, ef iman nnsen, s wawal iqenâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 88,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 557,
            "text": "Ur d Nuzen Amazan, siwa kan iwakken ad as aen awal, ma Irad Öebbi. Wid idensen iman nnsen, ma usan k id, da ssutren ssmaê i Öebbi, u issuter Umazan ad ppusemmêen, ad afen Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 88,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 558,
            "text": "Xaîi! S Mass ik, ur ppamnen, alamma rran k d amêaddi, deg wayen ief mgarraden. Sinna, ur ppafen, deg iman nnsen, ara ten ihewwlen, deg wayen id têuddev. Ad anzen yal annuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 88,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 559,
            "text": "Lemmer i sen Nuri: 'mminet'! Ne 'ffet seg ixxamen nnwen'! Ur p xeddmen, siwa kra segsen. Ppif, i nitni, lemmer xdimen ayen uuô pwanecden. D atebbet uûwib.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 560,
            "text": "Imiren ad asen Nefk, suône£, arraz ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 561,
            "text": "A ten Nenhu s abrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 562,
            "text": "Wid ippaen awal i Öebbi akked Umazan, widak atnan ar wid Iat Öebbi ger lambiyya, wid issdaqen, ccuhada, ûûalêin. Ay telha tdukli d wigi!",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 563,
            "text": "Wagi d lfevl suô Öebbi. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 70,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 564,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëadret iman nnwen! èéedmet d igrawen, ne ééedmet akw.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 71,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 565,
            "text": "Ih, garawen win ipâaîîilen. Ma tuem tiyta, ad yini: 'Iat iyi Öebbi, ur lli yidsen, d anagi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 71,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 566,
            "text": "Ma iusa kwen id lfevl suô Öebbi, ad yini, war ccekk, amzun ur telli tegmap garawen: 'a lemmer lli yidsen, ad rebêe rrbeê ameqwôaêan'!",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 71,
            "hizbQuarter": 35,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 567,
            "text": "Ad nnaen deg ubrid n Öebbi wid izznuzun tameddurt n ddunit i laxert. Win ipnaen deg ubrid n Öebbi, immut ne irbeê, ad as Nefk arraz ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 89,
            "ruku": 71,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 568,
            "text": "Acu kwen iuen, ula tepnaem ara deg ubrid n Öebbi? Uôhifen seg irgazen, tilawin, igwerdan, i la iqqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Ssuffe ane si temdint agi izeden imednas. Efk ane d bab suôeK, Efk ane d asettaô suôeK'.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 90,
            "ruku": 71,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 569,
            "text": "Wid iumnen pnaen deg ubrid n Öebbi. Wid ijehlen pnaen deg ubrid iôebbiten n tkerkas. Nnaet imeddukwal n Cciîan. Ni tiêeôci n Cciîan d tuôhift.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 90,
            "ruku": 71,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 570,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid iwumi nnan: 'brut i ifassen, ééalet, zekkit'? Mi sen iura umennu, arbaâ, segsen, ugaden imdanen, tugwdi n Öebbi, ne tugwdi i p ielben. Qqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Acimi i  Turiv amennu? A lemmer i t Teswexxôev cwiî'! Ini: 'zzhu n ddunit d amnuc, tif it laxert i win ipêezziben. Ur tepwadensem ula s yiclem utemôiw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 90,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 571,
            "text": "Anda tellam a kwen id tawev tmeppant, xas ma tellam di lebôuo ioehden. Ma iusa ten id yise, ad inin: 'wagi suô Öebbi'. Ma tusa ten id tucmip, ad inin: 'tagi suôek'. Ini: 'akw suô Öebbi'. Acu iuen agdud agi, ur izmir ad ifhem awalen?",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 90,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 572,
            "text": "Yal ise i k id iusan, suô Öebbi. Yal tucmip i k id iusan, suô iman ik. Nuzen ik id i medden, d Amazan. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Anagi.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 90,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 573,
            "text": "Win iuen awal i Umazan, iu awal i Öebbi. Win iwexxôen, ur k id Nuzen d amêareb nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 91,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 574,
            "text": "Qqaôen: 'annuz'! Mi k îîaxxôen, ad iêekku deg iv, urbaâ segsen, ayen ur d tenniv. Öebbi Ipparu ayen êekkun deg iv. Wexxeô asen, ppkel ef Öebbi. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Awkil.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 91,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 575,
            "text": "Day ur pmeyyizen ara Leqwôan? Lemmer illi si war Öebbi, ad afen degs aîas n wayen imgarraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 91,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 576,
            "text": "Ma iusa ten lameô n laman ne n lxuf, a t berrêen. Lemmer i t ssawven i Umazan akked imawlan n lameô nnsen, ad xebôen wid, segsen, iban ad éôen. Lemmer maççi d lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S fellawen, a ppeddum d Cciîan, siwa kra kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 91,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 577,
            "text": "Nna deg ubrid n Öebbi. D iman ik kan ara tkellfev. Efk afud i lmumnin. Izmer Öebbi ad Issers tazmert n wid ijehlen. Öebbi Yif iten tazmert, Yif iten aâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 91,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 578,
            "text": "Win icefâan ccafuâa ilhan, ad iawi, segs, amur. Win icefâan ccafuâa icemten, ad iawi, segs, sin imuren. Öebbi Izga Issenqad yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 91,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 579,
            "text": "Ma nnan awen d: 'azul'! Erret asen azul it yifen, ne erret asen t. Ih, Öebbi Izga Iêeppeb yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 91,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 580,
            "text": "Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, a kwen Issemlil, ass n tnekra, ur degs ccekk. Anwa i iqqaôen tidep sennig Öebbi?",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 92,
            "ruku": 72,
            "hizbQuarter": 36,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 581,
            "text": "Acu i kwen iuen: tebvam ef sin, ef ixabiten? Izzaâ ten Öebbi ilmend n wayen kesben. Day tebam a ppenhum win Itlef Öebbi? Win Itlef Öebbi, ur as teppafev abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 92,
            "ruku": 73,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 582,
            "text": "Ban a ppilim d ijehliyen am nitni, a ppemcabim. Ur sâut iêbiben segsen, alamma unagen deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ma wexxôen, îîfet pen, nnaet pen anda ten tufam, ur sâut segsen aêbib ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 92,
            "ruku": 73,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 583,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid iusan ar ugdud ukud tesâam laâqed, ne i kwen id iusan, gguman wulawen nnsen a kwen nnaen, ne ad nnaen agdud nnsen. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili Ifka yasen adabu fellawen, a kwen nnaen. Ma âazlen iman nnsen segwen, ur kwen nnuen, ssutren awen d tifrat, ur kwen Ippawi Öebbi uôsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 92,
            "ruku": 73,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 584,
            "text": "A ppafem wiyav i iban tifrat yidwen, akked tifrat akked ugdud nnsen. Yal tikelt ideg ara ten rren ar lfetna, ad kecmen degs. Ma ur aâzilen ara iman nnsen segwen, ur awen ssutren ara tifrat, ur fukken ara amennu, îîfet pen, nnaet pen anda ten tufam. Widak, Nefka yawen fellasen adabu n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 92,
            "ruku": 73,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 585,
            "text": "Ur ippunefk ara i lmumen ad ine lmumen, siwa ma ilev. Win inan lmumen di lewlav, ad iserreê i wakli iumnen, a ppeppunefk ddeyya i twacult is, siwa ma seddqen p. Ma illa seg ugdud acengu nnwen, u neppa d lmumen, ad iserreê i wakli iumnen. Ma illa seg ugdud ukud tesâam laâqed, a ppeppunefk ddeyya i twacult is, ad iserreê i wakli iumnen. Win ur nezmir ara, ad iuéum sin wagguren, wa deffir wa, d nndama i Öebbi. Öebbi Izga Iééeô, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 93,
            "ruku": 74,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 586,
            "text": "Win inan lmumen s lemâamda, aqeîîi ines d Loahennama, degs ad iwekkeô. A d Izâaf Öebbi fellas, a t Ixzu, ad as d Iheggi aâaqeb abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 93,
            "ruku": 74,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 587,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma tennuem deg ubrid n Öebbi, beggnet iman nnwen. Ur qqaôet i win i wen d ssutren tifrat: 'ur telliv d lmumen'! Tebam cci n tmeddurt n ddunit. £uô Öebbi, aîas uiti. Akka ay tellam zik. Öebbi Ifeôôeo fellawen. Beggnet iman nnwen. Ih, Öebbi Izga Issen ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 93,
            "ruku": 74,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 588,
            "text": "Ur aâdilen ara wid iqqimen si lmumnin, siwa wid ivôuôan, akked wid ijuhden deg ubrid n Öebbi, s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Ismenyaf Öebbi wid ijuhden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen, i wid iqqimen. Akw, Iwaââed asen Öebbi ûûam. Ifrez Öebbi imjuhad af wid iqqimen, s warraz ameqwôaêan,",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 94,
            "ruku": 74,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 589,
            "text": "aseqôeb uôeS, ssmaê, akked uêunu. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 94,
            "ruku": 74,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 590,
            "text": "Ih, i wid iwumi ddment lmalayek leôwaê, u densen iman nnsen, ad inint: 'anida tellam'? A d inin: 'nella d uôhifen di tmurt'. Ad inint: 'day ur tewsiâ ara tmurt n Öebbi, a ppinigem degs'? Widak, axxam nnsen d Loahennama. A tualin tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 94,
            "ruku": 75,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 591,
            "text": "Kkes ed uôhifen, argaz, tameîîut, agrud, ur nezmir i tsensert, ur nepwanhu s abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 94,
            "ruku": 75,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 592,
            "text": "Widak, amar Öebbi ad asen Isemmeê. Öebbi Izga Ipqili, Ipsemmiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 94,
            "ruku": 75,
            "hizbQuarter": 37,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 593,
            "text": "Win iunagen deg ubrid n Öebbi, ad iaf, di tmurt, aîas n ssôanat akked lufa. Win iffen seg uxxam is, d iminig ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, sinna, temmuger it tmeppant, arraz is atan ar Öebbi. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 94,
            "ruku": 75,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 594,
            "text": "Mi teppeddum di tmurt, ulac uilif ma teééeméim taéallit, ma tugadem a d ééedmen fellawen wid ijehlen. Ih, ijehliyen banen d icenga nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 94,
            "ruku": 76,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 595,
            "text": "Ma telliv garasen, tezwaôev asen i téallit, ilaq a ppili terbaât, segsen, yidek, s ibeddi, ad îîfen leslaê nnsen. Mi knan, ad ilin deffir wen. A d tas terbaât nniven ur neééul, ad ééalen yidek, ad êadren iman nnsen, akked leslaê nnsen. Ssarmen wid ijehlen, a peflem ef leslaê nnwen akked lqecc nnwen, iwakken a d ééedmen fellawen, yiwet n ééedma. Ulac uilif ma tessersem leslaê nnwen, ma ihero ikwen ugeffur ne tuvnem. Ëëadret iman nnwen. Ih, Öebbi Ihegga, i ijehliyen, aâaqeb isdullun.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 95,
            "ruku": 76,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 596,
            "text": "Mi tfukkem taéallit, mmektit ed Öebbi s ibeddi, s iimi, s tuééla. Mi teppuvemnem, ééalet. Taéallit, ih, tura i lmumen, s lewqat is.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 95,
            "ruku": 76,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 597,
            "text": "Ur fecclet deg uvfaô n ugdud. Ma tmeênem, ula d nitni meênen am kunwi. Tessaramem, ar Öebbi, ayen ur ssaramen. Öebbi Izga Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 95,
            "ruku": 76,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 598,
            "text": "Ih, Nessers ak d Tazmamt, s tidep, iwakken a pêuddev ger imdanen, s wayen i k id Issenâat Öebbi. Ur ppili d axûim n lxeyyan.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 95,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 599,
            "text": "Ssuter ssmaê i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 600,
            "text": "Ur pnnavaê ef wid ixeynen iman nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara win ixeynen, idenben.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 601,
            "text": "Ban ad ffren i medden, ur zmiren ad ffren i Öebbi. Neppa Illa yidsen mara d qqaôen, deg iv, awalen ief ur Iôuva. Öebbi Izga Izzi i wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 602,
            "text": "Atan kunwi tnuvêem fellasen, di tmeddurt n ddunit. Anwa ara innavêen Öebbi fellasen, ass n tnekra? Ne anwa ar yilin fellasen d awkil?",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 603,
            "text": "Win ixedmen cceôô, ne idnes iman is, sinna, issuter ssmaê i Öebbi, ad iaf Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 604,
            "text": "Win ibbwin abekkav, ibbwi it, kan, i iman is. Öebbi Izga Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 605,
            "text": "Win ifalîan ne ibbwin abekkav, irra p id ef wur nexdim, ibbwi lâaô, akked ubekkav n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 77,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 606,
            "text": "Lemmer maççi d lfevl n Öebbi fellak, akked uêunu S, iaâzem urbaâ, segsen, a k telfen. Ur tellifan siwa iman nnsen. Ur k îîuôôun s wacemma. Issers ak d Öebbi Tazmamt akked ûûwab. Isselmed ak ayen ur tessinev. Izga lfevl n Öebbi, fellak, d ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 96,
            "ruku": 78,
            "hizbQuarter": 38,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 607,
            "text": "Aîas n wayen qqaôen ur imâin, siwa ayen iumôen ssadaqa, ne lqanun, ne lemûalêa ger medden. Win ixedmen aya, issarem ad Iôavi Öebbi, deqqal ad as Nefk arraz ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 78,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 608,
            "text": "Win ixuûmen Amazan, mbaâd ma tepwabeggen as d nnhaya, iteddun d ubrid ur d wid n lmumnin, a t Neoo akken iooa. A t Nenheô ar Loahennama. A tualin tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 78,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 609,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi ur Ipsemmiê ma ad aS carken. Ipsemmiê ayen nniven, i win i S ihwan. Win icurken i Öebbi, innetlef ttelfan umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 610,
            "text": "La pnujun ar nnta, war Neppa. La pnujun kan ar Cciîan aballa.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 611,
            "text": "Ixza t Öebbi. Inna: 'ad awi amur ippuêeppmen, seg imdanen ik.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 612,
            "text": "A ten telfe, a ten ssenêesse, ad asen amôe ad gezmen imeééuen ubeqôi, ad asen amôe ad bedlen lxelq n Öebbi'. Win idmen Cciîan d bab, war Öebbi, ixseô lexsaôa n tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 613,
            "text": "Ipâahad asen, issenêas iten. Ayen i sen iâahed Cciîan, d auôôu kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 614,
            "text": "Widak, axxam nnsen d Loahennama, ur ppafen, segs, tisensert.",
            "numberInSurah": 121,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 97,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 615,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Nessekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen, i lebda. Lemâahda n Öebbi a ppevôu. Anwa issawalen tidep sennig Öebbi?",
            "numberInSurah": 122,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 98,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 616,
            "text": "Ur illi s usirem nnwen, ne s win n At Tezmamt. Win ixedmen cceôô, ad ippuqeîîi fellas. Ur Ippaf, war Öebbi, bab ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 123,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 98,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 617,
            "text": "Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne d nnta, u neppa iumen…, widak ad kecmen Loennet, ur pwadensen s yiclem utemôiw.",
            "numberInSurah": 124,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 98,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 618,
            "text": "Anwa iûegmen ddin is sennig win iunzen i Öebbi, u neppa d laâûem, u idda d ddin n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep? Öebbi Irra Ibôahim d aêbib.",
            "numberInSurah": 125,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 98,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 619,
            "text": "N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Izga Izzi i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 126,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 98,
            "ruku": 79,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 620,
            "text": "Steqsayen k ef tlawin. Ini: 'Öebbi ad awen Issefhem fellasent. Ayen i wen ôan di Tezmamt, ef tlawin tigujilin, iwumi ur tefkim ara i sent iuran, u tebam a tent taem. Akked igwerdan imeéyanen. A pbeddem i igujilen s lmizan. Ayen akw txeddmem n lxiô, Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Iéôa t.",
            "numberInSurah": 127,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 98,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 621,
            "text": "Ma tugad tmeîîut ad as ibru, ne ad as iwexxeô urgaz is, ulac uilif fellasen ma ufan lemwafaqa garasen. Ppif lemwafaqa. Imdanen, deg iman nnsen d imceôôiyen. Ma tgerzem u têezzbem, Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Iéôa ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 128,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 99,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 622,
            "text": "Ur tezmirem a ppeddum s lmizan, ger tlawin, xas tebam. Ihi, ur pmalet yal tumlin a p teooem, amzun d tamejgugelt. Ma tgam ayen ilhan, u têezzbem, s tidep, Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 129,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 99,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 623,
            "text": "Ma mfaôaqen, ad Iit Öebbi yal wa, s ôôeéq iS. Öebbi Izga d Ajemmal, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 130,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 99,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 624,
            "text": "N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ni Nweûûa wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, u Nweûûa kwen, a pêezzbem i Öebbi. Ma tnekôem, ihi, n Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Izga d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 131,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 99,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 625,
            "text": "N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Awkil.",
            "numberInSurah": 132,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 99,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 626,
            "text": "Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Ikkes a yimdanen! A d Iawi wiyav. Öebbi Izga Izmer i waya.",
            "numberInSurah": 133,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 99,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 627,
            "text": "Win iban aellet n ddunit, ihi, ar Öebbi aellet n ddunit akked win n laxeôt. Öebbi Izga Issel, Ipwali.",
            "numberInSurah": 134,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 99,
            "ruku": 80,
            "hizbQuarter": 39,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 628,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Teddut s lmizan, d inagan n Öebbi, xas ef yiman nnwen, ne imawlan u llzem, ama d ameôkanti, ama d igellil. Izwar iten Öebbi. Ur teddut d lhawiyya, ur twezznem ara. Ma txutlem, ne twexxôem, ihi, Öebbi Izga Iéôa ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 135,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 100,
            "ruku": 81,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 629,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked Tezmamt id Issers i Umazan iS, akked Tezmamt id Issers, uqbel. Win inekôen Öebbi, lmalayek iS, Tizmamin iS, imazanen iS, akked wass aneggaru, ihi innetlaf ttelfan umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 136,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 100,
            "ruku": 81,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 630,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen, sinna, nekôen, sinna, umnen, sinna, nekôen, sinna, zaden di nnkeô, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, ur ten Ippawi d ubrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 137,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 100,
            "ruku": 81,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 631,
            "text": "Becceô ixabiten ar fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 138,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 100,
            "ruku": 81,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 632,
            "text": "Wid ipparan ijehliyen d iêbiben, war lmumnin, day ssarmen uôsen tazmert? Tazmert, s tidep, ar Öebbi yakw.",
            "numberInSurah": 139,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 100,
            "ruku": 81,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 633,
            "text": "Ni Nessers awen d, di Tezmamt: 'ma teslam la nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, la ttihin fellasen, ur pimit yidsen, alamma bedlen ameslay. Mulac a ppilim am nitni'. Öebbi, s tidep, a d Issemlil ixabiten akked ijehliyen di Loahennama, meôôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 140,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 100,
            "ruku": 81,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 634,
            "text": "Wid i kwen iquôâan, ma Ifka yawen d Öebbi lelb, a d inin: 'day ur nella ara yidwen'? Ma illa wayen rebêen ijehliyen, ad inin: 'day ur nêuôeb ara fellawen, nsellek ikwen si lmumnin'? Ad Iêudd Öebbi garawen, ass n tnekra. Ur Ippara ara Öebbi, i ijehliyen, abrid ar lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 141,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 101,
            "ruku": 81,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 635,
            "text": "Ih, ixabiten xedâen Öebbi. D Neppa iten Ixedâan. Ma kren d i téallit, a d kren d imaâguza, akken kan a ten id walin medden. Cwiî kan id smektayen Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 142,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 101,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 636,
            "text": "Ur banen akka, ne akka; eô wigi, ne eô wiyav. Win Itlef Öebbi ur as teppafev abrid, d awezi.",
            "numberInSurah": 143,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 101,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 637,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pparat ijehliyen d iêbiben, war lmumnin. Day tebam ad aS tefkem, i Öebbi, adabu ibanen, mgal kwen?",
            "numberInSurah": 144,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 101,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 638,
            "text": "Ih, ixabiten di lqaâa n wadda n tmes, ur asen teppafev asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 145,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 101,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 639,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid ituben, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, iîîfen di Öebbi, izzazdgen ddin nnsen ar Öebbi. Widak, ad ilin ar lmumnin. Deqqal a d Iawi Öebbi, i lmumnin, arraz ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 146,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 101,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 640,
            "text": "Acu ara Ixdem Öebbi s uâaqeb nnwen, ma tesnemmrem, tumnem? Ni Öebbi Ippara tajmilt, Iéôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 147,
            "juz": 5,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 101,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 40,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 641,
            "text": "Ur Iêemmel ara Öebbi nnaâlat, siwa seg win ipwadensen. Öebbi Izga Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 148,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 102,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 642,
            "text": "Ma txedmem lxiô âinani, ne teffrem t, ne tsemmêem abekkavu, Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, d Aêernuk.",
            "numberInSurah": 149,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 102,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 643,
            "text": "Ih, wid inekôen Öebbi akked imazanen iS, u ban ad ssemfaôqen Öebbi akked imazanen iS, qqaôen: 'numen s kra, nenkeô kra'. Ban ad awin abrid garasen.",
            "numberInSurah": 150,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 102,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 644,
            "text": "Widak, d ijehliyen n ûûeê. Nhegga, i ijehliyen, aâaqeb isdullun",
            "numberInSurah": 151,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 102,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 645,
            "text": "Wid iumnen s Öebbi akked imazanen iS, ur ten ssemgarraden, widak, deqqal a ten id ias warraz nnsen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 152,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 102,
            "ruku": 82,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 646,
            "text": "La k d ssuturen, At Tezmamt, ad asen d tessersev Tazmamt seg igenni. Ni ssutren, i Musa, sennig waya. Nnan as: 'ssenâat a d Öebbi, a T nwali'. Tebbwi ten ssiâqa, ilmend n ddens nnsen. Sinna, âabden aâjmi, mbaâd ma iusa ten id ubeggen. Nesemmeê asen aya. Nefka, i Musa, adabu n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 153,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 102,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 647,
            "text": "Nessuli adrar sennig sen, ilmend n laâqed nnsen. Nenna yasen: 'kecmet si tebburt s lekni'. Nenna yasen: 'ur txalafet ssebt'. Neîîef segsen laâqed iûeêêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 154,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 102,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 648,
            "text": "Imi neqven laâqed nnsen, u nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, u nan lambiyya, war ssebba, u nnan: 'ulawen nne duben'. Xaîi, d Öebbi iten Iselen, ilmend n tjehli nnsen. Drus kan i iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 155,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 649,
            "text": "Ilmend n nnekô nnsen, u gren d, ef Meryem, acehrir abarar;",
            "numberInSurah": 156,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 650,
            "text": "u nnan: 'nekwni nena Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Amazan n Öebbi'. Ur t nin, ur t semmôen ef umidag. D lexyal kan ger wallen nnsen. Ih, wid imgarraden fellas, atnan di ccekk fellas, ur éôin fellas acemma, teddun kan d nnwaya. Metbut, ur t nnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 157,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 651,
            "text": "Xaîi! Issuli t Öebbi uôeS. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 158,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 652,
            "text": "Ur illi yiwen, seg wAt Tezmamt, ur numin yis, uqbel tameppant is. Ass n tnekra ad yili d anagi nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 159,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 653,
            "text": "Ilmend n ddens n wudayen, Negdel asen tiéidanin i illan êellent asen, imi daen, îîeôôifen aîas seg ubrid n Öebbi;",
            "numberInSurah": 160,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 654,
            "text": "u ssexdamen rrba, i illan tepwakkes asen, u teppen ayla n medden, d aêerfi. Nhegga d, i ijehliyen segsen, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 161,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 655,
            "text": "Maca, wid, segsen, izaden di tmusni, lmumnin iumnen s wayen ik ed irsen, akked wayen id irsen, uqbel ik, wid ibedden i téallit, wid ipzekkin, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, widak, ad asen Nefk arraz ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 162,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 103,
            "ruku": 83,
            "hizbQuarter": 41,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 656,
            "text": "Ih, Nweêêa yak ed, akken Nweêêa i Nuê, akked lambiyya deffir es. Nweêêa i Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq, Iaâqub, laâôac, Âisa, Yub, Yunes, Harun, Sliman. Nefka Ihellilen i Dawed.",
            "numberInSurah": 163,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 657,
            "text": "Akked lambiyya ief ik ed Neêka, uqbel; akked lambiyya, ief ur ak ed Neêki. S tidep, Immeslay Öebbi i Musa.",
            "numberInSurah": 164,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 658,
            "text": "Lambiyya ipbecciôen, inedôen, iwakken ur pnamaren medden ef Öebbi, deffir imazanen. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 165,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 659,
            "text": "Maca, Icuhhed Öebbi ef wayen ik ed Issers, s tmusni S. Ad cehhdent lmalayek. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Anagi.",
            "numberInSurah": 166,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 660,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen, u îîeôôifen seg ubrid n Öebbi, ni nnetlafen ttelfan umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 167,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 661,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen u densen, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, ur ten Ippawi d ubrid,",
            "numberInSurah": 168,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 662,
            "text": "siwa abrid n Loahennama, degs ad wekkôen, i lebda. Ayagi, Izga d ayen isehlen i Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 169,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 663,
            "text": "A yimdanen! Ni iusa kwen id Umazan, s tidep, suô Mass nnwen. Amnet, ppif i kunwi. Ma tugim, ihi n Öebbi, i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izga Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 170,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 104,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 664,
            "text": "A yAt Tezmamt! Ur sfuhruyet ddin nnwen. Ur qqaret, ef Öebbi, siwa tidep. Lmasiê Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, d amazan kan n Öebbi; d awal iS i Irra ar Meryem, u d ôôuê s uôeS. Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked imazanen iS, ur qqaôet: 'krav'! Ëebset, ppif i kunwi. Öebbi d Yiwen kan n Öebbi. Gedha s yiS, ma ad Isâu mmi S! IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Awkil.",
            "numberInSurah": 171,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 105,
            "ruku": 84,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 665,
            "text": "Ur ismummi ara lmasiê, ma illa d amdan n Öebbi. Akken lmalayek tuqôibin. Wid ismummin a T âabden, u zuxxen, ad pwafessren akw uôeS.",
            "numberInSurah": 172,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 105,
            "ruku": 85,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 666,
            "text": "Wanag wid iumnen, u xedmen ayen ilhan, ad asen Ifk arraz nnsen, ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. Ma d wid ismummin u zuxxen, a ten Iâaqeb aâaqeb aqeôêan. Ur ppafen, war Öebbi, bab ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 173,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 105,
            "ruku": 85,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 667,
            "text": "A yimdanen! Ni iusa kwen id utebbet suô Mass nnwen, u Nessers awen ed tafat ibanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 174,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 105,
            "ruku": 85,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 668,
            "text": "Wanag wid iumnen s Öebbi, i iîîfen degS, a ten Issekcem ar uêunu S akked lfevl. A ten Inhu uôeS, deg ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 175,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 105,
            "ruku": 85,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 669,
            "text": "Cawôen k. Ini: 'Öebbi Isfehm awen d ef llzem. Ma immut urgaz, war tarwa, isâa taultmap, i neppat azgen n wayen id iooa. Neppa a p iwôet, ma ur tesâi tarwa. Ma snat ay llant, amur wis krav i yal ta, n wayen id iooa. Ma llan watmaten akked tessetmatin, i uqcic amur n snat n tullas'. Ibeggen awen d Öebbi akken ur tepnnetlafem. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 176,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 1,
            "page": 106,
            "ruku": 85,
            "hizbQuarter": 42,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 5,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المَائـِدَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Maaida",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Table",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 670,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Eîîfet deg iâahden nnwen. Ëellen awen lmal n tejlibt, kkes ed wid i wen nnan. Ur awen têell ara ûûyada, mara têuoem. Öebbi, s tidep, Ippameô ayen i S ihwan.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 106,
            "ruku": 86,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 671,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur ssiôxiset isekkiren n Öebbi, aggur iôqan, îêegga, snaoeq, wid iteddun ar Uxxam n Lêaôam, saramen lfevl akked llza n Mass nnsen. Üegdet mi tfukkem. Xas tcuênem agdud i wen igedlen Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ur iwata ara a pzegrem tilas. Mâawanet ar yise akked uêezzeb, ur ppemâawanet ar ubekkav akked lbewv. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. S tidep, Öebbi Iwâaô deg uâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 106,
            "ruku": 86,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 672,
            "text": "I wen ipwagedlen d loifa, idim, aksum n yilef, wayen ipwamezlen i war Öebbi, ayen ippuxenqen, ayen i pwaûerâan, ayen igrarben, ayen ippuberrzen, ayen içça lweêc - siwa ma tessawvem tezlam t -, îêegga i tezôa, aseqdec n tseqqaôt. Ayagi d ucmit. Assa, wid ijehlen uysen si ddin nnwen. Ur ten ppagwadet, agwadet iyI. Assa, Nnekmale awen ddin nnwen, Tame awen lit iW, Öuva awen annuz d ddin. Win terra tmara di tegwnip n llaé, ur iffi abrid, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 107,
            "ruku": 86,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 673,
            "text": "A k steqsayen acu i sen iêellen. Ini: 'iêell awen wayen imaânen. Ayen d teppawin s lewêuc ipûeggiden. Tesêefvem asen ayen i wen Isseêfev Öebbi. Eççet seg wayen i wen d îîfen, mmektit ed fellas isem n Öebbi'. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipawal deg uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 107,
            "ruku": 86,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 674,
            "text": "Assa, iêell awen wayen imaânen. Iêell awen lqut n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, - iêell asen lqut nnwen -; tilawin tiêuôiyin iumnen, tilawin tiêuôiyin seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, ma tefkam asent tuççit nnsent; d uwqimen maççi d ucmiten, ur teppeddum d temddukwal. Win iugin liman, mêan igiten is. Neppa, di laxeôt, seg imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 107,
            "ruku": 86,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 675,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma tekkrem ar téallit, ssirdet udmawen nnwen, ifassen nnwen alamma d tiwmaô, sâaddit ifassen illexsen ef iqweôôa nnwen, ssirdet ivaôen nnwen ar twelza. Ma tellam s loanaba, zzizdget. Ma tuvnem ne tunagem, ne iusa d yiwen segwen si ccicma, ne tennulem tilawin, ur tufim aman, ddmet akal zeddigen, sâaddit ep ef udmawen nnwen akked ifassen nnwen. Ur Iba ara Öebbi a kwen Iqelleq, maca Iba a kwen Izzizdeg, ad awen Itim lit iS, amar a pesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 108,
            "ruku": 87,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 676,
            "text": "Mmektit ed lit ikwen Iat Öebbi, akked nnesba ikwen Inuseb, mi tennam: 'nesla u nunez'. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Issen i illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 108,
            "ruku": 87,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 677,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Illit d ôôsem ar Öebbi, d inagan at lmizan. Ur kwen issencaf ddel n ugdud, ur twezznem. Wezznet. Lmizan iqôeb aîas ar uêezzeb. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Issen ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 108,
            "ruku": 87,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 678,
            "text": "Iâahed Öebbi ssmaê akked warraz ameqwôaêan, i wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 108,
            "ruku": 87,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 679,
            "text": "Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 109,
            "ruku": 87,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 680,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Mmektit ed lit ikwen Iat Öebbi, amek agdud ipheggi iman is, ad isâaddi afus is fellawen. Iîîef akin ifassen nnsen, segwen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 109,
            "ruku": 87,
            "hizbQuarter": 43,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 681,
            "text": "Ni Irra Öebbi laâqed i At Isôail. Nessuffe ed, segsen, mrawsin imvebbôen. Inna Öebbi: 'Nek yidwen ma téullem, tzekkam, tumnem s imazanen iW, u tâawnem ten, tôevlem i Öebbi aôeîîal igerzen. War ccekk, ad awen Kkse tucmitin nnwen, a kwen Skecme di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Win ijehlen segwen, deffir waya, ni innetlaf seg ubrid umâin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 109,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 682,
            "text": "Imi ooan laâqed nnsen, Nexza ten, Nesgursel ulawen nnsen. Ssexsaôen inumak n wawalen, ppun amur n wayen ief pwafekkôen. Mazal a d temlilev d lexdaâ nnsen, siwa drus segsen. Semmeê asen u ssuref. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 109,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 683,
            "text": "Wid iqqaôen: 'nekwni d imasiêiyen', Nerra laâqed yidsen, ppun amur n wayen ief pwafekkôen. Nessker ed, garasen, taâdawt akked ddel, ar ass n tnekra. Deqqal a ten Ixebbeô Öebbi ef wayen la ûenâan.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 110,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 684,
            "text": "A yAt Tezmamt! Ni iusa kwen id Umazan nne£. Ad awen ibeggen aîas n wayen la teppeffrem, n Tezmamt. Ad Ipsemmiê i waîas. Ni tusa kwen id tafat suô Öebbi, akked Tezmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 110,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 685,
            "text": "Inehhu yis Öebbi, ar iberdan n tifrat, wid iôeben llza S. A ten Issuffe si tillas ar tafat, s tsriê iS. A ten Inhu s abrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 110,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 686,
            "text": "Ni jehlen wid innan: 'Öebbi, s tidep, d lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem'. Ini: 'anwa isâan kra n lkwelf, suô Öebbi, ma ihwa yaS ad Ine lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem, imma s, akked wayen akw illan di tmurt'? N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 110,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 687,
            "text": "Udayen akked imasiêiyen, nnan: 'nekwni d tarwa n Öebbi, d wid Ismenyaf'. Ini: 'acimi, ihi, ikwen Ipâaqab ef ibekkaven nnwen? Xaîi, kunwi d imexlaq am wiyav'. Ad Isemmeê i win i S ihwan, ad Iâaqeb win i S ihwan. N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Taggara uôeS.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 111,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 688,
            "text": "A yAt Tezmamt! Ni iusa kwen id Umazan nne£, ad awen ibeggen, mi tâadda tallit war imazanen. Akka ur d teqqaôem ara: 'ur a d iusi ubeccaô, ne uneddaô'. Ihi, iusa kwen id ubeccaô, uneddaô. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 111,
            "ruku": 88,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 689,
            "text": "Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: 'a yagdud iw! Mmektit ed lit ikwen Iat Öebbi. Irra segwen lambiyya, Irra kwen d igeldan. Ifka yawen ayen ur Ifki i yiwen, deg imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 111,
            "ruku": 89,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 690,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Kecmet akal iôqan, i wen Iura Öebbi. Ur d ppualet er deffir wen, a d tegwrim txesôem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 111,
            "ruku": 89,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 691,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Musa! Degs agdud iâafriten, nekwni ur p nkeççem, d awezi, alamma ffen d segs. Mi d ffen segs, a nekcem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 111,
            "ruku": 89,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 692,
            "text": "Sin irgazen, seg wid iugaden - Isâad iten Öebbi -, nnan: 'kecmet uôsen si tebburt; ma tkecmem, kunwi, ih, a prebêem. Ppeklet af Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 111,
            "ruku": 89,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 693,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Musa! Nekwni ur p nkeççem, d awezi, skud mazal iten degs. Öuê, keçç d Mass ik, nnaet. Nekwni a neqqim dagi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 89,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 694,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Ay melke, nek, siwa iman iw akked gma; ihi, Semfaôeq a d ugdud'.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 89,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 695,
            "text": "Inna: 'ihi, tamurt agi tepwagdel asen. Ukuéet iseggwasen ad menîaôen di lberr. Ur webben ef ugdud iballaen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 89,
            "hizbQuarter": 44,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 696,
            "text": "Eêku yasen, s tidep, taqûit n sin warrac n Adem, mi îêeggan i sin. Suô yiwen tepwaqbel. Suô wayev ur tepwaqbel ara. Inna: 'war ccekk, a k ne'. Inna: 'Iqebbel kan Öebbi îêegga suô wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 697,
            "text": "Ma ibbwev iyi d ufus ik, ad iyi tenev, nek, ur k id ippawev ufus iw, a k ne. Nek, ppagwade Öebbi, Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 698,
            "text": "Nek, bi a ppawiv abekkav iw, akked ubekkav ik, a ppiliv seg wat tmes. Winna d aqeîîi imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 699,
            "text": "Iaâzem, deg iman is, ad ine gma s, da ina t. Igwra d seg imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 700,
            "text": "Iuzen ed Öebbi tagerfa, tkeôôev akal, iwakken ad as tessenâat amek ara iumm loeppa n gma s. Inna: 'a ssexv iw! Ur bbwive ad ili am tgerfa yagi, ad umme loeppa n gma'. Igwra d seg wid inedmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 112,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 701,
            "text": "Ilmend n waya, Nura i At Isôail, ar win inan amdan ur neni yiwen, ur nessefsed di tmurt, amzun ina imdanen meôôa. Win issadren yiwen, amzun issader imdanen meôôa. Ni usan ten id imazanen nne£, s ubeggen. Sinna, deffir waya, s tidep, aîas degsen ssuguten di tmurt.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 113,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 702,
            "text": "Aqeîîi n wid ipnaen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u ssenkaren asefsed di tmurt, siwa timeniwt, ne asemmeô ef umidag, ne anegzum ufus sya, uvaô sya, ne anfay si tmurt. Ayagi, d aqeîîi nnsen di ddunit. Di laxeôt, fellasen aâaqeb ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 113,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 703,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid inedmen, uqbel a pvebbôem fellasen. Cfut ar Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 113,
            "ruku": 90,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 704,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, nadit a pqeôôbem uôeS, nnaet deg ubrid iS, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 113,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 705,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen, xas ad sâun i illan akw di tmurt, rnu yas win i t icban, iwakken ad fdun, yis, iman nnsen seg uâaqeb, ass n tnekra, ur ipwaqbal segsen. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 113,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 706,
            "text": "Ad bun a d ffen si tmes, ur llin d wid id iteffen. Fellasen aâaqeb imezgi.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 114,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 707,
            "text": "Amakwar, tamakwart, gezmet asen ifassen nnsen, d aqeîîi n wayen xedmen, d aâaqeb suô Öebbi. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 114,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 708,
            "text": "Win inedmen, deffir ddens is, u iual d aâôvi, ad as Issuref Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 114,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 709,
            "text": "Day ur teéôiv ara n Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan? Ipâaqab win i S ihwan, Ipsemmiê i win i S ihwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 114,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 45,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 710,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Ur k weblen wid ipawalen ar tijehli, seg wid iqqaôen numen, s imawen nnsen, ur uminen wulawen nnsen, seg wudayen issemêasen i tikerkas, issemêasen i ugdud nniven, ur d nusi uôek. Pbeddilen awalen deffir ussefhem nnsen. Qqaôen: 'ma ippunefk awen d waya, ddemt ep; ma ur awen d ippunefk ara, uôwat'! Win Iba Öebbi a t Ihewwel, ur t tepsellikev, s wacemma, seg ufus n Öebbi. Widak, d wid iwumi ur Iba ara Öebbi, ad izdigen wulawen nnsen. Di ddunit ad pwaxzun. Di laxeôt fellasen aâaqeb abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 114,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 711,
            "text": "Wid issemêasen i tikerkas, iteppen leêôam, ma usan k id, fru garasen, ne eoo iten. Ma teooiv ten, ur k îîuôôun s wacemma. Ma têuddev, êudd garasen s lmizan. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid iweznen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 115,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 712,
            "text": "Amek ara k id asen, s aêuddu, u nitni sâan Tuôa, degs aêuddu n Öebbi? Sinna, deffir waya, ad wexxôen. Ur llin wigi si lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 115,
            "ruku": 91,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 713,
            "text": "Ih, Nessers ed Tuôa, degs nnhaya akked tafat, ferrun yis ger wudayen, lambiyya imvuâen. U iôabaniyen akked lecyux seg wayen jemâen, si Tezmamt n Öebbi, u llan d inagan is. Ur ppagwadet imdanen, agwadet iyI. Ur d ppaet, s issekniyen iW, ayen ôxisen. Wid ur nepêuddu yara s wayen id Issers Öebbi, widak d ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 115,
            "ruku": 92,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 714,
            "text": "Nura yasen degs: ôôuê s ôôuê, tiî s tiî, anzaren s wanzaren, ameééu s umeééu, tumest s tumest, leoruê ad ppuêesben. Win iooan, d leôama s. Wid ur nepêuddu yara s wayen id Issers Öebbi, widak d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 115,
            "ruku": 92,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 715,
            "text": "Nuzen ed, deffir sen, Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, a d itebbet ayen it id izwaren di Tuôa. Nefka yas Linoil, degs nnhaya akked tafat, a d itebbet ayen it id izwaren di Tuôa. D nnhaya u d anabi i wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 116,
            "ruku": 92,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 716,
            "text": "At Linoil, iwata ad êudden s wayen id Issers, degs, Öebbi. Wid ur nêudd ara s wayen id Issers Öebbi, widak d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 116,
            "ruku": 92,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 717,
            "text": "Nessers ak d Tazmamt, s tidep, a d tebbet ayen ip id izwaren n Tezmamt. Nvemn ip. Ihi, êudd garasen s wayen id Issers Öebbi. Ur teddu d lhawiyyat nnsen, beôôa n wayen i k id iusan n tidep. I yal wa, Nefka lqanun akked ubrid. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili Irra kwen d yiwen n lois. Maca, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb ef wayen i wen Ifka, mzizlet ar lxiô. Ar Öebbi tualin nnwen akw. A kwen Ixebbeô ef wayen tellam temgarradem.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 116,
            "ruku": 92,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 718,
            "text": "Ëudd garasen s wayen id Issers Öebbi. Ur teddu d lhawiyyat nnsen. £uôek a k hewwlen ef kra seg wayen i k d Issers Öebbi. Ma wexxôen, éeô ar Öebbi Iba kan a ten Iwwet ef kra ibekkaven nnsen. Ih, aîas n medden d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 116,
            "ruku": 92,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 719,
            "text": "Day ban aêuddu n zzman n war tussna? Anwa yifen Öebbi d Amêaddi, i ugdud ineûêen liman?",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 116,
            "ruku": 92,
            "hizbQuarter": 46,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 720,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pparat, d iêbiben, udayen akked imasiêiyen. Garasen d iêbiben. Win, segwen, i ten irran d iêbiben, ad yili segsen. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 117,
            "ruku": 93,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 721,
            "text": "A pwaliv imuvan n wul, ppazzalen uôsen, qqaôen asen: 'nugad ay d itezzin fella'. Ahat a d Ias Öebbi s lelb, ne s lameô suôeS. A d gwrin di nndama, ef wayen ffren deg iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 117,
            "ruku": 93,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 722,
            "text": "A d inin wid iumnen: 'day d wigi i iggullen s Öebbi, tagallit meqqwôen, ar nitni llan yidwen'? Mêan igiten nnsen, gwran d d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 117,
            "ruku": 93,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 723,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Win segwen iooan ddin is…, ihi, deqqal Öebbi a d Iawi agdud Iêemmel, i T iêemmlen; ad ôavin lmumnin, ad qesêen ar ijehliyen. Ad nnaen deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ur ppagwaden alummu n win iplummun. Ayagi d lfevl n Öebbi, Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 117,
            "ruku": 93,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 724,
            "text": "Imawlan nnwen siwa Öebbi akked Umazan iS, wid iumnen, wid ipéallan, pzekkin, u nitni îîinizen.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 117,
            "ruku": 93,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 725,
            "text": "Wid irran d imawlan nnsen, Öebbi, Amazan iS, akked wid iumnen…, ih, akabar n Öebbi, d nitni ara irebêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 117,
            "ruku": 93,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 726,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pparat d iêbiben wid id ilhan, di ddin nnwen, s wurar d utihi, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, akw seg ijehliyen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 117,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 727,
            "text": "Ma teddnem i téallit, fellas ad mmaâlken, ad uraren. Ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nefhim.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 118,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 728,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yAt Tezmamt! Acu ief la  ttehmem, siwa imi numen s Öebbi, akked wayen id Issers uône, akked wayen id Issers uqbel? Tegwti degwen d iballaen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 118,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 729,
            "text": "Ini: 'ad awen mle aqeîîi n Öebbi icemten sennig wagi? Wid Ixza Öebbi, sserfan T, Irra ten d iddawen, d ilfawen'. Âabden iôebbiten n tkerkas. Widak, atnan di liêala tucmip mavi, di ttelfan umiq seg ubrid uûwib.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 118,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 730,
            "text": "Mi d usan uôwen, qqaôen: 'numen'. Ni kecmen d s tijehli, u nitni ffen yis. Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen, ayen teffren.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 118,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 731,
            "text": "La tepwaliv aîas, degsen, pawalen ar ubekkav akked wanfal, teppen leêôam. I icmet wayen xeddmen!",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 118,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 732,
            "text": "A lemmer i sen kksen iôabiyen akked lecyax, awal ubekkav akked wuççi n leêôam? I icmet wayen la ûenâen!",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 118,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 733,
            "text": "Qqaôen wudayen: 'iskkweô ufus n Öebbi'. D ifassen nnsen i isekkwôen. Pwaxzan ilmend n wayen d qqaôen. Xaîi! Ifassen iS llin, Ipiti akken i S ihwa. Ayen i k d irsen, suô Mass ik, war ccekk, irennu i waîas segsen, lebwev akked tijehli. Nessker garasen cceêna, akked ddel, ar ass n tnekra. Yal tikelt ara caâlen times i îôad, a p Issexsi Öebbi. Pnadin asefsed di tmurt. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 118,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 734,
            "text": "At Tezmamt, lemmer day umnen u êezzben, yili, war ccekk, Nekkes asen tucmitin nnsen, u Nesskecm iten ar leonanat isaâdiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 119,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 735,
            "text": "Lemmer day îîifen di Tuôa akked Linoil, akked wayen i sen d irsen suô Mass nnsen, war ccekk, ad ççen sennig sen, akw seddaw ivaôen nnsen. Illa garasen lois iôeznen. Aîas, degsen, dirit wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 119,
            "ruku": 94,
            "hizbQuarter": 47,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 736,
            "text": "A yAmazan, mel ayen i k d irsen, suô Mass ik. Ma ur t temliv ara, ur tessawvev ara tabrap iS. Öebbi a k Ifukk si laci. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 119,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 737,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yAt Tezmamt! Ur tellim deg wacemma, alamma teddam d Tuôa, Linoil, akked wayen i wen d irsen, suô Mass nnwen'. Ayen i k d irsen suô Mass ik, war ccekk, irennu, i waîas segsen, lebwev akked tijehli. Ur webbel ef ugdud ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 119,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 738,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen, udayen, iûabiyen, imasiêiyen, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 119,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 739,
            "text": "Ni Nga laâqed i At Isôail, Nuzen asen imazanen. Yal tikelt ara ten id ias umazan s wayen ur asen nehwi, wa a t skiddben, wa a t nen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 119,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 740,
            "text": "£ilen ur ippili uhewwel. Drelen, âaégen. Sinna, Issuref asen Öebbi. Sinna, aîas degsen drelen, âaégen. Öebbi Ipwali acu xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 120,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 741,
            "text": "Ni jehlen wid iqqaôen: 'Öebbi, s tidep, d lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem'. U inna lmasiê: 'a yAt Isôail! Âabdet Öebbi, Mass iw, d Mass nnwen'. Ih, win icerken i Öebbi, Igdel as Öebbi Loennet. Axxam is d times. Ur llin isellaken i imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 120,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 742,
            "text": "Ni jehlen wid iqqaôen: 'Ih, Öebbi d wis krav n krav'. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi Yiwen. Ma ur xvin ara i wayen qqaôen, war ccekk, aâaqeb aqeôêan ad iêaz wid ijehlen segsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 120,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 743,
            "text": "Day ur tuben ara ar Öebbi, u ssuturen aS ssmaê? Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 120,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 744,
            "text": "Lmasiê, mmi s n Meryem, d amazan kan. Ni âaddan, uqbel is, imazanen. Imma s tessawal tidep. Llan teppen lqut. Wali amek i asen Nepbeggin issekniyen; sinna, wali amek la ppagwin.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 120,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 745,
            "text": "Ini: 'day a ppaâbdem, war Öebbi, ayen ur nezmir a kwen ivuôô, ne a kwen infaâ'? Öebbi, Neppa, Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 120,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 746,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yAt Tezmamt! Ur rennut, di ddin nnwen, ayen ur nelli d tidep. Ur teddut d lemcihwat n ugdud innetlafen zik, i itelfen aîas, u telfen seg ubrid uûwib.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 121,
            "ruku": 95,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 747,
            "text": "Pwaxzan wid ijehlen, seg wAt Isôail, suô iles n Dawed akked Âisa, mmi s n Meryem; ayagi, ef wayen âuûan, u zgaren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 121,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 748,
            "text": "Ur ppemyekkasen ayen xedmen n dir. I icmet wayen xeddmen!",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 121,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 749,
            "text": "A pwaliv aîas segsen, ad xalven wid ijehlen. War ccekk, icmet wayen xedmen i iman nnsen. Ad Izâaf Öebbi fellasen. Nitni ad wekkôen deg uâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 121,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 750,
            "text": "Lemmer uminen s Öebbi, Nnbi, akked wayen i sen d irsen, ur ten pparan d iêbiben. Maca aîas, segsen, d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 6,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 121,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 48,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 751,
            "text": "A ppafev icenga iqeûêanen mavi, n wid iumnen, d udayen akked wid ipcaraken. A ppafev wid iqeôben mavi, s lmaênana, ar wid iumnen, d wid innan: 'nekwni d imasiêiyen'. Ayagi, acku llan degsen ixelwiyen, iôehbaniyen, u nitni ur smewôen ara iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 121,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 752,
            "text": "Ma slan i wayen id iusan ar Umazan, a pwaliv allen nnsen ççuôent d imeîîi, seg wayen ufan n tidep. Qqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Numen, Aru ya seg inagan.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 122,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 753,
            "text": "Acu i  iuen ur numin s Öebbi akked wayen i  d iusan n tidep; ur nessarem a  Issekcem, Mass nne, s agdud iâaôviyen'?",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 122,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 754,
            "text": "A ten Ioazi Öebbi, ef wayen d qqaôen, s leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. Wagi d aoazi n lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 7,
