            "page": 122,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 755,
            "text": "Wid ijehlen, u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak, d at Loahennama.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 122,
            "ruku": 96,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 756,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pgeddilet ayen imaânen i wen Iêell Öebbi. Ur zegret tilas. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid izegren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 122,
            "ruku": 97,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 757,
            "text": "Eççet seg wayen ikwen Iôéeq Öebbi, iêellen, imaânen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. YiS, kunwi, ay tumnem.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 122,
            "ruku": 97,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 758,
            "text": "Ur kwen Ipqassa Öebbi ef tgallit n tkerkas. Maca, a kwen Iqiss ef tgallit n ûûeê. Takweffaôt is: a ppecceççem mraw imeban, akken tecceççam tawacult nnwen, ne a ten tesselsem, ne a pserêem i wakli. Win ur nwâa ara, ad iuéum krav wussan. D tagi ay d takweffaôt n tgallit nnwen, ma teggullem. Eîîfet di tgallit nnwen. Akka i wen d Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen, amar a ppesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 122,
            "ruku": 97,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 759,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ccôab, leqwmeô, tiâancuôin, taseqqaôt, d ayen kan icemten, seg igi n Cciîan. Ihi, veôôeft asen, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 123,
            "ruku": 97,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 760,
            "text": "Iba kan Cciîan ad isker ticenga akked ddel garawen, s ccôab akked leqwmeô, a kwen iveôôef seg usmekti n Öebbi, akked téallit. Day ur tepfukkum ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 123,
            "ruku": 97,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 761,
            "text": "Aet awal i Öebbi, aet awal i Umazan. £uôwat! Ma twexxôem, cfut ar Amazan, iwata yas kan anabi ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 123,
            "ruku": 97,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 762,
            "text": "Ur telli tiyta deg wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ef wayen ççan, ma êezzben, umnen, xedmen ayen ilhan, sinna êezzben, umnen, sinna, êezzben u maânen. Öebbi Iêemmel lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 123,
            "ruku": 97,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 763,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! War ccekk, a kwen Iweddeb Öebbi ef wayen tepûeggidem s ifassen nnwen, u s ixtucen nnwen, iwakken ad Iéeô Öebbi anwa i T ippagwaden, di tbavnit. Win izegren tilas, deffir waya, fellas aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 123,
            "ruku": 98,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 764,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pûeggidet di zzyaôa nnwen. Win iûeggden segwen, u iâammed, aqeîîi: ad iseddeq, si lmal is, ayen ina s ûûyada s, a d êudden, f waya, sin irgazen iêesbiyen segwen. D tikci ara iawven ar Lkaâba. Ne takweffaôt: ad icceçç imeban, ne, ayen iswan aya, ad iuéum. Ad ijeôôeb vveôô n lameô is. Öebbi Isemmeê i wayen iâaddan. Win iualen a d Irr Öebbi segs ppaô. Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 123,
            "ruku": 98,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 765,
            "text": "Têell awen ûûyada n yill akked uççi s. D lqut i kunwi akw iminigen. Tepwagdel awen ûûyada di tmurt, skud aql akwen d zziyyaô. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, uôeS ara tepwafesrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 98,
            "hizbQuarter": 49,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 766,
            "text": "Irra Öebbi Lkaâba d axxam iôqan ipwabnan i laci, aggur iôqan, asfel, isenoaq, ayagi iwakken a ppeéôem ar Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg igenwan u di tmurt, u Öebbi Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 98,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 767,
            "text": "Cfut iwâaô uâaqeb n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 98,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 768,
            "text": "Amazan, iwata yas kan unabi. Öebbi Iéôa ayen temmalem u ayen teppeffrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 98,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 769,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur iaâdil ara wayen n dir akked wayen imaânen', xas teswehm ik lkwetôa n wayen n dir. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, a yuâqilen, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 98,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 770,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur steqsayet ef tawsiwin ara kwen icweben, ma mlan awen tent. Ma testeqsam fellasent mara d iprusu Leqwôan, ad awen ppufessrent. Öebbi Isemmeê aya. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 771,
            "text": "Ni isteqsa fellasent ugdud, uqbel nnwen. Sinna, segsent, gwran d d ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 772,
            "text": "Ur d Ifki Öebbi Baêiôa, ne Sayba, ne Waûila, ne Ëami. Maca, wid ijehlen gren d tikerkas ef Öebbi. Tegwti degsen ur fhimen.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 124,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 773,
            "text": "Ma nnan asen: 'yyaw ar wayen id Issers Öebbi, u ar Umazan'. Qqaôen: 'beôka ya ayen id nufa, ef waya, eô imezwura nne'. I ma imezwura nnsen ur ssinen acemma, ur pwanhan?",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 125,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 774,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Fellawen iman nnwen. Ur kwen iîîuôôu win innetlafen, ma tepwanham. Ar Öebbi, tualin nnwen akw. A kwen Ixebbeô ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 125,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 775,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ccada garawen, ma tusa d tmeppant ar yiwen segwen. Di lawan uweûûi, sin irgazen iêesbiyen, segwen, ne wiyav war segwen, ma tellam d iminigen di tmurt, u tusa kwen id twait n tmeppant. A ten qesden deffir téallit. Ma tcukkem, sgallet pen s Öebbi: 'ur d nesfayday syis, xas iaâna llzem nne, ur nteffer ccada n Öebbi, mulac, nekwni a nili seg imednab'.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 125,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 776,
            "text": "Ma ivehô ed fellasen denben, ad ppuneûfen s wiyav, si loiha n wid vuôôen imezwura. Ad ggalen s Öebbi: 'ih, ccada nne tif ccada nnsen. Ur nzegger tilas, mulac, war ccekk, a nili seg imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 125,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 777,
            "text": "Ppif akka iwakken a d awin ccada iwulmen, ad agwaden a ppili tgallit deffir tgallit nnsen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ssemêesset, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 125,
            "ruku": 99,
            "hizbQuarter": 50,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 778,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara Issemlil Öebbi imazanen, ad Yini: 'acu i wen d jawben'? Ad inin: 'ur telli tussna uône. D Keçç, s tidep, i Issnen tibavniyin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 126,
            "ruku": 100,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 779,
            "text": "Mi Inna Öebbi: 'a Âisa, mmi s n Meryem! Mmekti d i kwen £ate, keçç akked imma k, mi k Âiwne s ôôuê iôqan. Tepmmeslayev i medden si dduê, am unqaqôi. Mi k Slemde Tazmamt, ûûwab, Tuôa, Linoil. Mi tûenâav, si talaxt, ûûifa n ufrux, s– tsriê iW; tûuvev degs, tual d afôux, s– tsriê iW. Tesseêlayev agugam, amuvin n lberû, s– tsriê iW. Mi tessenkarev lmeggtin, s– tsriê iW. Mi Sbaâde fellak At Isôail, mi d tusiv uôsen, s ubeggen, u nnan wid ijehlen segsen: 'ayagi iban d ssêur kan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 126,
            "ruku": 100,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 780,
            "text": "Mi Weêêa i inmahalen: 'amnet yissI, akw s umazan iW'. Nnan: 'numen. Echhed ar nekwni d imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
