            "page": 127,
            "ruku": 101,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 787,
            "text": "Ma Tâaqbev ten, ni d imdanen iK, ma Tsemmêev asen, Keçç, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab'.",
