          },
          {
            "number": 788,
            "text": "Inna Öebbi: 'wagi d ass ideg ara stenfâan imawlan n tidep, si tidep nnsen. I nitni leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen, i lebda'. Iôuva ten Öebbi, u ôuvan T, d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
