          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 6,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الأَنۡعَامِ",
        "englishName": "Al-An'aam",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Cattle",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 790,
            "text": "A neckeô Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan. Irra tillas, tafat. Sinna, wid ijehlen pparan tanudda i Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 791,
            "text": "Neppa, ikwen Ixelqen s talaxt, sinna, Iseyya lajel. £uôeS lajel ipwassnen. Deffir waya, kunwi la tepcukkum.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 792,
            "text": "Neppa, d Öebbi deg igenwan, di tmurt. Issen sser nnwen, d wayen d teqqaôem. Iéôa ayen tkesbem.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 793,
            "text": "Ur ten id ippas ussekni seg issekniyen n Mass nnsen, mebla ma ugin t.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 794,
            "text": "Ni skaddben tidep, mi ten id tusa. A ten id ias usali n wayen ief ttihin.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 795,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara acêal isuta, uqbel nnsen, ay Nekkes. Nesserked iten di tmurt akken ur kwen Nesserked. Nuzen asen aîas ugeffur, Nerra yasen isaffen, ppazzalen seddawat sen. Nesnegr iten ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Nxelq ed, deffir sen, sself nniven.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 796,
            "text": "Xas ad ak ed Nessers Tazmamt, di lkaev, ara nnalen s ifassen nnsen, war ccekk, a d inin wid ijehlen: 'wagi, s tidep, siwa ssêur n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 797,
            "text": "Qqaôen: 'a lemmer id irs uôes lmelk'. Lemmer a n Nessers lmelk, war ccekk, ad iûaô lameô, sinna, ur pganin.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 128,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 798,
            "text": "Lemmer i t Nerri d lmelk, yili Nerra t d argaz, ad as Nessels ayen plusun.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 799,
            "text": "Ni mmaâlken ef imazanen, uqbel ik. Ayen ief ttihin, izzi i wid, segsen, immaâlken.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 102,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 800,
            "text": "Ini: 'ddut di tmurt, sinna walit amek tevôa d wid iskiddiben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 801,
            "text": "Ini: 'w i t ilan wayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan'? Ini: 'd Öebbi'. Iura, deg iman iS, aêunu. A kwen Issemlil i wass n tnekra, ur ccekk fellas. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ur ppamnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 51,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 802,
            "text": "IneS i izeden deg iv, deg wass. Neppa Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 803,
            "text": "Ini: 'day ara sâu bab, war Öebbi, Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan? Neppa Icceççay ur t cceççayen'. Ini: 'nek pwamôe d ad ili d amenzu ara ianzen. Ur ppilit seg imcurak'.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 804,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek ugade, ma aâûa Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 805,
            "text": "Win imenâan segs, assen, ni Iêun fellas. Wagi d rrebê n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 806,
            "text": "Ma Isâadda Öebbi fellak cedda, ur p itekkes yiwen, siwa Neppa. Ma Isrebê ik, Neppa Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 807,
            "text": "D Neppa ay d Aqehhaô, sennig imdanen iS; d Neppa ay d Bab n ûûwab, i Iéôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 129,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 808,
            "text": "Ini: 'anda p ccada sennig akw tiyav'? Ini: 'Öebbi d Anagi gari yidwen. Iweêêa yi d Leqwôan agi, iwakken a kwen nabi yis, kunwi akked wid uuô ibbwev. Day, kunwi, war ccekk, a pcehhdem ar, ar tama n Öebbi, llan iôebbiten nniven'? Ini: 'ur cehhde'! Ini: 'Neppa d Öebbi, siwa Yiwen. Nek, rri akin ayen tepcarakem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 809,
            "text": "Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, ssnen p, akken ssnen arraw nnsen. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ihi, ur ppamnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 103,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 810,
            "text": "Anwa idensen sennig win d igren tikerkas ef Öebbi, ne iskaddben issekniyen iS? Ih, ur rebêen imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 811,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ten Nefser meôôa, sinna a Nini i wid icurken: 'anda ten icriken nnwen, i la tâabdem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 812,
            "text": "Deg uhewwel nnsen, siwa ma nnan d: 's Öebbi, Mass nne, ur nelli d imcurak'!",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 813,
            "text": "Wali amek skaddben ef yiman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen la d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 814,
            "text": "Garasen wid i k issemêasen. Nerra aêurrim ef ulawen nnsen, iwakken ur t fehmen. Tiâééegt deg imeééuen nnsen. Ma walan yal assekni, ur ppamnen yis. Alamma, ma usan d uôek, a k namren, ad ak inin wid ijehlen: ayagi siwa tiêkayin imezwura.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 815,
            "text": "Sîixxiôen segs, îîeôôifen segs. Ay squccun siwa iman nnsen, ur faqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 816,
            "text": "Lemmer a ten twaliv, mara bedden ar tmes, a d inin: a ssexv nne! Awi  irran, ur neskiddib issekniyen n Mass nne! A nili si lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 130,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 817,
            "text": "Xaîi! Iban asen d wayen teffren, zik. Lemmer a d kren, ad ualen ar wayen i sen ipwagedlen. Nitni, s tidep, d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 818,
            "text": "U qqaôen: 'siwa tameddurt n ddunit i illan. Nekwni, ur fella tanekra'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 819,
            "text": "Lemmer a pwaliv mara bedden ar Mass nnsen, ad Yini: 'ni ayagi s tidep'? A d inin: 'ih, s Mass nne'! Ad Yini: 'ihi jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tejhilem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 104,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 820,
            "text": "Ni xesôen wid iskaddben timlilit akked öÖebbi. Alamma, ma iusa ten id yimir, deqzalla, a d inin: 'a yamxix nne, ef wayen ideg nestehza'! Nitni ad bibben tiâakkwumin nnsen ef izugar nnsen. I icmet wayen bubben!",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 821,
            "text": "Tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan akked lhawiyya. Axxam aneggaru, war ccekk, yif ip i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tepmeyyizem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 822,
            "text": "Ni Neéôa iwebben ik, s tidep, wayen qqaôen. Ihi, nitni ur k skiddiben. Maca imednas veggôen issekniyen n Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 823,
            "text": "Ni skaddben imazanen uqbel ik. Üebôen ef wayen i ten skaddben, akked wayen i ten meêênen, armi i ten id iusa usellek nne£. Ur illi ubeddel i wawalen n Öebbi. Ni usan k id, kra isallen imazanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 824,
            "text": "Ma ééay fellak uwexxeô nnsen, ma tzemôev a tessarmev aderbuz di tmurt, ne sellum s igenni, ad asen d tawiv assekni. Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, a ten Issemlil ar nnhaya. Ur ppili seg wid ur nessin.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 131,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 52,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 825,
            "text": "Siwa wid isellen, ara d ijawben. Lmegtin a ten id Issker Öebbi, sinna, uôeS tualin nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 826,
            "text": "Qqaôen: 'acimi ur as d irs ara ussekni suô Mass is'? Ini: 'Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer a d Issers assekni', maca tegwti degsen ur éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 827,
            "text": "Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, ne ufrux ippafgen s wafriwen is, ur nelli d leoyus am kunwi. Ur Nestehza, di Tezmamt, ef wacemma. Sinna, ar Mass nnsen, ad pwafessren.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 828,
            "text": "Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, âaégen, gugmen, di tillas. Win i S ihwan i Öebbi, a t Itlef. Win i S ihwan, a t Iawi d ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 829,
            "text": "Ini: 'twalam ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb n Öebbi, ne ma iusa kwen id yimir, day ar war Öebbi ara tnaâôem, ma tessawalem tidep?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 830,
            "text": "Xaîi! £uôeS ara tnujem. Ad Issiferr ayen ief tnujem uôeS, ma ihwa yaS, a ppeppum ayen tcurkem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 105,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 831,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed ar leoyus, uqbel ik. Nesâadda fellasen tilufa, ccqa, amar ad êiwten.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 832,
            "text": "A lemmer êawten, mi ten id tusa tiyta nne£. Maca, qehôen wulawen nnsen. Cciîan Icebbeê asen ayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 833,
            "text": "Mi ppun ayen i sen d smmektin, Nelli yasen tibbura n yal cci, armi, mi feôêen s wayen i sen ippunefken, Newwet iten, deqzalla. Da qevâen layas.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 132,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 834,
            "text": "Pwakksen wid id igwran seg ugdud idensen. Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 835,
            "text": "Ini: 'twalam, ma Iddem awen Öebbi timesliwt nnwen, akked iéôi nnwen; ma Isle ulawen nnwen; anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ar awen ten id iawin'? Wali amek Nessefham issekniyen, u nitni, sinna, zzin akin.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 836,
            "text": "Ini: 'acu twalam, ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb n Öebbi, deqzalla, ne âinani? Day ara Ine, siwa agdud imednas'?",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 837,
            "text": "Ur d Nuzen imazanen, siwa i ubecceô, d unabi. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 838,
            "text": "Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, a ten iêaz uâaqeb, ilmend n wayen bewven.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 839,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur awen qqare sâi igerrujen n Öebbi, ur ssine tabavnit; ur awen qqare: nek, d lmelk. Nek, teddu kan akked wayen iyi d ippuweêêan'. Ini: 'day iaâdel uderal d win ipwalin? Day ur d tepmeyyizem ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 106,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 840,
            "text": "Nabi yis wid iugaden ad pwafessren ar Mass nnsen. Ur sâin bab, war Neppa, ne amcafaâ. Amar ad êezzben.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 107,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 841,
            "text": "Ur ppara wid ipnujun uô Mass nnsen, taûebêit, tameddit, pnadin udem iS. Ur fellak a ten têasbev deg wacemma, ur fellasen a k êasben, deg wacemma. Ma terriv ten, ihi, a ppiliv seg imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 133,
            "ruku": 107,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 842,
            "text": "Akka ay Nhewwel kra s wiyav, iwakken a d inin: 'day d wigi i Iat Öebbi, garane'? Day ur Issin ara Öebbi, sennig akw, wid isnemmiren?",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 134,
            "ruku": 107,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 843,
            "text": "Ma usan k id wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£, ini: 'tifrat fellawen'! Mass nnwen Iura, i iman iS, aêunu. Ihi, i win, segwen, ixedmen tucmip, ur iâammed, sin akin, isteôoaâ, u ixdem ayen ilhan, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 134,
            "ruku": 107,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 844,
            "text": "Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen, iwakken a d iban ubrid ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 134,
            "ruku": 107,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 845,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek, ippugdel iyi ad âabde wid uuô la tepnujum, war Öebbi'. Ini: 'ur teddu d lemcihwat nnwen, mulac ad nnetlafe, ur ppili seg wid ipwanhan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 134,
            "ruku": 108,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 846,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek, îîfe deg ubeggen n Mass iw. Teskaddbem t. Ur illi uôi wayen uuô têarem. Ih, aêuddu eô Öebbi kan. Issawal tidep. Neppa Yif akw wid issenqaden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 134,
            "ruku": 108,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 847,
            "text": "Ini: 'lemmer illi uôi wayen uuô têarem, yili iûaô lameô, gari yidwen'. Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 134,
            "ruku": 108,
            "hizbQuarter": 53,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 848,
            "text": "£uôeS tisura n tbavnit. Siwa Neppa itent Issnen. Iéôa i illan di lberr, di yill. Ur ielli ifer siwa ma Iéôa t. Akken aâqqa di tillas n tmurt, tizzegzewt, taeôt, akw di tezmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 134,
            "ruku": 108,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 849,
            "text": "D Neppa i wen ippaddamen leôwaê deg iv. Iéôa ay txeddmem, deg wass. Sinna, Ippara kwen id degs, iwakken ad ivôu lajel ipwassnen. Sinna, uôeS tualin nnwen, sinna, a kwen Ixebbeô ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 108,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 850,
            "text": "D Neppa ay d Aqehhaô sennig imdanen iS. Ippazen ed uôwen imêaraben, alamma, ma tusa d tmeppant ar yiwen segwen, ad ddmen ôôuê is, imceggâen nne£. Nitni ur stehzayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 851,
            "text": "Sinna, ad ualen ar Öebbi, Bab nnsen n tidep. Aêuddu, day maççi d ayla S? Neppa Yif akw akken Ipawal ar uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 852,
            "text": "Ini: 'anwa ara kwen Isellken si tillas n lberr d yill, uuô tnujem s uêiwet akked tugwdi'? 'Ma Isellek a si tagi, war ccekk, a nili seg wid isnemmiren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 853,
            "text": "Ini: 'Öebbi Isellek ikwen segs, akw si yal lhemm, sinna, kunwi la tepcarakem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 854,
            "text": "Ini: 'Neppa, Izmer ad awen d Iazen aâaqeb sennig wen, ne seddaw ivaôen nnwen. Ne a kwen Issemfaôaq, kra segwen ad jeôôben leqheô n wiyav'. Wali amek id Nemmal issekniyen, amar ad meêûen.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 855,
            "text": "Iskaddeb it ugdud ik, u neppa d tidep. Ini: 'ur awen lli d awkil.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 856,
            "text": "Yal asali s lweqt is. A ppualem a ppeéôem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 857,
            "text": "Ma twalav wid ipnamaren ef issekniyen nne£, eoo iten, alamma bedlen anamer. Ma iseppu k Cciîan, mi d temmektiv, ur pimi d ugdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 135,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 858,
            "text": "Ur isefk ara i wid ipêezziben, a ten êasben deg wacemma. Maca d asmekti, amar ad êezzben.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 136,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 859,
            "text": "Eoo wid irran ddin nnsen d urar, d aqesseô. Tuôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Mmekti d yis, ard a ipwaîîef umdan ef wayen ikseb. Ur isâi, war Öebbi, bab ne amcafaâ. Yal leôama ur tepwaqbal segs. Widak d wid ipwaîfen ef wayen kesben. I nitni tissit iôan, aâaqeb aqeôêan, ilmend n wayen la jehlen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 136,
            "ruku": 109,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 860,
            "text": "Ini: 'day a nâaô, war Öebbi, ayen ur a neneffaâ, ur a neîîuôôu? U a nual a nwexxeô, deffir nnhaya n Öebbi, am win ewwan ccwaîen di tmurt, u ippuêeyyeô'. Pnecciden t imeddukwal ar nnhaya: 'yya uône'! Ini: 'd nnhaya n Öebbi, s tidep, ay d nnhaya. Nepwameô a nanez i Mass imavalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 136,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 861,
            "text": "èéalet, êezzbet aS. £uôeS, Neppa, ara tepwafessrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 136,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 862,
            "text": "D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ass ideg ara Yini: 'ili'! Ad yili. Awal iS d tidep. IneS tagelda. Ass uûuvu n lbuq, Iéôa i iffren d wayen ivehôen. Neppa d Bab n ûûwab, i Iéôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 136,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 54,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 863,
            "text": "Mi inna Ibôahim i baba s, Azaô: 'day a pperrev tiâancuôin d iôebbiten? Nek wala k, keçç akked ugdud ik, di ttelfan n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 864,
            "text": "Akka, Nessken i Ibôahim, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan, iwakken ad yili seg wid itebbten.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 865,
            "text": "Mi t iumm yiv, iwala itri, inna: 'wagi d Mass iw'. Mi ixsi, inna: 'ur êemle ara wid ixessin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 866,
            "text": "Mi iwala iuli d waggur n tziri, inna: 'wagi d Mass iw'. Mi iab, inna: 'ma ur iyi Inha ara Mass iw, ad ili, war ccekk, seg ugdud imeôôqen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 867,
            "text": "Mi iwala iîij ineqqeô ed, inna: 'wagi d Mass iw, wagi meqqweô kteô'. Mi ili, inna: 'a yagdud iw! Nek rri akkin ayen tepcarakem.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 868,
            "text": "Nek zzi udem iw ar Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, male ar tidep. Ur lli, nek, seg imcurak'.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 869,
            "text": "Ixuûem it ugdud is, inna: 'day ad iyi txaûmem ef Öebbi? Ni Inha yi; ur ugade ayen i S tcurkem, siwa ma illa wayen i S ihwan i Mass iw. Tussna n Mass iw tezdi yal cci, day ur d tesmektayem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 870,
            "text": "Amek ara ugade ayen tepcarakem, ur tugadem mi kunwi tepcarakem, i Öebbi, ayen iwumi ur d Issers adabu fellawen? Anwa, ger sin ikabaran, i iklalen laman, maday tessnem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 137,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 871,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, ur sselsen ddens i liman nnsen, widak ad ilin di laman, u nitni pwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 110,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 872,
            "text": "D wagi ay d awal nne£. Nefka yas t i Ibôahim, mgal agdud is. Nessalay tiseddaôin, win i£ £ ihwan. Ih, Mass ik d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 873,
            "text": "Nefka yas Isêaq akked Yaâqub. I sin, Nenha ten. Nenha, zik, Nuê akw, ger tarwa s, Dawed, Sliman, Yub, Yusef, Musa, Haôun, - Akka ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen -",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 874,
            "text": "Zakarya, Yeêya, Âisa, Ilyas, - akw seg iâaôviyen -",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 875,
            "text": "Ismaâil, Lyasâa, Yunes, Luî, - akw Nesmenyaf iten ef imavalen -",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 876,
            "text": "akw seg ibabaten nnsen, si tarwa nnsen, akked watmaten nnsen. Nefren iten, u Nebbwi ten d ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 877,
            "text": "Tagi d nnhaya n Öebbi. Inehhu yis win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Lemmer curken, war ccekk, ad asen imêu wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 878,
            "text": "D wigi iwumi d Nebbwi Tazmamt, ûûwab, akked lambiyya. Ma jehlen widak yis, ihi, Nekwni Nwekkel ip i ugdud ur njehhel yis.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 879,
            "text": "Wigi d wid Inha Öebbi. Ddu d nnhaya nnsen. Ini: 'ur awen suture, fellas, taqdiât. Neppa d asmekti kan i imavalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 138,
            "ruku": 111,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 880,
            "text": "Ur qudôen Öebbi azal n lqedô iS, mi qqaôen: 'ur d Issers Öebbi acemma ar umdan'. Ini: 'anwa id Issersen Tazmamt, id ibbwi Musa, d tafat u d nnhaya i medden? Tepparam p di lkwaev i tesskanem. Aîas ay teppeffrem. Tlemdem ayen ur tessinem, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen'. Ini: 'D Öebbi'. Sinna, anef asen ad uraren s nnmara nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 139,
            "ruku": 112,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 881,
            "text": "Tagi d Tazmamt, Nessers ip id teôqa, a ptebbet ayen ip id izwaren, a ppendeô tayimmap n temdinin akked wayen i s d izzin. Wid iumnen s laxeôt, umnen yis. Nitni bedden i téilla nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 139,
            "ruku": 112,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 882,
            "text": "Anwa idensen sennig win d igren tikerkas ef Öebbi? Ne inna: 'ppuweêêa d', ur as d ippuweêêa wacemma? U win innan: 'a d sserse am wayen id Issers Öebbi'? Lemmer a pwaliv imednas, di maylellif n tmeppant, u lmalayek élent ed ifassen nnsent: 'ssuffet ed tiôwiêin nnwen. Assa, a ppeppuqeîîim s uâaqeb isneêcamen, ilmend n wayen teqqaôem ef Öebbi, ur d tidep. U tellam tessemwaôem iman nnwen, ef issekniyen iS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 139,
            "ruku": 112,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 883,
            "text": "Ni tusam a£ d, d ifôiden, akken ikwen Nexleq abrid amezwaru. Teooam deffir wen, ayen i wen Nefka. Ur Nwala, uôwen, imcafâen nnwen, wid i tâabdem, nitni, d icriken nnwen. Ni temfaôaqem, u ooan kwen wid la tâabdem.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 139,
            "ruku": 112,
            "hizbQuarter": 55,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 884,
            "text": "Öebbi, s tidep, Ifeôôec aâqqa, ies. Issuffu ed amuddir si lmegget. Issuffu ed lmegget seg umuddir. Akka ay d Öebbi. Acimi tugim?",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 140,
            "ruku": 113,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 885,
            "text": "Issenkar tafrara. Irra iv i ureyyeê, iîij d waggur i leêsab. D wagi ay d aseyyi n Uzmir, Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 140,
            "ruku": 113,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 886,
            "text": "D Neppa i wen Irran itran, ad awen mlen abrid, di tillas n lberr akked yill. Ni Nemmal issekniyen i ugdud issnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 140,
            "ruku": 113,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 887,
            "text": "D Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen si yiman afôid, sinna: amkan, tarusi. Ni Nemmal issekniyen i ugdud ifehhmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 140,
            "ruku": 113,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 888,
            "text": "D Neppa id Isrusun aman seg igenni. Nessuffu ed yissen yal iman. Nessuffu ed yissen tizzegzewt. Nessuffu ed yissen iâaqqayen mbabben, iguza n ppmeô id ipûubbun si tezdayin, leonanat n tfeôôant, uzemmur, n ôemman, ppemcabin ne ur ppemcabin. Walit ppemôa nnsen mi d teffe tebbwa. Ih, deg waya, war ccekk, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 140,
            "ruku": 113,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 889,
            "text": "Rran i Öebbi, leonun d icriken, u Ixelq iten. Snulfan aS d arrac, tullas, ur éôin. Gedha s yiS! Ay Aâlay sennig wayen d qqaôen!",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 140,
            "ruku": 113,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 890,
            "text": "Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, amek ara Isâu mmi S, ur Isâi tameddakwelt? U Ixleq yal cci, u Neppa, yal cci, Issen it.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 140,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 891,
            "text": "D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ixleq yal cci, ihi âabdet eP. Neppa d Awkil n yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 892,
            "text": "Ur T tepsami tmuli. Neppa Ipsami tamuli. Neppa d Laîif, i Izôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 893,
            "text": "Ni iusa kwen id ara twalim, suô Mass nnwen. Win iwalan, i iman is; win idrelen, mgal is. Ur lli nek d amêareb nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 894,
            "text": "Akka ay Nessefham issekniyen, iwakken ad inin: 'tlemdev', iwakken a t Nbeggen i ugdud issnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 895,
            "text": "Ddu d wayen ik ed ippuweêêan, suô Mass ik; ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Eoo imcurak.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 896,
            "text": "Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur curken. Ur k Nerra d amêareb nnsen, ur telliv d awkil nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 897,
            "text": "Ur naâlet wid uuô la pnujun, war Öebbi. Axaîeô ad naâlen Öebbi, s lbewv, war tamusni. Akka ay Ncebbeê igiten is i yal lois. Sinna, ar Mass nnsen, tualin nnsen; a ten Ixebbeô ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 898,
            "text": "Ggulen s Öebbi, tagalit meqqwôen, ar ma iusa ten id ussekni, ar ad amnen yis. Ini: 'issekniyen ar Öebbi kan'. Acu i kwen irran têussem ar, xas ma iusa ten id, ur ppamnen?",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 899,
            "text": "A Neppi ulawen nnsen, d yiéôi nnsen, akken ur uminen yis abrid amezwaru. A ten Neoo di lbewv nnsen, d ideralen.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 7,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 141,
            "ruku": 114,
            "hizbQuarter": 56,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 900,
            "text": "Xas Nekwni Nessers asen d lmalayek, u mmeslayen asen d lmeggtin, u Nefser asen d, yal cci, zdat sen, ur ppamnen, siwa ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi. Maca, aîas degsen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 901,
            "text": "Akka ay Nerra, i yal nnbi, acengu. Ccwaîen, seg imdanen akw si leonun, ppemweêêin garasen awal uziyn i uuôôu. Lemmer i S ihwi, i Mass ik, ur p xeddmen. Ihi, eoo iten ar wayen d snulfuyen,",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 902,
            "text": "iwakken ad mmalen uôes ulawen n wid ur numin s laxeôt, a t ôavin, ad gemren ayen zerâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 903,
            "text": "Day bi amêaddi, war Öebbi? D Neppa i wen d Issersen Tazmamt, s ussefhem. Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, éôan, ar neppat, ters ed suô Mass ik, s tidep. Ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
