            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 904,
            "text": "Awal n Mass ik ibbwev, s tidep akked lmizan. Ur illi ubeddel deg wawal iS. Neppa Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 905,
            "text": "Ma tuev awal i tegwti n wid illan di tmurt, a k telfen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Teddun kan d wayen nwan. Nitni snulfuyen d kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 906,
            "text": "Ih, Mass ik Issen sennig akw, anwi innetlafen seg ubrid iS. Neppa Issen sennig akw, anwi ipwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 907,
            "text": "Eççet ayen ief d immekti isem n Öebbi, ma tumnem s issekniyen iS.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 142,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 908,
            "text": "Acu ikwen iuen, ur teppeppem ara seg wayen ief d immekti isem n Öebbi? Ni Issfehm awen ayen i wen Igdel, siwa ma ipwaêeppem fellawen. Ih, aîas ay tellifen, s zzhu nnsen, war tussna. Ni Mass ik Iugar akw akken Issen wid izegren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 143,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 909,
            "text": "Ekkset abekkav uvhiô akked uffir. Ih, wid ibbwin abekkav, ad ppuqeîîin ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 143,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 910,
            "text": "Ur teppet ayen ief ur d immekti ara, isem n Öebbi. Ih, ayagi d ixmiô. Ih, ccwaîen pweêêin i imeddukwal nnsen, a kwen namren. Ma tuem asen awal, kunwi, s tidep, tcurkem.",
            "numberInSurah": 121,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 143,
            "ruku": 115,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 911,
            "text": "Ma win illan d lmegget, Nessider it id, Nga yas tafat, iteddu yis ger medden, day d amedya s, win illan di tillas, ur izmir ad iffe segsent. Akka, ippucebbeê i ijehliyen, wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 122,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 143,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 912,
            "text": "Akka ay Nerra, ad ppandin di yal tamdint, ibewviyen is, uqsiêen mavi. Ppandin kan i iman nnsen, ur faqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 123,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 143,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 913,
            "text": "Ma iusa ten id ussekni, ad inin: 'ur neppamen, alamma iusa ya d ayen id iusan ar imazanen n Öebbi'. Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen, anida ara Ifk tabôap iS. Ad iôxisen, ar Öebbi, wid ibewven. Fellasen aâaqeb uqsiê, ilmend n wayen ppandin.",
            "numberInSurah": 124,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 143,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 914,
            "text": "Win Iba Öebbi a t Inhu, ad illi idmaren is ar wannuz. Win Iba a t Itlef, ad Irr idmaren is deyqen, têeyyôen, amzun ippaâôav ad iali s igenni. Akka i Ippara Öebbi axerwaâ i wid ur numin.",
            "numberInSurah": 125,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 144,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 915,
            "text": "Wagi d abrid uwqim n Mass ik. Ni Nessefham issekniyen i ugdud ismektayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 126,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 144,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 57,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 916,
            "text": "I nitni, axxam n tifrat ar Mass nnsen. Neppa d Bab nnsen, ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 127,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 144,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 917,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ten Ifser meôôa: 'a yagraw n leonun, ni tcerrâem deg imdanen'? A d inin imawlan nnsen, seg imdanen: 'a Mass nne! Kra segne elten si kra, Nebbwev ar lajel nne, i  Terriv'. Inna: 'd times ay d tanezdut nnwen, ad degs twekkôem, siwa ma ur aS ihwi i Öebbi'. Ih, Mass ik d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 128,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 144,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 918,
            "text": "Akka ay Neppara kra imednas d iêbiben n kra, ilmend n wayen keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 129,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 144,
            "ruku": 116,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 919,
            "text": "'A yagraw n leonun d yimdanen, day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen segwen? Mmalen awen issekniyen iW, nedôen kwen ef temlilit n wass nnwen agi'. Nnan d: 'ncehhed ef yiman nne'. Tuôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Cehhden ef yiman nnsen ar nitni, s tidep, llan d ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 130,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 144,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 920,
            "text": "Akka, acku Mass ik ur Isquccu tamdint, s ddens, ma llan imezda is d iwefliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 131,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 144,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 921,
            "text": "I yal yiwen, tiseddarin seg wayen ixdem. Ur Ieffel Mass ik ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 132,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 145,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 922,
            "text": "Mass ik d Asâay, d Bab uêunu. Ma ihwa yaS a kwen Ikkes, a d Inûef, deffir wen, ayen i S ihwan, akken ikwen id Ixleq si tarwa n ugdud nniven.",
            "numberInSurah": 133,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 145,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 923,
            "text": "Ih, ayen i wen ippuâahden, a d ias, war ccekk. Ur tezmirem, kunwi, a ppesfunngem.",
            "numberInSurah": 134,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 145,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 924,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yagdud iw! Xedmet akken tewâam, nek ad xedme. Deqqal a ppeéôem iwumi ara telhu taggara n Uxxam'. S tidep, ur rebêen imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 135,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 145,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 925,
            "text": "Gan aS i Öebbi amur, seg wayen id Ifka n lella, akked lmal. Nnan: 'wagi i Öebbi –- di tikta nnsen -, wagi i icriken nne'. Ayen gan i icriken nnsen, ur ippawev ar Öebbi. Ayen gan i Öebbi, neppa, ad yawev ar icriken nnsen. I icmet wayen id pêuddun!",
            "numberInSurah": 136,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 145,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 926,
            "text": "Akka ay cebbêen icriken nnsen, i waîas n yimcurak, timeniwt n tarwa nnsen, iwakken a ten squccen, u ad irwi ddin nnsen, fellasen. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur p xeddmen. Eoo iten ar wayen d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 137,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 145,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 927,
            "text": "Nnan: 'lmal akked lella yagi ppugedlen, ur ten itepp, siwa win i  ihwan'. S tikta nnsen. Lmal iwumi gedlen iârar nnsen, lmal iwumi ur d ppadren fellasen, isem n Öebbi. D asnulfu mgal iS. A ten Iqeîîi ef wayen d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 138,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 146,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 928,
            "text": "Qqaôen: 'ayen illan deg iâabbav n lmal agi, i ddker nne kan, ipwagdel i tlawin nne'. Ma ilul ed immut, ad mlilen uôes. A ten Iqeîîi ef wayen d qqaôen. Neppa, s tidep, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 139,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 146,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 929,
            "text": "Ni xesôen wid inan arraw nnsen. D tiderwect, war tussna. Gedlen ayen i s iten Iat Öebbi, snulfan d mgal Öebbi. Ni nnetlafen, ur pwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 140,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 146,
            "ruku": 117,
            "hizbQuarter": 58,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 930,
            "text": "D Neppa id Ixelqen leonanat s iâricen, ne war iâricen, tizdayin, zerriâa n yal ûûenf, i wuççi; azemmur akked rreman ippemcabin, ne ur neppemcabi. Eççet si ppemôa nnsen, ma fkan d, efket leêqq is, ass uellet nnsen. Ur ssugutet. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid ipêawalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 141,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 146,
            "ruku": 118,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 931,
            "text": "Si lmal, aggway d wussu. Eççet seg wayen ikwen Iôéeq Öebbi. Ur teddut d iberdan n Cciîan. Neppa, s tidep, d acengu nnwen n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 142,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 146,
            "ruku": 118,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 932,
            "text": "Ïamt tyugiwin, snat uwelmi, snat umâiz. Ini: 'd sin n ddker i Igdel, ne d snat n nnta, ne d ayen illan deg iâabbav n snat n nnta? Xebbôet iyi d, s tussna, ma tessawalem tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 143,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 147,
            "ruku": 118,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 933,
            "text": "Seg ilewman, snat, seg ubeqôi, snat. Ini: 'd sin n ddker i Igdel, ne d snat n nnta, ne d ayen illan deg iâabbav n snat n nnta, ne tellam d inagan mi kwen id Iweûûa Öebbi ef waya'? Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas ef Öebbi, iwakken ad itlef imdanen, ur issin. Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 144,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 147,
            "ruku": 118,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 934,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur ufi ipwagdel a t içç yiwen, deg wayen iyi d ippuweêêan, siwa ma illa d loifa, ne d idim immaren, ne d aksum n yilef - wagi, war ccekk, d lewsex -, ne îêegga s dwel i war Öebbi. Win ief ippuêeppem, ur ibi, ur ibwiv, Mass ik, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 145,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 147,
            "ruku": 119,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 935,
            "text": "I wudayen, Negdel ayen akw isâan acaren, seg ubeqôi akked uwelmi, Negdel asen tassemt nnsen, siwa tin n iârar nnsen, iâabbav, akked wayen ipwaxelven akked isan. Akka ay ten Nepkafi, ilmend n îîeôô nnsen. Nekwni, war ccekk, d At Tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 146,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 147,
            "ruku": 119,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 936,
            "text": "Ma skaddben k, ini: 'Mass nnwen d Bab uêunu iwsâan, ur ipwexxiô ssexv iS, af ugdud ibewviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 147,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 148,
            "ruku": 119,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 937,
            "text": "Ad inin imcurak: 'lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, nekwni akked imezwura nne, ur ncurek, ur negdel acemma'. Akka ay skaddben imezwura nnsen, armi jeôôben ssexv nne£. Ini: 'day tesâam tussna ar a d tesseknem? Teppeddum kan d nnwaya, kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 148,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 148,
            "ruku": 119,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 938,
            "text": "Ini: 'n Öebbi timenna tunûiêin. Lemmer i S ihwi, yili Inha kwen akw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 149,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 148,
            "ruku": 119,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 939,
            "text": "Ini: 'awit ed inagan nnwen, ara icehhden ar Öebbi Igdel ayagi'. Ma cehhden, ur cehhed yidsen. Ur teddu d lhawiyya n wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, akked wid ur numin s laxeôt, u pparan tanudda i Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 150,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 148,
            "ruku": 119,
            "hizbQuarter": 59,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 940,
            "text": "Ini: 'yyaw, ad ini. I wen Igdel Mass nnwen: ur aS tepcarakem acemma; elhut ar imawlan nnwen; ur neqqet tarwa nnwen, di tigullelt - d Nekwni ara kwen Iôeéqen yidsen -, ur ppaéet ar lâaô, d uvhiô ne d uffir; ur neqqet amdan, d ayen Igdel Öebbi, siwa ma s lêeqq'. Ar waya i kwen Iweûûa, amar a pfehmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 151,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 148,
            "ruku": 120,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 941,
            "text": "Ur pqeôôibet s ayla ugujil, siwa s wayen ilhan, alamma immeêtel. Weznet, ktilet s lewqama. Ur Nepkellif amdan siwa ar wayen iwumi izmer. Ma thedôem d, weznet, xas ma eô llzem nnwen. Qadôet lemâahda n Öebbi. Iweûûa kwen ef waya, amar a d temmektim.",
            "numberInSurah": 152,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 149,
            "ruku": 120,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 942,
            "text": "D wagi ay d abrid iW uwqim, ddut degs. Ur teddut d iberdan ara kwen isîixôen seg ubrid iS. Iweûûa kwen ef waya, amar a pêezzbem.",
            "numberInSurah": 153,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 149,
            "ruku": 120,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 943,
            "text": "Sinna, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Tewqem i wid imaânen, tfeûûel yal cci, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Amar ad amnen s timlilit n Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 154,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 149,
            "ruku": 120,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 944,
            "text": "Tagi d Tazmamt, Nessers ip id, teôqa. Ihi, ddut yides, êezzbet, amar fellawen aêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 155,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 149,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 945,
            "text": "Ur d teqqaôem ara: 'ters ed kan Tezmamt eô sin leoyus, uqbel nne, ur neéôi d acu sselmaden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 156,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 149,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 946,
            "text": "Ne a d tinim: 'lemmer id ters Tazmamt uône, yili nif iten akken nepwanha'. Ni iusa kwen id ubeggen, suô Mass nnwen, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Anwa idensen sennig win iskaddben issekniyen n Öebbi, u iooa iten? A Nqeîîi wid iooan issekniyen nne£, s yir aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen la ppaooan.",
            "numberInSurah": 157,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 149,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 947,
            "text": "D acu pôaoun, siwa ma ten id asent lmalayek, ne a d Ias Mass ik, ne a d asen kra issekniyen n Mass ik? Ass ideg ara d asen kra issekniyen n Mass ik, ur infaâ umdan liman is, ma, iu lêal, ur iumin ara, ne ur iksib lxiô, di liman is. Ini: 'gganit, nekwni, ih, la nepgani'.",
            "numberInSurah": 158,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 948,
            "text": "Ih, wid ibvan ddin nnsen, u gan ikabaren, ur tepkkiv yidsen deg wacemma. Lameô nnsen ar Öebbi kan, sinna, a ten Ixebbeô ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 159,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 949,
            "text": "Win id iusan s yise, ines mraw i t icban; win id iusan s tucmip, ad ippuqeîîi s tin kan i p icban; nitni ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 160,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 950,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek, Inha iyi Mass iw, ar ubrid uwqim, d ddin n ddwam, win n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep, ur nelli seg imcurak'.",
            "numberInSurah": 161,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 951,
            "text": "Ini: 'ih, taéallit iw, iseflan iw, tudert iw, tameppant iw, i Öebbi, Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 162,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 952,
            "text": "Ur aS illi ucarek. Pwamôe d s waya: nek d amduâ amenzu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 163,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 953,
            "text": "Ini: 'day bi mass, war Öebbi? U Neppa d Mass n yal cci'. Ur ikesseb yal yiman, siwa mgal is. Ur ipbibbi win ibubben taâkkwemt n wayev. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen, tualin nnwen. Sinna, a kwen Ixebbeô ef wayen tellam temgaradem.",
            "numberInSurah": 164,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 954,
            "text": "D Neppa i kwen Irran d igensas di tmurt. Irra, kra segwen, tiseddaôin sennig wiyav, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb ef wayen i wen Ifka. Ih, Mass ik Ipawal deg uâaqeb. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 165,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 150,
            "ruku": 121,
            "hizbQuarter": 60,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 7,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الأَعۡرَافِ",
        "englishName": "Al-A'raaf",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Heights",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 955,
            "text": "Almû.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 956,
            "text": "Tazmamt ters ed uôek, ur teppili segs lhejna deg idmaren ik, iwakken a pnabiv yis; u d asmekti i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 957,
            "text": "Ddut d wayen id irsen uôwen, suô Mass nnwen. Ur teddut d imawlan, war Neppa. Drus id tesmektayem.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 958,
            "text": "Acêal n temdinin ay Nessenger. Tusa ten id tiyta nne£, deg ives nnsen, ne deg uqeggel nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 959,
            "text": "Tiôi nnsen, mi ten id tusa tiyta nne£, siwa mi d nnan: 'ih, nella d imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 960,
            "text": "War ccekk, a Nesteqsi wid uuô id Nuzen, a Nesteqsi imazanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 961,
            "text": "War ccekk, ad asen Neêku, s tmusni, ur Nelli Nab.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 962,
            "text": "Awzan, assen, d tidep. Wid iwumi ééayet lweznat nnsen, widak d wid irebêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 963,
            "text": "Wid iwumi fessuset lweznat nnsen, widak d wid ixesôen iman nnsen, seg akken sednasen issekniyen nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 964,
            "text": "Ni, s tidep, Nesrekd ikwen di tmurt, Nerra yawen, degs, tamâict nnwen. Drus ay tesnemmirem.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 122,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 965,
            "text": "Ni, s tidep, Nxelq ikwen, sinna, Nmesl ikwen, sinna, Nenna i lmalayek: 'knumt i Adem'! Knant, siwa Iblis. Ur illi seg wid iknan.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 151,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 966,
            "text": "Inna: 'acu k iîîfen ur tekniv ara, mi k d Umôe'? Inna d: 'Nek, ife t. Txelqev iyi si tmes, Txelqev t si talaxt'.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 967,
            "text": "Inna: 'ihi, ûûub segs! Ur ak ippunefk ara a ppesmewôev iman ik, degs. Effe, keçç seg wid ixuûen'!",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 968,
            "text": "Inna: 'Eoo iyi, ar ass ideg ara d kkren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 969,
            "text": "Inna: 'keçç, ih, seg wid ara iqqimen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 970,
            "text": "Inna d: 'imi iyi Tâammdev aewwu, ad asen qqime, war ccekk, deg ubrid iK uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 971,
            "text": "Sinna, ad asen d tekke zdat, deffir, yeffus, zelmev. Ur Teppafev, eô tugwti segsen, asnemmer'.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 972,
            "text": "Inna: 'effe segs, d ameêquô ippuvegôen! War ccekk, ad Acaôe Loahennama s wid, segsen, i k ivefôen, akked yiswen akw.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 973,
            "text": "A Adem, ezde Loennet, keçç akked tmeîîut ik, eççet seg wayen i wen ihwan. Ur pqeôôibet ttejôa agi, mulac a ppilim seg imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 974,
            "text": "Iewwa ten Cciîan, iwakken ad asen d iban âaryan nnsen i illan iffer. Inna: 'Ikkes awen, kan, Mass nnwen, ttejôa agi, iwakken ur teppilim d lmalayek, ne ur tepwekkiôem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 975,
            "text": "Iggul asen: 'nek, i kunwi, d unûiê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 976,
            "text": "Isdull iten s uuôôu. Mi âaôven si ttejôa nni, walan iman nnsen aâran. Lhan d la pcuddun, ef iman nnsen, afriwen n Loennet. Issawel asen d Mass nnsen: 'day ur awen Gdile ara ttejôa nni? Ad awen Ini: war ccekk, Cciîan, i kunwi, d acengu n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 152,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 977,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Mass nne! Nvuôô iman nne. Ma ur a Tsemmêev, ur Têunev fella, a nili seg imexsuôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 978,
            "text": "Inna: 'erset! Kra d icenga n kra. A pzedem di tmurt, a ppezhum, tallit kan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 979,
            "text": "Irna: 'degs a ppidirem, degs a ppemmtem, segs a d teffem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 123,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 980,
            "text": "A tarwa n Adem! Ni Nessers awen ed aceîîiv ara kwen issôen, ôôêuê, akked uceîîiv uêezzeb. Wagi yif iten'. Ayagi seg issekniyen n Öebbi, amar a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 124,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 981,
            "text": "A tarwa n Adem! £uôwat a kwen ihewwel Cciîan, akken id issuffe imezwura nnwen si Loennet! Ikkes asen iceîîiven nnsen, iwakken ad asen issken âaryan nnsen. Neppa, war ccekk, ipwali kwen - neppa akked ccetla s - seg wanda ur ten tepwalim. Ni Nerra ccwaîen d imawlan n wid ur numin.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 124,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 982,
            "text": "Mi xedmen ayen n dir, ad inin: 'nufa d akka ar imezwura nne, u Öebbi Iumeô a d uôes. Ini: 'Öebbi, s tidep, ur Ippameô ar wayen n dir. Day a d tinim ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 124,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 983,
            "text": "Ini: 'Iumeô ed Öebbi lmizan. Zzit uôeS udmawen nnwen di yal lekni, nujet uôeS. £uôeS, s ddin iûfan. Akken ikwen id Ixleq, a ppualem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 124,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 984,
            "text": "Arbaâ Inha it, arbaâ iura ttelfan fellas. Nitni, s tidep, rran ccwaîen d iêbiben, war Öebbi. U ilen nitni, war ccekk, pwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 153,
            "ruku": 124,
            "hizbQuarter": 61,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 985,
            "text": "A tarwa n Adem! Ccebêet i yal lekni, eççet, esswet, ur sîuqqutet. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid isîuqquten.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 154,
            "ruku": 124,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 986,
            "text": "Ini: 'anwa i igedlen ccbaêa n Öebbi, id Issuffe i imdanen iS, akked ôôeéq ilhan'? Ini: 'ayagi, di tmeddurt n ddunit, i wid iumnen. I nitni kan ass n tnekra'. Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen i ugdud issnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 154,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 987,
            "text": "Ini: 'Mass iw Igdel kan ayen n dir, d uvhiô ne d uffir, abekkav, temweô war ssebba, a pcarkem i Öebbi ayen iwumi ur d irs udabu, a ppinim ef Öebbi ayen ur tessinem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 154,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 988,
            "text": "Yal lois isâa lajel. Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiôen s ssaâa, ur t id ééaéan.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 154,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 989,
            "text": "A tarwa n Adem! Ma usan kwen id imazanen segwen, mmalen awen issekniyen iW, wid ipêezziben, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 154,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 990,
            "text": "Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, u smewôen iman nnsen fellasen, widak d at tmes, nitni degs ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 154,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 991,
            "text": "Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas ef Öebbi, ne iskaddben issekniyen iS? Widak, a ten iêaz umur i sen iuran di Tezmamt. Alamma, mi ten id usan imceggâen nne£, ad ddmen leôwaê nnsen, ad inin: 'anida ten wid uuô tepnujum, war Öebbi'? A d inin: 'ur ten nufi'. Ad cehhden, ef yiman nnsen, ar nitni llan d ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 154,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 992,
            "text": "Inna: 'kecmet di tmes ar leoyus n leonun akked yimdanen, i kwen id izwaren'! Yal tikelt ara ikcem lois, ad ixzu gma s. Alamma, mi mlalen degs akw, ad yini uneggaru nnsen ef umezwaru nnsen: 'a Mass nne! Wigi telfen a, Aâqeb iten s tmes, berdayen'. Inna: 'i yal yiwen berdayen, maca ur teéôim ara'.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 155,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 993,
            "text": "Inna umezwaru nnsen i uneggaru nnsen: 'ur kwen smenyafen i nekwni, ihi jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tkeppbem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 155,
            "ruku": 125,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 994,
            "text": "Ih, wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, u smewôen iman nnsen fellasen, ur asen tellin tibbura igenni, ur keçmen Loennet, skud ur iâadda ara ulem di tiî n tsegnit. Akka ay Nepqeîîi ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 155,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 995,
            "text": "I nitni ameîôeê di Loahennama, ad ummen s tmes. Akka ay Nepqeîîi imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 155,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 996,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan - ur Nepkellif i umdan siwa ayen iwumi izmer - widak, d at Loennet, nitni, degs, ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 155,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 997,
            "text": "A Nekkes i d igwran n ddel, deg idmaren nnsen. Isaffen ad ppazzalen ddawat sen. Ad inin: 'ccekôan i Öebbi i  Inhan eô waya. Ur nepwanhu, lemmer ur a Inha ara Öebbi. Ni usan d imazanen n Mass nne, s tidep'. Ad pwanecden: 'appan Loennet, tweôtem p, ilmend n wayen txeddmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 155,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 998,
            "text": "At Loennet ad siwlen i at tmes: 'ni nufa i  Iâahed Mass nne, s tidep. Ma tufam ayen i wen Iâahed Mass nnwen, s tidep'? A inin: 'Ih'. Iberreê uberraê garasen: 'xezzu n Öebbi i imednas,",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 999,
            "text": "wid iîîeôôifen seg ubrid n Öebbi, ssaramen t d uâwij, u nekôen laxeôt'.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1000,
            "text": "Garasen ssteô. £ef iqacucen, irgazen, ssnen ten akw, ar ûûiffat nnsen. Ad siwlen i at Loennet: 'tifrat fellawen'! Ur p keççmen, xas ssarmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 62,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1001,
            "text": "Mi zzint wallen nnsen ar at tmes, ad inin: 'a Mass nne! Ur a Ppara s agdud imednas'!",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 126,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1002,
            "text": "Ad siwlen at iqacucen i irgazen, ssnen ten ar ûûiffat nnsen. Ad inin: 'acu i wen d issuli wayen tjemâam akked wayen tzuxxem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 127,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1003,
            "text": "Day wigi d wid ief teggulem, ar ur sen ippak Öebbi aêunu? 'Kecmet Loennet, ur teppagwadem, ur tweblem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 127,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1004,
            "text": "At tmes ad siwlen i at Loennet: 'smiret ed fellane aman, ne seg wayen is ikwen Iat Öebbi'. Ad inin: 'Öebbi, s tidep, Igdel iten i ijehliyen,",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 127,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1005,
            "text": "wid irran ddin nnsen d zzhu, d urar, u tuôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit'. Ihi, assa, a ten Neppu, akken ppun timlilit n wass nnsen agi, u nekôen issekniyen nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 156,
            "ruku": 127,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1006,
            "text": "Ni Nusa ten id s Tezmamt, Nfeûûel ip s tussna. D nnhaya, d aêunu i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 157,
            "ruku": 127,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1007,
            "text": "Day la pôaoun kan veôôu s? Ass n tisin n veôôu s, ad inin wid illan, iu lêal, ppun p: 'ni usan d imazanen n Mass nne, s tidep. Day nesâa imcafâen ara  icafâen, ne ad a rren, a nexdem ayen mgirrden wayen nxeddem'? Ni sxeûôen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 157,
            "ruku": 127,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1008,
            "text": "S tidep, Mass nnwen d Öebbi. Ixelq ed tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan, sinna, Iâannec ef usgeld. Ipummu iv s wass, ipawalen uôes. Iîij, aggur, akked yitran unzen i lameô iS. Day maççi ineS lxelq akked lameô? D Asaâdi Öebbi, Mass imavalen!",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 157,
            "ruku": 128,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1009,
            "text": "Naâret Mass nnwen, s wannuz, di tbavnit. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara wid izegren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 157,
            "ruku": 128,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1010,
            "text": "Ur ssefsadet di tmurt deffir useêôet is. Naâôet eP, s tugwdi d usirem. Aêunu n Öebbi, s tidep, ar tama n lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 157,
            "ruku": 128,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1011,
            "text": "D Neppa id Ippaznen avu, d abecceô s uêunu S. Alamma, ma ibbub ed asigna aéayan, Nenheô it ar tmurt immuten. Nesseli d syis aman. Nessuffe ed yissen yal ppemôa. Akka ay d Nessuffu lmeggtin, amendeô ma d tesmektim.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 157,
            "ruku": 128,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1012,
            "text": "Di tmurt lâali, teffen d iman is, ma Irad Öebbi. Di tin icemten, teffen d kan d iweqweqen. Akka ay Nepbeggin issekniyen i ugdud isnemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 128,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1013,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is. Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Nek ugade fellawen aâaqeb, ass ameqwôaêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 129,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1014,
            "text": "Nnan imvebbôen n ugdud is: 'uône, s tidep, aql ak di ttelfan n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 129,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1015,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Ur illi dgi ttelfan. Maca nek d amazan suô Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 129,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1016,
            "text": "Bbwi awen d tibratin n Mass iw, a kwen neûêe. Ssne, suô Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 129,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1017,
            "text": "Day twehmem mi kwen id iusa usmekti suô Mass nnwen, ibbwi t id urgaz segwen, iwakken a kwen inabi, iwakken a pêezzbem, amar fellawen aêunu'?",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 129,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1018,
            "text": "Skaddben t. Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, di lbabuô. Nemeq wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Nitni, s tidep, d agdud aderal.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 129,
            "hizbQuarter": 63,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1019,
            "text": "Ar Âad, gmat sen Hud. Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Day ur tepêezziben ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1020,
            "text": "Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen seg ugdud is: 's tidep, uône, deg k tisselbi; uône, ih, keçç seg wid iskiddiben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1021,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Ur dgi tisselbi. Maca nek d amazan suô Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 158,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1022,
            "text": "Bbwi awen d tibratin n Mass iw. Nek, i kunwi, d aneûûaê muman.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 159,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1023,
            "text": "Day twehmem mi kwen id iusa usmekti suô Mass nnwen, ibbwi t id urgaz segwen, iwakken a kwen inabi. Mmektit ed mi kwen Irra d igensas, deffir ugdud n Nuê. Isemweô aîas lqedd nnwen. Mmektit ed lxiô n Öebbi, amar a prebêem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 159,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1024,
            "text": "Nnan: 'day a d tusiv, iwakken a naâbed Öebbi Yiwen, a neoo ayen llan âabden imezwura nne? Awi ya d ayen is la  tessagwadev, ma d tidep ay tessawalev'.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 159,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1025,
            "text": "Inna: 'ni iwwet ikwen id ddell akked zzâaf suô Mass nnwen. Day ad iyi namren ef ismawen i tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen, i wid iwumi ur d Issers Öebbi kra udabu. Ihi, gganit, nek yidwen seg wid ara igganin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 159,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1026,
            "text": "Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, s uêunu suône£. Nessenger wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, ur nelli d lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 159,
            "ruku": 130,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1027,
            "text": "£uô Tamud, gmat sen Üaliê. Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Ni iusa kwen id ubeggen suô Mass nnwen. Talwemt agi n Öebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Ooet ep a ppeçç di tmurt n Öebbi. Ur p îîuôôut, mulac a kwen iêaz uâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 159,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1028,
            "text": "Mmektit ed mi kwen Irra d igensas, deffir Âad. Isseqâad ikwen di tmurt, tepparram lebôuj di swaêel, teqqazem ixxamen deg durar. Ihi, mmektit ed lxiô n Öebbi, ur ssexsaôet tamurt, s usefsed'.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1029,
            "text": "Imvebbôen seg ugdud is, wid ismeawôen iman nnsen, nnan i wuôhifen, wid segsen iumnen: 'day teéôam ar ÛüÜaliê d amazan suô Mass is'? Nnan: 'ih, numen s wayen is id ippuceggaâ'.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1030,
            "text": "Nnan imzuxiyen: 'nekwni, s tidep, nenkeô ayen is tumnem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1031,
            "text": "Ëerrfen avaô n telwemt, gelzen lameô n Mass nnsen. Nnan: 'a Üaliê, awi ya d ayen is la  tessagwadev, ma d amazan ay telliv'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1032,
            "text": "Tewwet iten zzenzla, gwran d, deg ixxamen nnsen, d loeppat.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1033,
            "text": "Iwexxeô asen, u inna: 'a yagdud iw! Ni ssawve awen d tabôap n Mass iw, neûêe kwen, maca ur têemmlem ara win ineûêen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1034,
            "text": "I Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: 'day a txeddmem lâaô ur ixdim yiwen, uqbel nnwen, deg imavalen?",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1035,
            "text": "Ih, kunwi tpeddum ar irgazen, tcehwam ten, war tilawin. Kunwi, ih, d agdud izegren tilas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 160,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1036,
            "text": "Tiririt n ugdud is siwa nnan: 'ssuffet pen si temdint nnwen, nitni d imdanen issaramen tezdeg'.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 161,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1037,
            "text": "Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is, teqqim akked wid igwran.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 161,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1038,
            "text": "Nesseli d fellasen ageffur…Wali amek tevôa d ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 161,
            "ruku": 131,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1039,
            "text": "£uô Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb. Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi war Neppa. Ni iusa kwen id ubeggen suô Mass nnwen. Ktilet, weznet, s lewqama. Ur îîuôôut medden di cci nnsen, ur ssefsadet di tmurt, deffir useêôet is. I kunwi yif it wayagi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 161,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1040,
            "text": "Ur pimit di yal abrid, tessagwadem u tessefôaem seg ubrid n Öebbi, wid iumnen yiS. Tebam t d uâwij. Mmektit ed mi tellam d takwemmict, Iketteô ikwen. Walit amek tevôa taggara ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 161,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1041,
            "text": "Ma illa iumen urbaâ segwen s wayen is id ppuceggâa, arbaâ nniven ur iumin ara. Üebôet ard Iêudd Öebbi garane. Neppa Yif akw imêaddan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 8,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 161,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 64,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1042,
            "text": "Nnan d imvebbôen imzuxiyen, n ugdud is,: 'a k nessuffe a Cuâayeb, keçç, akked wid iumnen yidek, si temdint nne, ne a d tualev ar ddin nne'. Inna: 'xas nugi?",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1043,
            "text": "Ihi, nger ed tikerkas ef Öebbi, ma nual ar ddin nnwen, mbaâd ma Isellek a Öebbi, segs. Ur a ilaq ara a nual uôes, siwa ma Irad Öebbi, Mass nne. Mass nne Issemêalleq i yal cci s tmusni. Nepkel ef Öebbi'. A Mass nne! Fru p garane akked ugdud nne, s tidep. Keçç Tifev akw wid iferrun.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1044,
            "text": "Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen, n ugdud is: 'ma teddam d Cuâayeb, war ccekk a pxesôem.'",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1045,
            "text": "Tewwet iten zzenzla, gwran d, deg ixxamen nnsen, d loeppat.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1046,
            "text": "Wid iskaddben Cuâayeb, ualen amzun ur zdien. Wid iskaddben Cuâayeb, d nitni ay d imexûuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1047,
            "text": "Iwexxeô asen, u inna: 'a yagdud iw! Ni ssawve awen d tibôatin n Mass iw, neûêe kwen. Amek ara weble ef ugdud ijehliyen'?",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 132,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1048,
            "text": "Ur Nuzen ara nnbi ar temdint, mebla ma Newwet imezda is s cedda, akked lemveôôa, amar ad êiwten.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 133,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1049,
            "text": "Sinna, Nerra ise deg umkan n tucmip, armi wexxôen, nnan: 'ni jeôôben imezwura nne lemveôôa akked ttrika'. Newwet iten deqzalla, nitni ur bnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 162,
            "ruku": 133,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1050,
            "text": "Lemmer kan uminen u êezzben imezda n temdinin, war ccekk, ad asen Nelli lbaôakat seg igenni akked tmurt. Maca, skaddben. Nessemêalleq asen, ilmend n wayen keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 133,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1051,
            "text": "Day ilen imezda n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nne£, deg yiv, nitni îîsen?",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 133,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1052,
            "text": "Ne day ilen imezda n temdinin, ur ten id teppawev tiyta nne£, deg wazal, nitni ppuraren?",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 133,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1053,
            "text": "Day ilen sellken i tandit n Öebbi? Siwa agdud i ixesôen, i iilen sellken i tandit n Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 133,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1054,
            "text": "Ne day ur d Iban ara, i wid ara iweôten tamurt, deffir imezda is, ar, ma ihwa ya£, a ten Newwet ef ibekkaven nnsen, a Nesle ulawen nnsen, da nitni ur sellen?",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 134,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1055,
            "text": "D timdinin agi, ief ak Nêekku, si teqûivin nnsent. Ni usan uôsent imazanen nnsent, s ubeggen. Ur llint d tid ara iamnen deg wayen skaddbent uqbel. Akka i Iselle Öebbi ulawen ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 134,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1056,
            "text": "Ur Nufi nnesba ar tegwti nnsen. Nufa, tegwti nnsen, d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 134,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1057,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir sen, Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£, ar Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Densen ten. Wali amek tevôa d ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 134,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1058,
            "text": "Inna Musa: 'a Ferâun! Nek d amazan suô Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 163,
            "ruku": 134,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1059,
            "text": "D ûûeê, ur qqaôe, ef Öebbi, siwa tidep. Ih, usi kwen id, s ubeggen n Mass nnwen. Ihi, azen yidi At Isôail'.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 164,
            "ruku": 134,
            "hizbQuarter": 65,
