            "page": 165,
            "ruku": 135,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1077,
            "text": "Inna Ferâun: 'day tumnem yis, uqbel ma âammde awen? Ayagi, war ccekk, d tifxep. Tundim p di temdint, iwakken a ppessuffem, segs, imezda is. Ihi, deqqal a ppeéôem.",
