            "page": 165,
            "ruku": 135,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1081,
            "text": "Imvebbôen n ugdud n Ferâun, nnan: 'day a ppeooev Musa akked ugdud is, ad ssefsaden di tmurt, a kwen ooen, keçç akked iôebbiten ik'? Inna: 'a nene arrac nnsen, a nessider tilawin nnsen. Nekwni, sennig sen, d iqehhaôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 127,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 165,
            "ruku": 136,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1082,
            "text": "Inna Musa i ugdud is: 'ppret afus n Öebbi, u ûebôet. Tamurt, war ccekk, n Öebbi. A p iwôet win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Taggara i wid ipêezziben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 128,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 165,
            "ruku": 136,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1083,
            "text": "Nnan: 'njaf uqbel a  d tasev, u deffir tisin ik'. Inna: 'amar Mass nnwen ad Ine acengu nnwen, a kwen Irr d igensas di tmurt, ad Iwali amek ara txedmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 129,
            "juz": 9,
