            "page": 165,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1085,
            "text": "Ma iusa ten id ise, ad inin: 'nne wagi'. Ma tusa ten id tucmip, a p sbibben i Musa akked wid illan yides. Ayen iveôôun yidsen, day maççi ar Öebbi kan? Maca, tegwti segsen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 131,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 166,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1086,
            "text": "Nnan: ' wicqa assekni ara d tawiv, ur a tepseêêirev yis. Nekwni, ur neppamen yisek'.",
            "numberInSurah": 132,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 166,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1087,
            "text": "Nuzen asen aêemmal, ajôad, tilkin, imqweôqwôen, idammen, d issekniyen ifeûlen. Smewôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 133,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 166,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1088,
            "text": "Mi tevôa yidsen twait, qqaôen: 'a Musa! Nâaô Mass ik i nekwni, s wayen i k Iâahed. Ma tekksev a tawait, a namen yisek, a nazen yidek At Isôail'.",
            "numberInSurah": 134,
