            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 166,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1091,
            "text": "Nessewôet i ugdud i illan qehôen t, igmav akked ituram n tmurt, i Neôqa. Itam wawal ûûam n Mass ik, ef At Isôail, ilmend n wayen ûebôen. Nhudd ayen iûennaâ Ferâun akked ugdud is, u wayen bennun.",
            "numberInSurah": 137,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 166,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1092,
            "text": "Nesâadda ill i At Isôail. Mmugren d agdud i iâabden tiâancuôin is. Nnan: 'a Musa! Err ane ôebbi am iôebbiten nnsen'. Inna: 'kunwi, s tidep, d agdud ur nessin.",
            "numberInSurah": 138,
