            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 167,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1095,
            "text": "Mi kwen Nsellek si lois n Ferâun, sukken fellawen aâaqeb uqsiê mavi; neqqen arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Deg waya, ajeôôeb suô Mass nnwen ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 141,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 167,
            "ruku": 137,
            "hizbQuarter": 66,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1096,
            "text": "Nemlal akked Musa kravet wavan, Nerna yasen mraw. Tebbwev tallit n Mass is, kuzet wavan. Inna Musa i gma s Haôun: 'enûef iyi ar ugdud iw, exdem ayen ilhan, ur teddu d ubrid ifessaden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 142,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 167,
            "ruku": 138,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1097,
            "text": "Mi d iusa Musa ar temlilit nne£, u Immeslay as Mass is, inna: 'a Mass iw! Ssenâat iyi d, a K wali'. Inna d: 'ur iyI tepwaliv, d awezi, maca muqel s adrar. Ma iqqim deg umekkan is, ad iyI twaliv'. Mi d Iusa Mass is s adrar, Irra t d saêel. Ili Musa, ixsef. Mi d iuki, inna: 'gedha s yiseK! Utube K, nek d amezwaru n lmumnin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 143,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 167,
            "ruku": 138,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1098,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Musa! Aql I Smenyafe k ef imdanen, i tebôatin iW, i wawal iW. Ddem ayen i k d Fki, ili seg wid isnemmiren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 144,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 168,
            "ruku": 138,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1099,
            "text": "Nura yas, di tlewêin, si yal cci, anabi akked ufeûûel n yal cci. Ddem itent s tezmert, ameô i ugdud ik a tent iîîef s lmaâna nnsent. Ad awen Ssekne tanezdut iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 145,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 168,
            "ruku": 138,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1100,
            "text": "Ad Veôôfe, seg issekniyen iW, wid ismewôen iman nnsen di tmurt, war ssebba. Mi walan yal assekni, ur ppamnen yis. Ma walan abrid uûwib, ur teddun degs. Ma walan abrid n lewlav, a t awin. Ayagi, acku, s tidep, skaddben issekniyen nne£, ur d celâen degsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 146,
            "juz": 9,
