            "page": 168,
            "ruku": 138,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1101,
            "text": "Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, akked temlilit n laxeôt, ur swin igiten nnsen. Day a ten kafin ef wayen ur nelli d ayen xeddmen?",
            "numberInSurah": 147,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 168,
            "ruku": 138,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1102,
            "text": "Agdud n Musa, deffir es, isbedd, s ôôêuê is, aâjmi bu loeppa isrugmuten. Day ur walan ara ar, s tidep, ur asen d ipmeslay, ur la ten inehhu s abrid? Âabden t, llan d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 148,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 168,
            "ruku": 139,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1103,
            "text": "Mi ppuêeccmen, u walan ar, zi nnetlafen, nnan: 'ma ur Iêun ara fella Mass nne, ma ur a Isemmeê ara, war ccekk, a nual seg imexsuôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 149,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 168,
            "ruku": 139,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1104,
            "text": "Mi d iual Musa ar ugdud is, s wurrif akked lêemûa, inna: 'ay d ucmit wayen is iyi tneûfem, deffir iw! Tebam a d iiwwel lameô n Mass nnwen'? Iveggeô tilewêin, iîîef gma s seg uqeôôu, ijebt it id uôes. Inna d: 'a mmi s n yimma, s tidep, iêqeô iyi ugdud, qôib iyi nan. Ur ssefôaê icenga yissi. Ur iyi pparra seg ugdud imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 150,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 169,
            "ruku": 139,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1105,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Semmeê ane, nek akked gma, Ssekcem a ar uêunu K. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun'.",
            "numberInSurah": 151,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 169,
            "ruku": 139,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1106,
            "text": "Ih, wid iâabden aâajmi, a d ili fellasen wurrif n Mass nnsen, ad ndellen di tmeddurt n ddunit. Akka ay Nepqeîîi wid id isnulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 152,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 169,
            "ruku": 140,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1107,
            "text": "Wid ixedmen tucmitin, sinna, steôoâen deffir sent, u umnen, Mass ik, s tidep, deffir sent, ar Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 153,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 169,
            "ruku": 140,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1108,
            "text": "Mi irs wurrif is, iddem ed Musa tilewêin. Di tira nnsent, nnhaya akked uêunu i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 154,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 169,
            "ruku": 140,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1109,
            "text": "Ifren ed Musa ûatet irgazen seg ugdud is, ad mlilen yidne£. Mi ten tewwet zzenzla, inna: 'a Mass iw! Lemmer i K ihwi, yili, iu lêal, Teniv ten, u Tegliv yissi. Day ad a Temêuv, ilmend n wayen xedmen ijelufen segne? Wagi d ahewwel iK kan, Tettellifev syis win i K ihwan, Tnehhuv win i K ihwan. Keçç d Bab nne, Semmeê a, Ëun fella, Keçç Tifev akw wid ipsemmiêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 155,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 169,
            "ruku": 140,
            "hizbQuarter": 67,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1110,
            "text": "Aru ya ise di ddunit, di laxeôt; aql a nual ed uôeK'. Inna d: 'aâaqeb iW, a t Sâaddi ef win iyI ihwan. Aêunu W ijemmel yal cci. A t Aru i wid ipêezziben, ipzekkin, akked wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£,",
            "numberInSurah": 156,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 170,
            "ruku": 140,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1111,
            "text": "wid iteddun d Umazan, Nnbi ur neôi, i ufan iura uôsen di Tuôa akked Linoil'. Iumeô asen d lqanun, Itekkes asen ayen n dir. Iêell asen lâali, igdel asen dduni. Ikkes asen aruz akked lqid nnsen. Ihi, wid iumnen yis, i t iâawnen, i t isellken, iddan d tafat id irsen yides, widak d imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 157,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 170,
            "ruku": 140,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1112,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yimdanen! Nek d Amazan n Öebbi uôwen meôôa. Neppa, ineS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Issidir, Ineqq'. Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, Nnbi ur neôi, i iumnen s Öebbi akked wawal iS. Ddut yides, amar a ppepwanhum.",
            "numberInSurah": 158,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 170,
            "ruku": 141,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
