          },
          {
            "number": 1114,
            "text": "Nessemfaôaq iten ef mrawsin laâôac, n leoyus. Mi s issuter ugdud is tissit, Nweêêa i Musa: ewwet aéôu s tâakwaz ik. Fent ed segs mrawsnat tliwa; akka, yal amdan iéôa anda ara issew. Nesbur iten s usigna, Nessers asen d lmenna akked ifeôôuoen: 'eççet seg wayen ilhan, is ikwen Nat'. Ur a£ dnisen, maca la ddennisen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 160,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 171,
            "ruku": 141,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1115,
            "text": "Mi pwanecden: 'zedet di temdint agi, eççet segs, ayen i wen ihwan, init: 'laâfu'! Âaddit di tebburt, s lekni. Ad awen Nsemmeê tuccva nnwen. A Nernu i lâuûam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 161,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 171,
            "ruku": 141,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1116,
            "text": "Wid idensen segsen, neûfen awalen s wid ur nelli d wid i sen nnan. Nuzen asen tiyta seg igenni, ilmend n wayen ddennisen.",
            "numberInSurah": 162,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 171,
            "ruku": 141,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1117,
            "text": "Steqsi ten ef temdint i illan ef rrif n yill, mi ur d rzin di ssebt, mi ten id usan iselman nnsen, walan ten, ass n ssebt. Ass, war ssebt, ur ten id ppasen. Akka ay ten Njeôôeb, deg wayen ssexsaôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 163,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 171,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1118,
            "text": "Mi d inna lois, segsen: 'iwumi la tepnabim agdud ara Isqucc Öebbi, ne ara Iâaqeb s leqseê'? Nnan: 'd astefeô ar Mass nnwen, amar ad êezzben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 164,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 172,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1119,
            "text": "Mi ppun ayen ief pwafekkôen, Nsellek wid itekksen ayen n dir, Nesâadda aâaqeb adiran ef imednas, ilmend n wayen ssexsaôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 165,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 172,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1120,
            "text": "Mi smewôen iman nnsen ef wayen i sen ipwakksen, Nenna yasen: 'ilit d uddawen ucmiten'!",
            "numberInSurah": 166,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 172,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1121,
            "text": "Mi Ixebbeô Mass ik, ard asen d Iazen ara ten iâaqben, s ééuô, alamma d ass n tnekra. Mass ik, s tidep, Ipawal ar uâaqeb. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 167,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 172,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1122,
            "text": "Nessemfaôaq iten di tmurt, d leoyus, garasen wid imaânen, garasen wid ur nemâin. Njeôôeb iten s iseiyen akked tucmitin, amar a d ualen s abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 168,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 172,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1123,
            "text": "Neûfen ten, deffir sen, ineûûafen i iweôten Tazmamt. Ppaddamen lerbaê n ddunit, qqaôen: 'ad a semmêen'. Ma rnan usan ten id lerbaê, am widen, a ten ddmen. Day ur âahden ara s Tezmamt, ard tidep kan, ara inin ef Öebbi? U lemden i illan degs. Ppif axxam aneggaru, i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tfehmem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 169,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 172,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1124,
            "text": "Wid iîîfen di Tezmamt, ipéallan, s tidep, ur Nveggiâ arraz n lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 170,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 172,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 68,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1125,
            "text": "Mi Nessuli adrar sennig sen, amzun d tili, ilen, s tidep, ara d ili fellasen. Ïîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, smektit ed ayen illan degs, amar a pêezzbem.",
            "numberInSurah": 171,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 142,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1126,
            "text": "Mi d Iddem Mass ik, si tgeééal n tarwa n Adem, dderya nnsen, Inna yasen a d cehhden ef yiman nnsen: 'day ur Lli ara d Mass nnwen'? Nnan: 'ih, ncehhed'. Akka ur d teqqaôem ara, ass n tnekra: 's tidep, ayagi d ayen ur neéôi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 172,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1127,
            "text": "Ne a d tinim: 'd imezwura nne kan i icurken, zik. Nekwni d tarwa deffir sen. Day a Tenev, ilmend n wayen xedmen wid iôejjnen'?",
            "numberInSurah": 173,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1128,
            "text": "Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen, amar a d ualen s abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 174,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1129,
            "text": "Eêku yasen d tadyant n win iwumi Nefka issekniyen nne£. Irra ten akin. Idda yides Cciîan, iual seg wid ieôqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 175,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1130,
            "text": "Lemmer i £ ihwi, Nessuli t yissen. Maca, iba tamurt, idda d lhawiyya s. Ihi, amedya s am win n waydi, ma teddiv p fellas, ad ilehhet, ma teooiv t, ad ilehhet. D wagi ay d amedya n ugdud i iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Eêku d tadyant, amar a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 176,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1131,
            "text": "Agdud iskaddben issekniyen nne£, d yir amedya. Pddennisen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 177,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1132,
            "text": "Win Inha Öebbi, ihi, idda d ubrid. Wid Itlef Öebbi, nitni d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 178,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 173,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1133,
            "text": "Ni Neswejd ed, i Loahennama, aîas n leonun akked yimdanen. Sâan ulawen, ur fehhmen yissen; sâan allen, ur pwalin yissent; sâan imeééuen, ur sellen yissen. Nitni am lmal, ne nnetlafen kteô. Wigi d iwefliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 179,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1134,
            "text": "I Öebbi, ismawen ûûam. Naâôet eP, yissen. Veôôfet seg wid issexsaôen ismawen iS. Ad ppuqeîîin ef wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 180,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1135,
            "text": "Deg wayen Nexleq, yiwen n lois ivfeô tidep. Ipêuddu syis.",
            "numberInSurah": 181,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 143,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1136,
            "text": "Wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£, a ten Nawi, cwiî, cwiî, ar wanda ur éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 182,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 144,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1137,
            "text": "Ad asen Fke lmudda. Ih, ticeôkep iW d tunûiêt.",
            "numberInSurah": 183,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 144,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1138,
            "text": "Day ur d tepmeyyizem ara? Ur illi umeddakwel nnwen d aôehbani. Neppa, d aneddaô kan ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 184,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 144,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1139,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara tagelda n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen Ixleq Öebbi n cci? Ni, ahat, iqeôb ed lajel nnsen. Anwa awal, deffir wagi, ar amnen?",
            "numberInSurah": 185,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 144,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1140,
            "text": "Win Itlef Öebbi, ur Isâi nnahi. A ten Ioo ad hemlen di tjehli nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 186,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 144,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1141,
            "text": "A k steqsayen ef yimir, melmi ara d yili. Ini: 'i t Iéôan siwa Mass iw. D Neppa kan a t id Isseknen, di lweqt is. Ad iaéay di tmurt akked igenwan. Ur kwen id ippawev siwa deqzalla'. A k steqsayen amzun tesâiv asali fellas. Ini: 'i t Issnen siwa ÔÖebbi', maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 187,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 174,
            "ruku": 144,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1142,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur ksibe i iman iw, abauô ne vveôô, kkes ed ayen Irad Öebbi. Lemmer ssine tabavnit, ad ôwu lxiô, ur iyi ipnal ixmiô. Nek d aneddaô kan, u d abcir, i ugdud iumnen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 188,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 144,
            "hizbQuarter": 69,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1143,
            "text": "D Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen si yiwen n yiman. Iddem ed segs tameîîut is, ad izde yides. Mi insa yides, tebbwi tadist tafessast; telêa yis. Mi d teûbeê ééayet, naâôen Öebbi: 'a Mass nne! Ma Tefkiv a d aâeôvi, war ccekk, a nili seg wid isnemmiren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 189,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1144,
            "text": "Mi sen d Ifka aâeôdi, rran aS icriken s wayen i sen d Ifka. I aâlay Öebbi, sennig wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 190,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1145,
            "text": "Day ad carken ayen ur nexliq acemma, u d nitni i ipwaxelqen?",
            "numberInSurah": 191,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1146,
            "text": "Ur zmiren a ten âiwnen, ne ad âiwnen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 192,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1147,
            "text": "Ma tnecdem ten ar nnhaya, ur teddun yidwen. Iâuva fellawen ma tnecdem ten, ne ma tessusmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 193,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1148,
            "text": "S tidep, wigi tnaâôem, war Öebbi, d imdanen am kunwi. Naâret pen, ma ad awen d rren, maday tessawalem tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 194,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1149,
            "text": "Day sâan ivaôen, ad lêun fellasen, ne sâan ifassen, ad ddmen yissen, ne sâan allen, ad walin yisent, ne sâan imeééuen, ad slen yissen. Ini: 'naâret icriken nnwen, sinna, andit iyi. Ur iyi sganayet'.",
            "numberInSurah": 195,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 175,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1150,
            "text": "Ih, Bab iw d Öebbi id Issersen Tazmamt, i Iêemmlen lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 196,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1151,
            "text": "Wid tnaâôem, war Neppa, ur zmiren a kwen âawnen, ne ad âawnen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 197,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1152,
            "text": "Ma tnecdem ten ar nnhaya, ur sellen. A ten twaliv a k id pmuqulen, nitni ur pwalin.",
            "numberInSurah": 198,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1153,
            "text": "Ddem ayen ilhan, ameô ar lewqama, veôôef i wid ur nessin.",
            "numberInSurah": 199,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1154,
            "text": "Ma ilaâj ik Cciîan ar dduni, ppkel ef Öebbi. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 200,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1155,
            "text": "Ih, wid ipêezziben, ma innul iten urbaâ n ccwaîen, a d mmektin, da ad asen llint wallen.",
            "numberInSurah": 201,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1156,
            "text": "Zgan elîen atmaten nnsen, da nitni ur xevvun.",
            "numberInSurah": 202,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1157,
            "text": "Ma ur asen d tebbwiv ara assekni, ad ak inin: 'acimi ur t id isnulfa ara'? Ini: 'teddu kan d wayen iyi d ippuweêêan, suô Mass iw'. Wagi, suô Mass nnwen, d tafat, d nnhaya, d aêunu, i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 203,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1158,
            "text": "Ma qqaôen Leqwôan ssemêesset as, ssusmet, amar fellawen aêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 204,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1159,
            "text": "Mmekti d Mass ik, deg iman ik, s wannuz akked lxuf, s wawal irsen, taûebêit, tameddit. Ur ppili seg iwefliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 205,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1160,
            "text": "Ih, wid illan ar Mass ik, ur smewôen ara iman nnsen, ef uâbad iS. Sbuccuâen T, i Neppa kennun.",
            "numberInSurah": 206,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 176,
            "ruku": 145,
            "hizbQuarter": 70,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 1,
              "recommended": true,
              "obligatory": false
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 8,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الأَنفَالِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Anfaal",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Spoils of War",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 1161,
            "text": "Steqsan k ef rrbeê. Ini: 'rrbeê i Öebbi akked Umazan. Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, elhut garawen, aet awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ma d lmumnin ay tellam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 177,
            "ruku": 146,
            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1162,
            "text": "Lmumnin d wid kan iwumi ippergigi wul nnsen, ma Ipwabder ed Öebbi. Ma ôan asen issekniyen iS, ad innerni liman nnsen. £ef Mass nnsen, ay ppeklen.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 177,
            "ruku": 146,
            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1163,
            "text": "Wid ibedden i téallit, ipûeôôifen seg wayen is iten Nat.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 177,
            "ruku": 146,
            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1164,
            "text": "Wigi d ûûeê, d lmumnin. I nitni, ar Mass nnsen, tiseddaôin, ssmaê, akked lit uùkyis.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 177,
            "ruku": 146,
            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1165,
            "text": "Akken ik id Issuffe Mass ik, seg uxxam ik, s tidep, wanag ur ibi urbaâ si lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 177,
            "ruku": 146,
            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1166,
            "text": "La k pnamaren ef tidep, deffir ubeggen is, amzun kan pwanehôen ar tmeppant, nitni pêekkiôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 177,
            "ruku": 146,
            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1167,
            "text": "Mi wen Iâahed Öebbi, ara ppili nnwen, yiwet si snat n trebbuyaâ, tessarmem a ppili nnwen tin ur nepwaselleê. Öebbi Iba a d itebbet tidep s wawalen iS, ad ôéen wakali ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 9,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 177,
