            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1170,
            "text": "Irra t kan Öebbi d abecceô iwakken ad nnevmanen yis wulawen nnwen. Ur illi lelb, siwa suô Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
