            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1171,
            "text": "Mi kwen Iumm s yives, d îîmana suôeS; Isseli d fellawen aman seg igenni; a kwen Izzizdeg yissen, ad Issebâad, fellawen, away n Cciîan, ad Isseohed ulawen nnwen, ad Itebbet, yissen, isurifen.",
