            "hizbQuarter": 71,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1173,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku nitni, s tidep, xuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS. I win ixuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ihi, Öebbi Iwâaô deg uâaqeb.",
