          },
          {
            "number": 1184,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Jawbet i Öebbi akked Umazan, ma Inced ikwen ar wayen ikwen issidiren. Cfut ar Öebbi Ippili ger umdan akked wul is. £uôeS, Neppa, s tidep, ara tepwafessrem.",
