            "hizbQuarter": 72,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1186,
            "text": "Mmektit ed mi, kunwi, drus ay tellam, d uôhifen di tmurt, teppagwadem a kwen xevfen medden. Iûûeô ikwen, Isellek ikwen s lelb iS, Iat ikwen s wayen ilhan, amender ma a ppesnemmrem.",
