            "hizbQuarter": 72,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1188,
            "text": "Cfut ar, ayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen, d ahewwel kan, u ar £uô Öebbi, ôôaîeb ameqwôaêan.",
