            "page": 180,
            "ruku": 149,
            "hizbQuarter": 72,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1190,
            "text": "Ma ppandin ak, wid ijehlen, iwakken a k êebsen, ne a k nen, ne a k ssuffen; ppandin u Öebbi Ippandi. Öebbi Yif akw imendayen.",
