            "hizbQuarter": 72,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1191,
            "text": "Ma ôan asen issekniyen nne£, ad inin: 'ih, nesla. Ma ihwa ya a d nini am ayagi. Ayagi, s tidep, siwa d timucuha imezwura'.",
