            "ruku": 150,
            "hizbQuarter": 73,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1204,
            "text": "Mi wen ten Issenâat, mi ten temmugrem, twalam ten d takwemmict. Iééeméi kwen ar tmuli nnsen, iwakken ad Isâaddi Öebbi lameô ara iâaddin. Ar Öebbi ppualen lumuô.",
