            "text": "Lemmer a pwaliv mara ddment lmalayek leôwaê n wid ijehlen, ad kkatent udmawen nnsen, izugar nnsen. 'Jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmeôiwt!",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
