            "hizbQuarter": 73,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1212,
            "text": "Am tikli n ugdud n Ferâun akked wid i ten id izwaren. Nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi. Issemêaleq asen Öebbi s ibekkaven nnsen. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, Iqseê deg uâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
