            "ruku": 152,
            "hizbQuarter": 73,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1213,
            "text": "Akka, acku Öebbi ur Ipbeddil lit is Iat agdud, alamma bedlen i illan deg iman nnsen. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
