            "text": "Ma ban a k xedâan, ihi, âammed ef Öebbi, Neppa i k Ifkan afus s tallalt iS, akked lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 153,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1223,
            "text": "Issemlal ulawen nnsen. Lemmer a pûeôfev i illan akw di tmurt, ur tessemliliv ulawen nnsen. Maca, Öebbi Issemlal iten. Neppa, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 153,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1224,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Âammed ef Öebbi, keçç, akked wid iddan yidek si lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 153,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1225,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Eg lêir i lmumnin, ad nnaen. Ma llan segwen warem iûebôiyen, ad rnun snat twinas. Ma llan segwen twinas, ad rnun agim n wid ijehlen, acku, nitni d agdud ur nfehhem.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 154,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1226,
            "text": "Tura, Issafes Öebbi fellawen. Iéôa tella garawen rrehma. Ihi, ma llan segwen twinas iûebôiyen, ad rnun snat twinas, ma llan segwen agim, ad rnun sin igima, ma Irad Öebbi. Öebbi ar iûebôiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 154,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1227,
            "text": "Ur issefk ara i Nnbi ad isâu imeêbas, alamma pwaelben di tmurt. Tebam tukci n ddunit. Öebbi Iba laxeôt. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 154,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1228,
            "text": "Lemmer maççi d ayen iuran suô Öebbi, izwar ed, yili a kwen iwwet uâaqeb abarar, ilmend n wayen tebbwim.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 154,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1229,
            "text": "Eççet ayen ilhan, iêellen, seg wayen i telltem, êezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 185,
            "ruku": 154,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1230,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Ini i wid teîîfem seg imeêbas: 'ma Iufa Öebbi lxiô deg ulawen nnwen, ad awen Ifk ayen yifen ayen i wen ipwakksen, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 186,
            "ruku": 155,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1231,
            "text": "Ma ban a k xedâan, ni iu lêal xedâen Öebbi. Da, Ikkes asen ôôay. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 186,
            "ruku": 155,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1232,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen, iunagen, ijuhden s wayla nnsen, akked yiman nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, wid isnubgten u fkan afus, widak d imeddukwal bwaygarasen. Wid iumnen ur unagen, ur awen llin d imeddukwal, s wacemma, alamma unagen. Ma ppren afus nnwen di ddin, iwata yawen ad asen tefkem afus, siwa mgal agdud ukud tâaqdem. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 186,
            "ruku": 155,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1233,
            "text": "Wid ijehlen d imeddukwal bwaygarasen. Ma ur tgim ara akka, a ppili lfetna di tmurt, akked usefsed ameqwôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 186,
            "ruku": 155,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1234,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, iunagen, ijuhden deg ubrid n Öebbi, wid isnubgten u fkan afus, widak, s tidep, d lmumnin. I nitni ssmaê akked lit ukyis.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 186,
            "ruku": 155,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1235,
            "text": "Wid iumnen syin er da, u unagen, u juhden yidwen, widak segwen. Llzem ppemyilin kteô di Tezmamt n Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Izôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 186,
            "ruku": 155,
            "hizbQuarter": 74,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 9,
        "name": "سُورَةُ التَّوۡبَةِ",
        "englishName": "At-Tawba",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Repentance",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 1236,
            "text": "Öebbi akked Umazan iS kksen aêeppem i imcurak ukud tâaqqdem.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 187,
            "ruku": 156,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1237,
            "text": "Ddut di tmurt kué wagguren. Cfut ar kunwi ur tesfunnugem i Öebbi, u Öebbi ad Isdull ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 187,
            "ruku": 156,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1238,
            "text": "Aberreê i medden, suô Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ass n êioo ameqwôaêan, ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, kksen aêeppem i imcurak. 'Ma testeôoâam, ppif i kunwi, ma twexxôem, cfut ar kunwi ur tesfunnugem i Öebbi'. Becceô wid ijehlen s uâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 187,
            "ruku": 156,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1239,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid ukud tâaqqdem seg imcurak, sinna ur kwen bbwiven s wacemma, ur ullen yiwen mgal nnwen. Ïîfet di lemâahda nnsen ar lmudda s. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 187,
            "ruku": 156,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1240,
            "text": "Mi âaddan wagguren iôqan, nnaet imcurak anda ten tufam. Ïîfet pen, êeôset pen, andit asen yal taxettalt. Ma steôoâan, ééulen, zekkan, ooet asen abrid. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 187,
            "ruku": 156,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1241,
            "text": "Ma issuter ak laânaya, yiwen seg imcurak, êareb fellas, ard issel i wawal n Öebbi, sinna, ssiwev it s amkan is n laman. Akka, acku nitni, s tidep, d agdud ur nessin.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 187,
            "ruku": 156,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1242,
            "text": "Amek ara tili i imcurak, lemâahda suô Öebbi u suô Umazan iS, siwa wid tâahdem ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam. Skud sweqmen yidwen, sweqmet yidsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 188,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1243,
            "text": "Amek, mi kwen elben, ur kwen qudôen ilmend n yies, ne n lemâahda. Öuvan kwen s imawen nnsen; ulawen nnsen ugin. Tegwti segsen d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 188,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1244,
            "text": "Uen s issekniyen n Öebbi ayen ôxisen. Ssefôaen ef ubrid iS. S tidep, ay dir wayen xeddmen nitni!",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 188,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1245,
            "text": "Ur qudôen lmumen ilmend n yies, ne n lemâahda. Wigi, ih, d wid izegren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 188,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1246,
            "text": "Ma steôoâan, ééulen, zekkan, d atmaten nnwen di ddin. Nepfeûûil issekniyen i ugdud issnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 188,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1247,
            "text": "Ma sêenten tagalit nnsen, deffir lemâahda nnsen, u wwten di ddin nnwen, nnaet iqweôôa n tijehli. Nitni, s tidep, ur ppaîafen di tgallit. Amar ad fukken.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 188,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1248,
            "text": "Day ur tepnaem ara agdud i isêenten tagalit nnsen, u iban ad ssuffen Amazan, u nitni heomen kwen d imezwura? Day ten tugadem? D Öebbi i iklalen a T tagwadem, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 188,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1249,
            "text": "Nnaet pen, a ten Iâaqeb Öebbi s ufus nnwen, a ten Ixzu, a kwen Iserbeê fellasen, ad Icfu idmaren n ugdud n lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 189,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1250,
            "text": "Ad Ikkes urrif n wulawen nnsen. Öebbi Issuruf i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 189,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1251,
            "text": "Day tilem a ppepwaterkem, wanag ur Iéôi Öebbi wid, degwen, ijuhden, ur neddi d imawlan, war Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked lmumnin? Öebbi Iéôa ay txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 189,
            "ruku": 157,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1252,
            "text": "Ur issefk ara i imcurak ad kecmen leowamaâ n Öebbi, ad cehhden ef tijehli nnsen. Widak neqven igiten nnsen, di tmes ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 189,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1253,
            "text": "Ara ikecmen kan leowamaâ n Öebbi, d wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, iééulen, izekkan, ippagwaden siwa Öebbi. Ahat wigi ad ilin seg wid ipwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 189,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 75,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1254,
            "text": "Day terram win i isswan iéaâlak, i ibedden i Loamaâ n Lêaôam, am win iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru u innu deg ubrid n Öebbi? Ur aâdilen ar Öebbi. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 189,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1255,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, iunagen, u nnuen deg ubrid n Öebbi s wayla nnsen akked iman nnsen, aâlay umekkan nnsen, ar Öebbi. Wigi d wid ara irebêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 189,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1256,
            "text": "Ibecceô iten Mass nnsen s uêunu suôeS, akked llza, akked leonanat, degsen ssaâd imezgi;",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 190,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1257,
            "text": "ad wekkôen degsen i lebda. Ih, ar Öebbi, arraz ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 190,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1258,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur pparat d imawlan, ibabaten nnwen akked watmaten nnwen, ma smenyafen tijehli i liman. Wid segwen i ten iran d imawlan, ad ilin, nitni, d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 190,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1259,
            "text": "Ini: 'maday, sennig Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked umennu deg ubrid iS, ay têemmlem ibabaten nnwen, tarwa nnwen, atmaten nnwen, tilawin nnwen, alag nnwen, ayla i tkesbem, ttjaôa i tugadem a ppeli, tinezduin i kwen iâaoben, ihi, gganit ar d Ias Öebbi, s lameô iS. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 190,
            "ruku": 158,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1260,
            "text": "Ni Isrebê ikwen Öebbi deg waîas imukan, akked wass n Ëunain, mi kwen taâoeb îîaqa nnwen. Ur awen d tebbwi acemma. Tamurt iwsâan, tual awen tediyeq. Da tezzim d, trewlem.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 190,
            "ruku": 159,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1261,
            "text": "Sinna, Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS ef Umazan iS, akked lmumnin, Issers ed iâsekôiwen ur tepwalim. Iâaqeb wid ijehlen. D wagi ay d aqeîîi ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 190,
            "ruku": 159,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1262,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir waya, Öebbi Issuruf i win i S ihwan. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 191,
            "ruku": 159,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1263,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Imcurak maâfunit kan. Ur d pqeôôiben ar Loamaâ n Lêaôam, mara ifukk useggwas agi nnsen. Ma tugadem lqella, a kwen Iit Öebbi, s lfevl iS, ma ihwa yaS. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 191,
            "ruku": 159,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1264,
            "text": "Nnaet wid ur numin ara s Öebbi, u s wass aneggaru, ur pgeddilen ayen Igdel Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur xeddmen ddin n tidep, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, alamma xelûen tabzert s war amunnu, d imejjîuêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 191,
            "ruku": 159,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1265,
            "text": "Nnan wudayen: 'Âuzayeô d mmi S n Öebbi'. Nnan imasiêiyen: 'lmasiê d mmi S n Öebbi'. Ayagi, nnan t id s imawen nnsen. Ppaâwaden d awal n wid ijehlen, n zik. A ten Ine Öebbi! Acêal îeôôifen!",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 191,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1266,
            "text": "Rran lquôôaê nnsen, ixelwiyen nnsen, lmasiê mmi s n Meryem, d imawlan war Öebbi. Pwamôen kan ad âabden Öebbi Yiwen; ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Gedha syiS, seg wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 191,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1267,
            "text": "Ban s yimawen nnsen ad ssexsin tafat n Öebbi. I Iba Öebbi, ad Itim kan tafat iS, di nneqwma ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 192,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1268,
            "text": "D Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS, s nnhaya akked ddin n tidep, iwakken a t Issifer ef ddin meôôa, xas ugin ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 192,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 76,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1269,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Aîas n lqweôôaê d ixelwiyen, s tidep, teppen d aêerfi ayla n medden. U îeôôifen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Wid ixeznen ddheb d lfeîîa, ur ten pseddiqen deg ubrid n Öebbi, becceô iten s uâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 192,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1270,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ôen di tmes n Loahennama, ad kwin, yissen, inyiren nnsen, ibeôdiyen nnsen, iârar nnsen. 'D ayagi ay txezznem i iman nnwen. Jeôôbet ayen txezznem!'",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 192,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1271,
            "text": "Ih, ar Öebbi, amvan n wagguren: mrawsin; di Tezmamt n Öebbi, ass ideg Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan. Garasen, kué ôqan. D wagi ay d ddin n ddwam. Ur ddenniset iman nnwen degsen. Nnaet ijehliyen ef ccfa, akken i kwen nnuen ef ccfa. Cfut, Öebbi Iteddu d wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 192,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1272,
            "text": "Aswexxeô n waggur d timerniwt kan n tijehli. Nnetlafen yis wid ijehlen. Aseggwas a t êellen, aseggwas a t gedlen, iwakken ad wafqen amvan n wayen Igdel Öebbi. Ad êellen ayen Igdel Öebbi. Âaoben ten yir igiten nnsen. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 193,
            "ruku": 160,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1273,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Acu kwen iuen? Ma nnan awen: 'hejjmet ar ubrid n Öebbi', a ppebrum i iman nnwen. Day kwen taâoeb tmeddurt n ddunit, sennig tin n laxeôt? Zzhu n tmeddurt n ddunit d amejîiîuê kan, zdat win n laxeôt.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 193,
            "ruku": 161,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1274,
            "text": "Ma ur tehjjimem ara, a kwen Iâaqeb s lqeôê, a d Iawi agdud nniven, deg umekkan nnwen. Ur T teîîuôum s wacemma. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 193,
            "ruku": 161,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1275,
            "text": "Ma ur t tsellkem, ihi, Isellek it Öebbi, mi t ssuffen wid ijehlen. Wissin n sin, mi llan deg ifri, mi inna i umeddakwel is: 'kkes awbel, Öebbi, s tidep, yidne'. Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS fellas, Iâawen it s iâsekriwen, ur ten twalam. Isseli mavi awal n wid ijehlen. Awal n Öebbi, neppa, aâlay sennig akw. Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 193,
            "ruku": 161,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1276,
            "text": "Hejjmet fessusit u ééayit, juhdet s wayla nnwen akked yiman nnwen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ppif wakka i kunwi, lemmer teéôim.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 194,
            "ruku": 161,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1277,
            "text": "Lemmer d abauô isehlen, d inig wezzilen, yili vefôen k in. Maca, wezzif fellasen umecwaô. Ad ggalen s Öebbi: 'lemmer nezmir, yili neffe yidwen'. Nnan iman nnsen, Öebbi Iéôa ar nitni, war ccekk, d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 194,
            "ruku": 161,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1278,
            "text": "Ad ak Isemmeê Öebbi! Acimi i sen tserêev? Ard ak d iban anwi innan tidep, a ppissinev ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 194,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1279,
            "text": "Ur ak d ssutren ara tsriê, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, mi juhden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Öebbi Issen wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 194,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1280,
            "text": "I k issutren tsriê, d wid ur numin s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Cukken wulawen nnsen, da, s ucukku nnsen, kukran.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 194,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 77,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1281,
            "text": "Lemmer bin tuffa, yili heggan as d ayen ilaqen. Maca, Iugi Öebbi ad ppucegâan, Iurez iten. Nnan asen: 'qqimet d wid iqqimen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 194,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1282,
            "text": "Lemmer ffien yidwen, ar awen rnun siwa ccwal. War ccekk, ad kecmen garawen, ban ahewwel nnwen. Kra segwen ssemêasen asen. Öebbi Issen imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 194,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1283,
            "text": "Ni ban, si zik, ahewwel. Sxeôben ak lumuô, armi d tusa tidep. Ivehô ed lameô n Öebbi, nitni ur bin.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 195,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1284,
            "text": "Garasen win id innan: 'serreê iyi, ur iyi gar di lfetna'! Day ur lin ara di lfetna? Loahennama, s tidep, a ppezzi i ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 195,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1285,
            "text": "Ma iusa k id yise ad weblen. Ma tusa k id twait, ad inin: 'ni, iu lêal, neqva lameô nne'. Ad wexxôen, zzhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 195,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1286,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur a ipêaz wacemma, siwa ayen i  Iura Öebbi'. Neppa d Bab nne. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 195,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1287,
            "text": "Ini: 'acu teggunim ad ivôu yidne, siwa yiwen si sin iseiyen? Nekwni negguni a kwen Iwwet Öebbi, s uâaqeb ara d iasen suôeS, ne seg ifassen nne. Ihi gganit, nekwni a neggani yidwen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 195,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1288,
            "text": "Ini: 'seddqet, tebam ne tugim, d ayen ur neppwaqbal segwen, d awezi. Kunwi, s tidep, d agdud iballaen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 195,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1289,
            "text": "Ay sen ikksen a tepwaqbal ssadaqa nnsen, imi kan jehlen, s tidep, ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u s laâgez kan ay d ppasen ar tpéallit, s usmiglez kan ay pseddiqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 195,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1290,
            "text": "Ur k ippaâoab wayla nnsen, ne tarwa nnsen. Iba kan Öebbi a ten Iâaqeb yissen di tmeddurt n ddunit, ad iffe ôôuê nnsen, nitni d ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 196,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1291,
            "text": "Ad ggalen s Öebbi, ar nitni, war ccekk, segwen. Ur nitni segwen, maca d agdud iugaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 196,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1292,
            "text": "Lemmer ad afen ssôan, ne ifran, ne anda ara kecmen, ad ôuêen uôes s tazla.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 196,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1293,
            "text": "Garasen, wid ikkaten deg k, ef ssadaqat. Ma ippunefk asen segsent, ad ôavin, ma ur asen ippunefk, ad neêwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 196,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1294,
            "text": "Lemmer nitni, s tidep, ôuvan ayen i sen Ifka Öebbi akked Umazan iS, u nnan d: 'nesteqnaâ s Öebbi. Ad a d Ifk, si lfevl iS, Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ih, d Öebbi ief neôeb'.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 196,
            "ruku": 162,
            "hizbQuarter": 78,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1295,
            "text": "Ssadaqat siwa i imeban, iéawaliyen, i wid icewlen degsent, i usemlili n wulawen, i userreê imeêbas, i imeîîulba, i ubrid n Öebbi, i win d ifka ubrid. D aêeppem suô Öebbi. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 196,
            "ruku": 163,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1296,
            "text": "Garasen, wid icettmen deg Umazan, qqaôen: 'neppa d aêessas'. Ini: 'd aêessas n lxiô i kunwi. Iumen s Öebbi, iumen lmumnin. D aêunu i wid iumnen segwen'. I wid icettmen deg Umazan n Öebbi, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 196,
            "ruku": 163,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1297,
            "text": "Ad awen ggalen s Öebbi, iwakken a kwen ôavin. Öebbi akked Umazan iS, Iklal kteô a T ôavin, lemmer llin d lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 197,
            "ruku": 163,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1298,
            "text": "Day ur éôin ara ar, win ixuûmen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, i neppa times n Loahennama, ad iwekkeô degs? D wagi ay d ddell abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 197,
            "ruku": 163,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1299,
            "text": "Ixabiten ugaden ad asen d ters tsuôep, ad asen tessken i illan deg ulawen nnsen. Ini: 'mmaâlket. Öebbi, s tidep, a d Issuffe ayen tugadem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 197,
            "ruku": 163,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1300,
            "text": "Ma testeqsav ten, a d inin, war ccekk: 'la nheddeô kan, nepqessiô'. Ini: 'day la tettihim di Öebbi akked issekniyen iS, akked Umazan iS?",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 197,
            "ruku": 163,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1301,
            "text": "Ur steôoiâat. Ni tualem ar tijehli, deffir liman nnwen'. Ma Nsemmeê i urbaâ segwen, a Naâqeb arbaâ, imi nitni llan d ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 197,
            "ruku": 163,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1302,
            "text": "Ixabiten akked txabitin, wa ippameô i wa, ayen n dir, ppemyegdalen lewqama, pcuddun ifassen nnsen. Ppun Öebbi, Ippu ten. Ih, ixabiten d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 197,
            "ruku": 164,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1303,
            "text": "Iwaââed Öebbi, i ixabiten, txabitin, akked ijehliyen, times n Loahennama, degs ad wekkôen. Beôka ten. Ixza ten Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb imezgi,",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 197,
            "ruku": 164,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1304,
            "text": "am imezwura nnwen. Llan ifen kwen tazmert, elben kwen ayla, tarwa. Zhan deg umur nnsen, tezham deg umur nnwen, akken zhan imezwura nnwen deg umur nnsen. Teccvem akken ccven nitni. Widak, mêan igiten nnsen di ddunit, di laxeôt. Widak d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 198,
            "ruku": 164,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1305,
            "text": "Day ur ten id iusa ara usali imezwura nnsen? Agdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, agdud n Ibôahim, At Median, tid ippin. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen. Ur ten Idennis Öebbi, maca llan dennisen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 198,
            "ruku": 164,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1306,
            "text": "Lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, d imeddukal wa n wa. Ppamôen lewqama, pgeddilen ayen n dir. Péallan, pzekkin, ppaen awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Wigi, ad Iêun Öebbi fellasen. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 198,
            "ruku": 164,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1307,
            "text": "Iwaââed Öebbi i lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen; ixxamen igerzen di leonanat n Âaden, akked llza suô Öebbi - iten ielben akw -. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 198,
            "ruku": 164,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1308,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Jahed ijehliyen akked ixabiten. Iqsiê uôsen. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d taggara tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 199,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1309,
            "text": "Ggulen s Öebbi ur d nnin, wanag nnan awal n tijehli. Jehlen deffir wannuz nnsen. Vemâen ayen iwumi ur wâan. Ur êzinen imi iten Iat, si lfevl iS, Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma steôoâen, yif it i nitni. Ma wexxôen, a ten Iâaqeb Öebbi s leqôeê, di ddunit, di laxeôt. Ur sâun, di tmurt, bab ne amâiwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 199,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 79,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1310,
            "text": "Garasen, wid iâahden Öebbi: 'ma Ifka ya d, si lfevl iS, a nseddeq, a nili si lâuûam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 199,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1311,
            "text": "Mi sen Ifka si lfevl iS, a t bexwlen, ad wexxôen, ad namren.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 199,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1312,
            "text": "Issegwra yasen d tanaâuôt deg ulawen nnsen, ar ass ideg ara mlilen yideS, imi xedan Öebbi deg wayen i S âahden, imi llan skiddiben.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 199,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1313,
            "text": "Day ur éôin ara Öebbi Issen sser nnsen akked wayen qqaôen u, ar Öebbi Issen tibavniyin?",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 199,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1314,
            "text": "Wid ipqeôôiven di lmumnin i iban ad seddqen, u deg wid i iufan siwa tazmert nnsen, da ttihin fellasen; ad Ittihi Öebbi fellasen. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 199,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1315,
            "text": "Ssuter ad ppusemmêen, ne qqim. Ma tessutrev ûavet iberdan, ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awezi. Akka, imi nitni jehlen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 200,
            "ruku": 165,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1316,
            "text": "Wid igwran, feôêen mi llan deffir Umazan n Öebbi. Ugin ad nnaen s wayla nnsen akked teôwiêt nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Nnan: 'Ur pôuêut deg unauô'. Ini: 'times n Loahennama teêma kteô, lemmer day fehhmen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 200,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1317,
            "text": "Anef ad vsen cwiî, ad run aîas, d aqeîîi n wayen keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 200,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1318,
            "text": "Ma Irra k id Öebbi ar urbaâ segsen, u ssutren ak d tsriê ad ffen, ini: 'd awezi, ur teppeffem yidi, ur tepnaem acengu yidi. Akken, kunwi, iâoeb ikwen iimi, abrid amenzu, ihi, qqimet akked ineggura.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 200,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1319,
            "text": "Ur péalla ef yiwen degsen, ma immut, d awezi. Ur pbedda ar tenîelt is. Nitni, s tidep, jehlen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, mmuten nitni d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 200,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1320,
            "text": "Ur k ippaâoab wayla nnsen, ne dderya nnsen. Öebbi Iba kan a ten Iâaqeb yissen di ddunit, ad asen teffe taôwiêt nitni d ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 200,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1321,
            "text": "Ma ters ed tsuôep: 'amnet s Öebbi, jahdet akked Umazan iS', imeôkantiyen nnsen a k ssutren tsriê, ad inin: 'anef ane ar wid iqqimen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 200,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1322,
            "text": "Öuvan ad ilin akked wid igwran. Ppuselen wulawen nnsen, ur fehhmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 201,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1323,
            "text": "Maca, amazan akked wid iumnen yides, jehden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Widak, nnsen lxiô. Widak, d nitni ara irebêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 201,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1324,
            "text": "Ihegga yasen d Öebbi leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 201,
            "ruku": 166,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1325,
            "text": "Wid id iufan ssebba, seg waâôaben n ucluê, usan d, ad asen ifk tsriê. Wid iskaddben Öebbi akked Umazan iS, qqimen. Wid ijehlen, segsen, ad sâaddin aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 201,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1326,
            "text": "Ur telli tuzzma ef uôhifen, imuvan, wid ur nufi ara fken, ma neûêen ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ur telli tuzzma ef iâaôviyen. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 201,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1327,
            "text": "Am akken, i wid ik id iusan a ten tneqqlev, tenniv: 'ur awen ufi ara kwen ineqqlen'. Ualen, allen feggvent seg imeîîawen, weblen imi ur ufin ara sedqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 10,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 201,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 80,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1328,
            "text": "Tuzzma kan ef wid ik issuturen tsriê, nitni d imeôkantiyen. Öuvan ad ilin akked ineggura. Isle Öebbi ulawen nnsen, da ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 201,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1329,
            "text": "Ad awen ssutren ssmaê, ma tualem d uôsen. Ini: 'ur ssuturet ssmaê, ur kwen numin d awezi. Ni Imla ya Öebbi asali nnwen. Ad Iéeô Öebbi akked Umazan iS, igiten nnwen. Sinna, a ppualem ar Umusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir, ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 202,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1330,
            "text": "Ad awen gren Öebbi, mi d tualem uôsen, iwakken ad asen tanfem. Wexxeôt asen; nitni, s tidep, d laâôuô; axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d aqeîîi n wayen keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 202,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1331,
            "text": "Ad awen ggalen iwakken a ten tôavim. Ma tôuvam ten, ihi, Öebbi ur Ipôavi agdud iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 202,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1332,
            "text": "Aâôaben n ucluê zaden di tijehli akked nnxayel, zeggwiren ar uzgar n tilas id Issers Öebbi i Umazan iS. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 202,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1333,
            "text": "Ger waâôaben n ucluê, wid iêesben ayen seddqen d tabzert. Ggunin a ppekêes fellawen teswiât. Fellasen abeddel adiran n teswiât! Öebbi Issel, Issen.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 202,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1334,
            "text": "Ger waâôaben n ucluê, wid iumnen s Öebbi d wass aneggaru, êesben ayen seddqen a ten iééié ar Öebbi akked téilla Umazan. Day maççi, s tidep, d ayen ara ten iééiéen? A ten Issekcem Öebbi deg uêunu S. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 202,
            "ruku": 167,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1335,
            "text": "Imenza i izwaren, seg iminigen, imâiwnen, akked wid i ten iâanden ar lewqama, Iôuva ten Öebbi, ôuvan T. Ihegga yasen d leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen degsen, i lebda. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 203,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1336,
            "text": "Ger waâôaben n ucluê, i wen d izzin, llan at sin wudmawen, akw ger imezda n Lmadina. Zgan di nnxayel. Ur ten tessinev. Nekwni, Nessen iten. A ten Nâaqeb berdayen, sinna, ad ppunefken i uâaqeb abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 203,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1337,
            "text": "Wiyad qaôôen s ibekkaven nnsen, ssemlalen igi ilhan d win nniven icemten. Izmer Öebbi ad asen Issuref. S tidep, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 203,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1338,
            "text": "Eddem ed ssadaqa seg wayla nnsen, a ten tezzizdeg, a ten tûeffi. èÈéal ilmend nnsen. Ih, tiéilla k d talwit nnsen. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 203,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1339,
            "text": "Day ur éôin ara Öebbi, Neppa, Iqebbel asteôoaâ suô ixdimen iS? Ippaîaf ssadaqat. Ih, Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 203,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1340,
            "text": "Ini: 'xedmet! Ad Iwali igiten nnwen, Öebbi, Umazan iS, akked lmumnin. Tualin nnwen ar Umusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir, ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 203,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1341,
            "text": "Wiyav pganin lameô n Öebbi, a ten Iâaqeb, ne ad asen Issuref. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 203,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1342,
            "text": "Wid irran loamaâ i lemveôôa akked tijehli, i lefôaq ger lmumnin; d taxettalt i wid, iu lêal, llan pnaen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad ggalen, war ccekk: 'ay neba siwa lewqama'. Ad Icehhed Öebbi ar nitni, s tidep, d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 204,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1343,
            "text": "Ur ppili, degs, d awezi. Iklal kteô, tilin ik, loamaâ ibnan ef uêezzeb, seg wass amenzu. Degs irgazen i iêemmlen ad izdigen. Öebbi Iêemmel izedganen.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 204,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1344,
            "text": "Day win issersen lebni s ef uêezzeb i Öebbi akked llza, ur yif ara win issersen lebni s ef rrif n ucôuf ara iseggxen? Iseggex yis ar tmes n Loahennama. Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 204,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1345,
            "text": "Izga lebni, bnan, ippara ccekk deg ulawen nnsen, alamma gezmen wulawen nnsen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 204,
            "ruku": 168,
            "hizbQuarter": 81,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1346,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi Iu ar lmumnin, iman nnsen akked wayla nnsen, imi Loennet i nitni. Pnaen deg ubrid n Öebbi. Nnan, pwanan. D lemâahda fellas, s tidep, di Tuôa, di Linoil akked Leqwôan. Anwa yifen Öebbi di tuîîfa n lemâahda s? Feôêet, ihi, di ssuq tsewwqem. Wagi d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 204,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1347,
            "text": "Wid isteôoâen, wid iâabden, wid ipcekkiôen, ixelwiyen, wid iîîinizen, wid ikennun, wid ippamôen lewqama, wid ipgeddilen ayen n dir, wid ipêaraben ef tlisa n Öebbi ... Becceô lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 205,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1348,
            "text": "Ur issefk ara i Nnbi akked wid iumnen, ad ssutren ad pwasemmêen imcurak, xas ppilin asen, ma iban asen d ar, nitni, war ccekk, d at tmes.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 205,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1349,
            "text": "Ibôahim ur issuter ara ad ipwasemmeê baba s, siwa ilmend n lemâahda i s ifka. Mi s d iban ar neppa d acengu n Öebbi, ifra p yides. Ibôahim, war ccekk, ippanez, iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 205,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1350,
            "text": "Ur p Ixeddem Öebbi, ad Itlef agdud mbaâd ma Inha ten, alamma i sen Ibeggen acu ara êezzben. Öebbi, s tidep, Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 205,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1351,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi, IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan, Issidir, Ineqq. Ur awen illi, war Öebbi, bab ne amâiwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 205,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1352,
            "text": "Ni Issuref Öebbi i Nnbi akked iminigen, akked imâiwnen i iddan yides, di lweqt uwâiô, mbaâd ma qôib nneqlaben wulawen n urbaâ segsen. Sinna, Issuref asen. Ih, Neppa, i nitni, dUmâin, d'Aênin.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 205,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1353,
            "text": "U i krav id igwran, armi, tamurt iwsâan, tediyyeq fellasen. Vaqen deg iman nnsen. Ufan ur illi ssôan si Öebbi, siwa Neppa. Sinna, Issuref asen, akken ad steôoâen. Öebbi, s tidep, Issuruf, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 206,
            "ruku": 169,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1354,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, ilit seg imawlan n tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 206,
            "ruku": 170,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1355,
            "text": "Ur issefk ara i imezda n Lmadina, d wayen i sen d izzin n waâôaben n ucluê, ad gwrin deffir Umazan n Öebbi, ne ad smenyafen iman nnsen i iman is. Ayagi, acku ur ten ipêaz fad, ne âaggu, ne llaé, deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ur keçmen akal ara isserfun ijehliyen, ur ppaîîafen acemma suô ucengu, siwa ma dayen i sen iuran d igi n wayen ilhan. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Isôuêu arraz iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 206,
            "ruku": 170,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1356,
            "text": "Ur pûeôôifen cwiî ne aîas, ur zeggren asif, siwa ma iura yasen, iwakken a ten Ikafi Öebbi ef wayen ilhan deg wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 121,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 206,
            "ruku": 170,
            "hizbQuarter": 82,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1357,
            "text": "Ur Issefk ara i lmumnin ad ffen akw. Awufan ad iffe ugraw si yal arbaâ, ad bun di ddin, ad nabin agdud nnsen, mara ualen uôsen. Amar ad steêdren.",
            "numberInSurah": 122,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 206,
            "ruku": 170,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1358,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Nnaet ijehliyen i kwen iqeôben. Ad afen, uôwen, teqseê. Cfut, Öebbi Ippili d wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 123,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 207,
            "ruku": 171,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1359,
            "text": "Mi d ters tsuôep, llan garasen wid iqqaôen: 'anwa degwen, iwumi terna tagi, di liman'? Ma d wid iumnen, terna yasen liman, u nitni feôêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 124,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 207,
            "ruku": 171,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1360,
            "text": "Ma d wid iwumi blan wulawen, terna ammus i wammus nnsen. Mmuten u nitni d ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 125,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 207,
            "ruku": 171,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1361,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara, ar nitni la d sskaren lfetna, yal aseggwas, yiwen ubrid ne berdayen? Sinna, ur steôoiâen, ur d smektayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 126,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 207,
            "ruku": 171,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1362,
            "text": "Mi d ters tsuôep, ad mesmuqalen: 'day illa yiwen ikwen id Ipwalin'? Sinna, ad wexxôen. Isswexxeô Öebbi ulawen nnsen, imi nitni d agdud ur nfehhem.",
            "numberInSurah": 127,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 207,
            "ruku": 171,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1363,
            "text": "Ni iusa kwen id Umazan seg iman nnwen. èéay fellas laâtab nnwen. Ipêarab fellawen, d umâin, d aênin i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 128,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
            "page": 207,
            "ruku": 171,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1364,
            "text": "Ma wexxôen, ini: 'Iqadd iyi Öebbi. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. FellaS ppekle. Neppa d Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 129,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 2,
