            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1372,
            "text": "Wigi, axxam nnsen di tmes, ilmend n wayen keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 209,
            "ruku": 172,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1373,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Inhu Mass nnsen, s liman nnsen. Ad ppazzalen isaffen seddawat sen, di leonanat isaâdiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 209,
            "ruku": 172,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1374,
            "text": "Anuju nnsen degs: 'gedha s yissek a Öebbi'! Azul nnsen d: 'tifrat'. Anuju nnsen aneggaru: 'ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 209,
            "ruku": 172,
            "hizbQuarter": 83,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1375,
            "text": "Lemmer ad Iaâoel Öebbi cceôô ar imdanen, akken nitni êaren ef lxiô, yili ibbwev asen lajel nnsen. A Nanef i wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidne£, ad ddebdben di lbewv nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 209,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1376,
            "text": "Amdan, ma iêuza t ccqa, ad a£ £ d isiwel, iééel, iqqim ne ibedd. Mi s Nekkes ccqa s, ad iteddu amzun ur d inuj uône£ilmend n ccqa i t iêuzan. Akka ay ppucebêen igiten nnsen i imaâfan.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 209,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1377,
            "text": "Ni Nesqucc isuta, uqbel nnwen, imi densen. Ussan d uôsen imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen, ur llin d wid ara iamnen. Akka ay Nepqeîîi agdud ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 209,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1378,
            "text": "Sinna, Nerra kwen d igensas di tmurt, deffir sen, a Nwali amek ara txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 209,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1379,
            "text": "Ma ôan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, wid ur negguni ara timlilit yidne£, ad inin: 'awi d Leqwôan nniven, ne beddel it'. Ini: 'ur felli a t beddle, s lebi n yiman iw. Teddu kan akked wayen iyi d ippuweêêan. Nek ugade, ma xedâa Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 210,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1380,
            "text": "Ini: 'lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur awen t id mli, ur awen t id mmekti. Ni zede yidwen tameddurt, uqbel is. Day ur tfehmem ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 210,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1381,
            "text": "Anwa i idensen kteô, ger win id igren tikerkas ef Öebbi, ne win inekôen issekniyen iS? Ih, ur rebêen ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 210,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1382,
            "text": "La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen ur ten neîîuôu, ur ten nenfaâ. La qqaôen: 'wigi d imcafâen nne ar Öebbi'. Ini: 'day a pxebbôem Öebbi ef wayen ur Issin, di tmurt akked igenwan'? Gedha s yiS! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 210,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1383,
            "text": "Llan imdanen d yiwen n lois kan. Sinna, mgaraden. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal, suô Mass ik, ad yili uêuddu, garasen, ef wayen ief mgaraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 210,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1384,
            "text": "La qqaôen: 'a lemmer id irs uôes ussekni n Mass is'! Ini: 'tabavnit ar Öebbi kan. Ihi, gganit. Nek, yidwen, seg wid iggunin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 210,
            "ruku": 173,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1385,
            "text": "Ma Nesêess i imdanen aêunu, deffir twait i ten iêuzan, atnan la ppandin i issekniyen nne£. Ini: 'Öebbi Yif akw akken Ipawal di tiêeôci'. Imersulen nne£, s tidep, pparun ayen teppandim.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 211,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1386,
            "text": "Neppa i kwen Ippawin di lberr, di yill. Alamma, mi tellam di lembwabeô, teppedum degsen s wavu uûwib, feôêen yis, tusa d tbucivant uôsen, ppasent ed lemwao uôsen, si yal tama, êulfan a d tezzi fellasen. Naâôen Öebbi, s lqaâida i Neppa: 'ma Tsellkev a si tagi, ar a nili seg wid isnemmiren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 211,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1387,
            "text": "Mi ten Isellek, imiren ualen bewven di tmurt, war ssebba. A yimdanen! Lbewv nnwen, siwa ef yiman nnwen. Zzhu di tmeddurt n ddunit, sinna, uône£ tualin nnwen, ad awen Nmel ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 211,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1388,
            "text": "Amedya n tmeddurt di ddunit, am aman kan. Nesseli ten id seg igenni, xelven akked iman n tmurt, iseg teppen imdanen akked lmal. Mi tcebbeê tmurt, tual d tuzyint, ilen, imezda is, ar deg ufus nnsen ay tella. Iusa p id lameô nne£, deg iv, ne deg wass, Nerra p d ahicuô, amzun ur teoouoeg ass izeryen. Akka ay Nfeûûel issekniyen i ugdud ipxemmimen.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 211,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1389,
            "text": "Inecced Öebbi s axxam n tifrat. Inehhu win i S ihwan, ar ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 211,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 84,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1390,
            "text": "I wid iweqmen, lewqama, ternuv as. Udmawen nnsen, ur ten ipnal bufsus, ne ddell. Widak, d at Loennet, nitni, degs ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1391,
            "text": "Aqeîîi n wid id ibbwin tucmitin, d tucmip itent icban. Ad ndellen. Ur sâun amenêul ar Öebbi. Amzun ummen wudmawen nnsen, s ccevyat n yiv iberkanen. Widak d at tmes, nitni, degs, ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1392,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ten Nfesser akw, a Nini, imiren, i wid icurken: 'imukan nnwen, kunwi akked icriken nnwen'! Sinna Nessemfaôaq iten. A d inin, icriken nnsen: 'maççi d nekwni ay tâabdem.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1393,
            "text": "Ad Iqadd Öebbi, d Anagi garane yidwen, ar ur d necliâ deg uâbbed nnwen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1394,
            "text": "Din, yal amdan ad iwali ayen iwasa. Ad ualen ar Öebbi, Bab nnsen n tidep. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 174,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1395,
            "text": "Ini: 'anwa ikwen Ipitin seg igenni akked tmurt? Anwa ay d Bab n tmejjin akked yiéôi? Anwa id Issuffuen amuddir si lmegget, id Issuffuen lmegget seg umuddir? Anwa i Iseyyin lameô'? A d inin: 'd Öebbi'. Ini: 'ihi, day ur tepêezzibem ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1396,
            "text": "D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen n tidep. Deffir tidep, acu i illan, siwa ttelfan? Ihi, acimi texdâam?",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1397,
            "text": "Akka i iûaô wawal n Mass ik, ef wid ixedmen tucmitin. Ih, nitni ur ppamnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 212,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1398,
            "text": "Ini: 'day illa ger icriken nnwen, win id inzan lxelq, sinna, iules as d'? Ini: 'Öebbi inezzu lxelq, sinna, Ippales as d. Ihi, amek ara twexxôem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1399,
            "text": "Ini: 'day illa, ger icriken nnwen, win i inehhun ar tidep'? Ini: 'Öebbi Inehhu ar tidep. Win Inehhun ar tidep, day ur Yif ara, akken Iklal tikli yideS, win ur nennehhu, siwa ma ipwanha? Acu ikwen iuen? Amek tepseyyim'?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1400,
            "text": "Tegwti, segsen, teddun kan d nnwaya. Nnwaya, war ccekk, ur tebbwi acemma si tidep. Ih, Öebbi Issen acu xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1401,
            "text": "Leqwôan agi ur d innulfa ara, war Öebbi. Maca, d atebbet n wayen it id izwaren, d afeûûel n Tezmamt, ur degs ccekk, suô Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1402,
            "text": "Ne la qqaôen: 'isnulfa t id'. Ini: 'awit ed tasuôep i t icban, neccdet seg wanda tzemrem, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1403,
            "text": "Xaîi, skaddben ayen ur nekcim di tmusni nnsen, ur ten id iusi usefhem is. Akka ay skaddben, wid i ten id izwaren. Wali, ihi, amek tevôa d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1404,
            "text": "Garasen, wid iumnen yis; garasen, wid ur numin yis. Mass ik Yif akw akken Issen ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 175,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1405,
            "text": "Ma skaddben k, ini: 'i nek igiten iw, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Ur teppkam deg wayen xedme, ur ppka deg wayen txedmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1406,
            "text": "Garasen, llan wid i k issemêasen. Day tzemrev a pperrev ad slen iâeééugen, ma llan ur fehhmen?",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 213,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1407,
            "text": "Garasen, llan wid i k ipmuqulen. Day tzemrev a ppenhuv ideralen, ma llan ur pwalin?",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1408,
            "text": "Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iddennis imdanen, s wacemma, maca imdanen densen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1409,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ten Ifser, amzun sâaddan kan saâa n wass, ad msaâqalen. Ni xesôen wid iskaddben timlilit d Öebbi. Ur pwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1410,
            "text": "Ad ak Nessken kra seg wayen i sen Nâahed, ne a k id Nawi uône£. Ihi, uône£ tualin nnsen. Sinna, Öebbi d Anagi n wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1411,
            "text": "I yal lois, amazan. Ma iusa d umazan nnsen, a ppefru garasen s lmizan, ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1412,
            "text": "Qqaôen: 'melmi lemâahda agi, ma tessawalem tidep?",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1413,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur mlike i iman iw vveôô, ne abauô, siwa ayen Iba Öebbi. Yal lois s lajel is'. Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiôen s saâa, ur t id sseqôaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1414,
            "text": "Ini: 'acu twalam, ma iusa kwen id uâaqeb iS, deg iv, ne deg wass? Acimi êaren uôeS ibewviyen?",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1415,
            "text": "Da, ma iusa d, a ppamnem yis? Tura, aql akwen teûbem fellas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1416,
            "text": "Sinna, ad asen inin i wid idensen: 'jeôôbet aâaqeb n lebda. Ma teppuqeîîan siwa kan ef wayen tkeppbem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 85,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1417,
            "text": "Steqsayen k: 'd tidep ayagi'? Ini: 'ih, s Mass iw, ar ayagi d tidep! Kunwi ur tezmirem i usfunneg'.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 214,
            "ruku": 176,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1418,
            "text": "Xas ad isâu, yal amdan idensen, i illan di tmurt, ur d ifeddu yis. Ffren nndama mi walan aâaqeb. Aêuddu garasen, s lmizan, ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 177,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1419,
            "text": "Day, s tidep, maççi n Öebbi i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ih, day lemâahda n Öebbi maççi d tidep? Maca, tegwti segsen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 177,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1420,
            "text": "Neppa Issidir, Ineqq. £uôeS ara tualem.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 177,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1421,
            "text": "A yimdanen! Ni iusa kwen id unabi suô Mass nnwen, akked ccfa n wayen iblan ulawen, akked nnhaya, akked uêunu i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 177,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1422,
            "text": "Ini: 's lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, s waya, xas ad feôêen'. Yif ayen pkemmimen.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 177,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1423,
            "text": "Ini: 'twalam ayen i wen d Issers Öebbi n ôôeéq? Terram segs leêlal d leêôam'. Ini: 'Iâammed awen Öebbi, ne tesnulfam d ef Öebbi'?",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 177,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1424,
            "text": "Acu ara meyyzen, ass n tnekra, wid id igren tikerkas ef Öebbi? Ih, Öebbi d Bab n lfevl af imdanen, maca tegwti segsen ur snemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 177,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1425,
            "text": "Ur teppiliv di liêala, ur temmalev si Leqwôan, ur tepcewilem di kra, mebla ma Nella d Inagan nnwen, mara tweqmem. Lmizan ubelkim di tmurt u deg igenni, ur idrig i Mass ik. Akken seddaw waya, ne sennig es. Akw, di Tezmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 215,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1426,
            "text": "Ih, s tidep, iêbiben n Öebbi ur ppagwaden, ur weblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1427,
            "text": "Wid iumnen u llan êezzben,",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1428,
            "text": "a ten beccôen s lxiô di tmeddurt n ddunit, di laxeôt. Ur illi ubeddel deg wawalen n Öebbi. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1429,
            "text": "Ur k iwebbel wawal nnsen. Ih, tazmert akw n Öebbi. Neppa Isell, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1430,
            "text": "S tidep, day maççi n Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt? D acu îîafaôen wid ipnujun, war Öebbi, ar icriken? Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya. Oaââlen kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1431,
            "text": "Neppa, i wen Irran iv i ureyyeê nnwen, ass iwakken a pwalim. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i ugdud isellen.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1432,
            "text": "Nnan: 'Öebbi Isâa aqcic. Gedha s yiS! Neppa d Ameôkanti. IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ur tesâim adabu ef waya. Day a d tinim ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1433,
            "text": "Ini: 's tidep, wid id igren tikerkas ef Öebbi, ur rebêen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1434,
            "text": "Zzhu di ddunit, sinna, uône£ tualin nnsen. Da, ad asen Nsâaddi aâaqeb uqsiê, imi llan jehlen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 216,
            "ruku": 178,
            "hizbQuarter": 86,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1435,
            "text": "Eêku yasen d tadyant n Nuê, mi inna i ugdud is: 'a yagdud iw! Ma ééayit fellawen tilin iw, akked usmekti w n issekniyen n Öebbi, ef Öebbi ppekle, ihi, zduklet lameô nnwen akked icriken nnwen. Sinna, ur awen teppili lhejna ef lameô nnwen, da, frut ep felli, ur iyi sganit.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1436,
            "text": "Ma twexxôem, ur awen ssuture taqdiât. Ih, taqdiât iw ar Öebbi kan. Felli lameô ad ili seg imvuâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1437,
            "text": "Skaddben t. Nsellek it, akked wid illan yides, di lbabuô. Nerra ten d igensas. Nemeq wid iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Wali amek tevôa d wid ippunedôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1438,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir es, Nuzen ed imazanen ar igduden nnsen. Usan ten id s ubeggen. Ur ssawven ad amnen ef wayen nekôen zik. Akka ay Nselle ulawen ixabiten.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1439,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir sen, Nuzen ed Musa akked Haôun, ar Ferâun akked imvebbôen is, s issekniyen nne£. Smewôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1440,
            "text": "Mi ten id tusa tidep, suône£, nnan: 'wagi, ih, d ssêur n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1441,
            "text": "Inna Musa: 'day a tinim d ssêur wagi, i tidep mi kwen id tusa'? Ur rebêen iseêêaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1442,
            "text": "Nnan: 'day d tusiv uône, ad a tesîixxôev seg wayen id nufa ar imezwura nne, a ppualem, di sin, d imeqwôanen di tmurt? Ur numin, nekwni, yiswen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 217,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1443,
            "text": "Inna Ferâun: 'awit iyi d yal aseêêar amusnaw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1444,
            "text": "Mi d usan iseêêaren, inna yasen Musa: 'veggôet ara tveggôem'!",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1445,
            "text": "Mi veggôen, inna Musa: 'ayen d tebbwim d ssêur. S tidep, a t Inqev Öebbi'. Ih, Öebbi ur Issewqam ara igiten ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1446,
            "text": "Öebbi Itebbit tidep, s wawal iS, xas ugin ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 179,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1447,
            "text": "I iumnen s Musa, siwa tarwa seg ugdud is, ilmend n tugdi uhewwel n Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ih, Ferâun d abewvi di tmurt. Neppa, s tidep, seg imaâfan.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1448,
            "text": "Inna Musa: 'a yagdud iw! Ma teppamnem s Öebbi, ppeklet fellaS ma d imvuâen ay tellam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1449,
            "text": "Nnan: 'neppkel ef Öebbi. A Mass nne, ur a ppara d ahewwel i ugdud imednas;",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1450,
            "text": "Sellek a, s uêunu K, seg ugdud ijehliyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1451,
            "text": "Nweêêa i Musa akked gma s: 'ebnut ixxamen i ugdud nnwen di Maûeô, erret ixxamen nnwen ar lqibla, beddet i téallit. Becceô lmumnin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1452,
            "text": "Inna Musa: 'a Mass nne! S tidep, Tefkiv i Ferâun akked imvebbôen is, ôôêuê akked wayla di tmeddurt n ddunit, a Mass nne, iwakken ad nnetlafen seg ubrid iK. A Mass nne, Squcc ayla nnsen, Seô ulawen nnsen, ur ppamnen alamma walan aâaqeb aqeôêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 218,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1453,
            "text": "Inna: 'ih, tepwaqbel tnaâôit nnwen. Ddut di lewqam, ur teddut d ubrid n wid ur nessin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 87,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1454,
            "text": "Nezzger At Isôail di yill. Vefôen ten Ferâun akked iâsekôiwen is, s lebwev d lewâaôa. Armi ibbwev ad imeq, inna: 'umne! Ih, ur illi ôebbi siwa Win is umnen At Isôail. Nek seg imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1455,
            "text": "Tura! Ni zik taâûav, telliv seg ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1456,
            "text": "Assa, a Nsellek loeppa k, a d tegwri d assekni i wid ara k id ineûfen. Aîas n medden, s tidep, stehzan deg issekniyen nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 180,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1457,
            "text": "Ni Nessers At Isôail deg umkan umâin, u Nat iten s wayen ilhan. Ur mgaraden armi ten id tusa tussna. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, ilmend n wayen ief llan mgaraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1458,
            "text": "Ma tcukkev ef wayen i k ed Nessers, steqsi wid i iqqaôen Tazmamt, uqbel ik. Ni tusa k id tidep, suô Mass ik, ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1459,
            "text": "Ur ppili seg wid i iskaddben issekniyen n Öebbi, a ppiliv seg imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1460,
            "text": "Ih, wid ief iûaô Wawal n Mass ik, ur ppamnen,",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1461,
            "text": "xas usan ten id akw issekniyen, alamma walan aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 219,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1462,
            "text": "A lemmer telli temdint iumnen, u infaâ p liman is, siwa agdud n Yunes! Mi umnen, Nveôôef segsen aâaqeb imdelli di tmeddurt n ddunit. Neooa ten zzhan tallit kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1463,
            "text": "Ma ihwa yaS i Mass ik, ad amnen wid illan di ddunit, akken ma llan. Day a pêeppmev, keçç, i imdanen ad amnen?",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1464,
            "text": "Ur ippamen umdan siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Isdullu wid ur nfehhem ara.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1465,
            "text": "Ini: 'walit i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ula iwumi issekniyen akked ineddiôen, i ugdud ur neppamen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1466,
            "text": "Day a pganin kan amedya n wussan n wid i ten id izwaren? Ini: 'gganit, nek yidwen, seg wid ipganin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1467,
            "text": "Sinna, a Nsellek imazanen nne£, akked wid iumnen. Akka ay d lwajeb fella£, a Nsellek lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 181,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1468,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yimdanen! Ma tcukkem di ddin iw, nek ur âabde wid tâabdem, war Öebbi. Maca, âabde Öebbi ara Idmen leôwaê nnwen. Pwamôe ad ili si lmumnin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 182,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1469,
            "text": "Sbedd udem ik i ddin, s umili ar tidep, ur ppili seg imcurak.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 182,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1470,
            "text": "Ur pnuju, war Öebbi, ar wayen ur k inefâan, ur k iîîuôôun. Ma txedmev akken, keçç, imiren, a ppiliv seg imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 220,
            "ruku": 182,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1471,
            "text": "Ma Isâadda fellak Öebbi ccqa, ur ak illi ujebbaô siwa Neppa. Ma Irad ak lxiô, ur illi usebîîel i lfevl iS. Ippak it i win i S ihwan, deg ixdimen iS. Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 182,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1472,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yimdanen! Ni tusa kwen id tidep suô Mass nnwen! Win ipwanhan, ipwanha kan i iman is; win innetlafen, innetlef kan i iman is. Ur lli, nek, d awkil nnwen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 182,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1473,
            "text": "Ddu d wayen ik ed ippuweêêan, eûbeô ard Iêudd Öebbi. Neppa, Yif akw imêaddan.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 182,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 11,
        "name": "سُورَةُ هُودٍ",
        "englishName": "Hud",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Hud",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 1474,
            "text": "Alô. Tazmamt, issekniyen iS ppuûewwben, sinna, ppufeûûlen suô Uûwib i Ipwaxebbôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1475,
            "text": "Ur âabdet siwa Öebbi. Nek, suôeS uôwen, d aneddaô u d abcir.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1476,
            "text": "Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, steôoâet aS, ad Ifeôôeo fellawen afeôôeo ilhan, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ippak lfevl iS i yal bab n lfevl. Ma twexxôem, nekk ugade a ppeppuâqbem, ass ameqwran.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1477,
            "text": "Tualin nnwen, ar Öebbi. Neppa Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1478,
            "text": "Day nitni, s tidep, ur snefvasen ara idmaren nnsen, iwakken ad ffren fellaS? Xas ummen s iceîîiven nnsen, day ur Iéôa ara ayen teffren akked wayen d qqaôen? Neppa, s tidep, Issen i illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 11,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 221,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 88,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1479,
            "text": "Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, mebla ma illa ôôeéq is ar Öebbi. Issen tanezdut is, tanîelt is. Meôôa, di Tezmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 222,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1480,
            "text": "D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Asgeld iS illa ef waman. A kwen Ijeôôeb anwi segwen ara ixedmen ayen ilhan, sennig wiyav. Ma tenniv: 'ih, kunwi a d tekkrem deffir tmeppant nnwen', wid ijehlen, war ccekk, a d inin: 'ayagi, kan, d ssêur n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 222,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1481,
            "text": "Ma Neswexxeô asen aâaqeb ar imir ipwassnen, war ccekk, a d inin: 'd acu iT iîîfen'? Ass ideg ara ten id iawev, day illa wa ara ten iveôôfen segs? Ad asen izzi wayen ief pmmaâliken.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 222,
            "ruku": 183,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1482,
            "text": "Ma Nesêess i umdan aêunu nne¨£, sinna, Nekkes as t, atan ad iayes, ad ijhel.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 222,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1483,
            "text": "Ma Nesêess as lit, deffir twait i t innulen, atan ad yini: 'fukkent felli lemêayen', da, neppa, ad ifôeê, ad izux.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 222,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1484,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid iûebbôen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I widak ssmaê akked tikci meqqwôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 222,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1485,
            "text": "Ahat teppaoav kra n wayen ik ed ippuweêêan. Pzemmiven yis idmaren ik mara qqaôen: 'a lemmer i s d irs ugerruj, ne idda d, yides, lmelk'! Keçç d aneddaô kan. Öebbi d Awkil n yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 222,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1486,
            "text": "Ne ad inin: 'isnulfa t id'. Ini: 'awit ed, s usnulfu, mraw n tsuôtin am neppa. Naâôet ayen iwumi tzemrem, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 223,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1487,
            "text": "Ma ur awen d rran ara, cfut ar irs ed kan s tussna n Öebbi, ar ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, ma kunwi d imvuâen?",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 223,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1488,
            "text": "I wid iban tameddurt n ddunit akked ôôêuê is, a Nkafi, degs, igiten nnsen, ur asen Ntekkes.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 223,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1489,
            "text": "Widak, ur ppafen, di laxeôt, siwa times. Ad ili wayen ûenâen degs; inqev wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 223,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1490,
            "text": "Day win iddan d ubeggen, suô Mass is, u immal as t unagi suôeS…? U, uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Wigi umnen yis. Win i p inekôen, seg ikubar, ppaâud is d times. Ur ppili di ccekk fellas. Neppa, ih, d tidep suô Mass ik. Maca, tegwti n medden ur ppamnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 223,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1491,
            "text": "Anwa idensen sennig win id isnulfan tikerkas ef Öebbi? Wigi a d rsen i Mass nnsen. A d inin inagan: 'd wigi i iskaddben ef Mass nnsen'. Day Öebbi ur Ixezzu yara imednas?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 223,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1492,
            "text": "I isîixxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, i t issarmen d uâwij, nitni ur uminen s laxeôt?",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 223,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1493,
            "text": "Wigi, ur sfunnugen di tmurt, ur asen illi bab, war Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb ar wayev. Ur zmiren ad slen, ur pwalin.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1494,
            "text": "D wigi i isxesôen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1495,
            "text": "Ur illi ccekk, ih, nitni ad xesôen, di laxeôt, sennig wiyav.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1496,
            "text": "Ih, wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, u unzen aS i Mass nnsen, widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 89,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1497,
            "text": "Amedya n snat n trebbuyaâ am uderal, uâééug, akked win ipwalin, win isellen. Day âadlen sin imedyaten agi? Day ur d tesmektayem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 184,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1498,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is: 'nek d aneddaô nnwen ipbegginen,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1499,
            "text": "iwakken ur tâabdem siwa Öebbi. Nek ugaded aâaqeb fellawen, ass aqeôhan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1500,
            "text": "Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen, seg ugdud is: 'keçç, uône, d amdan am nekwni. Nwala, d ôôdiyen nne, kan, war ameyyez, i k ivefôen. Ur nwala s wacu i  tifem. Xaîi, nêesb ikwen d ikeddaben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1501,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu suôeS. Idreg fellawen. Day a t nêeppem fellawen, ma kunwi tugim t?",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 224,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1502,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture ayla, ilmend is; taqdiât iw ar Öebbi kan. Ur ppara, nek, wid iumnen. S tidep, ad mlilen d Mass nnsen. Maca, nek wala kwen d agdud ur nessin.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1503,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, lemmer i ten rri akin, day ur d tesmektayem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1504,
            "text": "Ur awen qqaôe: uôi lexzayen n Öebbi. Ur ssine tabavnit. Ur qqaôe: nek d lmelk. Ur qqaôe i wid êeqôent wallen nnwen: ur asen Ippak ara Öebbi lxiô, d awezi. Yif akw Öebbi akken Iéôa, i illan deg iman nnsen. Mulac ad ili seg imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1505,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Nuê! Ni tnamrev a, tessugtev a anamer. Ihi, awi ya d ayen i  tâahdev, ma tessawalev tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1506,
            "text": "Inna: 'd Öebbi kan ar awen t id Iawin, ma ihwa yaS. Kunwi ur tesfunnugem.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1507,
            "text": "Xas bi a kwen neûêe, ur tesfaydayam seg wanûaê iw, ma Iba Öebbi a kwen Itlef. Neppa d Mass nnwen; tualin nnwen uôeS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1508,
            "text": "Ne qqaôen: 'isnulfa t id'. Ini: 'ma snulfa t id, lbewv iw i yiri w. Nek, ur ppka di lbewv nnwen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 185,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1509,
            "text": "Ippuweêêa d i Nuê: 'ur ippamen yiwen, d awezi, seg ugdud ik, siwa wid illan umnen. Ihi, ur k icqi wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1510,
            "text": "Eûnaâ lbabuô, ger wallen nne£, s uweêêi nne£. Ur iyI d pmeslay ef wid idensen, war ccekk, ad emqen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 225,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1511,
            "text": "La iûennaâ lbabuô. Yal tikelt ara âaddin uôes imvebbôen n ugdud is, tkaâriren fellas. Inna: 'ma temmaâlkem degne, ihi, a nemmaâlek degwen akken temmaâlkem.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1512,
            "text": "Deqqal a ppeéôem, uuô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, ara iêaz uâaqeb imezgi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1513,
            "text": "Alamma, mi d iusa lameô nne£, la pfeggiven igwefran d ihedman, Nenna: 'awi degs tayuga n yal ûûenf, tawacult ik - siwa wid ief id izwar wawal -, akked wid iumnen'. Drus kan i iumnen yides.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 90,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1514,
            "text": "Inna: 'rekbet degs, s yisem n Öebbi, acali s akked trusi s. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1515,
            "text": "Icula yissen, di lemwao anect idurar. Issawel Nuê i mmi s, i illan weêdes: 'a mmi ali d yidne, ur teppiliv ar ijehliyen'!",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1516,
            "text": "Inna: 'ûûôan iw d adrar, ad iyi isellek seg waman'. Inna: 'assa, ulac leslak si lameô n Öebbi, siwa i win ief Iêun'. Âaddant lemwao garasen. Iûebê ed seg wid ipwaemqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1517,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a tamurt, seblaâ aman im, a yigenni eûûfu'. Aman zzren. Iûaô lameô: irs ef Loudi. Iffe uberraê: akin agdud imednas!",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1518,
            "text": "Inuj Nuê ar Mass is, inna: 'a Mass iw! Ni mmi n twacult iw. Ih, lemâahda K d tidep, Keçç Tifev akw imêaddan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 226,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1519,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Nuê! Neppa, s tidep, ur illi n wacult ik. Ih, neppa ur ixdim ayen ilhan. Ihi, ur iyI d steqsay ef wayen ur tessinev. Nek a k Ssakwaye, ur teppiliv seg wid ur nessin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1520,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Ili di lâawen iw, iwakken ur K id steqsaye ef wayen ur ssine. Ma ur iyi Tsemmêev, ur Têunev felli, ad ili seg imexsuôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1521,
            "text": "Nnan d: 'a Nuê! Ers ed s tifrat suône£, akked lbaôaka, fellak akw ef leoyus i illan yidek. Kra n legyus, a ten Nit. Sinna, fellasen suône£, aâaqeb aqeôêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1522,
            "text": "Tagi si teqûivin n tbavnit, Nweêêa yak tent. Ur tent tessinev, keçç, ne agdud ik, uqbel wagi. Ihi, eûbeô, taggara, war ccekk, i wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 186,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1523,
            "text": "I Âad, gmat sen Hud, inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1524,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture taqdiât ef waya. Taqdiât iw ar Win kan, iyi d Ixelqen. Day ur tefhimem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1525,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, sinna, steôoâet aS. Ad awen d Isseli ageffur d ihedman, ad awen irnu tazmert i tezmert nnwen. Ur ppualet d ibewviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1526,
            "text": "Nnan as: 'a Hud! Ur a d tusid s ubeggen, ur neppaoa, nekwni, iôebbiten nne, ilmend n wawal ik, ur numin yisek.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 227,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1527,
            "text": "Neqqaô kan, d kra iôebbiten nne, i k ieôqen'. Inna: 'nek, Anagi w d Öebbi, u cehhdet ar ur ppka ara deg wayen tepcarakem,",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1528,
            "text": "war Neppa. Ihi, andit iyi akken ma tellam, sinna ur iyi sganayet.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1529,
            "text": "Nek, ppekle af Öebbi, Mass iw u Mass nnwen. Ur illi umexluq ur Iîîif seg ixef is. Ih, Mass iw deg ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1530,
            "text": "Ma wexxôen, ni ssawve awen d ayen ief id ppuceggâa uôwen. A d Inûef, Mass iw, agdud war kunwi. Ur T teîîuôum s wacemma. Mass iw, s tidep, d Amêareb n yal cci'.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1531,
            "text": "Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Hud akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu suône£. Nsellek iten seg uâaqeb uwâiô.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1532,
            "text": "Akka Âad. Nekôen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, âuûan imazanen iS. Ddan d lameô n yal aqehhaô iggernennen.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1533,
            "text": "A ten ivfeô xezzu di ddunit agi, u deg wass n tnekra. Day, war ccekk, ur jhilen ara Âad, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: 'akin Âad, agdud n Hud'?",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 187,
            "hizbQuarter": 91,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1534,
            "text": "I Tamud, gmat sen ÛüÜaliê, inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Neppa Ixelq ikwen seg wakal, Izzde ikwen fellas. Ssutret aS ssmaê, sinna, steôoâet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, Iqeôb ed, Ippara d awal.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1535,
            "text": "Nnan as: 'a Üaliê, ni telliv garane, uqbel aya, d asirem nne. Day ad a tekksev aâbad n wayen âabden imezwura nne? Nekwni, s tidep, aql a di ccekk imcebbwel, ef wayen uuô la  tneccdev'.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 228,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1536,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu suôeS. Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, ma aâûa uôeS? Iyi ternam, siwa taxessaôt.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1537,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Tagi d talwemt n Öebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Eooet ep a ppeks di tmurt n Öebbi. Ur p pjeyyifet, mulac a kwen id isami uâaqeb iqeôben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1538,
            "text": "Gezmen as ivaôen. Inna: 'zhut deg ixxamen nnwen, krav wussan. Apan lemâahda ur nepwankaô'.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1539,
            "text": "Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Üaliê akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu suône£, si ddell n wass nni. Ih, Mass ik d Uohid, d Uzmir.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1540,
            "text": "Asuu iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen,",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1541,
            "text": "amzun ur rbiêen degsen. Day, s tidep, ur jhilen ara Tamud, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: 'akin Tamud'?",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 188,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1542,
            "text": "Ni usan d imceggâen nne£ ar Ibôahim, s ubecceô. Nnan: 'tifrat'! Inna: 'tifrat'! Ur iâaîîel ara ibbwi d aâjmi icwin.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1543,
            "text": "Mi iwala ifassen nnsen ur d ééilen ara uôes, isêassef iten, iugad iten. Nnan: 'ur ppagwad, nekwni neppuceggaâ ed ar ugdud n Luî'.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1544,
            "text": "Tameîîut is tbedd, tevûa. Nbecceô ip s Isêaq, akked Yaâqub, deffir Isêaq.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 229,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1545,
            "text": "Tenna: 'a lêif iw, day a d arwe, nek d tamaôt, u argaz agi inu, wesser? Ayagi, s tidep, d lwehma'!",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1546,
            "text": "Nnan: 'day twehmev di lameô n Öebbi? Aêunu n Öebbi, akked lbaôaka S, fellawen ay at uxxam. Ih, Neppa d Amaâzuz, Mucaâ'.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1547,
            "text": "Mi s tekkes tugwdi i Ibôahim, u iusa t id ubecceô, inumer a£ ef ugdud n Luî.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1548,
            "text": "Ibôahim, s tidep, iêellem, ippanez, isteôoiâ.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1549,
            "text": "'A Ibôahim, ur keççem deg waya. Ni iusa d lameô n Mass ik. Nitni, a ten id ias uâaqeb, war tifrat'.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1550,
            "text": "Mi usan imceggâen nne£ ar Luî, innuben, ur isâi iil a ten ifukk. Inna: 'wagi d ass uwâiô'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1551,
            "text": "Iusa d ugdud is, zeêfen d uôes. Llan, zik, xeddmen tucmitin. Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Atent an issi, nitenti zeddigit, i kunwi. Ëezbet i Öebbi, ur iyi pêeccimet ar inebgawen iw. Day ur illi ara, garawen, urgaz aêesbi'?",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1552,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ni teéôiv ur nesâi lêeqq deg issi k. Keçç, s tidep, teéôiv d acu neba'.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1553,
            "text": "Inna: 'a lemmer i wen zmire, ne sâi tayep ioehden'!",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1554,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Luî, nekwni d imceggâen n Mass ik. Ur k id ppawven. Öuê akked twacult ik, deg iv. Yiwen degwen ur d itezzi! Kkes ed tameîîut ik. Neppat, s tidep, a ppepwwet s wayen ara ten iwwten. Ih, ppaâud nnsen, taûebêit. Ni tqeôb ed tûebêit'?",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 230,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1555,
            "text": "Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nesredm ip. Nesseli d fellas abruri n yiéôa ibelbaven n talaxt.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 231,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1556,
            "text": "Pwanesxen ar Mass ik. Nitni, ur bâiden i imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 231,
            "ruku": 189,
            "hizbQuarter": 92,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1557,
            "text": "I Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb, inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Ur ssenqaset di lkil akked lmizan. Nek, wala kwen teôwam, u ugade fellawen aâaqeb, ass itezzin.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 231,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1558,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Ktilet, weznet, s lewqama. Ur îîuôôut imdanen deg wayla nnsen, ur pdenniset, tessefsadem di tmurt.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 231,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1559,
            "text": "Yif it i kunwi wayen d iqqimen i Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam. Ur lli, nek, d amêareb nnwen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 231,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1560,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Cuâayeb, day a umôen wawalen ik, a neoo ayen âabden imezwura nne? Ne a nexdem, deg wayla nne, ayen ur a nehwi? Keçç, s tidep, d uêlim, d uûwib'.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 231,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1561,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Acu twalam, ma ddi d ubeggen n Mass iw? Iat iyi yis, lit imaânen. Ur bi a kwen mgirrde, siwa ef wayen i wen gedle. Bi kan, s wayen zemre, ad awen ûegme tikli. Lâawen iw suô Öebbi kan. Ppekle fellaS, utube T.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 231,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1562,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Awer kwen teppara nnmara w d ibewviyen, a ppevôu yidwen akken tevôa d ugdud n Nuê, ne win n Hud, ne win n Üaliê! Agdud n Luî, ur ibâad ara segwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1563,
            "text": "Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, sinna, steroâet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipêunu, Ipêemmil'.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1564,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Cuâayeb, ur nefhim ara aîas n wayen id tenniv. Aql a nwala k d uôhif garane. Lemmer maççi d alag ik, war ccekk, a k neôoem. Ur a tezmirev'.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1565,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Day Öebbi, uôwen, yif iT walag iw, di tezmert? Terram T ar deffir n waârur nnwen. Mass iw, s tidep, Izzi i wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1566,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Xedmet deg umekkan nnwen, nek ad xedme. Deqqal a ppeéôem, uuô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, anwa ay d akeddab. Âasset, nek, yidwen, ad âasse'.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1567,
            "text": "Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Cuâayeb akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu suône£. Asuu iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen,",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1568,
            "text": "amzun ur rbiêen degsen. Day maççi: 'akin Madian'! Am: 'akin Tamud'?",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 190,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1569,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£, akked udabu n ûûeê,",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1570,
            "text": "uô Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ddan d lameô n Ferâun. Lameô n Ferâun ur illi d uûwib.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 232,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1571,
            "text": "Ad izwir i ugdud is, ass n tnekra, a ten inheô ar usario n tmes. A yasario ucmit uuô pwanehôen!",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1572,
            "text": "A ten ivfeô xezzu di tagi, u deg wass n tnekra. A tikci tucmip ippunefken!",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1573,
            "text": "Ayagi, si teqûivin n temdinin, i k d Nessawal. Garasent tid ibedden, tid ipwamegren.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1574,
            "text": "Ur ten Nednis. Maca, densen iman nnsen. Ur ten nefâan s wacemma, iôebbiten nnsen i la naâôen, war Öebbi, mi d iusa lameô n Mass ik. I sen rnan, siwa ssxev.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1575,
            "text": "Akka tiyta n Mass ik. Mi Iwwet timdinin i idensen, s tidep, tiyta S teqôeê, teqseê.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1576,
            "text": "Ih, deg waya, assekni i wid iugaden aâaqeb n laxeôt. Ass nni, d ass unejmaâ n yimdanen. Ass nni, d ass n ccada.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1577,
            "text": "A t Neswexxeô kan ar lajel iuran.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1578,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara d ias, ur d ipmeslay yiwen, siwa ma s tesriê iS. Ad ilin igeswaêen, isaâdiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1579,
            "text": "Wanag igeswaêen ad ilin di tmes, s unazaâ d imeîîi,",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1580,
            "text": "ad wekkôen dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. Ih, Mass ik Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 93,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1581,
            "text": "Wanag isaâdiyen, di Loennet, ad wekkôen, dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. D tikci n war tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 233,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1582,
            "text": "Ur k ikeççem ccekk ef wayen âabden widak. Ayen âabden am wayen âabden imezwura nnsen, zik. War ccekk, ad asen Nefk amur nnsen, ur inqis.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 191,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1583,
            "text": "Ni, s tidep, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal suô Mass ik, yili useyyi garasen. Haaten, ih, di ccekk imcebbwel fellas.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1584,
            "text": "War ccekk, akken ma llan, ad Ikafi Mass ik igiten nnsen, s lmizan. Neppa, s tidep, Issen ayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1585,
            "text": "Ihi, ili d uwqim, akken i k ippunefk lameô, keçç akked wid isteôoâen yidek. Ur bewvet. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ay txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1586,
            "text": "Ur pqeôôibet ar wid idensen, a kwen tnal tmes! Ur tesâim bab, war Öebbi, ihi, ur tepwasellkem.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1587,
            "text": "èéal ûbeê, tameddit, kra n lewqat n yiv. S tidep, iseiyen neqqven tucmitin. Ayagi d asmekti i wid ismektayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1588,
            "text": "Eûbeô! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iveggiâ taqdiât n lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1589,
            "text": "A lemmer llan, di tsuta i kwen id izwaren, imezgiyen ineqqven asefsed di tmurt! Qlilit kan seg wid Nsellek segsen. Wid idensen ddan akked wayen i ten izhan, ualen d ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1590,
            "text": "Ur Isquccu ara Mass ik timdinin, d aêerfi, ma llan imezda nnsent d lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 234,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1591,
            "text": "Lemmer i S ihwi i Mass ik, ad Irr imdanen d yiwen n lois. Zgan mgarraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1592,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid ief Iêun Mass ik. Ixelq iten i wayagi. Itam wawal n Mass ik: 'ad Acaôe Loahennama, war ccekk, s leonun akked yimdanen mejmulen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1593,
            "text": "Ayen akw i k ed Neêka n tmucuha imazanen, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yissent. Id iusan dagi d tidep, d anabi u d asmekti i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1594,
            "text": "Ini i wid ur numin ara: 'xedmet ay tzemrem, nekwni s tidep, la nxeddem.",
            "numberInSurah": 121,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1595,
            "text": "Gganit, nekwni la nepgani'.",
            "numberInSurah": 122,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1596,
            "text": "N Öebbi tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. £uôeS ara ualen akw lumuô. Ihi, âabed iT, ppkel fellaS. Ur Ieffel ara Mass ik, ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 123,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 192,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 12,
        "name": "سُورَةُ يُوسُفَ",
        "englishName": "Yusuf",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Joseph",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 1597,
            "text": "Alô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tazmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 193,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1598,
            "text": "Ih, Nessader it id d Leqwôan, s taâôabt, amar a pfehmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 193,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1599,
            "text": "Nekwni Nêekku yak tiêkayin igerzen mavi, deg wayen i k Nweêêa di Leqwôan agi, xas telliv, uqbel is, seg wid istehzan.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 193,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1600,
            "text": "Mi inna Yusef i baba s: 'a baba! Nek wala mrawyan itran, iîij, akked waggur, wala ten knan iyi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 235,
            "ruku": 193,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1601,
            "text": "Inna: 'a mmi! Ur êekku ayen twalav i watmaten ik, ad ak andin ticeôkep. Cciîan, s tidep, d acengu n ûûeê n umdan.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 193,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1602,
            "text": "Akka, a k Ifren Mass ik, u ak Isselmed asefru n temsal, u ad Itim lit iS, i keçç akked twacult n Yaâqub, akken it Itam, zik, af lejdud ik: Ibôahim akked Isêaq. Mass ik, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d Uûwib'.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 193,
            "hizbQuarter": 94,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1603,
            "text": "Ni, di Yusef akked watma s, illa ussekni i wid isteqsayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1604,
            "text": "Mi nnan: 'war ccekk, ifen a, Yusef akked gma s, akken iten iêemmel babat nne, u nekwni d îîeôma. Babat nne, s tidep, haat di ttelfan n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1605,
            "text": "Enet Yusef, ne nfut ep si tmurt, a d ilhu degwen babat wen, sinna, a ppualem d imdanen ixeddmen ayen ilhan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1606,
            "text": "Inna win d immeslayen, degsen: 'ur neqqet Yusef, veggôet ep ar lqaâa n wannu. Ma tgam akka, a t iddem yiwen umsebrid'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1607,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a babat nne, acu k iuen, ur a tuminev ara, ef Yusef. Nekwni, fellas, s tidep, d unûiêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1608,
            "text": "Sseddu t yidne azekka, ad izhu, ad iurar. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nêareb fellas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1609,
            "text": "Inna: 'nek, s tidep, weble ma tebbwim t yidwen, ugade a t içç lweêc, kunwi testehzam degs'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1610,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ma içça t lweêc, u nekwni d îîeôma, s tidep a nili d imexsuôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 236,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1611,
            "text": "Mi t bbwin, mwafaqen a t rôen ar lqaâa n wannu, Nweêêa yas: 'ad asen temlev, s tidep, lameô agi nnsen, nitni ur éôin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1612,
            "text": "Ualen d tameddit, ar babat sen, pprun.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1613,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a babat nne, s tidep, nôuê a nemzizzel, neooa Yusef ar lqecc nne, içça t lweêc. Ur a teppamnev, xas nenna d tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1614,
            "text": "Bbwin d tasedrit is, degs idamen n rrya. Inna: 'xaîi! D iman nnwen i wen d iccacven lameô. Ilha ûûbeô. Anuju eô Öebbi, mgal ayen d teêkam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1615,
            "text": "Usan d iminigen, uznen win id ippagwmen, issader ssvel is. Inna: 'a lxiô, wagi d aqcic'! Ffren t, amzun d sselâa. Öebbi Iéôa acu xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1616,
            "text": "Zzenzen t, s ôôxa, s kra iûuôdiyen. Ur as fkin ara azal.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 194,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1617,
            "text": "Inna, i tmeîîut is, Umaûôi i t iuen: 'eôêeb yis, amar ad a infaâ, at nerr d mmit nne'. Akka ay Nesseqâad Yusef di tmurt, iwakken ad as Nesseêfev asefru n temsal. Öebbi d Amezwaru s lameô iS, maca tegwti n medden ur éôin ara.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1618,
            "text": "Mi d immeêtel, Nefka yas ûûwab, tussna. Akka ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 237,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1619,
            "text": "Teba t tin uur izde. Terra tibbura, u tenna: 'eyya keçç'! Inna: 'ad iyi Ineooi Öebbi! Ni bab iw iôêeb yissi. S tidep, ur rebêen imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1620,
            "text": "S tidep, teba t, u neppa iba p, lemmer ur iwala ara atebbet n Mass is. Akka, iwakken a Nessebâad fellas tuccva, lâaô. Neppa, s tidep, seg imdanen nne£ izedganen.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1621,
            "text": "Uzzlen ar tebburt, tcerreg as tasedrit is, si zdeffir. Mmugren, argaz is, ar tebburt. Tenna: 'acu ay d aqeîîi n win iâabwlen ad iccmet tawacult ik, siwa lêebs ne aâaqeb aqeôêan'?",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1622,
            "text": "Inna: 'd neppat iyi iban'. Icuhhed ed yiwen unagi si twacult is: 'ma teqqeôs tsedrit si zdat, tenna d tidep, u neppa d akeddab.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1623,
            "text": "Ma teqqeôs tsedrit si zdeffir, teskaddeb, u neppa seg at tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1624,
            "text": "Mi iwala teqqeôs tsedrit si zdeffir, inna: 'ayagi, war ccekk, si nncub nnkwent. Ih, nncub nnkwent d timeqwôaêanin.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1625,
            "text": "A Yusef, ppu ayagi, u kem ssuter ssmaê ubekkav im. Kem, s tidep, teccvev'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 195,
            "hizbQuarter": 95,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1626,
            "text": "La qqaôent tlawin, di temdint: 'tameîîut umdebbeô têemmel acrik is. Teshebl ip tayri. F akken nwala, appan, s tidep, di ttelfan n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 238,
            "ruku": 196,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1627,
            "text": "Mi tesla s nncub nnsent, tuzen uôsent, thegga yasent tanalt. I yal yiwet segsent, tefka tafrut. Tenna: 'effe ed garasent'. Mi t walant, isdehc itent, jerêent ifassen nnsent, nnant: 'êaca Öebbi, wagi maççi d amdan, wagi siwa d lmelk ukyis'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 239,
            "ruku": 196,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1628,
            "text": "Tenna: 'd wagi ief iyi tlummemt. Ih, bi t, neppa iqqim zeddig. Ma ur ixdim ara ay s umôe, war ccekk, ad ipwaêbes, ad ipwaêqeô'.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 239,
            "ruku": 196,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1629,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Smenyafe lêebs i wayen uur iyi d ssawalent. Ma ur Tesbaâdev ara felli nncub nnsent, ad male uôsent, ad ili seg wid ur nessin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 239,
            "ruku": 196,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1630,
            "text": "Ijaweb as d Mass is. Issebâad fellas nncub nnsent. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 239,
            "ruku": 196,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1631,
            "text": "Sinna, mi ten usan issekniyen, ufan, war ccekk, ilaq a t irr ar lêebs, kra n tallit.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 239,
            "ruku": 196,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1632,
            "text": "Kecmen yides, ar lêebs, sin ilmeéiyen. Inna yiwen degsen: 'nek wala iman iw, la teééme ccôab'. Inna d wayev: 'nek wala iman iw, la ppawi aôum ef uqeôôu w, la teppen segs ifrax. Ssefru ya p id. Ih, nwala k seg iâaôviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 239,
            "ruku": 197,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1633,
            "text": "Inna: 'seg wayen iyi sseô Mass iw, ad awen p id ssefru, uqbel a kwen id iawev lqut i wen ppakken. Nek ooi ddin n ugdud ur numin s Öebbi, u nitni nekôen laxeôt.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 239,
            "ruku": 197,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1634,
            "text": "Ddi d ddin n lejdud iw: Ibôahim, Isêaq akked Yaâqub. Ur a ippunefk a nezdukkel acemma i Öebbi. Ayagi si lfevl n Öebbi fellane, akw ef imdanen. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen ur snemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 240,
            "ruku": 197,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1635,
            "text": "A yimeddukwal iw n lêebs, menyif imawlan imfaôaqen, ne Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô?",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 240,
            "ruku": 197,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1636,
            "text": "Ay tâabdem, war Neppa, d ismawen kan i sen tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur asen d Issers ara Öebbi kra udabu. Lêukm ar Öebbi kan. Iumeô ed ur tâabdem, siwa Neppa. D wagi ay d ddin uûwib, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 240,
            "ruku": 197,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1637,
            "text": "A yimeddukwal iw n lêebs, wanag yiwen degwen ad ismiri ccôab, i bab is, wayev ad ippusemmeô ef umidag, ifrax ad nneqben aqeôôu s. Ippuseyya lameô ef wayen iyi d testeqsam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 240,
            "ruku": 197,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1638,
            "text": "Inna i win iêûa ad islek, segsen: 'ar bab ik, smekti iyi d'. Cciîan iseppu t, ur t id ismekti ar bab is. Irna, di lêebs, kra iseggwasen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 240,
            "ruku": 197,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1639,
            "text": "Inna ugellid: 'nek wala ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. A yimvebbôen, ssefrut iyi d targit, ma tellam seg wid issefruyen tirga'.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 240,
            "ruku": 198,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1640,
            "text": "Nnan: 'd tirga iwlellsen. Ur nelli d imusnawen i usefru n tirga'.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 198,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1641,
            "text": "Win i isellken si sin nni, armi tallit id immekti, inna: 'nek, ad awen d awi asefru ines, aznet iyi.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 198,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1642,
            "text": "A Yusef, bab n tidep, ssefru ya d: ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. Amar, ma uale ar imdanen, amar ad éôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 198,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1643,
            "text": "Inna: 'zerâat ûa iseggwasen imyevfaôen. Ayen tzerâam, eooet ep di tyedrin is, siwa cwiî ara teççem.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 198,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1644,
            "text": "Sinna, deffir sen, a d asen ûa iwaâôen. Ad ççen ayen i sen theggam siwa cwiî, seg wayen txeznem.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 198,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1645,
            "text": "Sinna a d ias, deffir waya, useggwas n tallalt i medden, ideg ara éden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 198,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1646,
            "text": "Inna ugellid: 'awit ep id uôi'. Mi t id iusa umersul, inna: 'ual ar bab ik, u steqsi t acu ay d leôv n tlawin i ijerêen ifassen nnsent. Mass iw, s tidep, Issen nncub nnsent'.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1647,
            "text": "Inna: 'acu ara d tinimt mi tebamt Yusef'? Nnant: 'êaca Öebbi, ur nufi uôes tuccva'. Tenna d tmeîîut umvebbeô: 'tura, a d tban tidep. D nek i t iban, ma d neppa, s tidep, d bab n tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1648,
            "text": "'Akka, iwakken ad iéeô ur t xdiâa ara s tuffra. Öebbi ur Inehhu nncub n lxeyyan.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 12,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 241,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 96,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1649,
            "text": "Ur pzekki iman iw. Tanefsit, s tidep, tezzuuô ar tuccva, siwa ma Iêun Mass iw. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1650,
            "text": "Inna ugellid: 'awit ep id uôi, d laâtiq iw'. Mi s immeslay, inna: 'keçç, assa, nefka yak adabu, laman'.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1651,
            "text": "Inna: 'wekkel iyi ef lemxazen n tmurt, nek d amêareb amusnaw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1652,
            "text": "Akka ay Nesseqâad Yusef di tmurt, ad izde anda i s ihwa. Nepêunu ef win i £ ihwan, ur Nesôuêu arraz iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1653,
            "text": "S tidep, arraz n laxeôt yif it, i wid iumnen u llan pêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 199,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1654,
            "text": "Usan watmaten n Yusef, kecmen uôes, iâqel iten, nitni ur t âqilen.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1655,
            "text": "Mi sen ifka ppâabgat nnsen, inna: 'awit iyi d gmat wen s babat wen. Day ur twalam ara zade awen lkil, u, nek, ife akw wid isnebgaten?",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1656,
            "text": "Ma ur iyi t id tebbwim ara, ur awen nepktili uôi, ur iyi d tepsamim '.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1657,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a nêawet baba s fellas; akka ara nexdem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1658,
            "text": "Inna i iqeddacen is: 'rret selâa nnsen deg icekkaôen nnsen, amar a p âaqlen mara awven ar twacult nnsen, amar a d ualen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1659,
            "text": "Mi bbwven ar babat sen, nnan: 'a babat nne, igdel fella lkil, azen gmat nne yidne, iwakken a d nektil. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nêareb fellas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 242,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1660,
            "text": "Inna: 'day a kwen amne fellas, akken i kwen umne, zik, ef gma s? Öebbi Yif akw imêaraben. Neppa Iphunu sennig akw iêninen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 243,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1661,
            "text": "Mi ldin lqecc nnsen, ufan tual iten id selâa nnsen. Nnan: 'a babat nne, ur nebi tagi, selâa nne tual a d. A d nessikrer i twacult nne, a nêareb ef gmat nne, a d nernu ppâabga n ulwem. Tagi d ppâabga tushilt'.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 243,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1662,
            "text": "Inna: 'ur t sedduye yidwen, d awezi, siwa ma tcubkem iyi s Öebbi, ard a yi t id terrem, siwa ma zzin awen'. Mi s âahden, inna: 'Öebbi d Awkil ef wayen id nenna'.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 243,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1663,
            "text": "Inna: 'a tarwa, ur keççmet si yiwet n tebburt, kecmet si tebbura imgarraden. Ula i wen xedme, bippa, ar loiha n Öebbi. Aêuddu siwa win n Öebbi. FellaS ppekle, fellaS ay ppeklen wid ippkalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 243,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1664,
            "text": "Mi kecmen akken i sen iumeô babat sen, ula i sen ixdem, bippa, ar loiha n Öebbi. D ayen ilezmen kan i iseyya Yaqub, deg iman is. Neppa, s tidep, isâa tamusni i s Nesselmed, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 243,
            "ruku": 200,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1665,
            "text": "Mi kecmen ar Yusef, ibbwi gma s uôes, inna: 'nekkini d gma k, ur webbel ef wayen xeddmen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 243,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1666,
            "text": "Mi sen ifka ppâabgat nnsen, irra taqbuct deg ucekkaô n gma s. Sinna, iberreê uberraê: 'a yat terkaf, kunwi, war ccekk, d imakwaren'!",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1667,
            "text": "Nnan, u zzin uôsen: 'd acu tesôuêem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1668,
            "text": "Nnan: 'nesôuê taqbuct ugellid. Win ip id ibbwin, ad as nefk ppâabga n ulwem. Nek, vemne t'.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1669,
            "text": "Nnan: 's Öebbi, nni teéôam ur d nusa ara a nessefsed tamurt, ur nelli d imakwaren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1670,
            "text": "Nnan: 'd acu ay d aqeîîi s, ma teskadbem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1671,
            "text": "Nnan: ' aqeîîi n win i p ibbwin di tcekkaôt is, d yiman is. Akka ay nepkafi imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1672,
            "text": "Ibda la ipqellib icekkaôen, uqbel win n gma s, sinna, issuffe ip id seg ucekkaô n gma s. Akka ay Nefka ticeôkep i Yusef. Ur izmir ad iîîef gma s, s lqanun ugellid, siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Nessalay, tiseddaôin, win i £ihwan. Sennig bu tussna, illa Umusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 97,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1673,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ma iuker, ni iuker, zik, yiwen n watma s'. Iffer ip Yusef uôes, ur asen p id inna ara. Inna: 'aql akwen deg yir êala. Öebbi Yif akw akken Iéôa ayen d teqqaôem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1674,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a yameqwôan, baba s, s tidep, wesser. Eîîef yiwen segne deg umekkan is. Nwala k, ih, telliv si lâuûam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 244,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1675,
            "text": "Inna: 'ur a Iâammed Öebbi a neîîef, siwa win uuô nufa taawsa nne. Mulac, war ccekk, a nili d imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 201,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1676,
            "text": "Mi uysen segs, mcawaôen, inna umeqwôan segsen: 'day ur teéôim ara, ar babat wen tcubkem t s Öebbi, u, zik, tveggâam Yusef? Ihi, ur pôuêu si tmurt a, d awezi, alamma iserreê iyi baba, ne Ifra Öebbi felli. Neppa, Yif akw imêaddan.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1677,
            "text": "Ualet ar babat wen, tinem as: a babat nne, mmi k, s tidep, iuker. Ncehhed kan ef wayen neéôa, ur nessawev i tbavnit.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1678,
            "text": "Steqsi tamdint ideg i nella, akked terkift ukud nedda. Ih, d tidep, ay d nenna'.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1679,
            "text": "Inna: 'xaîi! Lameô seg iman nnwen. Ilha ûûbeô. Amar Öebbi a yi ten id Iawi akw. Neppa, s tidep, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1680,
            "text": "Ijuneb iten, u inna: 'a lêif iw ef Yusef'! Allen is ijegger itent uilif, innuben.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1681,
            "text": "Nnan: 's Öebbi, tezgiv tesmektayev d Yusef, alamma tualev d amuvin, ne seg wid immuten'.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1682,
            "text": "Inna: 'la pcetki kan i Öebbi, s uneémi w akked uwbel iw. Ssne, suô Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 245,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1683,
            "text": "A yarraw iw, ôuêet, steqsit ef Yusef akked gma s. Ur ppayset di tecvaî n Öebbi. Ih, i ippaysen di tecvaî n Öebbi, siwa agdud ijehliyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1684,
            "text": "Mi bbwven uôes, nnan as: 'a yameqwôan, nekwni akked twacult nne, nepwa. Nusa d s selâa ôxisen, semd as lkil, seddeq a. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipkafi wid ipseddiqen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1685,
            "text": "Inna: 'teéôam i tgam i Yusef akked gma s, mi kunwi, d wid ur nessin'?",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1686,
            "text": "Nnan: 'keçç, s tidep, maççi d Yusef '? Inna: 'nek d Yusef, atan gma. Ni Iat a Öebbi. Ih, wid ipêezziben, wid iûebbôen ... Öebbi, s tidep, ur Isôuêu arraz iâaôviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1687,
            "text": "Nnan: 's Öebbi ar k Ismenyaf Öebbi garane. Nekwni, s tidep, neccev'.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1688,
            "text": "Inna: 'ur telli tiyta degwen, assa. Ad awen Isemmeê Öebbi! Neppa Yif akw wid ipêunun.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1689,
            "text": "Awit tasedrit iw agi, erret ep ef udem n baba, ad iêlu yiéôi s. Aset ed uôi, s twacult nnwen, meôôa'.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 202,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1690,
            "text": "Mi teqlaâ terkift, babat sen ibda la iqqaô: 'nek, s tidep, sraêe rriêa n Yusef, awi d kan ur teqqaôem ara: la isxeôwiv'.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1691,
            "text": "Nnan: 's Öebbi, ar k mazal di ttelfan ik n zik'.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 246,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1692,
            "text": "Mi d iusa ubcir, issers as p ef udem is, llint ed wallen is, inna: 'day ur awen nni ara: nek ssne, suô Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 247,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1693,
            "text": "Nnan as: 'a babat nne, ssuter ad a pwasemmêen ibekkaven nne. S tidep, nella d imednab'.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 247,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1694,
            "text": "Inna: 'deqqal ad ssutre, i Mass iw, ad awen Isemmeê. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 247,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1695,
            "text": "Mi bbwven ar Yusef, isteôêeb s imawlan is. Inna: 'kecmet ar Maseô, di laman, ma Irad Öebbi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 247,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1696,
            "text": "Issuli imawlan is ar usgeld. £lin, knan as. Inna: 'a baba! D wagi ay d asefru n targit iw, n zik. Ni Issuffe ip Mass iw! Ni Iga yi leqôaô mi yi d Issuffe si lêebs. Ikkes ikwen id si sseêôa, deffir tismin i isker Cciîan, gari d watma. Mass iw, s tidep, d Laîif i win i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 247,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 98,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1697,
            "text": "A Mass iw, ni Tefkiv iyi si tgelda, Tesêefvev iyi asefru n temsal. Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, Keçç, d Bab iw di ddunit, di laxeôt, Eddem ôôuê iw d amvua, Ssiwev iyi ar wid imaânen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 247,
            "ruku": 203,
            "hizbQuarter": 99,
