            "hizbQuarter": 99,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1705,
            "text": "Nuzen ed kan, uqbel ik, irgazen seg imezda n temdinin, iwumi Nweêêa. Day ur unagen ara di tmurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren? Ih, pifxiô axxam aneggaru i wid ipêezziben. Day ur tefhimem ara?",
