            "page": 248,
            "ruku": 204,
            "hizbQuarter": 99,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1706,
            "text": "Alamma, mi uysen imazanen, u meyyzen ar skaddben ten, tusa ten id tallalt suône£. Nepsellik win i £ ihwan. Ur ipwakkas ara ssxev nne£, i ugdud ibewviyen.",
