            "sajda": {
              "id": 2,
              "recommended": true,
              "obligatory": false
            }
          },
          {
            "number": 1723,
            "text": "Ini: 'anwa ay d Mass n tmurt akked igenwan'? Ini: 'd Öebbi. Ihi day a pperrem d iêbiben, war Neppa, wid ur nemlik, i yiman nnsen, abauô ne vveôô'? Ini: 'day iaâdel uderal akked win ipwalin? Ne, day âadlent tillas akked tafat? Ne, rran imcurak i Öebbi, i ixelqen am lxelq iS, ufan t ippemcabi'? Ini: 'd Öebbi i Ixelqen yal cci. D Neppa ay d Yiwen, d Aqehhaô'.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 13,
