            "ruku": 206,
            "hizbQuarter": 100,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1726,
            "text": "Day win iéôan ar ayen i k d irsen, suô Mass ik, d tidep, am win idrelen? Siwa uâqilen id ismektayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 252,
            "ruku": 207,
            "hizbQuarter": 101,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1727,
            "text": "Wid iîîfen di laâqed n Öebbi, ur pôuéun nnesba.",
