            "hizbQuarter": 101,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1728,
            "text": "Wid issemlilen ayen id Iumeô Öebbi ad imlil, u ppagwaden Mass nnsen, u ppagwaden aqeîîi adiran.",
