          },
          {
            "number": 1729,
            "text": "Wid iûebôen, ssaramen udem n Mass nnsen, bedden i téallit, pseddiqen seg wayen is iten Nat, s tuffra u âinâni, swexxiôen tucmip s yise. I nitni, agwav s Axxam.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
