            "hizbQuarter": 101,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1730,
            "text": "Leonanat n Âaden ara kecmen, akked wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, seg ibabaten nnsen, si tlawin nnsen, si tarwa nnsen. Lmalayek a d ppasent uôsen si yal tabburt.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
