            "number": 1732,
            "text": "Wid ipôuéun laâqed n Öebbi, deffir lemwafaqa s, wid igezmen ayen d Iumeô Öebbi ad imlil, u ssefsaden di tmurt, wigi, i nitni xezzu, i nitni yir axxam.",
