            "text": "La qqaôen wid ijehlen: 'a lemmer id iris, uôes, ussekni suô Mass is'! Ini: 'Öebbi, s tidep, Itellif win i S ihwan. Inehhu uôeS, wid isteôoiâen,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 13,
