            "ruku": 208,
            "hizbQuarter": 101,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1739,
            "text": "Ni mmaâlken, uqbel ik, deg imazanen. Ooi lmudda i wid ijehlen, sinna, Ïîfe ten. A yaâaqeb iW imiren!",
