            "page": 253,
            "ruku": 209,
            "hizbQuarter": 101,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1740,
            "text": "Day Win Ibedden, ar yal amdan, ef wayen ikseb…? Curken aS i Öebbi. Ini: 'semmit asen! Ne, ad aS temlem ayen ur Iéôi di tmurt? Ne d ismawen n tkerkas'? Xaîi! Wid ijehlen, âaobent pen nncub nnsen. Ppuveôôfen seg ubrid. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi w ara t inhun.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
