            "hizbQuarter": 101,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1741,
            "text": "Fellasen aâaqeb, di tmeddurt n ddunit. Aâaqeb n laxert, s tidep, aâer. Ur sâin ara ten ifukken, seg ufus n Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
