            "ruku": 209,
            "hizbQuarter": 101,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1742,
            "text": "Amek tga Loennet i ippuweââden i wid iêezzben: ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen, lqut is akked tili s, d imezgiyen. D tagi ay d taggara n wid iêezzben. Taggara ijehliyen, d times.",
