            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1744,
            "text": "Akka ay t id Nessers, d ûûwab, s taâôabt. Ma teddiv d lhawiyya nnsen, deffir tisin n tussna uôek, ur k ipfukku bab ne asettaô, seg ufus n Öebbi.",
