            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 254,
            "ruku": 210,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1749,
            "text": "Ni ppandin wid i ten id izwaren. Tiêeôci, akw, ar Öebbi. Iéôa i ikseb yal iman. Ad éôen ijehliyen anwa ara iawven s Axxam.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 254,
            "ruku": 210,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1750,
            "text": "Qqaôen wid ijehlen: 'ur telliv d amazan'. Ini: 'ad Iqadd Öebbi d Anagi gari yidwen, akked kra isâan tussna n Tazmamt'.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 255,
            "ruku": 210,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 14,
        "name": "سُورَةُ إِبۡرَاهِيمَ",
        "englishName": "Ibrahim",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Abraham",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 1751,
            "text": "Alô. Tazmamt, Nessers ak p id, iwakken a ppessuffev imdanen si tillas ar tafat, s wannuf n Mass nnsen, s abrid n Wuzmir, Amaâzuz,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 255,
            "ruku": 211,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1752,
            "text": "Öebbi ilan i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. A ssxev ijehliyen, ilmend uâaqeb uqsiê,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 255,
            "ruku": 211,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1753,
            "text": "i ismenyafen tameddurt n ddunit wala laxeôt, i iswexxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, u ssaramen t d uâwij! Widak, atnan di ttelfan umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 255,
            "ruku": 211,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1754,
            "text": "Ur d Nuzen amazan, siwa s tmeslayt n ugdud is, iwakken ad asen ibeggen. Öebbi Itellif win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 255,
            "ruku": 211,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1755,
            "text": "Ih, ni Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£: 'ssuffe agdud ik, si tillas ar tafat. Mmekti yas d ussan n Öebbi'. Deg waya, war ccekk, d issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 255,
            "ruku": 211,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1756,
            "text": "Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: 'mmektit ed lit ikwen Iat Öebbi, mi kwen Isellek si lois n Ferâun, i issuken fellawen lhemm uqsiê. Zellun arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Deg waya, suô Mass nnwen, d cedda tameqwôaêant'.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 256,
            "ruku": 211,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1757,
            "text": "Mi d Inna Mass nnwen: 'ma tesnemmrem, ih, ad awen Rnu. Ma tjehlem, aâaqeb iW, war ccekk, ad iwâaô'.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 256,
            "ruku": 212,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1758,
            "text": "Inna Musa: 'ma tjehlem, kunwi akked wid n tmurt meôôa, ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz'.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 256,
            "ruku": 212,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1759,
            "text": "Day ur kwen id ibbwiv ara usali imezwura nnwen: agdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, akked wid iten ivefôen? Ur ten issin yiwen, siwa Öebbi. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen. Rran ifassen nnsen s imawen nnsen, nnan: 'S tidep, nejhel ayen ief d teppuceggâam. Ih, nekwni di ccekk imcebbwel, ef wayen uuô la  tneccdem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 256,
            "ruku": 212,
            "hizbQuarter": 102,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1760,
            "text": "Nnan imazanen nnsen: 'day illa ccekk di Öebbi, Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan? Inecced ikwen id, iwakken ad awen Isemmeê kra ibekkaven nnwen, a kwen Ioo ar lajel ipwassnen'. Nnan: 'kunwi, s tidep, d imdanen kan, am nekwni. Tebam ad a tesîixxôem, seg wayen llan âabden imezwura nne. Awit a d adabu n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 256,
            "ruku": 212,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1761,
            "text": "Nnan asen imazanen nnsen: 'nekwni d imdanen kan, am kunwi, maca Öebbi Iteg ccan i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS. Ur a ippunefk ara ad awen d nawi adabu, siwa s wannuf n Öebbi. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 212,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1762,
            "text": "Acu i  iuen, ur nepkal ara ef Öebbi? Ni Imla ya iberdan nne; neûbeô, war ccekk, i lmerta i tesâaddam fella. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen, at letkal'.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 212,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1763,
            "text": "Nnan wid ijehlen i imazanen nnsen: 'war ccekk, a kwen nessuffe si tmurt nne, ne a d tualem ar ddin nne'. Iweêêa yasen d Mass nnsen: 's tidep, a Nesqucc imednas,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1764,
            "text": "da, war ccekk, a kwen Nerr d imezda n tmurt, deffir sen'. Ayagi, i win ippagwaden tilin iW, ippagwaden aberri W.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1765,
            "text": "Ssarmen lelb. Ixseô yal aqehhaô amnafeq.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1766,
            "text": "Loahennama deffir es, ad ites aman iwexmiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1767,
            "text": "Tissit d tijewimin, ur izmir ad isseblaâ. Tameppant a d teppas si yal tamnaî, neppa ur ipmeppat. Deffir es aâaqeb uqsiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1768,
            "text": "Amedya n wid ijehlen, ar Mass nnsen: igiten nnsen am iiden ief iédem wavu, ass n tbucivant. Ur d ppawin acemma, seg wayen kesben. D wagi ay d ttelfan umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 257,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1769,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara, Öebbi Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep? Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Ikkes, a d Iawi lxelq amaynut.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 258,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1770,
            "text": "Ayagi, i Öebbi, ur illi d ayen izzenzafen.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 258,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1771,
            "text": "A d rsen akw zdat Öebbi. Ad inin uôhifen i imzuxiyen: 's tidep, nella nedda yidwen, ma tzemrem ad a tsellkem kra, seg uâaqeb n Öebbi'? A d inin: 'lemmer i  Inha Öebbi, yili nwelleh ikwen. Iâuva fella, neêmeq ne neûbeô, ur a illi ssôan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 258,
            "ruku": 213,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1772,
            "text": "Mi isuyya lameô, a d yini Cciîan: 'Öebbi, d ûûeê, Iweââd awen lemâahda n tidep. Weââde awen, uôe kwen. Ur sâi adabu fellawen, siwa anecced nnwen. Tuem awal iw. Ur iyi plummut, lummet iman nnwen. Ur zmire a kwen âawne, ur tezmirem ad iyi tâawnem. Nekôe wid iyi tepcarakem, zik. I imednas, s tidep, aâaqeb aqeôêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 258,
            "ruku": 214,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1773,
            "text": "Ad skecmen wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen dinna, s wannuf n Mass nnsen. Azul nnsen dinna d: 'tifrat'!",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 258,
            "ruku": 214,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1774,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara, amek id Ifka Öebbi amedya? Awal lâali am ttejôa lâali, iéuôan is ôûan, iferkawen is di tegnewt.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 258,
            "ruku": 214,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1775,
            "text": "Teppak ed lfakia s, di yal imir, s wannuf n Mass is. Ippawi d Öebbi imedyaten i imdanen, amar a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 214,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1776,
            "text": "Amedya n wawal ucmit, am ttejôa tucmip, teqlaâ sennig wakal, war leqôaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 214,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1777,
            "text": "Öebbi Itebbit wid iumnen s wawal utebbet, di tmeddurt n ddunit akked laxeôt. Öebbi Itellif imednas. Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 214,
            "hizbQuarter": 103,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1778,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid ineûfen lit n Öebbi, s tijehli? Ssersen agdud nnsen deg uxxam n twait.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 215,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1779,
            "text": "Loahennama ad ôen degs: a yir leqôaô!",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 215,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1780,
            "text": "Gan aS i Öebbi tanudda, iwakken ad telfen seg ubrid iS. Ini: 'zzhut! S tidep, leqôaô nnwen d times'.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 215,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1781,
            "text": "Ini i imdanen iW iumnen, ad bedden i téallit, ad seddqen seg wayen iten Nat, s tuffra u âinani, uqbel a d ias wass ideg ur illi ssuq, ur telli tdukli.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 215,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1782,
            "text": "Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, id Isselayen aman seg igenni, Issufu ed yissen ppemôa, d ôôeéq i kunwi. Inub fellawen s isaffen, u s lbabuô i iteddun di yill, s lameô iS.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 215,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1783,
            "text": "Inub fellawen s yiîij d waggur, d imezgiyen. Inub fellawen s yiv akked wass.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 259,
            "ruku": 215,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1784,
            "text": "Ifka yawen seg wayen akw i S tessutrem. Ma pêesbem lit n Mass nnwen, ur tessawavem. Ih, amdan, s tidep, d amednus, d ajehli.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 215,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1785,
            "text": "Mi inna Ibôahim: 'a Mass iw! Err tamdint agi d tin n laman, Âatq a, nek d warraw iw, seg wannuz n tâancuôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 216,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1786,
            "text": "A Mass iw, nitenti, s tidep, telfent aîas n medden. Win iddan yidi, neppa, s tidep, sgi. Win iyi âuûan, Keçç, s tidep, Tepsemmiêev, Tepêunuv.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 216,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1787,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Nek rri tanezdut, i kra n warraw iw, di tezut ibuôen, ar Uxxam iK iôqan. A Mass nne! Iwakken ad bedden i téallit. Err ulawen n kra n medden, ad iêninen uôsen, £it iten s ppemôat, amar ad snemmren.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 216,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1788,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Keçç, s tidep, Teéôiv ayen neffer akked wayen nenna. Ur iffir wacemma i Öebbi, di tmurt ne deg igenni.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 216,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1789,
            "text": "Ccekôan i Öebbi iyi d Ifkan, di tewser iw, Ismaâil akked Isêaq. Mass iw, s tidep, Issemêas i tnaâôit.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 216,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1790,
            "text": "A Mass iw, Err iyi ad bedde i téallit. Akked kra, si tarwa w. A Mass iw, Steôêeb s unuju w.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 216,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1791,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Semmeê ane, nek d lwaldin iw, akked lmumnin, ass ideg ara d ias uqeîîi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 216,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1792,
            "text": "Ur pili ar Ifel Öebbi, ef wayen xeddmen imednas. Iooa ten kan, ar ass ideg ara beêêren allen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 260,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1793,
            "text": "Ad pawalen, iqweôôa ffen d, allen ur ferzent, ulawen d ilmawen.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1794,
            "text": "Nabi imdanen af wass ideg ara ten id yas uâaqeb. Ad inin wid idensen: 'a Mass nne! Efk ane lmudda wezzilen, a d njaweb i unabi K, a neddu d imazanen'. 'Day ur teggulem ara kunwi, zik, ar ur tepabem?",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1795,
            "text": "Tzedem ixxamen n wid ivuôôen iman nnsen. U Nbeggen awen d amek i sen Nga, u Nefka yawen d imedyaten'.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1796,
            "text": "Ni undin ccbukat nnsen. Ccbukat nnsen haatent ar Öebbi, xas ma ccbukat nnsen d tid ara isselin idurar.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1797,
            "text": "£uôek a pilev Öebbi ad Izgel lemâahda S, i imazanen. S tidep, Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1798,
            "text": "Ass ideg tamurt a ppual maççi d tamurt; akken igenwan; a d asen ar Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1799,
            "text": "A pwaliv, assen, ibewviyen pwaqqnen wa er wa.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1800,
            "text": "Lebsa nnsen d qevôan, times tumm udmawen nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1801,
            "text": "Iwakken ad Ikafi Öebbi yal amdan, ef wayen ikseb. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipawal di leêsab.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1802,
            "text": "Wagi d anecced i imdanen, ad pwanedôen yis, ad éôen ar siwa Neppa ay d Öebbi Yiwen, a d mmektin uâqilen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 13,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 261,
            "ruku": 217,
            "hizbQuarter": 104,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 15,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الحِجۡرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Hijr",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Rock",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 1803,
            "text": "Alô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt, u d Leqwôan ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1804,
            "text": "Ahat wid ijehlen ssaramen ad ilin d imvuâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1805,
            "text": "Eoo iten ad ççen, ad zhun, a ten issedhu usirem. Deqqal ad éôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1806,
            "text": "Ur Nesquccu tamdint, siwa ma d ayen i s iuran, ipwassnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1807,
            "text": "Ur illi lois ara d isqeôben, ne ara iswexxôen lajel is.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1808,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a win uuô d irs usmekti! Keçç, war ccekk, d aôehbani.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1809,
            "text": "Acimi ur a d tusiv ara, s lmalayek, ma d tidep ay tessawalev'?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1810,
            "text": "Ur Nesrusu lmalayek, siwa s tidep. Imiren, ur pganin.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1811,
            "text": "Ih, Nekwni Nessers ed asmekti. Ih, Nekwni a Nêareb fellas.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1812,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed, uqbel ik, i ikabaren imezwura.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1813,
            "text": "Ur ten id ippas umazan, mebla ma ttahan fellas.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1814,
            "text": "Akka ay t Nessekcam deg ulawen ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1815,
            "text": "Ur uminen yis, ulamma ooan d imezwura tannumi.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1816,
            "text": "Xas ad asen Nelli tabburt igenni, ad ppalin uôes,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1817,
            "text": "a d inin, war ccekk: 'ittules iéôi nne, ne nekwni d agdud iwumi sseêren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 262,
            "ruku": 218,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1818,
            "text": "Ni Nerra itran deg igenni. Ncebbeê iten i wid ipmuqulen.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 263,
            "ruku": 219,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1819,
            "text": "Nesdari ten, si yal cciîan imenfi.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 263,
            "ruku": 219,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1820,
            "text": "Kkes ed win d issemêessen s tufra, A p iddu, fellas, ujajiê n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 263,
            "ruku": 219,
            "hizbQuarter": 105,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1821,
            "text": "Tamurt Nessewsaâ p; Nerra fellas idurar; Nessemi d, degs, yal cci, s lmizan.",
