            "text": "Ih, Öebbi Iumeô ed lêeqq, akked lewqama, talalt i llzem. Igdel tucmitin, ayen n dir, ddeôk. A kwen Ipnabi, amar a d temmektim.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 277,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1992,
            "text": "Eîîfet di lemâahda n Öebbi ma tâahdem. Ur êentet di tgallit ma tetebbtem, u tcubkem Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa acu txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 277,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1993,
            "text": "Ur cebbut tin ifsin lxiv is, mbaâd ma tcudd it, s loehd. Tepparam tagallit nnwen i umkellex garawen: ad ikk lois sennig wayev. Öebbi Ipjeôôib ikwen kan, yis. War ccekk, ad awen Ibeggen, ass n tnekra, ayen ief temgarradem.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 277,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1994,
            "text": "Lemmer i S ihwi, i Öebbi, a kwen Irr d yiwen n lois. Maca, Itellif win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. S tidep, a ppepusteqsim ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 277,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1995,
            "text": "Ur pparat tagallit nnwen i umkellex garawen. Ad iccev uvaô mbaâd ma iîîef. A pjeôbem tawait, ilmend n wayen tveôôfem seg ubrid n Öebbi. I kunwi, aâaqeb abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1996,
            "text": "Ur ppaet s lemâahda n Öebbi ayen ôxisen. Ih, yif it i kunwi wayen illan eô Öebbi, lemmer teéôim.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1997,
            "text": "Ayen illan uôwen, ad ifukk; ayen illan eô Öebbi, ad idum. War ccekk, a Nkafi wid iûebôen, s wazal n wayen xeddmen ifuqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1998,
            "text": "Wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne d nnta, u umnen, a ten Nessider di tmeddurt tumâint, a ten Nkafi s wazal n wayen xeddmen ifuqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 1999,
            "text": "Mara teôev Leqwôan, ssuter a k Iaâteq Öebbi, si Cciîan imenfi.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2000,
            "text": "Neppa, s tidep, ur isâi adabu ef wid iumnen, i ippeklen ef Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2001,
            "text": "Adabu ines, ef wid kan i t irran d bab, d wid i S ipcaraken.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 236,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2002,
            "text": "Ma Nbeddel assekni s ussekni, u Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen ayen id Issers, a d inin: 'keçç, d win kan id isnulfuyen'. Xaîi! Tegwti, degsen, ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2003,
            "text": "Ini: 'Issers it id ôôuê iôqan, suô Mass ik, s tidep, iwakken ad itebbet wid iumnen; d nnhaya u d abecceô i imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 278,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2004,
            "text": "Ih, Neéôa, qqaôen: 'd amdan kan it isselmaden'. Tameslayt n win d gren, d tabeôôanit, wagi d awal aâôab n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2005,
            "text": "Ih, wid ur numin ara s issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten Inehhu Öebbi. I nitni, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2006,
            "text": "Ih, gren d kan tikerkas, wid ur numin ara s issekniyen n Öebbi. Widak, d nitni ay d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2007,
            "text": "Win inekôen Öebbi, deffir liman is, siwa ma êeppmen fellas, u ul is izga iumen…. Ma d wid illin idmaren nnsen, ar tijehli, ad Izâaf Öebbi fellasen. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2008,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku smenyafen tameddurt n ddunit i laxeôt. Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2009,
            "text": "D wigi iwumi Isle Öebbi ulawen nnsen, timejjin nnsen, iéôi nnsen. Wigi d iefliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2010,
            "text": "War ccekk, nitni, di laxeôt, ad ilin d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2011,
            "text": "Sinna, Mass ik, s tidep, i wid iunagen mbaâd ma thewwlen, sinna juhden, ûebôen; ih, Mass ik, deffir waya, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 279,
            "ruku": 237,
            "hizbQuarter": 111,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2012,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara d ias, yal yiwen, ad inamer ef yiman is, u yal yiwen ad iîîukafi ef wayen ixdem, nitni ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2013,
            "text": "Ifka d Öebbi amedya n temdint, i illan di laman u îîmana. Ippas ip id ôôeéq is, s lufa, si yal tama. Tenkeô lit n Öebbi. Isukk Öebbi fellas tawait n llaé akked lweêc, ilmend n wayen la ûûenâan.",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2014,
            "text": "Ni iusa ten id umazan, segsen. Skaddben t, iwwet iten uâaqeb, nitni densen.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2015,
            "text": "Eççet seg wayen is ikwen Iat Öebbi, i iêellen, i imaânen. Snemmret lit n Öebbi, ma d Neppa ay tâabdem.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2016,
            "text": "I yawen Igdel siwa loifa, idim, aksum n yilef, akked wayen id irsen s yisem ur nelli d win n Öebbi. Ma d win terra tmara, ur ijuô, ur inufeq, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2017,
            "text": "Ur qqaôet tikerkas id ppawin ilsawen nnwen: 'aya d leêlal, aya d leêôam'. A d tegrem tikerkas ef Öebbi. Wid id iggaren tikerkas ef Öebbi, ur rebêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2018,
            "text": "Drus ara zhun, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2019,
            "text": "I wudayen, Negdel ayen ief i k Neêka, iu lêal. Ur ten Nednis, maca nitni ddennisen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 280,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2020,
            "text": "Sinna, Mass ik, i wid ixedmen cceôô, ur ssinen, da steôoâen deffir waya, u sweqmen, Mass ik, war ccekk, deffir waya, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 238,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2021,
            "text": "Ibôahim, ih, d amdan i imalen ar tidep, i iunzen i Öebbi. Ur illi seg imcurak.",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2022,
            "text": "Isnemmar lit iS. Ifren it u Inha t s abrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 121,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2023,
            "text": "Nefka yas di ddunit ise, u, di laxeôt, neppa, s tidep, ad yili seg izedganen.",
            "numberInSurah": 122,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2024,
            "text": "Sinna, Nweêêa yak d a ppedduv d ddin n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep. Ur illi seg imcurak.",
            "numberInSurah": 123,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2025,
            "text": "Ssebt, iual kan i wid imgarraden fellas. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, ef wayen llan mgarraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 124,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2026,
            "text": "Enced s abrid n Mass ik, s ûûwab akked nnhaya tumâint. Mmeslay iten, s yiles aéidan mavi. Ih, Mass ik Yif akw akken Issen, anwi i iffen seg ubrid iS. Neppa Yif akw akken Issen, anwi i ipwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 125,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2027,
            "text": "Ma tâaqbem, âaqbet akken teppuâaqbem. Ma tûebôem, yif it i iûebôiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 126,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2028,
            "text": "Eûbeô. Üûebô ik s Öebbi kan. Ur webben ilmend nnsen, ur pveyyiq si tcengal nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 127,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2029,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi Atan ar wid ipêezziben, akked wid issewqamen.",
            "numberInSurah": 128,
            "juz": 14,
            "manzil": 3,
            "page": 281,
            "ruku": 239,
            "hizbQuarter": 112,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 17,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الإِسۡرَاءِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Israa",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Night Journey",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 2030,
            "text": "Gedha s Win Ibbwin amdan iS, d iminig n yiv, si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ar Loamaâ ibaâden mavi, ideg Neôqa i as d izzin, iwakken ad as Nessken, seg issekniyen nne£. Ih, Neppa, d Win Isellen, Ipwalin.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 282,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2031,
            "text": "Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, u Nerra p d nnhaya i At Isôail. 'Ur sâut awkil, war Nek'.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 282,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2032,
            "text": "D tarwa n wid i Nebbwi akked Nuê. Neppa, s tidep, d amdan isnemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 282,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2033,
            "text": "Nsseyya di Tezmamt, i At Isôail: 'war ccekk, a ppesfesdem, di tmurt, berdayen, u aîas ara tesmewôem iman nnwen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 282,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2034,
            "text": "Mi d iusa usefsed amenzu segsen, Nuzen awen d imdanen nne£, s loehd uqsiê, kecmen ixxamen; lemâahda tevôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 282,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2035,
            "text": "Sinna, Nerra d ppaô nnwen, segsen. Nebbwi yawen d ayla, tarwa. Nesîuqqet iâsekôiwen nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 282,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2036,
            "text": "Ma tmaânem, i iman nnwen, ma tdensem, i iman nnwen. Mi d tusa lemâahda taneggarut, ssexven udmawen nnwen, kecmen Loamaâ, akken i t kecmen abrid amenzu; hudden, wakali, ayen is ipzuxxun.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 282,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2037,
            "text": "Ahat Mass nnwen ad Iêun fellawen. Ma tulsem, a Nales. Nerra Loahennama d lêebs i ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2038,
            "text": "Ih, Leqwôan agi inehhu ar wayen iweqmen mavi, ibecceô lmumnin i ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar i nitni akafi meqqwôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2039,
            "text": "Wanag wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, Nhegga yasen d aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 240,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2040,
            "text": "Amdan issawal i cceôô, akken issawal i lxiô. Amdan izga d aêemmaq.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2041,
            "text": "Nerra, iv akked wass, d sin issekniyen. Assekni n yiv Nerra d tellis, Nerra win n wass d win ipwalin, iwakken a pnadim lfevl n Mass nnwen, a ppissinem amvan iseggwasen, akked leêsab. Yal taawsa, Nfeûûel ip akken iwata.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2042,
            "text": "I yal amdan, Ncudd as lbext is s amgarv is. Ass n tnekra, ad as d Nessuffe tazmamt ara iaf teldi.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2043,
            "text": "'£eô tazmamt ik! Tqaddev, assa, s yiman ik, i uqeîîi k'.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2044,
            "text": "Win ipwanhan, i iman is kan, win innetlafen, innetlaf mgal iman is kan. Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev. Ur Nekkat, alamma Nuzen amazan.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2045,
            "text": "Ma Neba a Nesqucc tamdint, Neppak lameô i isâiyen is, ad xedmen, degs, cceôô. Ad iâaddi fellas Wawal, a p Nhudd wakali.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2046,
            "text": "Acêal n tsuta ay Nesqucc, deffir Nuê! Ad Iqadd Mass ik, i tussna akked tmeéôiwt ibekkaven n imdanen iS.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 283,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2047,
            "text": "Win iban taêemmaqt, Nezzazzal as degs, i £ ihwan, i win i £ Neba. Sinna, Nerra yas Loahennama ad din iô, indell, ippuveggeô.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2048,
            "text": "Win iban laxeôt, iaâzem fellas yal laâzem, u neppa iumen; widak, tajmilt i laâzem nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2049,
            "text": "I akw, i wigi d wiyav, Nwessaâ tikci suô Mass ik. Tikci n Mass ik, ur meêdudet.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2050,
            "text": "Wali amek Nesmenyaf kra i wiyav. War ccekk, di laxeôt, lfeôq d usmenyef, ad ilin sennig waya.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2051,
            "text": "Ur sâu, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, mulac a ppualev d imdelli, d imveggaâ.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 241,
            "hizbQuarter": 113,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2052,
            "text": "Iseyya d Mass ik: ur tâabdem siwa Neppa, elhut ar imawlan. Ma, uôek wesser yiwen, ne ma wessren i sin, ur asen qqaô: 'ttfuh'! Ur ten ppara. Mmeslay asen s lkyasa.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2053,
            "text": "Zger fellasen tacvat n lmaênana. Ini: 'a Mass iw! Ëun fellasen, akken iyi d ssekren d amejtuê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2054,
            "text": "Mass nnwen Yif akw akken Issen, i illan deg iman nnwen. Ma telham, Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê wid isteôoiâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2055,
            "text": "Efk i llezm ik amur is, akw i umebun akked win d ibbwi ubrid. Ur pjeggiê d ajeggeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2056,
            "text": "Ijeggaêen, s tidep, d atmaten n Cciîan. Cciîan ijhel ar Mass is.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 284,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2057,
            "text": "Ma tfuôqev ten, tôebev u tegguniv aêunu suô Mass ik, ini yasen awal aéidan.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2058,
            "text": "Ur pcuddu afus ik ar yiri k, ur as berru aîas, mulac a ppualev d ambaûi, d amebun.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2059,
            "text": "S tidep, Mass ik Iennu win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali, Issen imdanen iS.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 242,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2060,
            "text": "Ur Neqqet arraw nnwen, ma tugadem tiggulelt. D Nekwni ara ten Iôezqen, kunwi yidsen. Ih, timeniwt nnsen d tucmip meqqwôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2061,
            "text": "Ur zennut, d ayen n dir, d abrid ucmit.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2062,
            "text": "Ur neqqet amdan i wen Igdel Öebbi, siwa ma di tidep. Win ipwanan s ledeô, ihi, a Nefk adabu i walag is. Ur ipjuôôu di tmeniwt, ihi, neppa, ad ippusellek.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2063,
            "text": "Ur pnalet ayla ugujil, siwa ar wayen imaânen, ar d immeêtel. Qadôet lemâahda; ih, lemâahda s usteqsi.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2064,
            "text": "Qadôet lkil ma tektalem, weznet s lmizan imaânen. Yif it wakka, a ppelhu taggara.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2065,
            "text": "Ur îîafaô ayen ur tessinev. Timejjin, iéôi, ul, s tidep, ad ppuseqsin akw.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2066,
            "text": "Ur teddu di tmurt, d amzuxxi. Ih, keçç ur tezmirev, d awezi, a pneqôev tamurt, ne a ppessiwvev laâli idurar.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2067,
            "text": "Adiran, deg waya akw, Ikerh it Mass ik.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 285,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2068,
            "text": "Ayagi, seg wayen i k Iweêêa Mass ik, n ûûwab. Ur ppara, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, mulac a ppepwaveggôev ar Loahennama d ambaûi, d amnafeq.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2069,
            "text": "Day wen d Ifren Mass nnwen arrac, u Iddem, i iman iS, tullas, si lmalayek? S tidep, kunwi tegrem d awal anecilat.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 243,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2070,
            "text": "Ih, ay d Nebbwi di Leqwôan agi, iwakken a d mmektin. I yasen d irna, siwa aunfu.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2071,
            "text": "Ini: 'lemmer llin yides iôebbiten, akken la d qqaôen, yili ad nadin abrid ara ten iawin ar n Bab n usgeld'.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2072,
            "text": "Gedha s yiS, aîas i Aâlay sennig wayen d qqaôen!",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2073,
            "text": "Ppanzen aS igenwan di ûa, tamurt, u wayen illan degsen. Ur illi wayen ur aS neppanez, ur T Nesbuccuâ s ccekôan. Maca, ur tfehmem ara annuz nnsen. Ih, Neppa Iêellem, Ipsemmiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2074,
            "text": "Mara teqqaôev Leqwôan, Neppara, garak d wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, aêurrim abavni.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2075,
            "text": "Nerra ef ulawen nnsen ssteô, iwakken ur t fehmen; di tmejjin nnsen, tiâéegt. Ma tesmektiv d, di Leqwôan, Mass ik d Yiwen, ad zzin akin, s uunfu.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2076,
            "text": "Nekwni, Nif akw akken Neéôa, acu iwumi sellen, mara k ssemêasen, mara hedôen, mi qqaôen imednas: 'la teppeddum kan d urgaz iwumi sseêren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2077,
            "text": "Wali amek i k d bbwin imedyaten. Nnetlafen. Ur zmiren ad afen abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2078,
            "text": "Nnan: 'day mi nual d isan, d awebbaô, d ûûeê a d nual di lxelq amaynut'?",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 286,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 114,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2079,
            "text": "Ini: 'ilit d azôu ne d uzzal,",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2080,
            "text": "ne d lxelq id iusan deg idmaren nnwen'. A d inin: 'anwa ara a  d irren'? Ini: 'd Win ikwen id Ixelqen, abrid amenzu'. Ad huzen iqweôôa nnsen uôek, ad inin: 'melmi ayagi'? Ini: 'izmer ad yili iqeôb ed'.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2081,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara awen d Isiwel, a d tjawbem s ccekôan iS, a pilem cwiî kan ay teqqimem.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 244,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2082,
            "text": "Ini i imdanen iw ad inin awal ifuqen. Cciîan, s tidep, isskar ameôéi garasen. Ih, Cciîan d acengu n ûûeê i umdan.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2083,
            "text": "Mass nnwen Yif akw akken ikwen Issen. Ad Iêun fellawen, ma Iba; a kwen Iâaqeb ma Iba. Ur k id Nuzen ara d awkil nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2084,
            "text": "Mass ik Yif akw akken Iéôa i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ni Nesmenyaf kra n lambiyya i wiyav. I Dawed Nefka Ihellilen.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2085,
            "text": "Ini: 'nujet eô wid tepkabarem, war Neppa. Ur zmiren ad awen kksen ccqa, ne a t bedlen.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2086,
            "text": "Wigi uuô la pnujun, la pqelliben ppawil ara ten isqeôben nezzeh ar Mass nnsen. Ssaramen aêunu S, ppagwaden aâaqeb iS'. Ih, aâaqeb n Mass ik, issagwad.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2087,
            "text": "Ur telli temdint ur Nesquccu, uqbel ass n tnekra, ne ur Nâaqeb s leqseê. Ayagi iura di Tezmamt.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 287,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2088,
            "text": "I £ iîîfen ef uceggaâ issekniyen, d nnkeô nnsen, kan, suô imezwura. Nuzen ed talwemt i Tamud, d ayen pwalin. Densen p. Ur d Neppazen issekniyen siwa i ussigwed.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2089,
            "text": "Mi k Nenna: 'Mass ik, s tidep, Izzi i imdanen'. Ma dayen i k Nerra teéôiv t, d ahewwel kan i medden. Akken ttejôa tamenâult di Leqwôan. Nessagwad iten. Ay sen d irennu siwa nnfaq ameqwôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 245,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2090,
            "text": "Mi Nenna i lmalayek: 'knumt i Adem', knant, siwa Iblis. Inna: 'day ad knu i win Txelqev s talaxt'?",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2091,
            "text": "Inna: 'Twalav wagi i Tâuzzev sennig iw, lemmer a yi Teooev, ar ass n tnekra, war ccekk, ad wu tarwa s, siwa ixeîîayen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2092,
            "text": "Inna: 'Öuê! Wid, segsen, i iddan yidek, ihi, aqeîîi nnwen d Loahennama, d aqeîîi meqqwôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2093,
            "text": "Laâaj win iwumi tzemôev, degsen, s tawect ik. £ewwes fellasen s imnayen ik, d iterrasen ik. Ecrek yidsen ayla, tarwa. Âahed asen'. I yasen iâahed Cciîan, siwa auôôu.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2094,
            "text": "' Ma d imdanen iW, ur tesâiv adabu fellasen'. Mass ik Iqadd d Awkil.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2095,
            "text": "Mass nnwen, i wen Isselêayen lbabuô di yill, a pnadim lfevl iS. Ih, Neppa Ipêunu fellawen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 288,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2096,
            "text": "Ma tevôa yidwen lmuûiba di yill, ayen uuô tepnujum, war Neppa, ittellif. Mi kwen Isellek ar lberr, twexxôem. Amdan izga d lkaraâ.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2097,
            "text": "Day tilem ur Ipseggix ara tamurt yiswen, ne ur awen d Ippazen ara tabucivant, da ur teppafem awkil?",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2098,
            "text": "Ne day tilem ur kwen id Ippara ara tikelt nniven, ad awen d Iazen aûeôûaô, a kwen Imes ilmend n tijehli nnwen, sinna ur teppafem, mgal a£, amalal?",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 115,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2099,
            "text": "Ni Nkeyyes tarwa n Adem. Nebbwi ten di lberr, di yill, Nat iten s wayen ilhan, Nesmenyaf iten, nezzeh, i waîas seg wid i Nexleq.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 246,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2100,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara Nenced akw imdanen, s imvebôen nnsen; win id tusa tezmamt is yeffus is, widak ad ôen tazmamt nnsen, ur pwadensen s tissegnit;",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 247,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2101,
            "text": "win illan d aderal di tagi, ad yili d aderal di laxeôt, ad izid di tuffa n ubrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 247,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2102,
            "text": "S tidep, qôib i k hewwlen ef wayen i k d Nweêêa, a d tesnulfuv ayen nniven, mgal a£. Da, a k rren d aêbib.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 247,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2103,
            "text": "Lemmer ur k Ntebbet ara, qôib tmalev cwiî uôsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 247,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2104,
            "text": "Yili ad ak Nesâaddi tudert akked tmeppant, berdayen, sinna, ur teppafev, mgal a£, w ara k isellken.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 289,
            "ruku": 247,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2105,
            "text": "Ih, qôib i k id srewlen si tmurt, a k id ssuffen segs. Yili cwiî kan ara d gwrin, deffir ek.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 247,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2106,
            "text": "D tannumi imazanen nne£, id Nuzen, uqbel ik. Ur teppafev ara abeddel, di lâadda nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 247,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2107,
            "text": "Bedd i téallit mi istula yiîij, alamma d tellis n yiv. Leqwôan, tafrara. Ih, Leqwôan, tafrara, isâa inagan.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 248,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2108,
            "text": "Aâwez yis kra n yiv, d nnafila k, amar a k id Irr Mass ik, deg umkan i pcekkiôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 248,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2109,
            "text": "Ini: 'a Mass iw! Ssekcem iyi, anekcum n tidep. Ssuffe iyi, tuffa n tidep. Efk iyi, suôeK, adabu ipselliken'.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 248,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2110,
            "text": "Ini: 'tusa d tidep, abent tkerkas. Ih, tikerkas ilaq ad abent'.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 248,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2111,
            "text": "Nesrusu d, si Leqwôan, ayen illan d êellu akked uêunu i lmumnin. I irennu, i imednas, siwa lexsaôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 248,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2112,
            "text": "Ma Nat amdan ad iwexxeô, ad iveôôef iman is. Ma iêuza t wugur ad iayes.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 248,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2113,
            "text": "Ini: 'yal yiwen ixeddem akken ipwali. Mass nnwen Yif akw akken i Issen anwa i ipwanhan kteô'.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 248,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2114,
            "text": "Steqsan k id ef ôôuê. Ini: 'ôôuê si lameô n Mass iw. Drus kan n tmusni i wen ippunefken'.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2115,
            "text": "Ma ihwa ya£, a Nekkes ayen i k Nweêêa. Da ur teppafev, mgal a£, awkil,",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 290,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2116,
            "text": "siwa aêunu suô Mass ik. Ih, lfevl iS, i keçç, izga meqqweô.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2117,
            "text": "Ini: 'lemmer ad mlilen imdanen akked leonun, iwakken a d awin am Leqwôan agi, ur d ppawin i t icban, xas mâawanen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2118,
            "text": "Ni Nefka d i imdanen, di Leqwôan agi, si yal imedyaten. Tegwti n yimdanen ur bin, siwa tijehli.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2119,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ur k neppamen alamma tesfeggvev a d abalu, si tmurt;",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2120,
            "text": "ne, tesâiv leonan n tezdayin akked tfeôôant, ideg feggven isaffen;",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2121,
            "text": "ne, a d tesseliv igenni d ifeûlan, akken i  tzuxxev; ne, a d tasev s Öebbi akked lmalayek, zdat nne;",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2122,
            "text": "Ne a ppesâuv axxam imzewweq, ne a ppaliv s igenni. Ur neppamen, s walluy ik, alamma tessersev ane d tazmamt ara neô'. Ini: 'gedha s Mass iw! Day lli d ayen nniven, siwa d amdan amazan'?",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 249,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2123,
            "text": "I iîîfen imdanen ur uminen, mi ten id tusa nnhaya, mara d inin kan: 'Iuzen ed Öebbi amdan d amazan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 250,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2124,
            "text": "Ini: 'lemmer llint, di tmurt, lmalayek, teddunt di laman, yili Nessers asent ed, seg igenni, lmelk amazan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 250,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2125,
            "text": "Ini: 'Iqadd Mass iw d Anagi, gari yidwen. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali imdanen iS, Issen iten'.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 291,
            "ruku": 250,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2126,
            "text": "Win Inha Öebbi, atan idda d ubrid. Wid Itlef, ur asen teppafev imawlan, war Neppa, d awezi. A ten id Nefser ass n tnekra ef udmawen nnsen, drelen, gugmen, âaégen. Axxam nnsen d Loahennama. Mi tenqes tmes, ad asen Nernu ajajiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 250,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2127,
            "text": "D wagi ay d aqeîîi nnsen, imi nekôen issekniyen nne£, u nnan: 'day mi nual d isan, d awebbaô, a d nual di lxelq amaynut'?",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 250,
            "hizbQuarter": 116,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2128,
            "text": "Ne, day ur walan ara ar Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, Izmer a d Ixleq i ten icban? Irra yasen lajel, ur degs ccekk. Ur bin imednas, siwa tijehli.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 250,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2129,
            "text": "Ini: 'lemmer tesâim igerrujen uêunu n Mass iw, ur ten tepnalem, a ppagwadem a ten tûeôôfem. Amdan izga d imceêêi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 250,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2130,
            "text": "Ni Nefka, i Musa, tza issekniyen iberrzen. Steqsi At Isôail. Mi d iusa uôsen, inna yas Ferâun: 'a Musa! Nek, wala, war ccekk, seêêern ak'.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2131,
            "text": "Inna: 'ni teéôiv ur d issers yiwen wigi, d tiftilin, siwa Mass n tmurt akked igenwan. Nek, wala, a Ferâun, war ccekk, tîeêênev'.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2132,
            "text": "Iba a ten iééaâ si tmurt, Nemmeq it, akked wid iddan yides, meôôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2133,
            "text": "Deffir es, Nenna i At Isôail: 'zedet tamurt. Mi d tusa lemâahda n laxeôt, a kwen id Nawi, d îayfat'.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 292,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2134,
            "text": "Nessers it id s tidep. S tidep, ay d irs. Nuzen ik id, kan, i ubecceô d uneddeô.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 293,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2135,
            "text": "Leqwôan Nfeôq it, iwakken a t temlev i medden, s laâqel. Nessader it id, s leôv.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 293,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2136,
            "text": "Ini: 'amnet yis, ne qqimet'. Ih, ma mlan t i wid tebbwev tussna, uqbel is, ad lin ef udmawen, knan.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 293,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2137,
            "text": "Ad inin: 'gedha s Mass nne! Tûaô lemâahda n Mass nne'.",
