            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 293,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2138,
            "text": "Ad lin ef udmawen s imeîîawen. Ad innerni wannuz nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 293,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 4,
              "recommended": true,
              "obligatory": false
            }
          },
          {
            "number": 2139,
            "text": "Ini: 'nujet er Öebbi, ne nujet er Uênin. Akken tnujem, ineS ismawen imaânen yifen akw wiyav'. Di téallit ik, ur saâlay ûûut ik, ur t ssrusu. Ad isker kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 293,
            "ruku": 251,
            "hizbQuarter": 117,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2140,
            "text": "Ini: 'ccekôan i Öebbi, ur Nesâi aqcic, ur Nesâi acrik di tgelda, ur Nesâi bab mgal asdullu'. Ssemweô iT yal temweô.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 15,
            "manzil": 4,
