            "hizbQuarter": 121,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2219,
            "text": "Lbabuô nni, n igellilen i ixedmen di yill. Bi a t ôée, acku yiwen ugellid, deffir sen, itekkes yal lbabuô, s yiil.",
