            "page": 302,
            "ruku": 261,
            "hizbQuarter": 121,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2221,
            "text": "Neba ad asen d Irr, Mass nnsen, it yifen: win iûfan, iqeôben nezzeh aêunu.",
