            "ruku": 262,
            "hizbQuarter": 121,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2239,
            "text": "Assen, a ten Neoo ad ddehmen wa ef wa. Aûuvu di lbuq, da a ten Nessemlil akw.",
