            "text": "Izzi Ferâun, ijmaâ ed ccbukat is, da iusa d.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 315,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2409,
            "text": "Inna yasen Musa:'a tawait nnwen! Ur d garet tikerkas ef Öebbi, a kwen Isxev s uâaqeb. Ni ad ixseô win d igren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 315,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2410,
            "text": "Mcawaôen f lameô nnsen, ffren ayen mmeslayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 315,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2411,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ihi, sin agi d iseêêaren, ban a kwen ssuffen seg wakal nnwen, s ssêur nnsen. Ad kksen abrid nnwen amxallef.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 315,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2412,
            "text": "Jemâat ed ccbukat nnwen, sinna aset ed d leûfuf. Ni ad irbeê, assa, win iufraren'!",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 315,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2413,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Musa! A pveggôev keçç, ne d nekwni ara iveggôen d imezwura'?",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2414,
            "text": "Inna: 'xaîi, veggôet'! Si ssêur nnsen, iwala amzun leêêun imraren akked tâakwzin nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2415,
            "text": "Musa, deg iman is, iêus i lxuf.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2416,
            "text": "Nenna: 'ur ppagwad! Keçç, s tidep, sennig sen.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2417,
            "text": "Veggeô i illan deg ufus ik ayeffus! Ad isseblaâ ay d snulfan'. Ay d snulfan, siwa ccbukat iseêêaren. Anda idda useêêar, ur irebbeê ara.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2418,
            "text": "£¨lin iseêêaren, knan, nnan: 'numen s Mass n Haôun akked Musa'.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2419,
            "text": "Inna: 'day tumnem yiS, uqbel i wen serrêe? Neppa, zi, d ameqwôan nnwen. Isêefv awen ssêur. War ccekk, ad awen gezme, avaô sya, afus sya, u a kwen ûemmôe af umidag n leodar n tezdayin. A ppeéôem, s tidep, anwa ay d bab uâaqeb meqqwôen, u ara idumen sennig wiyav'.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2420,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ur k nesmenyaf, d awezi, i wayen i  d iusan ubeggen, akw i Win i  Ixelqen. Seyyi i k ihwan a pseyyiv. Aseyyi k, d aseyyi ef tmeddurt n ddunit agi kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2421,
            "text": "Ih, numen s Mass nne, iwakken ad a Isemmeê tuccva nne, akked wayen n ssêur i têeppmev fellane. Pifxiô Öebbi d Imezgi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2422,
            "text": "Ih, Loahennama i win iusan ar Mass is, d abewvi. Ur ipmeppat degs, ur d ippidir.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2423,
            "text": "Win i iusan uôeS d lmumen u ixdem ayen ilhan, widak ad ilin deg imukan aâlayen mavi,",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2424,
            "text": "leonanat n Âaden, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen din. Ayagi, d akafi i win zeddigen.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 316,
            "ruku": 272,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2425,
            "text": "Ni Nweêêa i Musa: 'ôuê, deg iv, akked imdanen iW. Egg asen abrid akiwan, di yill. Ur ppagwad a kwen in vefôen, ur ppiwêic'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2426,
            "text": "Ferâun, s iâsekôiwen is, vefôen ten. Isseblaâ ten yill, içça ten.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2427,
            "text": "Itlef Ferâun agdud is, ur inhi.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2428,
            "text": "A yAt Isôail! Ni Nsellek ikwen seg ucangu nnwen. Nefka yawen ppaâud, ar loiha tayeffus n udrar. Nessers awen d lmenna, ifeôôuoen.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2429,
            "text": "Eççet si lmakla ilhan, i s ikwen Nat. Ur zegret tilas fellas, mulac a kwen immager urrif iW. Win immuger urrif iW, ni igrareb.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2430,
            "text": "U Nek, s tidep, Psemmiêe i win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, da ipwanha.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 126,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2431,
            "text": "'Acu i k ieûben seg ugdud ik, a Musa'?",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2432,
            "text": "Inna: 'zgan deffir i. £awle d ureK, a Mass iw, iwakken a Pôaviv'.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2433,
            "text": "Inna: 'ih, ni Njeôôeb agdud ik, deffir ek. Itelf iten Usamiri'.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2434,
            "text": "Iual ed Musa s agdud is, s zzâaf d wumri. Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Day ur awen Ifka ara, Mass nnwen, lemâahda lâali? Day tâaîîel fellawen lemâahda? Ne day tebam a kwen immager urrif n Mass nnwen? Tzeglem ppaâud iw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2435,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ur nezgil ppaâud ik, s lebi nne. Maca, nbubb tiâakkwmin n ôôêuê n ugdud, da nveggeô iten. Akken i iveggeô Usamiri'.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 317,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2436,
            "text": "Issuffe asen d aâejmi, d ameslux isrugmuten. Nnan: 'wagi d ôebbi nnwen u d ôebbi n Musa. Ippu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2437,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara, ur asen d ippara awal, ur izmir a ten ivuôô, ne a ten infaâ?",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 273,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2438,
            "text": "Ni Haôun inna yasen, uqbel: 'a yagdud iw! Teppuhewwlem kan, yis. Mass nnwen, s tidep, d Aênin. Ddut yidi, vefôet lameô iw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2439,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ur tnepfukku akaber is, d awezi, alamma iual ed Musa uône'.",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2440,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Haôun! D acu i k iîîfen, mi ten twalav nnetlafen?",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2441,
            "text": "Day ur teddiv ara yidi? Day tugiv lameô iw'?",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2442,
            "text": "Inna: 'a mmi s n yimma! Ur iyi ppaîîaf si tamart iw, ne seg uqeôôu w. Nek, s tideps, ugade ad iyi d tiniv: tessemfaôaqev At Isôail, ur tuev awal iw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2443,
            "text": "Inna: 'd acu t leqsed ik a Usamiri'?",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2444,
            "text": "Inna: 'wala ayen ur walan. Ddme d tummeét n lateô umazan, veggôe p. Akka ay êusse deg iman iw'.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2445,
            "text": "Inna: 'ôuê ihi, a ppevôu yidek di tmeddurt a ppeqqaôev: ur iyi pnalet! U, s tidep, uôek ppaâud ik ur tezmirev a t tzeglev. Muqel ôebbi ik, uuô mazal teqqimev, ard a t nesseô, a t ssebruzzaâ ar yill, wakali'.",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2446,
            "text": "Mass nnwen, siwa Öebbi. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Tamusni S tjemmel yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 318,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2447,
            "text": "Akka i k Nêekku, seg isallen n zik. Ni Nefka yak d, suône£, asmekti.",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2448,
            "text": "Win i s iwexxôen, ad iâabbi taâkkwemt, ass n tnekra.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2449,
            "text": "Ad wekkôen dinna. Ay dir ip fellasen ppaâbga, ass n tnekra!",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2450,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara d ûuven di lbuq, a d Nefser ibewviyen, zgezwen assen.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2451,
            "text": "Ad swecwicen wa i wa: 'mraw kan i teqqimem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2452,
            "text": "Nekwni, Nif akw akken Nessen, ayen d qqaôen, mi sen inna yiwen umxallef degsen: 'teqqimem kan ibwass'.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 274,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2453,
            "text": "Steqsayen k ef idurar. Ini: 'a ten Issebruzzaâ Mass iw, d iwzan.",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2454,
            "text": "A ten Irr d azaaô ibuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2455,
            "text": "Ur tepwaliv degs i iâawjen, ne i izzren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2456,
            "text": "Assen, ad vefôen aberraê, war zzrug. Ad irs ûûut zdat Uênin, a ppeslev kan i uswecwec.",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2457,
            "text": "Assen, ur ten tenfaâ ccafuâa, siwa i win Iooa Uênin, u Iôuva t ef wawal.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2458,
            "text": "Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ur illi sanda ara T issinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 127,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2459,
            "text": "Ad îîinzen wudmawen i Umuddir n lebda. Ara ixesôen d win ibubben ddens.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2460,
            "text": "Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan, u neppa iumen, ur ippagwad ddens, ne aqhaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2461,
            "text": "Akka, Nessers it id, d Leqwôan s taâôabt. Nenewwel ed, degs, aâeggen, amar ad êezben, u a ten id ias usmekti.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 319,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2462,
            "text": "D Ameqwôan Öebbi, Agellid, Tidep. Ur pêiri, di tuôi, uqbel ma ifukk uweêêi s, uôek. Ini: 'a Mass iw! Ernu yi di tmusni'.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 320,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2463,
            "text": "Ni Nâahed, zik, Adem. Ippu, ur Nufi uôes laâzem.",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 320,
            "ruku": 275,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2464,
            "text": "Mi Nenna i lmalayek: 'knumt i Adem', knant, siwa Iblis i iugin.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 320,
            "ruku": 276,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2465,
            "text": "Nenna: 'a Adem, wagi, s tidep, d acengu k, akked tmeîîut ik. £urwat a kwen id issuffe, si Loennet, a pweblem.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 320,
            "ruku": 276,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2466,
            "text": "Ih, keçç, degs, ur teplaéev, ur tâarruv.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 320,
            "ruku": 276,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2467,
            "text": "S tidep, keçç, degs, ur tepfadev, ur k iîîuôôu yiîij'.",
            "numberInSurah": 119,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 320,
            "ruku": 276,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2468,
            "text": "Iwa t Cciîan, inna: 'a Adem, ad ak ssekne ttejôa uwekkeô, akw n tgelda n lebda'?",
            "numberInSurah": 120,
            "juz": 16,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 320,
            "ruku": 276,
            "hizbQuarter": 128,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2469,
