            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 335,
            "ruku": 287,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2620,
            "text": "Ih, i wid ijehlen i issefôaen abrid n Öebbi, akked Loamaâ n Lêaôam, i Nerra i imdanen, ama d amezda n din, ama d abeôôani; i win iban degs tijehli, s ddens, a Nesâaddi aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 335,
            "ruku": 287,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2621,
            "text": "Mi Nhegga i Ibôahim, amkan n Uxxam: 'ur iyI pcarak acemma! Zizdeg axxam iW i wid idewwiôen, wid ibedden, wid iîîinizen, iknan.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 335,
            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2622,
            "text": "Enced medden ar lêio. A d asen uôek ef uvaô, ne ef yal amerkub ulîif. A d asen si yal abrid ibaâden.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 335,
            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2623,
            "text": "Ad cehhden ef lit nnsen. A d smektin ism n Öebbi, deg ussan ipwassnen, ef ubhim n lmal i sen Ifka. Eççet segs, cceççet amebun, aéawali.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
