            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2624,
            "text": "Sinna, ad ssirden, ad qenâen asirem nnsen, ad dewwôen i Uxxam aqdim'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 335,
            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2625,
            "text": "Akka. Win ippâuzzun ayen Igdel Öebbi, ilha yas kteô, ar Mass is. Ëellen awen lmal, siwa wid i wen mlan. Janbet lâaô n tâancuôin, janbet awal n ééuô;",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 335,
            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2626,
            "text": "am wid imalen ar tidep ar Öebbi, ur aS pcaraken. Win ipcaraken i Öebbi, amzun ili d seg igenni, u iccelqef it ufôux, ne inheô it wavu, s amekkan lqayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2627,
            "text": "Akka. Win ippâuzzun isekkiren n Öebbi, ihi, d aêezzeb n wulawen.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2628,
            "text": "I kunwi degs abauô ar lajel ipwassnen, sinna, îêegga nnsen ar Uxxam aqdim.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 288,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2629,
            "text": "I yal lois, Nefka asekkir, iwakken a d smektin ism n Öebbi, ef ubhim n lmal is iten Nat. Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen. Ihi, anzet aS. Becceô itubiyen,",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 289,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2630,
            "text": "wid iwumi ppergigin wulawen nnsen mara d mmektin Öebbi, wid iûebbôen i wayen iten iuen, wid ipéallan u pseddiqen seg wayen is iten Nat.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 289,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2631,
            "text": "Lmal iqebbwan, Nerra yawen ten, seg isekkiren n Öebbi. Degsen lfayda i kunwi. Bedret fellasen isem n Öebbi, mara d rsen. Mi lin ef ibeôdiyen nnsen, eççet segsen, cceççet aâîîaô, aéawali. Akka ay d Nenub fellawen yissen, amar a ppesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 289,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2632,
            "text": "Ur ippawev ar Öebbi uksum nnsen, ne idamen nnsen, d awezi. Ara T iawven, d aêezzeb nnwen. Am akka, Inub fellawen yissen, iwakken ad aS tgem ccan i Öebbi, ilmend n nnhaya nnwen suôeS. Becceô wid imaânen.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 289,
            "hizbQuarter": 134,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2633,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi Ipfukku wid iumnen. Ih, Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara yal lxayen ajehli.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 336,
            "ruku": 289,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2634,
            "text": "Tsriê i wid ipwawwven imi pwadensen - Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer a ten Isellek -,",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 337,
            "ruku": 290,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2635,
            "text": "wid id ssuffen seg ixxamen nnsen, war ssebba, imi kan qqaôen: 'Mass nne d Öebbi'. Lemmer ur Iswexxiô ara Öebbi imdanen, kra s kra, ara ipwahudden, war ccekk, d tiqwebtin, timezgida, lemûellat, lowamaâ ideg d smektayen, aîas, ism n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ippaâwan win iT ippaâwanen. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uohid, d Uzmir.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 337,
            "ruku": 290,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2636,
            "text": "Wid, ma Nessqâad iten di tmurt, bedden i téallit, pzekkin, ppamôen lewqama, gedlen tuccva. Ar Öebbi ara d gwrin lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 337,
            "ruku": 290,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2637,
            "text": "Ma skaddben k, ni skaddben, uqbel nnsen, igduden n Nuê, Âad, akked Tamud,",
