            "page": 337,
            "ruku": 290,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2640,
            "text": "Acêal n temdinin ay Nesqucc imi densent. Haatent ppint. Xlan lebyar, akked lebruo uohiden.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 337,
            "ruku": 290,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2641,
            "text": "Day ur unagen ara di tmurt? Ad sâun, ef waya, ulawen ad fehmen yissen, imeééuen ara islen yissen. Maca, maççi d allen, d ulawen deg idmaren i idrelen.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 17,
