            "page": 338,
            "ruku": 291,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2647,
            "text": "Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, amazan ne nnbi, mebla ma ikecm ed Cciîan, deg wayen imenna, ma imenna. Itekkes Öebbi ayen d issekcam Cciîan, sinna, Itebbit issekniyen iS. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 338,
            "ruku": 291,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2648,
            "text": "Iwakken ad Irr aggway n Cciîan d ahewwel, i at wulawen iblan akked at wulawen aquôan. Ih, imednas atnan di tennant tumiqt.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 338,
            "ruku": 291,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2649,
            "text": "Iwakken ad éôen wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni, ar neppa d tidep, suô Mass ik. Ad amnen yis. Ad as anzen wulawen nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Inehhu wid iumnen, s abrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 338,
            "ruku": 291,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2650,
            "text": "Zgan wid ijehlen di ccekk fellas, ar ten id ias yimir, deqzalla, ne ibbwev iten id uâaqeb n wass abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 338,
            "ruku": 291,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2651,
            "text": "Assen, tagelda i Öebbi. Ad Iêudd garasen. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad ilin di Loennet n ssuâada.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 291,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2652,
            "text": "I wid ijehlen, iskaddben issekniyen nne£, aâaqeb isdullun.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 291,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2653,
            "text": "Wid iunagen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, sinna, pwanan ne mmuten, a ten Iit Öebbi, war ccekk, s ôôeéq umâin. Ih, Öebbi Yif akw imiten.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 292,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2654,
            "text": "A ten Issekcem anekcum ara ôadin. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 292,
            "hizbQuarter": 135,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2655,
            "text": "Akka. Win iâaqben akken ippuâaqeb, sinna, ipwadnes, war ccekk, a t Isellek Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ipqili, Ipsemmiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 292,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2656,
            "text": "Akka, acku Öebbi Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. U Öebbi Issel, Ipwali.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 292,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2657,
            "text": "Akka, acku Öebbi d tidep, ma d ayen uuô pnujun, war Neppa, d tikerkas. Ih, Öebbi d Aâlâyan, d Ameqwôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 292,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2658,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara Öebbi Isseli d aman, seg igenni, da izzegzew wakal? Ih, Öebbi d Laîif, Iéôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 292,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2659,
            "text": "IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ih, Öebbi, ar Neppa d Asâay d Amaâzuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 339,
            "ruku": 292,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2660,
            "text": "Ur twalav ara Öebbi Inub ed fellawen s wayen illan di tmurt, akked lbabur ippazalen di yill, s lameô iS. Iîîef igenni ur d ielli f tmurt, siwa ma Iunef as. Ih, Öebbi, war ccekk, Issuruf u Ipêunu i imdanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2661,
            "text": "D Neppa ikwen Issadren, sinna, ara kwen Inen, sinna, ara kwen id Issadren. Amdan, s tidep, d ajehli.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2662,
            "text": "I yal lois, Nefka asekkir, teddun degs. Ulayeô i k pnaen ef lameô. Nuj ar Mass ik; ih, aql ak, keçç, di nnhaya tuwqimt.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2663,
            "text": "Ma numren k, ini: 'Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2664,
            "text": "Öebbi ad Iêudd garawen, ass n tnekra, ef wayen tellam temgarradem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2665,
            "text": "Day ur teéôiv ara Öebbi Issen i illan deg igenni akked tmurt? Ayagi, s tidep, di Tezmamt. Ih, ayagi ishel i Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2666,
            "text": "La âabden, war Öebbi, ayen iwumi ur d Issers adabu, ayen ur ssinen. Imednas, ur illi wa ara ten isellken.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2667,
            "text": "Ma mlan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, a pâaqlev asmmummi deg udmawen n wid ijehlen. Qôib ad éevmen ef wid i sen iqqaôen issekniyen nne£. Ini: 'a kwen xebbôe af wayen ielben aya: times i Iâahed Öebbi i wid ijehlen'. A tualin tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 340,
            "ruku": 293,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2668,
            "text": "A yimdanen! Ippunefk ed umedya, selt as d: ih, wid uuô tepnujum, war Öebbi, ur zmiren, d awezi, a d xelqen izi, xas mlalen ef waya. Ma illa wayen i sen iuker yizi, ur zmiren ad as t id kksen. D uôhif umsuter, d uôhif win issuter.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 341,
            "ruku": 294,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2669,
            "text": "Ur qudôen ara Öebbi, azal n lqedô iS. Ih, Öebbi d Uohid, d Uzmir.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 341,
            "ruku": 294,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2670,
            "text": "Öebbi Iferren imazanen ger lmalayek, u ger imdanen. Ih, Öebbi Issel, Ipwali.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 341,
            "ruku": 294,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2671,
            "text": "Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ar Öebbi ad ualen lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 341,
            "ruku": 294,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2672,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ïîinzet u knut, âabdet Mass nnwen, xedmet lxiô, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 341,
            "ruku": 294,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 7,
              "recommended": true,
              "obligatory": false
            }
          },
          {
            "number": 2673,
            "text": "Jahdet ar Öebbi lêeqq ujahed iS. Neppa Ifren ikwen. Ur kwen Ihejjen ara di ddin, ddin ubabat wen Ibôahim. Neppa, i wen isemman, zik, imvuâen. Deg waya, ad yili Umazan d anagi nnwen, u a ppilim d inagan n medden. Ihi, ééallet, zekkit, teîîfem di Öebbi. Neppa d Bab nnwen. D Bab amxallef, d Asellak amxallef.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 17,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 341,
            "ruku": 294,
            "hizbQuarter": 136,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
