            "hizbQuarter": 137,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2692,
            "text": "Nxelq awen, yissen, leonanat n tezdayin akked téuôin; degsen, i kunwi, aîas n yizwayen, teppeppem segsen;",
