            "ruku": 296,
            "hizbQuarter": 137,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2697,
            "text": "Nnan imvebbôen ijehliyen, n ugdud is: 'wagi d amdan kan, am kunwi; iba a d ikk sennig wen. Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, a d Issers lmalayek. Ur nesli s waya, ar lejdud nne imezwura.",
