          {
            "number": 2706,
            "text": "Nnan imvebbôen ijehliyen n ugdud is, wid iugin u inekôen timlilit n laxeôt, wid Nena di tmeddurt n ddunit: 'wagi d amdan kan am kunwi, itepp seg wayen teppeppem, itess seg wayen teppessem.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 137,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2707,
            "text": "Ma tessemêessem i umdan i kwen icban, war ccekk, kunwi seg imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 137,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2708,
            "text": "Day i wen iâahed ard a d teffem mara temmtem, tualem d akal, d isan?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 137,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2709,
            "text": "Ibâad, Ibâad, ayen i wen ippuwaââden.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2710,
            "text": "I illan kan, d tameddurt n ddunit. A nemmet, a nidir, nekwni ur d neppenkar.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2711,
            "text": "Neppa, d argaz kan id igren tikerkas ef Öebbi. Nekwni, ur numin yis'.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2712,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Awes iyi, skaddben iyi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2713,
            "text": "Inna: 'garane d cwiî, a d gwrin di nndama'.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2714,
            "text": "Iwwet iten usuu, s tidep. Nerra ten d rrmim. Err akin, agdud imednas!",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2715,
            "text": "Sinna, Nxelq ed, deffir sen, isuta nniven.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 344,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2716,
            "text": "Lois ur d isseqôab, ur iswexxiô, lajel is.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2717,
            "text": "Sinna, Nuzen ed imazanen nne£, wa deffir wa. Yal tikelt ideg ara d ias umazan, ar lois is, a t skiddben. Nerra ten mestebâan, Nerra ten d tidyanin. Err akin, agdud ur neppamen!",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2718,
            "text": "Sinna, Nuzen ed Musa akked gma s Haôun, s issekniyen nne£, akked udabu n ûûeê,",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2719,
            "text": "eô Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Smewôen iman nnsen. Llan d agdud amzuxxi.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2720,
            "text": "Nnan: 'Day a namen sin imdanen am nekwni, u agdud nnsen d aklan nne'?",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2721,
            "text": "Skaddben ten, da ualen seg wid ipwanan.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2722,
            "text": "Ni Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, amar ad pwanhun.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2723,
            "text": "Nerra mmi s n Meryem, akked imma s, d assekni. Nesduri ten di tiilt, degs laman d waman.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 297,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2724,
            "text": "A yimazanen, eççet seg wayen imaânen, xedmet ayen ilhan, Nek, èôi ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2725,
            "text": "Lois agi nnwen, s tidep, d lois yiwen. Nek, d Mass nnwen, ihi êezbet iyI.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2726,
            "text": "Bvan lameô nnsen garasen, mi mfaôaqen. Yal akabar ifôeê s wayla s.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2727,
            "text": "Eoo iten di maylellif nnsen, tallit kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2728,
            "text": "Day ilen mi sen Nefka ayla, tarwa,",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2729,
            "text": "ad asen Nezzazal lxiô? Xaîi, ur faqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2730,
            "text": "Ih, wid, si tugwdi n Mass nnsen, pêadaren,",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2731,
            "text": "wid iumnen s issekniyen n Mass nnsen,",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2732,
            "text": "wid ur nepcarak i Mass nnsen,",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 345,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2733,
            "text": "wid ippaken ayen fkan, ulawen nnsen ugaden mi, nitni, ad ualen ar Mass nnsen,",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 346,
            "ruku": 298,
            "hizbQuarter": 138,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2734,
            "text": "widak, pêirin ar lxiô u, uôes, zeggwiren.",
