            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 347,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2758,
            "text": "A d inin: 'd Öebbi'. Ini: 'ihi, day ur d tesmektayem ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 347,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2759,
            "text": "Ini: 'anwa ay d Mass n ûa igenwan? Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan'?",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 347,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2760,
            "text": "A d inin: 'd Öebbi'. Ini: 'ihi, day ur tepêezzibem ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 347,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2761,
            "text": "Ini: 'anwa i Isâan tagelda n yal cci, ger ifassen iS; Neppa Ipêarab, ur illi uêareb fellaS, ma teppissinem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 347,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2762,
            "text": "A d inin: 'd Öebbi'. Ini: 'ihi, acimi tepwamelkem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 347,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2763,
            "text": "Xaîi! Nefka yasen tidep, nitni, war ccek, d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2764,
            "text": "Ur Isâi Öebbi mmi S. Ur illi ôebbi ar tama S. Mulac yal ôebbi ad iawi ayen id ixleq, wa ad iagwar wa. Gedha s Öebbi, seg wayen id snulfuyen!",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2765,
            "text": "Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. D Aâlayan, sennig wayen pcaraken.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 299,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2766,
            "text": "Ini: 'a Mass iw! Lemmer a yi d Tesseknev acu i sen ippuâahden.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2767,
            "text": "A Mass iw, ur iyi Ppara deg ugdud imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 94,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2768,
            "text": "'S tidep, Nezmer ad ak Nessken acu i sen Nâahed'.",
            "numberInSurah": 95,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2769,
            "text": "Err akin tucmip s lfayeq. Nekwni Neéôa, sennig wiyav, ayen d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 96,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2770,
            "text": "Ini: 'a Mass iw! Ëerz iyi seg uwayen n ccwaîen. Êë",
            "numberInSurah": 97,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2771,
            "text": "Ëerz iyi, a Mass iw! Ur dgi ppilin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 98,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2772,
            "text": "Armi, mi d tusa tmeppant yiwen degsen, inna: 'a Mass iw! Err iyi,",
            "numberInSurah": 99,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2773,
            "text": "amar ad xedme ayen ilhan deg wayen ooi'. Xaîi, d awal kan id inna. Tella, deffir es, tselit, alamma d ass n tnekra.",
            "numberInSurah": 100,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2774,
            "text": "Ma ûuven di lbuq, assen, ur ppemyilin, ur pmesteqsayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 101,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2775,
            "text": "Wid iwumi ééay lmizan nnsen, nitni rebêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 102,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2776,
            "text": "Wid iwumi fessus lmizan nnsen, d nitni i issexsôen iman nnsen. Di Loahennama ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 103,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2777,
            "text": "A ppesser tmes udmawen nnsen, ad asen zelgen icenfiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 104,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 348,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2778,
            "text": "Day ur awen qaren ara issekniyen iW, wanag la ten tnekôem?",
            "numberInSurah": 105,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2779,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a Mass nne! Ileb ane ccum nne. Nella d agdud imeôqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 106,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2780,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Ssuffe ane segs. Ma nesnager, ihi, d imednas ay nella'.",
            "numberInSurah": 107,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2781,
            "text": "Ad Yini: 'qqimet degs, ur pmeslayet'!",
            "numberInSurah": 108,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2782,
            "text": "Ih, illa urbaâ n imdanen iW i iqqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Numen. Semmeê ane, Ëun fella, Keçç Tifev akw wid ipêunun'.",
            "numberInSurah": 109,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2783,
            "text": "Tettihim fellasen armi i wen sseppun asmekti W, u tdessem degsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 110,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2784,
            "text": "Nek, assa, Kufa ten ef wayen ûebôen. D nitni, war ccekk, ay d imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 111,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2785,
            "text": "Inna: 'acêal iseggwasen i teqqimem deg wakal'?",
            "numberInSurah": 112,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2786,
            "text": "Nnan: 'Neqqim ass, ne ur ibbwiv wass, steqsi wid iêepben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 113,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2787,
            "text": "Inna: 'cwiî kan ay teqqimen, lemmer, s tidep, day tessinem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 114,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2788,
            "text": "Day tilem Nxelq ikwen, kan, di rrayaâ; ar ur d teppualem uône£?",
            "numberInSurah": 115,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2789,
            "text": "Ay Meqqweô Öebbi, Agellid, Tidep! Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ukyis.",
            "numberInSurah": 116,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2790,
            "text": "Win inaâôen, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, ur isâi ppbut fellas, aqeîîi s ar Mass is kan. Ih, ur rebêen ara ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 117,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2791,
            "text": "Ini: 'a Mass iw! Semmeê u Ëun. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun'.",
            "numberInSurah": 118,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 349,
            "ruku": 300,
            "hizbQuarter": 139,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 24,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النُّورِ",
        "englishName": "An-Noor",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Light",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 2792,
            "text": "Tasurep, Nessader ip id, Nêeppem ip id; Nessader ed, degs, issekniyen iberrzen, amar a d temmektim.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2793,
            "text": "Tin ne win iznan, jekwvet, yal yiwen segsen, tawinest iberdan; ur kwen paven ef udem n Öebbi, ma tellam tumnem s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Arbaâ n lmumnin, ad yili d anagi uâaqeb nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2794,
            "text": "Win iznan ur ippa siwa tin iznan, ne tamcarekt. Tin iznan ur p ippa siwa win iznan, ne amcarek. Ipwagdel waya i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2795,
            "text": "Wid itehmen tiâaôviyin, da ur d bbwin kué inagan, jekwvet pen îamet iberdan; ur qeblet ccada nnsen, d awezi. Widen d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2796,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid isteôoâen, deffir waya, u xedmen lfayeq. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2797,
            "text": "Wid itehmen tilawin nnsen, ur sâin inagan, siwa iman nnsen, yiwen segsen ad iggal s Öebbi, kué iberdan, ar neppa d bab n tidep,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2798,
            "text": "akked ubrid wis smus ar a t Ixzu Öebbi ma iskaddeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2799,
            "text": "Ur teppuâaqeb tmeîîut, ma teggul s Öebbi, kué iberdan, ar neppa seg wid iskadben,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2800,
            "text": "akked ubrid, wis smus ar fellas zzâaf n Öebbi, ma issawel ed tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2801,
            "text": "A lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S! Öebbi, s tidep, Issuruf, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 350,
            "ruku": 301,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2802,
            "text": "Ih, wid isweûlen tikerkas, d agraw segwen. Ur pilit d cceôô i kunwi, xaîi, d lxiô nnwen. Yal yiwen, degsen, ibbwi ayen ibbwi ubekkav. Aâaqeb abarar i win, segsen, i ibbwin amur ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2803,
            "text": "A lemmer lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, mi s slan, meyyzen lxiô, deg iman nnsen, u nnan: 'wagi d tikerkas ibanen'!",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2804,
            "text": "A lemmer d bbwin, fellas, kué inagan! Ma ur d bbwin ara inagan, ar Öebbi, wigi, d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2805,
            "text": "Lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, di ddunit akked laxeôt, a ppesâaddim aâaqeb abarar ef wayen ief temcawaôem.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2806,
            "text": "Mi p id teggarem s yilsawen nnwen, u teqqaôen s imawen nnwen ayen ur tessinem, tilem d ulac. Neppa, ar Öebbi, d abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2807,
            "text": "Lemmer, mi as teslam, tennam: 'ur a issefk ara umeslay ef waya! Gedha s yiseK! Wagi d acehrir abarar'.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2808,
            "text": "Inuba kwen Öebbi ur teppalsem, am akka, d awezi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2809,
            "text": "Ipbeggin awen Öebbi issekniyen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2810,
            "text": "Ih, wid iban a d iazel lâaô, ar wid iumnen, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan di ddunit, di laxeôt. Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2811,
            "text": "A lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S! U Öebbi d Umâin, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 351,
            "ruku": 302,
            "hizbQuarter": 140,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2812,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur teddut di lateô n Cciîan. Win iteddun di lateô n Cciîan, ar la iteddu di lâaô akked tuccva. Lemmer ur illi fellawen lfevl n Öebbi akked uêunu S, ur ippizdig degwen yiwen, d awezi. Maca, Öebbi Izzizdig win i S ihwan. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 352,
            "ruku": 303,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2813,
            "text": "Wid, degwen, iwumi ippunefk lfevl akked terkunt, ur pgalan ef tikci i llzem, i imeban, i wid iunagen deg ubrid n Öebbi. Ad semmêen, ad ssurfen. Day ur têemmlem ara mara awen Isemmeê Öebbi? Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 352,
            "ruku": 303,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2814,
            "text": "Ih, wid ipqeôôiven tilawin zeddigen, istehzan, iumnen, ad pwaxzun di ddunit, di laxeôt. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 352,
            "ruku": 303,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2815,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara d cehhden ef igiten nnsen, ilsawen nnsen, ifassen nnsen, ivaôen nnsen,",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 352,
            "ruku": 303,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2816,
            "text": "assen, ad asen Ifk Öebbi ayen ppalasen, s tidep. Ad éôen ar Öebbi d Tidep ibanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 352,
            "ruku": 303,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2817,
            "text": "Yir tlawin i yir irgazen, yir irgazen i yir tlawin. Tilawin n lâali i irgazen n lâali, irgazen lâali i tlawin n lâali. Wigi ur ppkan deg wayen qqaôen. I nitni, ssmaê akked ôôeéq ukyis.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 352,
            "ruku": 303,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2818,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur keçmet ixxamen ur nelli nnwen, alamma s tsriê, u alamma tselmem ef imawlan nnsen. Ppif akka i kunwi, amar a d tesmektim.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 352,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2819,
            "text": "Ma ur tufim êedd degsen, ur keçmet alamma s tsriê. Ma nnan awen d: 'ualet', ualet. Yif it wakka i ûûfawa nnwen. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 353,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2820,
            "text": "Ulac uilif fellawen ma tkecmem ixxamen ur nepwazde, ma tella tawsa nnwen degsen. Öebbi Iéôa acu d teqqaôem, u wacu teppeffrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 353,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2821,
            "text": "Ini i wid iumnen ad brun i wallen nnsen, ad ssôen tuzzuft nnsen. Yif it wakka i ûûfawa nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 353,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2822,
            "text": "Ini i tid iumnen ad brunt i wallen nnsent, ad ssôent tuzzuft nnsent, ur d sskanent, di zzin nnsent, siwa ayen d ivehôen segs, ad umment idmaren nnsent. Ur d sskanent ccbuê nnsent, siwa i irgazen nnsent, ne ibabaten nnsent, ne imaôen nnsent, ne iqcicen nnsent, ne irbiben nnsent, ne atmaten nnsent, ne iqcicen n watmaten nnsent, ne wid n tsetmatin nnsent, ne tiqeddacin nnsent, ne taklatin nnsent, ne iqeddacen imudduzen, ne arrac ur nelleméi. Ur kkatent dderz, ad ipwassen zzin nnsent uffir. Steôoâet akw i Öebbi, a lmumnin, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 353,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2823,
            "text": "Jewoet i iâzriyen nnwen, akked wid imaânen seg waklan nnwen, akked teklatin nnwen. Ma d imeban ay llan, a ten Iôéeq Öebbi, s lfevl iS. Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 354,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2824,
            "text": "Wid ur nufa ara ar aen, ad ûebôen ar ten id Iôéeq Öebbi, s lfevl iS. Wid, seg waklan nnwen, i iban ad asen tarum aserreê, arut asen ma teéôam ten, d at lxiô ay llan. Fket asen seg ayla i wen Ifka Öebbi. Ur pêeppimet ef teklatin nnwen, tiquêbit, i rrbeê nnwen di tmeddurt n ddunit, ma bant tezdeg. Ma têeppmen, Öebbi, deffir uêeppem nnsent, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 354,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2825,
            "text": "Ni Nessader awen ed issekniyen iberrzen, akked umedya n wid iâacen uqbel nnwen, d anabi i wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 354,
            "ruku": 304,
            "hizbQuarter": 141,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2826,
            "text": "Öebbi d tafat n tmurt akked igenwan. Amedya n tafat iS d takwap degs taftilt. Taftilt daxel n tqeôâap. Taqeôâap, amzun d itri acôaôaq, tecâal it ttejôa iôqan, tazemmurt ur nelli n ugmuv ne n utaram. Qôib a pfet zzit is, ur p tennul tmes. Tafat ef tafat. Ippawi Öebbi win i S ihwan ar tafat iS. Ippak ed Öebbi imedyaten i medden. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 354,
            "ruku": 305,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2827,
            "text": "Deg ixxamen i Iba Öebbi ad ufraren, ideg ara d immekti yisem iS, sbuccuâen T ssbeê, tameddit.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 354,
            "ruku": 305,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2828,
            "text": "Irgazen ur tesafal ttjaôa, ne ssuq, ef usmekti n Öebbi, ef téallit, ef zzakat; ppagwaden ass, ideg ara nehwwalen wallen akked wulawen.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 355,
            "ruku": 305,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2829,
            "text": "Iwakken a ten Ikafi Öebbi ef wayen xeddmen d amxallef, ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. Öebbi Ipiti win i S ihwan, war aktili.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 355,
            "ruku": 305,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2830,
            "text": "Igiten n wid ijehlen, am aylal deg uzaaô. Win ifuden, ad iil d aman. Alamma mi ibbwev uôes, ur ippaf acemma. A n iaf Öebbi, Issuli as leêsab is. Öebbi Ipawal deg uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 355,
            "ruku": 305,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2831,
            "text": "Ne am tillas di yill lemiq. Tumm it lmuja, sufella lmuja, sufella asigna. Tillas sennig tiyav. Ma issuffe ed afus is, ur issawev a t iwali. Win iwumi ur Iga ara Öebbi tafat, ur isâi tafat.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 355,
            "ruku": 305,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2832,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara, sbuccuâen Öebbi i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ifrax deg waffug. Issen taéallit akked usbuccaâ n yal yiwen. Öebbi Iéôa ayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 355,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2833,
            "text": "N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. £uô öÖebbi tualin.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 355,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2834,
            "text": "Ur twalav ara Öebbi Isselêay asigna, sinna, a t Izdi, sinna, a t Issemweô? Da a pwaliv ageffur a d iffe si zdaxel is. Isrusu d, seg idurar igenni, abruri. Ad Iwwet yis, win i S ihwan, a t Iveôôef ef win i S ihwan. Tafat n lebôaq iS qôib a ppeglu s yiéôi.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 355,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2835,
            "text": "Öebbi Ismizwar iv akked wass. Deg wayagi, s tidep, d aselmed i wid isâan iéôi.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2836,
            "text": "Öebbi Ixleq akw lêayawan, seg waman. Garasen, illa win ippeênunufen ef uâabbuv is, win ileêêun ef sin ivaôôen, win ileêêun ef kué. Ixelleq Öebbi ayen i S ihwan. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2837,
            "text": "Ni Nessader ed issekniyen iberrzen. Öebbi Inehhu win i S ihwan, ar ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2838,
            "text": "Qqaôen: 'numen s Öebbi akked Umazan, nu awal'. Sinna, deffir waya, iwexxeô urbaâ segsen. Wigi ur llin d lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2839,
            "text": "Mi pwanecden ar Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad Iêudd garasen, arbaâ segsen iwexxeô.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2840,
            "text": "Ma sâan lêeqq, a d asen uôes, d imvuâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2841,
            "text": "Day helken wulawen nnsen, ne cukken, ne ugaden a ten Isneêyaf Öebbi akked Umazan iS? Xaîi, widak d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 306,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2842,
            "text": "Timenna n lmumnin, mara ssutren aêuddu n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad Iêudd garasen, d tigi kan: 'nesla, nôuva'. D wigi ay d imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 307,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2843,
            "text": "Win iôuvan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ippagwaden Öebbi, ipêezziben, nitni d isaâdiyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 307,
            "hizbQuarter": 142,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2844,
            "text": "Ggulen s Öebbi, tagallit meqqwôen, ar ma tumôev asen, ard ad ffen, war ccekk. Ini: 'ur pgallat, annuz ipwassen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen txeddmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 356,
            "ruku": 307,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2845,
            "text": "Ini: 'ôavit Öebbi, ôavit Amazan'. Ma wexxôen, fellas, neppa, ayen kan i s sbabben, fellawen kunwi ayen i wen sbabben. Ma tôuvam T, a ppeppwanhum. I iwatan i Umazan, siwa awal ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 357,
            "ruku": 307,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2846,
            "text": "Iâahed Öebbi, i wid iumnen segwen, u xedmen ayen ilhan, ara ten Irr, war ccekk, d igensas di tmurt, akken Irra wid i ten id izwaren; ara ad asen Isseqâad ddin nnsen ief i ten Iôuva; ar ad asen Issegwri laman, deffir tugdi. Âabden iyI, ur iyI pcaraken acemma. Wid ijehlen, deffir waya, widak d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 357,
            "ruku": 307,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2847,
            "text": "Beddet i téallit, zekkit, aet awal i Umazan. Amar aêunu fellawen.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 357,
            "ruku": 307,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2848,
            "text": "£uôwat a pilem wid ijehlen sfunnugen di tmurt. Axxam nnsen d times. A tualin tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 357,
            "ruku": 307,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2849,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! S uâammed nnwen ara d kecmen, uôwen, waklan nnwen akw wid, degwen, ur nebli ara, krav iberdan ideg ur telsim ara: uqbel taéallit n tafrara, ef îîhuô mara tekksem iceîîiven, deffir téallit n lâica. Ulac uilif fellawen ne fellasen, ma wa iéuô wa, deffir lewqat agi. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 357,
            "ruku": 308,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2850,
            "text": "Ma belen warrac nnwen, s uâammed nnwen, am wid i ten id izwaren. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen iS. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 358,
            "ruku": 308,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2851,
            "text": "Ulac uilif ef tâuqaô i iâaddan i jwao, ma kksent iceîîiven nnsent, mebla ma sseknent ccbuê nnsent. Ma setêant, yif it i nitenti. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 358,
            "ruku": 308,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2852,
            "text": "Ur telli tiyta deg uderal, ne deg urejdal, ne deg umuvin, ne degwen, ma teççam deg ixxamen nnwen, deg wid n ibabaten nnwen, deg wid n tyimmatin nnwen, deg wid n watmaten nnwen, deg wid n tsetmatin nnwen, deg wid iâammiten nnwen, deg wid n tâammitin nnwen, deg wid ixaliten nnwen, deg wid n txaltitin nnwen, deg wid ideg tesâam tisura, ar uêbib nnwen. Ulac uilif fellawen ma teççam d agraw, ne d ifôiden. Mara tkecmen ixxamen, msalamet s wazul iôqan, aêmayan, suô Öebbi. Akka i wen d Ibeggen Öebbi issekniyen. Amar a pfehmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 358,
            "ruku": 308,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2853,
            "text": "Lmumnin, siwa wid iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma llan yides ef lameô iten icerken, ur pôuêun alamma ssutren as tsriê. Ih, wid i k issuturen tsriê, d nitni i iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ma ssutren ak tsriê, ef kra iten iaânan, serreê i win i k ihwan, segsen. Ssuter i Öebbi ad sen Isemmeê. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 359,
            "ruku": 309,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2854,
            "text": "Ur êepbet asiwwel garawen i Umazan, am mara temsawalem. Ih, Iéôa Öebbi wid, segwen, ippensaren s tuffra. Ad steêdren wid mgirrden lameô iS: ad ppuhewwlen, ne ad sâaddin aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 359,
            "ruku": 309,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2855,
            "text": "Ih, day maççi n Öebbi, i illan di tmurt akked igenwan? Ni Iéôa amek tellam uôeS. Ass n tualin nnsen uôeS, ad asen Imel d acu xedmen. Öebbi Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 359,
            "ruku": 309,
            "hizbQuarter": 143,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 25,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الفُرۡقَانِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Furqaan",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Criterion",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 2856,
            "text": "Ad Iôqu Win id Issadren afraz, i umdan iS, iwakken ad yili d aneddaô imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 359,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2857,
            "text": "Win Ilan tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; ur Isâi mmi S; ur aS illi ucrik di tgelda. Ixleq yal cci, Iwezn it s lmizan.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 359,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2858,
            "text": "Ddmen, war Neppa, iôebbiten ur nexliq acemma. D nitni i ipwaxelqen. Ur pseyyin vveô ne abauô, i iman nnsen. Ur pseyyin di tmeppant ne di tmeddurt, ne di tnekra.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2859,
            "text": "Nnan wid ijehlen: 'ayagi, d tikerkas kan. Isnulfa tent id, iâawen it, fellas, ugdud nniven. Ni densen u skaddben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2860,
            "text": "Nnan: 'd timucuha imezwura, i iura; qqaôen as tent ûûbeê, tameddit'.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2861,
            "text": "Ini: 'Issader it id, Win Issnen sser n tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, s tidep, Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2862,
            "text": "Nnan: 'd acut Umazan agi i iteppen lqut, iteddun ar leswaq? A lemmer id irs uôes lmelk, ara yilin yides d aneddaô,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2863,
            "text": "ne ippunefk as ugerruj, ne isâa aqwiô itepp segs'! Nnan imednas: 'la teppeddum kan d urgaz iwumi sseêren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2864,
            "text": "Wali amek id ppaken fellak imedyaten. Nnetlafen, ur zmiren ad pwanhun.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
