            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 310,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2865,
            "text": "Ad Iôqu Win ad ak Ifken, ma Irad, i ifen ayagi: leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Ad ak Issali lebôuo.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2866,
            "text": "Xaîi, nekôen imir. Nhegga d times i win inekôen imir.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 360,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2867,
            "text": "Mi ten twala si tama ibaâden, ad as slen s leêôaôa akked zzhir.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2868,
            "text": "Mara lin degs, nitni pwarzen deg umekkan uqmiv, ad siwlen, dinna, i wangar.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2869,
            "text": "'Ur ssawalet ara, assa, i yiwet n wangar, ssiwlet i waîas n wangaren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2870,
            "text": "Ini: 'ppif ayagi, ne Loennet n lebda i Nâahed i wid ipêezziben? D neppat ay d arraz, ay d taggara, i nitni'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2871,
            "text": "I nitni degs, ayen i sen ihwan, i lebda. D lemâahda ief Iuksan Mass ik.",
