            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2873,
            "text": "A d inin: 'gedha s yiseK! Ur a issefk a neddu d bab, war Keçç. Maca, Tatev ten, nitni akked imezwura nnsen, armi ppun asmekti, ualen d agdud ixeûôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2874,
            "text": "Atan nekôen kwen ef wayen d tennam. Ihi ur tezmirem i tsensert, ne i leslak. Win idensen, degwen, a Nessukk fellas, aâaqeb ameqwôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2875,
            "text": "Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, imazanen, mebla ma llan teppen lqut, u teddun ar leswaq. Nerra kwen, wa ihewwel wa, ma a pûebôem. Mass ik Izga la d Ismuqul.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 18,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 361,
            "ruku": 311,
            "hizbQuarter": 144,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2876,
            "text": "Nnan wid ur nessarem ara timlilit yidne£: 'a lemmer id ssersen lmalayek uône, ne nwala Mass nne'! Ni smewôen aîas iman nnsen, u ffuhrin aîas.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 362,
            "ruku": 312,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2877,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara walin lmalayek, ur ippili wassen d abecceô ibewviyen, s lxiô. A d inin: d aêdid ur nepwazgar.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 362,
            "ruku": 312,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2878,
            "text": "Nezzi eô igiten nnsen, Nerra ten d aebbaô immebruzzâen.",
