            "page": 362,
            "ruku": 312,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2882,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ieéé umednus ifassen is, ad yini: 'a yamxix iw, a lemmer ddi d ubrid Umazan!",
