            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 363,
            "ruku": 312,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2889,
            "text": "Wid ara ipwafesren af udmawen nnsen, ar Loahennama, widak d at umkan n dir mavi, d at ubrid imeôôeq mavi.",
