            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 363,
            "ruku": 313,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2895,
            "text": "Ni âaddan ef taddart ief id ili ugeffur ageswaê. Day qqimen ur p walan ara? Xaîi, ur ssaramen ara tanekra.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 363,
            "ruku": 313,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2896,
            "text": "Mi k walan, ppemsexxiôen kan fellak: 'day d wagi id Iuzen Öebbi, d Amazan?",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 363,
            "ruku": 313,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2897,
            "text": "Qôib i  itlef seg iôebbiten nne, lemmer ur neûbiô fellasen'. Deqqal ad éôen mara walin aâaqeb, anwa i innetlafen, kteô, seg ubrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 363,
            "ruku": 313,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2898,
            "text": "Twalav win i irran lhawiyya s d ôebbi s? Day ad as tiliv, keçç, d awkil?",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 363,
            "ruku": 313,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2899,
            "text": "Day tilev tegwti, segsen, sellen ne fehmen? Nitni am lmal kan, aâer elben ten akken nnetlafen seg ubrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 364,
            "ruku": 313,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2900,
            "text": "Ma twalav Mass ik, amek id Ifka tili? Lemmer i S ihwi, Irra p d tusbiî. Da Nefka yas itij d ppbut.",
