            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 364,
            "ruku": 314,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2901,
            "text": "Sinna, Njebd ip id uône£, ajbad isehlen.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 364,
            "ruku": 314,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2902,
            "text": "D Neppa i wen Irran iv d aceîîiv, ives d areyyeê, u Irra ass d tanekra.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 364,
            "ruku": 314,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2903,
            "text": "D Neppa i wen d Iuznen avu, d abecceô s uêunu S. Nessers ed, seg igenni, aman iûfan;",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 364,
            "ruku": 314,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2904,
            "text": "iwakken a Neêyu yissen tamurt immuten; a Nessew yissen aîas seg wid id Nexleq n lmal, akked imdanen.",
