            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 364,
            "ruku": 314,
            "hizbQuarter": 145,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2908,
            "text": "D Neppa i Issemfaôaqen sin ilellen, yiwen êlaw, d aéidan, wayev ôéag, d ameôan. Irra, garasen, agadir, aêdid ur nepwazgar.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 364,
            "ruku": 314,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2909,
            "text": "D Neppa i Ixelqen amdan seg waman. Ifka yas laâmum, lexwal. Mass ik Izga d Win Izemren.",
