            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 365,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2918,
            "text": "Ixdimen n Uênin, i ileêêun di tmurt di lehna, ma numren ten at war tussna, qqaôen: 'tifrat'!",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 365,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2919,
            "text": "I ippaâwazen i Mass nnsen, knan ne bedden;",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 365,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2920,
            "text": "I iqqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Veôôef segne aâaqeb n Loahennama. Ih, aâaqeb is ipwaêeppem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 365,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2921,
            "text": "Neppat, s tidep, d tadirant, i tnezdut akked iimi.",
