            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 365,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2922,
            "text": "Wid, ma seôôfen, ur veggiâen, ur pcuêêun: igi iwulmen atan garasen.",
