            "page": 366,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2925,
            "text": "siwa win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I wigi, ad Inûef Öebbi tucmitin nnsen, s yiseiyen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
