            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 366,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2928,
            "text": "Wid, mara asen d smmektin issekniyen n Mass nnsen, ur d neggar tiâéegt ne tiderelt fellasen.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 366,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2929,
            "text": "Wid iqqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Err tilawin nne, akked dderya nne, d ssuâada n wallen. Err ane d wid inehhun wid ipêezziben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 366,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2930,
            "text": "Widak ad ppuoazin s tuôfatin, ilmend n wayen ûebôen. Ad magren, dinna, azul, tifrat.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 366,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2931,
            "text": "Dinna, ad wekkôen, d amkan amxalef i tnezdut d iimi.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 366,
            "ruku": 315,
            "hizbQuarter": 146,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2932,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur d Irezzu Mass iw, degwen, ma ur tnujem uôeS. Ni tnekôem? Ad iual waya d ayen ilezmen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 4,
            "page": 366,
            "ruku": 315,
