            "page": 367,
            "ruku": 316,
            "hizbQuarter": 147,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2936,
            "text": "Ma ihwa ya£, ad asen d Nessers assekni seg igenni, ad îinzent, zdat es, tmegôav nnsen, s wannuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 367,
            "ruku": 316,
            "hizbQuarter": 147,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2937,
            "text": "Ur ten id ippas usmekti amaynut, suô Uênin, mebla ma ualen as d inekkaôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 367,
            "ruku": 316,
            "hizbQuarter": 147,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2938,
            "text": "Ni skaddben. Ihi, ad asen d asen isallen, ef wayen ief pmmaâliken.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 367,
            "ruku": 316,
            "hizbQuarter": 147,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 2939,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara tamurt? Acêal i Nessenker degs n yal tayuga tukyist!",
