            "hizbQuarter": 150,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3156,
            "text": "Imedyazen, îîafaôen ten imeôôqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 224,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 376,
            "ruku": 326,
            "hizbQuarter": 150,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3157,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara, ar nitni, di yal tazut pmenîaôen?",
            "numberInSurah": 225,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 376,
            "ruku": 326,
            "hizbQuarter": 150,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3158,
            "text": "U nitni qqaôen ayen ur xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 226,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 376,
            "ruku": 326,
            "hizbQuarter": 150,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3159,
            "text": "Kkes ed wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, id ismektayen aîas Öebbi, i irebêen mbaâd ma pwadensen. Ad éôen, wid idensen, tama anida ara ppin.",
            "numberInSurah": 227,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 376,
            "ruku": 326,
            "hizbQuarter": 150,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 27,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّمۡلِ",
        "englishName": "An-Naml",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Ant",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 3160,
            "text": "Ïs. Atnan issekniyen n Leqwôan, akked Tezmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3161,
            "text": "D nnhaya u d abecceô i lmumnin:",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3162,
            "text": "wid ibedden i téallit, ippaken zzakat, ipputebbten ef laxeôt nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3163,
            "text": "Ih, wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, Ncebbeê asen igiten nnsen, da ddebdeben.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3164,
            "text": "Widak, fellasen aâaqeb ucmit mavi. Di laxeôt, d nitni ara ixesôen ugwar.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3165,
            "text": "S tidep, keçç iusa k id Leqwôan, suô Bab n ûûwab, Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3166,
            "text": "Mi inna Musa i twacult is: 'nek wala times, ad awen d awi, segs, asali, ne ad awen d awi asafu iôeqqen, amar a ppesseêmum'.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3167,
            "text": "Mi ibbwev uôes, ipwanced: 'ad iôqu wayen illan di tmes, akked wayen i as d izzin. Gedha s Öebbi, Mass imavalen!",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3168,
            "text": "A Musa! Ih, Nek d Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3169,
            "text": "Veggeô taâkwazt ik'! Mi p iwala la tesseêôiîiw, amzun d azrem, ibren, ur iwexxeô. 'A Musa! Ur ppagwad! Ar uôI, ih, ur ppagwaden imazanen,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3170,
            "text": "siwa win idensen, sinna, iual iwqem, deffir tuccva. Nek, s tidep, Psemmiêe, Pêunnu.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3171,
            "text": "Ger afus ik di loib ik, a d iffe d amellal, ur ihlik. Si tza issekniyen, i Ferâun akked ugdud is. Nitni, war ccekk, d agdud icemten'.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3172,
            "text": "Mi ten id usan issekniyen nne£, âinani, nnan: 'wagi iban d ssêur'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 377,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3173,
            "text": "Ugin ten s ddens d pnefxa, u, deg iman nnsen, pputebbten. Wali, ihi, amek tevôa d ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 327,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3174,
            "text": "Ni Nefka tamusni i Dawed akked Sliman. Nnan: 'ccekôan i Öebbi, i a Ismenyafen i waîaû n yimdanen iumnen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3175,
            "text": "Sliman iwôet Dawed, u inna: 'a yimdanen! Nepwaselmed tutlayt n yifôax; ippunefk a si yal cci. Ayagi, s tidep, ard lfevl n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3176,
            "text": "Pwajemmlen d, i Sliman, i²âsekôiwen is si leonun, imdanen, ifôax. Mdarraren.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3177,
            "text": "Armi, mi bbwven ar tezut n twevfin, tenna d tweîuft: 'a yaweîîuf, kecmemt ar ixxamen nnkwent, mulac, war ccekk, a kwent iéd Sliman, neppa akked iâsekôiwen is, ur faqen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3178,
            "text": "Icmumeê, ivûa, ef wayen d tenna. Inna: 'a Mass iw! Err iyi ad snemmre lit iK, is i  Tatev, nek akked imawlan iw; ad xedme ise ara Tôaviv; Ssekcem iyi, s uêunu K, ar imdanen iK imaânen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3179,
            "text": "Issefqed ifôax, inna: 'acimi ur wala ara iççibib, day d layeb?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3180,
            "text": "War ccekk, ad sâaddi fellas aâaqeb uqsiê, ne a t zlu, ne a d iawi tasebbiwt tubrizt'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3181,
            "text": "Ur iâaîîel ara. Inna d: 'fehme ayen ur tefhimev. Usi d uôek si Saba, s usali unûiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 378,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3182,
            "text": "Ih, ufi en tameîîut d tagelliî nnsen. Ippunefk as si yal cci. £uôes asgeld abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3183,
            "text": "Ufi p in, neppat akked ugdud is, la kennun i yiîij, war Öebbi. Cciîan icebbeê asen igiten nnsen. Iveôf iten seg ubrid, da nitni ur pwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3184,
            "text": "Acimi ur knan ara i Öebbi, id Issufuen lesrar, di tmurt akked igenwan, i Iéôan ayen teppeffrem u ayen d tepberriêem?",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3185,
            "text": "Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 151,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 9,
              "recommended": true,
              "obligatory": false
            }
          },
          {
            "number": 3186,
            "text": "Inna: 'a néeô ma tessawlev d tidep, ne ma keçç seg ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3187,
            "text": "Öuê s tebôap iw agi, veggeô asen p, sinna, wexxeô asen, wali acu ara d rren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3188,
            "text": "Tenna: 'a yimvebbôen, tepwaveggeô iyi d tebôap tukyist.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3189,
            "text": "Ih, suô Sliman. Apan: s yisem n Öebbi Aênin Ipêunun.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3190,
            "text": "Ur ssemwaôet ara iman nnwen uôi, aset ed uôi, d imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 328,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3191,
            "text": "Tenna: 'a yimvebbôen, fket ed ôôay nnwen af lameô iw. Ur pseyyi lameô, siwa garawen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3192,
            "text": "Nnan: 'nekwni d imawlan n tezmert, nesâa lemêella tuqsiêt. Lameô i kem. Muqel d acu ara d tseyyiv'.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3193,
            "text": "Tenna: 's tidep, igeldan ssefsaden tamdint ara kecmen. Sdullun imdanen is lâali. Akka ay xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3194,
            "text": "Nek, ad asen azne tarzeft, ad aôou acu ara d awin imcegâan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 379,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3195,
            "text": "Mi tebbwev ar Sliman, inna: 'day ad iyi tâawnem s terkunt? Ayen i yi Ifka Öebbi, yif ayen i wen Ifka. D kunwi kan i ifeôêen, s terzeft nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3196,
            "text": "Ual uôsen. Ih, a nôuê uôsen s lâaskeô, iwumi ur zmiren. A ten id nessuffe, syenna, ndellen, d imejîuêen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3197,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yimvebbôen, anwa degwen, ara yi d iawin asgeld is, uqbel a yi d asen d imvuâen'?",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3198,
            "text": "Aâfrit si leonun, inna d: 'ad ak t id awi, uqbel ma tekkrev seg umekkan ik. I wayagi, war ccekk, nek d uzmir muman'.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3199,
            "text": "Inna d bab n tmusni si Tezmamt: 'nek ad ak t id awi, uqbel a pfukkev asmeômec'. Mi t iwala irs ed uôes, inna: 'wagi si lfevl n Mass iw, ad iyi ijeôôeb ma ad snemmre, ne ma ad jehle. Win isnemmren, isnemmer kan i iman is. Win ijehl, ihi, Mass iw d Asâay, d Ukyis'.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3200,
            "text": "Inna: 'bedlet as udem usgeld is, a néeô ma tepwanha, ne haap seg wid ur nepwanha'.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3201,
            "text": "Mi d tusa, nnan as: 'day am wagi, usgeld inem'? Terra d: 'amzun d neppa'. 'Tusa ya d tmusni, uqbel neppat, nuzen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3202,
            "text": "Isôuê ip wayen tunez, war Öebbi. Tella, s tidep, seg ugdud ijehliyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3203,
            "text": "Nnan as: 'ekcem ar lbeôo'! Mi t twala, til degs aman; tesban ed ifadden is. Inna: 's tidep, d lbeôo ulelluc imzin'. Tenna: 'a Mass iw! Ih, dense iman iw. Akked Sliman, unze aS i Öebbi, Mass imavalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 380,
            "ruku": 329,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3204,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed, i Tamud, gmat sen Üaliê: 'âabdet Öebbi'! Maca, rran snat n trebbuya, ppemnamarent.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3205,
            "text": "Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Acimi tepawalem ar tucmip, uqbel ise? Lemmer a ppestefôem Öebbi, ahat aêunu fellawen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3206,
            "text": "Nnan: 'tkeêêesev a, keçç akked wi iddan yidek'. Inna: 'lfal nnwen ar Öebbi, u kunwi d agdud ara ippuhewwlen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3207,
            "text": "Llan, di temdint, tza iterrasen i issefsaden di tmurt, ur pleqqimen.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3208,
            "text": "Nnan: 'yyaw a nemmesgal s Öebbi, ard a neévem deg iv fellas, neppa akked twacult is. Sinna, a nini i bab is: ur nelli d inagan n tmeniwt n tawacult is. Ih, nekwni, d imawlan n tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3209,
            "text": "Undin ticeôkep, Nundi ticeôkep, nitni ur faqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3210,
            "text": "Wali amek tevôa di tceôkep nnsen. Nened iten, nitni, akked ugdud nnsen, meôôa.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3211,
            "text": "Atnan hudden ixxamen nnsen, ilmend n ddens nnsen. Deg wayagi, war ccekk, assekni i ugdud issnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3212,
            "text": "Nsellek wid iumnen u llan pêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3213,
            "text": "I Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: 'teppeddum ar wayen n dir, u kunwi tepwalim.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3214,
            "text": "Ih, kunwi teppeddum ar irgazen, tebam ten, war tilawin. Ih, kunwi d agdud ur nessin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 381,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 152,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3215,
            "text": "Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi d nnan: 'ssuffet tawacult n Luî, si temdint nnwen, nitni d imdanen i iban tezdeg'.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3216,
            "text": "Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is. Nseyya a ppili seg wid igwran.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3217,
            "text": "Nesseli d fellasen ageffur. I icmet ugeffur n wid ippunedôen!",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 330,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3218,
            "text": "Ini: 'ccekôan i Öebbi. Talwit i imdanen iS, wid Ifren'. Ppif Öebbi, ne ayen pcaraken?",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3219,
            "text": "Day Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, i wen d Isselin aman, seg igenni - Nessenkar, yissen, iqwiôen ippembehwaoen, ur teêwaoem a d tessemim ttjuô is -, day illa ôebbi, ar tama n Öebbi? Maca, nitni d agdud issaâdalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3220,
            "text": "Day Win Irran tamurt d tanezdut, Irra degs isaffen, Irra yas idurar, Irra agadir ger sin ilellen, day illa ôebbi ar tama n Öebbi? Xaîi, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3221,
            "text": "Day Win Issemêasen i umevôuô, mara S d isiwel; Itekksen ayen n dir; i kwen Ipparan d igensas di tmurt; day illa ôebbi, ar tama n Öebbi? Drus id tesmektayem.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3222,
            "text": "Day Win i kwen Inehhun, di tillas n lberr akked yill, id Ippaznen avu, d abecceô n ccira uêunu S; day illa ôebbi, ar tama n Öebbi? Ay Aâlay Öebbi, sennig wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 382,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3223,
            "text": "Day Win Ibeddun lxelq, sinna, Ippales as; ikwen Iaten seg igenni akked tmurt; day illa ôebbi ar tama n Öebbi? Ini: 'awit ed atebbet nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep'!",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3224,
            "text": "Ini: 'tabavnit, di tmurt akked igenwan, ur p issin yiwen siwa Öebbi. Ur éôin melmi ara d kkren'.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3225,
            "text": "Ih, tamusni nnsen ur tessawev ar laxeôt? Xaîi, nitni di ccekk fellas. Xaîi, nitni, fellas, drelen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 331,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3226,
            "text": "Nnan wid ijehlen: 'day ma nual d akal, am imezwura nne, s tidep, fella tanekra?",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3227,
            "text": "Ni waââden a aya, i nekwni akw i imezwura nne, zik. Ayagi, d timucuha kan imenza'.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3228,
            "text": "Ini: 'iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevôa d ibewviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3229,
            "text": "Ur webben fellasen, ur pxiqqi ilmend n nncub nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3230,
            "text": "Nnan: 'melmi lemâahda agi, ma d tidep ay tessawalem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3231,
            "text": "Ini: 'kra n wayen ief têarem, ahat atan ivfeô kwen id'.",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3232,
            "text": "Mass ik, s tidep, meqqweô lfevl iS, ef imdanen. Maca, tegwti degsen ur snemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3233,
            "text": "Mass ik, s tidep, Iéôa ayen teffren idmaren nnsen, akked wayen d qqaôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3234,
            "text": "Ur illi wayen iffren, deg igenni akked tmurt, ur nuri di Tezmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3235,
            "text": "Ih, Leqwôan agi iêekku d i At Isôail, tegwti n wayen ief mgarraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 383,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3236,
            "text": "Neppa, war ccekk, ard nnhaya akked uêunu i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3237,
            "text": "Mass ik, s tidep, ad Iseyyi garasen s uêuddu S. Neppa d Uzmir, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3238,
            "text": "Ppkel ef Öebbi, ih, aql ak di tidep ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3239,
            "text": "Ih, keçç, ur tepparav lmeggtin ad slen, ur tepparav iâeééugen ad slen i wancad, ma wexxôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3240,
            "text": "Ur fellak nnhaya ideralen, mgal ttelfan nnsen. Ara islen, siwa wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£. Nitni d imvuâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 153,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3241,
            "text": "Mi iûaô wawal fellasen, ad asen d Nessuffe lweêc si tmurt; ad asen yini ar imdanen ur metbutit ef issekniyen nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 332,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3242,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara d Nefser, si yal lois, arbaâ n wid inekôen issekniyen nne£, d tirni,",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3243,
            "text": "alamma, mi d usan, ad Yini: 'day tnekôem issekniyen iW, ur ten teskecmem di tmusni? Ne d acu tellam txeddmem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3244,
            "text": "Iûaô wawal fellasen, imi densen. Ur d pmeslayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3245,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara ar Nerra yasen iv i ureyyeê nnsen, ass iwakken ad walin? Deg wayagi, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3246,
            "text": "Ass uûuvu n lbuq, ad iagwad i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, siwa wid i S ihwan i Öebbi. A d asen akw uôeS, s uêiwet.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3247,
            "text": "A pwaliv idurar i tilev sebken, la teddun am usigna. D igi n Öebbi i Iûegmen yal cci. Neppa, s tidep, Iéôa d acu txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 384,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3248,
            "text": "Win id iusan s ise, ad iawi it yifen. Widak, assen, mevmunit si tugdi.",
            "numberInSurah": 89,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3249,
            "text": "Wid id iusan s tucmip, ad ppin wudmawen nnsen ar tmes. Ni a ppeppuqeîîim kan ef wayen txeddmem?",
            "numberInSurah": 90,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3250,
            "text": "Pwamôe kan ad âabde Mass n temdint agi, i Iôqa. IneS yal cci. Pwamôe d ad ili seg imduâen,",
            "numberInSurah": 91,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3251,
            "text": "ad male Leqwôan. Win ipwanhan, ipwanha kan i iman is. Win innetlafen, ini: 'nek d aneddaô kan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 92,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3252,
            "text": "Ini: 'a neckeô Öebbi. Ad awen Issken issekniyen iS. A ten tâaqlem'. Mass ik ur Ieffel ara ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 93,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 333,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 28,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القَصَصِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qasas",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Stories",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 3253,
            "text": "Ïsm.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3254,
            "text": "Atnan issekniyen n Tezmamt ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3255,
            "text": "Ad ak d Neêku si teqûiî n Musa akked Ferâun, s tidep, i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3256,
            "text": "Ih, Ferâun issemweô iman is di tmurt; imezda ifeôq iten d iêôumen. Isrewrew îayfa segsen, izellu arrac nnsen, issidir tilawin nnsen. Ih, neppa seg ifessaden.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3257,
            "text": "Neba a Nfeôôeo ef wid irewrwen di tmurt, a ten Nerr d imeqwôanen, a ten Nerr d iweôôaten.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 385,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3258,
            "text": "A ten Nesseqâad di tmurt. A Nessken i Ferâun, Haman, akked iâsekôiwen nnsen, ayen ppagwaden segsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3259,
            "text": "Nweêêa i imma s n Musa: 'ssuîîev it, sinna, ma tugadev fellas, err it ar wasif. Ur ppagwad, ur webben. Ad am t id Nerr, u a t Nerr seg imazanen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3260,
            "text": "Teddem it twacult n Ferâun. Ad asen iual d acengu, d ailif. Ih, Ferâun, Haman, akked iâsekôiwen nnsen llan d imsaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3261,
            "text": "Tenna tmeîîut n Ferâun: 'd nnûib n tiî, i nek akked keçç. Ur tneqq, ahat ad a infaâ, ne a t nerr d mmit nne'. Nitni ur faqen ara.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3262,
            "text": "Temmar ed tasa n yimma s n Musa. Qôib it id tessken, lemmer ur Nzeyyeô ara ul is, iwakken a ppili si lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3263,
            "text": "Tenna i ultma s: 'evfeô it'! Teqquôa t si mbâid, nitni ur faqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 154,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3264,
            "text": "Uqbel, Negdel as tid iûûuîuven. Tenna: 'ad awen ssekne axxam ar awen itkwelfen fellas, u nitni ad as bedden'?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3265,
            "text": "Nerra t id i imma s, iwakken ad as kkawent wallen is, ur twebben, iwakken a péeô ar lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Maca, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 386,
            "ruku": 334,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3266,
            "text": "Mi meqqweô, ittaâqel, Nefka yas tussna, ûûwab. Akka ay Nepkafi imdanen lâali.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3267,
            "text": "Ikcem tamdint, di lweqt ideg stehzan imezda is. Iufa n sin irgazen pnaen, yiwen seg uêôum is, wayev seg icenga s. Win n uêôum is, issuter as d afus, mgal win n icenga s. Iwwet it Musa s lbunia, ina t. Inna: 'ayagi, seg igi n Cciîan. Neppa, s tidep, d acengu n ûûeê, itellifen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3268,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Nek dense iman iw, Semmeê iyi'. Isemmeê as. Ih, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3269,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! S lit iK felli, ur ppili, d awezi, si loiha ibewviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3270,
            "text": "Iufa d iman is di temdint, iugad, iquôaâ. Atan a d ipâaggiv uôes, win i s d issutren afus, ass izeryen. Inna yas Musa: 'keçç, s tidep, d imeôôeq n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3271,
            "text": "Acengu nnsen, mi iba a t iwwet, inna d: 'a Musa! Day tebiv ad iyi tenev, akken teniv yiwen, ivelli? Tebiv kan a ppiliv d aqehhaô di tmurt, ur tebiv ara a ppiliv seg iâaôviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3272,
            "text": "Iusa d urgaz si îîerf n temdint, ippazal. Inna d: 'a Musa! S tidep, imvebbôen mlalen ef loal ik, a k nen. Effe, nek, seg wid ik ipweûûin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3273,
            "text": "Iffe segs, iugad, iquôaâ. Inna: 'a Mass iw! Sellek iyi seg ugdud imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 387,
            "ruku": 335,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3274,
            "text": "Mi ibbwi tikli ar Madian, inna: 'ahat Mass iw ad iyi Iawi d ubrid umâin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 388,
            "ruku": 336,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3275,
            "text": "Mi ibbwev s aman n Madian, iufa n arbaâ n laci, la sswan. Iufa, di îîerf nnsen, snat n tlawin, îîfent lmal nnsent. Inna: 'd acu txeddmemt'? Nnant ed: 'ur nesswa alamma wexxôen imeksawen. Babat ne d amaô ameqwôan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 388,
            "ruku": 336,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3276,
            "text": "Issew asent, iual ar tili, inna: 'a Mass iw! Nek ôebe ef yal lxiô, ar iyi d Tessersev'.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 388,
            "ruku": 336,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3277,
            "text": "Tusa t id yiwet segsent, s tikli ikukran, tenna: 'atan ak d issawal baba, a k ikafi imi  tesswev'. Mi iôuê uôes, u iêka yas i ivôan, inna: 'ur ppagwad, tepwasellkev seg ugdud imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 388,
            "ruku": 336,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3278,
            "text": "Yiwet segsent, tenna: 'a baba! Eîîef it d acrik, ih, yif icriken ik, iohed, muman'.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 388,
            "ruku": 336,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3279,
            "text": "Inna: 'bi, nek, ad ak fke yiwet si yissi yagi, s cceôt a pxedmev uôi îam iseggwasen. Ma tessawdev mraw, s lebi k. Ur bi a k hejjne. Ad ak ili, ma Irad Öebbi, seg iâaôviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 388,
            "ruku": 336,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3280,
            "text": "Irra: 'ayagi, gari yidek. A tin sâadda ger snat n tallitin, ur ippili felli uilif. Öebbi d Awkil, ef wayen id nenna'.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 388,
            "ruku": 336,
            "hizbQuarter": 155,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3281,
            "text": "Mi ifukk Musa tallit, u iseyyeê akked twacult is, iwala times ar tama n udrar. Inna i twacult is: 'qqimet, wala times, ahat ad awen d awi, segs, asali ne asafu, amar a ppesseêmum'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 389,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3282,
            "text": "Mi ibbwev uôes, ipwanced ed si ttejôa, di rif ayeffus n tezut, deg umviq iôqan: 'a Musa! S tidep, Nek d Öebbi, Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 389,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3283,
            "text": "Veggeô taâkwazt ik'. Mi p iwala, la tesseêôiîiw amzun d azrem, ibren ur iwexxeô. 'A Musa! Qeddem, ur ppagwad, aql ak, ih, di laman.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 389,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3284,
            "text": "Err afus ik di loib ik, a d iffe d amellal, ur ihlik. Sseqôeb ed uôek iil ik, ad ak tekkes tugwdi. Tigi d sin n ppbut suô Mass ik, i Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ih, nitni d agdud iballaen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 389,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3285,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Nek ni yiwen segsen, ugade ad iyi nen.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 389,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3286,
            "text": "Gma Harun yif iyi afeûûeê umeslay. Azen it id yidi d amâiwen, ad iyi tebbet. Nek ugade ad iyi nekôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 389,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3287,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Nesseohed tayepp ik s gma k. Ad awen Nefk, i sin, adabu; ur kwen id ppawven. S issekniyen nne£, d kunwi akked wid iddan yidwen ara irebêen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 389,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3288,
            "text": "Mi ibbwev uôsen Musa, s issekniyen iberrzen, nnan: 'ayagi, siwa ssêur id innulfan. Ur nesli s waya, uô ibabaten nne imezwura'.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3289,
            "text": "Inna Musa: 'Mass iw Iéôa sennig wiyav, anwa iwumi Ifka nnhaya suôeS, anwa ara d igwrin deg Uxxam. Imednas, s tidep, ur rebêen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3290,
            "text": "Inna Ferâun: 'a yimvebbôen, ur awen mli ara kra n ôebbi, war nekkini. Ecâal iyi times ar talaxt, a Haman; bnu yi lbeôo aâlayen; ahat ad ali ar ÖÔebbi n Musa. Nek, s tidep, êesbe t seg wid iskiddiben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3291,
            "text": "Neppa, akked iâsekôiwen is, smewôen iman nnsen di tmurt, war ssebba. £ilen, ar nitni, ur d ppualen uône£.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3292,
            "text": "Neppa, akked iâsekôiwen is, Neîîef iten. Nger iten ar yill. Wali amek tevôa d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3293,
            "text": "Nerra ten d imeqwôanen i ineccden ar tmes. Ass n tnekra, ur ppusellken.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3294,
            "text": "Neqqen asen xezzu di ddunit agi. Ass n tnekra, nitni seg ucmiten.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 337,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3295,
            "text": "Ni Nefka Tazmamt i Musa, mbaâd ma Nesqucc isuta imezwura. D tafat i imdanen, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Amar a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 390,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3296,
            "text": "Ur telliv ara di loiha utaram, mi Nseyya lameô i Musa. Ur telliv seg inagan.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 391,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3297,
            "text": "Maca, Nxelq ed tisuta, wezzif laâmeô nnsent. Ur tellid seg imezda n Madian, la sen teqqarev issekniyen nne£. Maca, Nella Neppazen.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 391,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3298,
            "text": "Ur telliv ar tama n udrar, mi d Nessawel. Maca d aêunu suô Mass ik, iwakken a pnedrev agdud, uuô ur d iusi uneddaô, uqbel ik. Amar a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 391,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3299,
            "text": "Mulac, ma têuza ten tiyta id urwen ifassen nnsen, a d inin: 'a Mass nne! A lemmer i  d Tuznev amazan, a neddu d issekniyen iK, a nili seg wid iumnen'!",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 391,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3300,
            "text": "Mi ten id tusa tidep suône£, nnan: 'a lemmer id iusi am wayen id iusan i Musa'! Day ur ugin ara, zik, ayen id iusan i Musa? Nnan: 'd sin ssêurat'. Mwafaqen, nnan: 'nekwni nugi ten i sin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 391,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3301,
            "text": "Ini: 'awit ed Tazmamt, suô Öebbi, i yifen snat agi, i nnhaya, ad ddu yides, ma tessawalem tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 391,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3302,
            "text": "Ma ur ak d rran ara, efhem ar ddan kan d lhawiyyat nnsen. Anwa innetlafen, sennig win iteddun d lhawiyya s, war nnhaya suô Öebbi? Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 391,
            "ruku": 338,
            "hizbQuarter": 156,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3303,
            "text": "Aql a£ Nessawwev asen awal, amendeô ma d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3304,
            "text": "Umnen yis wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, uqbel tagi.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3305,
            "text": "Ma ôan asen t, ad inin: 'numen yis. Ih, ar neppa d tidep, suô Mass nne. Uqbel is, s tidep, nella d imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3306,
            "text": "Wigi a ten id ias ukafi nnsen berdayen, ef wayen ûebôen, swexxiôen tucmip s yise, u seg wayen iten Nat, pseddiqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3307,
            "text": "Mi slan i yir awal, ad as veôfen, u qaôen: 'i nekwni igiten nne, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Fellawen talwit. Ur neôeb ef at war tussna'.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3308,
            "text": "Keçç, s tidep, ur tnehhuv win têemlev. Maca, Öebbi Inehhu win i S ihwan. Neppa, Yif akw akken Iéôa wid ipwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3309,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ma nedda d nnhaya yidek, a nepwaxvef seg wakal nne'. Day ur ten Nesseqâad ara di loamaâ n laman, uuô d ppawvent yal lellat? D lit suône£. Maca, tegwti degsen, ur éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3310,
            "text": "Acêal Nesqucc n temdininn, cerrâent di temâict nnsent. Atnan ixxamen nnsen, ay ten izeden, deffir sen, siwa ixeîîayen. D Nekwni ay d iweôôaten.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3311,
            "text": "Ur Isquccu Mass ik timdinin, alamma iuzen i imezda nnsent, amazan i sen immalen issekniyen nne£. Ur Nesquccu timdinin, mebla ma llan imezda nnsent, d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 392,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3312,
            "text": "Kra n wayen i wen ippunefken n cci, d zzhu n tmeddurt n ddunit, akked ccbuê is. Ayen illan eô Öebbi, yif it, ad idum kter. Day ur pmeyyizen ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 339,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3313,
            "text": "Day win iwumi Nefka lemâahda igerzen, u immuger ip, am win i Nezha s lit n tmeddurt n ddunit; sinna, ass n tnekra, neppa seg wid ara d irsen?",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3314,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad Yini: 'anda ten wid iyY tepcarakem, u tellam tepkabarem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3315,
            "text": "A d inin wid ief iûaô wawal: 'a Mass nne! Wigi i njeggeê, njeggeê iten, akken i nepwajeggeê. A nzekki ureK: maççi d nekwni ay âabden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3316,
            "text": "Ad asen inin: 'naâôet wid tepcarakem'. Ad ten naâôen, ur asen d pparan. Walan aâaqeb. A lemmer llan pwanhan!",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3317,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad Yini: 'acu d terram i imazanen'?",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3318,
            "text": "Assen, ad dergen fellasen isalen, nitni ur pmesteqsayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3319,
            "text": "Ma d win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan, ahat ad yili seg imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3320,
            "text": "Mass ik Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan, u Ismenyafa. Ur ten id iûaê usmenyif. Gedha s Öebbi! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3321,
            "text": "Mass ik Iéôa ayen iffren deg idmaren nnsen, akked wayen cennâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3322,
            "text": "Neppa d Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. I Neppa, annuz di tmezwarut, u di tneggarut. I Neppa aêuddu, uôeS tualin nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 393,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3323,
            "text": "Ini: 'acu tmeyyzem, ma Isseli d Öebbi iv imezgi, fellawen, alamma d ass n tnekra? Anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ara wen d iawin tafat? Day ur tsellem ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 394,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3324,
            "text": "Ini: 'acu tmeyyzem, ma Issuli Öebbi ass imezgi, fellawen, alamma d ass n tnekra? Anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ara wen d iawin iv, a ppestaâfum degs? Day ur tepwalim ara'?",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 394,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3325,
            "text": "Seg uêunu S, Iga yawen iv akked wass, i ustaâfu nnwen, akked unadi n lfevl iS. Amar a ppesnemmrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 394,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3326,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad asen Yini: 'anda ten wid iyY tepcarakem, u tellam tepkabarem'?",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 394,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3327,
            "text": "A d Nawi anagi, si yal lois. A Nini: 'awit ed atebbet nnwen'. Ad éôen ar tidep n Öebbi. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 394,
            "ruku": 340,
            "hizbQuarter": 157,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3328,
            "text": "Ih, Qaôun illa seg ugdud n Musa. Iqehô iten. Nefka yas igerrujen; s tezmert ugraw ioehden, arfad n tsura nnsen. Mi s inna ugdud is: 'ur zehhu! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara izehwaniyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 394,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3329,
            "text": "Deg wayen i k Ifka Öebbi, nadi axxam aneggaru. Ur teppu amur ik, di ddunit. Elhu, akken i Ilha Öebbi uôek. Ur ssaram lefsad di tmurt. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ifessaden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 394,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3330,
            "text": "Inna: 'ippunefk iyi kan, ilmend n tmusni i sâi'. Day ur iéôa ara ar Öebbi Isqucc, uqbel is, ger isuta, wid i t iugaren di tezmert, isemmden kteô? Ur illi usteqsi ibewviyen, af ibekkaven nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 395,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3331,
            "text": "Iffe ed s agdud is, s ôôêuê is. Wid iban tameddurt n ddunit, nnan: 'awufan nesâa am wayen ippunefken i Qaôun! Ih, neppa d bab n terkunt tabarart'.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 395,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3332,
            "text": "Wid, iwumi teppunefk tmusni, nnan: 'a ssexv nnwen! Ppwab n Öebbi yif it, i win iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ara d iûaê siwa win iûebôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 395,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3333,
            "text": "Nger it seddaw tmurt, neppa akked uxxam is. Ur as telli terbaât ara t isellken, war Öebbi. Ur illi seg wid ipselliken iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 395,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3334,
            "text": "Wid issaramen amkan is, ivelli nni, ualen nnan: 'zi Öebbi Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, u iwezzen. Lemmer ur a Iat ara Öebbi, yili Iger a seddaw tmurt. Ih, ur rebêen ijehliyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 395,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3335,
            "text": "Axxam nni aneggaru, a t Nerr i wid ijunben temweô akked usefsed, di tmurt. Tirect i wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 395,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3336,
            "text": "Win id iusan s yise, ad iawi ayen it yifen. Win id iusan s tucmip, ihi, ad ppuqeîîin wid ixedmen tucmitin, ef wayen kan xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 395,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3337,
            "text": "Ih, Win Ilezmen fellak Leqwôan, war ccekk, a k id Irr s axxam. Ini: 'Mass iw Yif akw akken Issen anwa id iusan s nnhaya, anwa i illan di ttelfan n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3338,
            "text": "Ur tessarmev ara, ad ak ed ters Tezmamt, lemmer maççi d aêunu suô Mass ik. Ur ppili d amâiwen ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 86,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3339,
            "text": "Ur k swexxiôen seg issekniyen n Öebbi, deffir trusi nnsen uôek. Nuj ar Mass ik, ur ppili seg wid ipcaraken.",
            "numberInSurah": 87,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3340,
            "text": "Ur nâaô, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven. Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa. Yal cci ad inger, siwa udem iS. IneS aêuddu. £ureS ara tualem.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 341,
            "hizbQuarter": 158,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 29,
        "name": "سُورَةُ العَنكَبُوتِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Ankaboot",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Spider",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 3341,
            "text": "Alm.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3342,
            "text": "Day ilen imdanen a ten ooen qqaôen: 'numen', u nitni ur ppuhewwlen?",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3343,
            "text": "Ni Nhewwel wid i ten id izwaren. War ccekk, ad Yissin Öebbi wid iqqaôen tidep, ad Yissin ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3344,
            "text": "Ne ilen ad a£ zwiren wid ixedmen tucmitin? Dir it wayen pêuddun.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3345,
            "text": "Win iggunin timlilit akked Öebbi, s tidep, a d ias, war ccekk, lajel n Öebbi. Neppa, Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3346,
            "text": "Win ijuhden, ijuhed kan i iman is. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêwao ara imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 396,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3347,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, war ccekk, ad asen Nekkes tucmitin nnsen, a ten Nkafi ef wayen xeddmen ifuqen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3348,
            "text": "Nweûûa amdan ar lewqama, s imawlan is. Ma lezmen fellak, ad iyI tcarkev ayen ur tessinev, ur asen ppa awal. Tualin nnwen, uôI. Ad awen Mle acu txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3349,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan, war ccekk, a ten Nessekcem ar iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3350,
            "text": "Ger imdanen, wid iqqaôen: 'numen s Öebbi'. Ma meênen, deg ubrid n Öebbi, ad êesben ahewwel n medden, d aâaqeb n Öebbi. Mi d iusa lelb, suô Mass ik, ar ad inin: 'ih, nella yidwen'. Day ur Iéôa ara Öebbi, i illan deg idmaren imavalen?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3351,
            "text": "War ccekk, Öebbi Issen wid iumnen, Issen ixabiten.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3352,
            "text": "Nnan wid ijehlen, i wid iumnen: 'ddut d ubrid nne, a nbibb tuccva nnwen'. Nitni ur pbibbin acemma, si tuccva nnsen. S tidep, nitni d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3353,
            "text": "War ccekk, ad bibben tiâekkwmin nnsen, akked tiâekkwmin nniven. Ih, ad ppusteqsin, ass n tnekra, af wayen id snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 342,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3354,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed Nuê, i ugdud is. Izde yides, agim kkes ed smuset iseggwasen. Ibbwi ten uêemmal, nitni d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 397,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3355,
            "text": "Nsellek it, neppa akked wid iddan di lbabuô. Nerra t d assekni i imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3356,
            "text": "Ibôahim, mi inna i ugdud is: 'âabdet Öebbi, êezzbet aS. Yif it wakka, i kunwi, lemmer teéôim.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3357,
            "text": "Tâabdem kan tiâancuôin, war Öebbi. Tesnulfam d tikerkas. Ih, wid tâabdem, war Öebbi, ur zmiren a kwen iten. Ssutret lit i Öebbi, âabdet eP, snemmret aS. £uôeS ara tualem.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3358,
            "text": "Ma tnekôem, ihi, uqbel nnwen, nekôen leoyus'. I iwatan, i umazan, siwa assiwev ubeggen.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3359,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara, amek id Inezzu Öebbi lxelq, sinna, Ippales as. Ih, ayagi, i Öebbi, d ushil.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3360,
            "text": "Ini: 'iniget di tmurt, walit amek id Inza lxelq. Sinna, Öebbi a d Iawi lxelq aneggaru. Ih, Öebbi Izmer i yal cci'.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3361,
            "text": "Ikkat win i S ihwan; Ipêunu ef win i S ihwan. £ureS jebbu nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3362,
            "text": "Ur tesfunnugem, kunwi, di tmurt, ne deg igenni. Ur tesâim, war Öebbi, bab ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 343,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3363,
            "text": "Wid iugin issekniyen n Öebbi, akked temlilit yideS, widak ad aysen aêunu W. I widak, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 398,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3364,
            "text": "Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi d nnan: 'enet ep, ne sseôet ep'. Isellek it Öebbi, si tmes. Deg waya, s tidep, d assekni i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 399,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3365,
            "text": "Inna: 'teddmem kan tiâancuôin, war Öebbi. Temêemmalem di tmeddurt n ddunit, sinna, ass n tnekra, kra degwen ad nekôen wiyav, kra ad xzun wiyav. Axxam nnwen d times, ur awen illi usellak'.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 399,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 159,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3366,
            "text": "Iumen it Luî. Inna: 'nek, d iminig ar Mass iw. Ih, Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab'.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 399,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3367,
            "text": "Nat it s Isêaq akked Yaâqub. I tarwas, Nefka lambiyya, Tazmamt. Nefka yas taqviât is, di ddunit; u neppa, di laxeôt, war ccekk, seg iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 399,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3368,
            "text": "Luî, mi inna i ugdud is: 'ih, aql akwen la txedmem lâaô, ur ixdim yiwen, zik, deg imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 399,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3369,
            "text": "La teppeddum, ih, ar irgazen, tgezzmem abrid, txeddmem ayen icemten, deg igrawen nnwen'. Tiririt n ugdud is, siwa mi nnan: 'awi a d aâaqeb n Öebbi, ma telliv seg wid issawalen tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 399,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3370,
            "text": "Inna: 'a Mass iw! Efk iyi afus, mgal agdud ifessaden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 399,
            "ruku": 344,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3371,
            "text": "Mi d usan imceggâen nne£, ar Ibôahim, s ubecceô, nnan as: 'ih, a Nesqucc imezda n temdint agi. Imezda is, s tidep, d imednas'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3372,
            "text": "Inna d: 'ni degs Luî'. Nnan as: 'Nekwni, Neéôa sennig akw, i illan degs. A t Naâteq, neppa akked twacult is, siwa tameîîut is, ara yilin seg wid igwran'.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3373,
            "text": "Mi usan imceggâen nne£, ar Luî, iwbel ilmend nnsen, ur izmir a ten ifukk. Nnan as: 'ur ppagwad, ur webbel. Nekwni a k Naâteq, keçç d twacult ik, siwa tameîîut ik, ara yilin seg wid igwran.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3374,
            "text": "Ih, nekwni a d Nesseli ssxev seg igenni, ef imezda n temdint agi, ilmend n lâaô nnsen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3375,
            "text": "Ni Neooa d segs, assekni iberrzen, i ugdud ipmeyyizen.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3376,
            "text": "Ar Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb. Inna: 'a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi, gganit ass aneggaru, ur oouôut di tmurt d ifessaden!'.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3377,
            "text": "Nekôen t. Tewwet iten zzenzla. Gwran d, d loeppat, deg ixxamen nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3378,
            "text": "Âad akked Tamud - ni iban awen d seg ixxamen nnsen -, icebbeê asen Cciîan igiten nnsen. Issuffe iten seg ubrid, nitni pfeôôioen.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 400,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3379,
            "text": "Qaôun, Ferâun, Haman, ni iusa ten id Musa, s ubeggen. Smewôen iman nnsen, di tmurt, ur rbiêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 401,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3380,
            "text": "Yal wa, Newwet it ef ubekkav is. Llan wid iwumi Nuzen tabucivant. Llan wid i iwwet usuu. Llan wid i Nger seddaw wakal. Llan wid i Nemeq. Maççi d Öebbi iten idensen, d nitni i idensen iman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 401,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3381,
            "text": "Wid iteddun d imawlan, war Öebbi, cban rtila. Tebna tissist. Ihi, axxam ahcican mavi, d tissist n rtila, lemmer ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 401,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3382,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi Iéôa akw ayen uuô naâôen, war Neppa. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 401,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3383,
            "text": "Imedyaten agi, Neppawi ten id, i laci. Siwa imusnawen ara ten ifehmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 401,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3384,
            "text": "Ixleq Öebbi tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ih, deg waya, assekni i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 401,
            "ruku": 345,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3385,
            "text": "Mel ayen i k id ippuweêêan si Tezmamt. Bedd i téallit. Ih, taéallit teppekkes lâaô, tuccva. War ccek, iugar ip usmekti n Öebbi. Öebbi Iéôa acu tûenâam.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 20,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 401,
            "ruku": 346,
            "hizbQuarter": 160,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3386,
            "text": "Ur pnamaret At Tezmamt, siwa s wawal aéidan, siwa wid degsen idensen. Init: 'numen s wayen id irsen uône, id irsen uôwen. Öebbi nne, akked Öebbi nnwen, Yiwen. Nekwni uôeS d imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 402,
            "ruku": 346,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3387,
            "text": "Akka ay ed Nessers, uôek, Tazmamt. Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, umnen yis. Ger wigi, kra umnen yis. I inekôen issekniyen nne£, siwa ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 402,
            "ruku": 346,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3388,
            "text": "Ur telliv temmalev kra n Tezmamt, uqbel tagi; ur p tepparuv, s uyeffus ik. Yili ad cukken inekkaôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 402,
            "ruku": 346,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3389,
            "text": "Xaîi, neppa d issekniyen iberrzen, deg idmaren n wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni. Siwa imednas, i inekôen issekniyen nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 402,
            "ruku": 346,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3390,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a lemmer id rsen fellas, issekniyen suô Mass is'! Ini: 'issekniyen ar Öebbi kan. Nek, d aneddaô kan, ipbegginen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 402,
            "ruku": 346,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3391,
            "text": "Ne, ur steqnaâen ara s trusi uôek, suône£, n Tezmamt, malen asen p. Deg waya, s tidep, aêunu, akked usmekti i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 402,
            "ruku": 346,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3392,
            "text": "Ini: 'Iqadd Öebbi, d anagi gari yidwen. Issen i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Wid iumnen di tkerkas, u ugin Öebbi, widak d imexsuôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 402,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3393,
            "text": "Sêirin k ef uâaqeb. Lemmer maççi d lajel ipwassnen, a ten id ias uâaqeb. Ih, a ten id ias, deqzalla, ur bnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3394,
            "text": "Sêirin k ef uâaqeb. Ih, Loahennama a ppezzi i ijehliyen",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3395,
            "text": "Ass ideg ar asen isbur uâaqeb, sennig sen, akw seddaw ivaôen nnsen, ad Yini: 'jeôôbet ayen txeddmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3396,
            "text": "A yimdanen iW iumnen, ni tamurt iW tewsaâ. Ihi, âabdet iyI, Nek.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3397,
            "text": "Yal iman, ad ijeôôeb tameppant; sinna, uône£ a d tualem.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3398,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad asen Nerr tanezdut di Loennet m tuôfatin, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen, degs ad wekkôen. D asaâdi warraz n wid ixedmen lxiô,",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3399,
            "text": "wid iûebôen, ippeklen ef Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3400,
            "text": "Acêal n lewêuc, ur d neppawi ôôeéq nnsen. Öebbi Iôeéq iten, u Iôeéq ikwen. Neppa, Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3401,
            "text": "Ma testeqûav ten: 'anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, i Inuben s yiîij akked waggur'? A d inin, war ccekk: 'd Öebbi'. Ihi, acimi wexxôen?",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3402,
            "text": "Öebbi Issugut lit i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, u Iwezzen as. Ih, Öebbi Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3403,
            "text": "Ma testeqûav ten: 'anwa id Isselayen aman seg igenni, Issidir yissen akal, deffir tmeppant is'? A d inin, war ccekk, 'd Öebbi'. Ini: 'ccekôan i Öebbi'. Maca, tegwti degsen, ur fhimen.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 403,
            "ruku": 347,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3404,
            "text": "Tameddurt agi, di ddunit, siwa lhawiyya, d wurar. D axxam aneggaru, war ccekk, ay d amuddir, lemmer éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 404,
            "ruku": 348,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3405,
            "text": "Mara rekben di lbabuô, ad naâôen Öebbi, d idiniyen zeddigen uôeS. Mi ten Isellek ar lberr, atnan la pcaraken.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 404,
            "ruku": 348,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3406,
            "text": "Ad nekôen ayen i sen Nefka, ad zhun, deqqal ad éôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 404,
            "ruku": 348,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3407,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara, Nerra loamaâ n laman, wanag la pwaxvafen imdanen i sen d izzin? Day ad amnen di tkerkas, u ad nekôen lit n Öebbi?",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 404,
            "ruku": 348,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3408,
            "text": "Anwa i idensen kteô: win id isnulfan tikerkas af Öebbi, ne win irran tidep d tikerkas, mi t id tusa? Day maççi d Loahennama ay d tanezdut i ijehliyen?",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 21,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 404,
            "ruku": 348,
            "hizbQuarter": 161,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3409,
            "text": "Wid ijuhden ar loiha nne£, a ten Nenhu, war ccekk, s iberdan nne£. Ih, Öebbi Ippili ar lâuûam.",
