            "page": 440,
            "ruku": 381,
            "hizbQuarter": 176,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3717,
            "text": "Ih, Nekwni Nessidir lmeggtin. Nepparu ayen xeddmen akked lateô nnsen. Neêseb yal cci di Tezmamt ipbegginen.",
