          },
          {
            "number": 3992,
            "text": "Mi kecmen ar Dawed, iugad iten. Nnan: 'ur ppagwad, d sin ixûimen, yiwen degne, ijuô ef wayev. Eêkem garane s tidep, war taneêyaft. Enhu ya s abrid umâin.",
