            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3993,
            "text": "Ihi, gma yagi, isâa tza u tzat n wulli, nek tixsi yiwet. Inna yi d: kwellef iyi p. Irna yi s wawal'.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
