            "ruku": 392,
            "hizbQuarter": 182,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3997,
            "text": "Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di rrayaâ, akken nwan wid ijehlen. A tawait n tmes, i wid ijehlen!",
