          },
          {
            "number": 4058,
            "text": "Mi tâadda tallit, war ccekk, a kwen id iawev usali s.",
            "numberInSurah": 88,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 458,
            "ruku": 395,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 39,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الزُّمَرِ",
        "englishName": "Az-Zumar",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Groups",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4059,
            "text": "Tarusi n Tezmamt suô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 458,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4060,
            "text": "Ih, Nessader ak d Tazmamt, s tidep. Ihi, aâbed Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 458,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4061,
            "text": "Day maççi i Öebbi laâqida? Wid ippaddamen imawlan, war Neppa, nnan: 'naâbed iten kan, iwakken ad a rnun aseqôeb ar Öebbi'. Ih, Öebbi ad Iêudd garasen, ef wayen ief mgarraden. Öebbi, war ccekk, ur Inehhu win illan d akeddab, d ajehli.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 458,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4062,
            "text": "Lemmer Ibi Öebbi ad Isâu aqcic, yili Ifren, deg wayen Ixelleq, ayen i S ihwan. Gedha s yiS! Neppa d Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 458,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4063,
            "text": "Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Innev Iv i wass, Innev ass i yiv. Iêeppem i yiîij akked waggur, ad lêun, yal wa, ar lajel ipwassnen. Day Neppa maççi d Uzmir Ipsemmiêen?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 458,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4064,
            "text": "Ixelq ikwen si yiwen n lxelq. Irra, segs, tislit is. Issers awen d îam n tyugiwin n lmal. Ixelq ikwen di tâabbuvin n tyimmatin nnwen, lxelq deffir lxelq, di krav n tellisat. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. IneS tagelda, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Amek ihi tugim?",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 459,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4065,
            "text": "Ma tjehlem, Öebbi ur kwen Iêwao ara. Ur Ipôadi tijehli i imdanen iS. Ma tesnemmrem, a kwen Iôavi. Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev; sinna, ar Mass nnwen tualin nnwen; ad awen Imel acu txeddmem. Ih, Neppa, Issen i illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 459,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 183,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4066,
            "text": "Amdan, ma iêuza t ccqa, ad inuj ar Mass is, d ucâif uôes; sinna, ma Iat it suôeS, ad ippu ayen ief inuj uôeS, uqbel; ad irr i Öebbi tanudda, ad innetlaf seg ubrid iS. Ini: 'zzhu cwiî di tijehli k, ihi, keçç seg wat tmes'.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 459,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4067,
            "text": "Day win ippanzen deg iv, ikna u ibedd, ipêebbiô i laxeôt, issaram aêunu n Mass is…? Ini: 'day âadlen wid issnen akked wid ur nessin? Ay d ismektayen, kan, d uâqilen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 459,
            "ruku": 396,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4068,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yimdanen iW iumnen, êezzbet i Mass nnwen. Ayen ilhan i wid imaânen di ddunit agi. Tamurt n Öebbi tewsaâ. Ihi, arraz, war aktili, ad ippunefk i iûebôiyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 459,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4069,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek pwamôe d ad âabde Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4070,
            "text": "Pwamôe d, ad ili d amvuâ amenzu'.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4071,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek, ugade, ma aâûa Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4072,
            "text": "Ini: 'ad âabde Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4073,
            "text": "Ihi, âabdet i wen ihwan, war Neppa'. Ini: 'imexsuôen d wid iwedôen iman nnsen, akked twacult nnsen, ass n tnekra'. Ni d tagi ay d taxessaôt n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4074,
            "text": "Aembabu n tmes, sennig sen, wayev seddawat sen. Ayagi, Issagwad yis Öebbi imdanen iS: a yimdanen iW, êezzbet iyI!",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4075,
            "text": "Wid ijunben aâbad iôebbiten n tkerkas, u iutuben Öebbi, a ten id ias lfeôê. Ihi, ssefôeê imdanen iW",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4076,
            "text": "i issemêasen i wawal, teddun d ûûam ines. D wigi i Inha Öebbi, d wigi ay d uâqilen.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4077,
            "text": "Day win ief ippuseyya ad isâaddi aâaqeb, day a psellkev keçç, win illan di tmes?",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4078,
            "text": "Ma d wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen, ad sâun tiuôfatin, bnant ta sennig ta, isaffen seddawat sent ppazzalen, d lemâahda n Öebbi. Öebbi ur Ixeîîu i lemâahda.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4079,
            "text": "Ur twalav ara, Öebbi Isseli d aman, seg igenni, Issekcem iten ad sswen akal. Sinna, yissen, a d Issuffe iman n yal ini, ara iualen ad isliwen. A ten twaliv d iwôaen, sinna, a ten Irr d iquôanen. Deg waya, s tidep, asmekti i uâqilen.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 460,
            "ruku": 397,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4080,
            "text": "Day win iwumi Illi Öebbi, idmaren is, ar wannuz, da neppa di tafat suô Mass is…? A ssxev n at wulawen iqquôen, ur d smektayen Öebbi! Widak di ttelfan n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4081,
            "text": "Issader ed Öebbi ûûam n wawal. Tazmamt, degs acbi, allus. Ad ccirwen segs igwelman akked wulawen n wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, sinna, igwelman akked wulawen nnsen ad iêninen ar usmekti n Öebbi. D tagi ay d nnhaya n Öebbi. Inehhu yis, win i S ihwan. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur illi wa ara t inhun.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4082,
            "text": "Day win ipêezziben, s wudem is, seg uâaqeb ucmit, ass n tnekra…? Ad inin i imednas: 'jeôôbet ayen tkeppbem'!",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4083,
            "text": "Skaddben wid i ten id izwaren. Iusa ten id uâaqeb, seg wanda ur bnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4084,
            "text": "Issukk fellasen Öebbi aâaqeb, di tmeddurt n ddunit; war ccekk, aâaqeb n laxeôt iugar it, lemmer éeôôen!",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4085,
            "text": "Ni Nefka i imdanen, di Leqwôan agi, yal amedya, amar a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4086,
            "text": "Leqwôan s taâôabt, ur degs tiââawji; amar ad êezzben.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4087,
            "text": "Ifka d Öebbi amedya n urgaz icerken akked wid ipmeréan, u argaz di tifrat akked yiwen urgaz. Day âadlen sin imedyaten? Ccekôan i Öebbi. Xaîi, tegwti degsen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4088,
            "text": "War ccekk, keçç a ppemmtev, nitni ad mmten.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4089,
            "text": "Sinna, kunwi, ass n tnekra, ar Mass nnwen, a ppemqellaâm.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 23,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 461,
            "ruku": 398,
            "hizbQuarter": 184,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4090,
            "text": "Anwa i idensen sennig win iskaddben af Öebbi, iskaddben tidep ma tusa t id? Day maççi di Loahennama, i illa uxxam ijehliyen?",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4091,
            "text": "Wid id iusan s tidep, u pputebbten yis, wigi d wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4092,
            "text": "Ad sâun ayen ban, ar Mass nnsen. D wagi ay d arraz iâaôviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4093,
            "text": "Iwakken ad asen Ikkes Öebbi, ayen xedmen adiran mavi; a ten Iit s wayen xeddmen d amxallef.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4094,
            "text": "Day ur Ipqam ara Öebbi amdan iS? La k ssagwaden s wid, war Neppa. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur illi w ara t inhun.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4095,
            "text": "Win Inha Öebbi, ur illi w ara t itelfen. Ni Öebbi d Uzmir, Bab n ppaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4096,
            "text": "Ma testeqsav ten: 'anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan? Ad inin, war ccekk: d Öebbi'. Ini: 'ma twalam wigi tnaâôem, war Öebbi, day zemren, ma Iba yi Öebbi ccqa, ad kksen ccqa S? Ne, ma Iba yi aêunu, ad ssbeîlen aêunu S'? Ini: 'Iqennaâ iyi Öebbi; fellaS ay ppeklen wid ipkalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4097,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yagdud iw! Xedmet akken tennumen, nek la xeddme'. Deqqal a ppeéôem",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4098,
            "text": "anwa uuô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, uuô ara d irs uâaqeb imezgi.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 462,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4099,
            "text": "Ih, Nessader ed uôek, Tazmamt i medden, s tidets. Win ipwanhan, i iman is, win innetlafen, innetlaf kan, mgal is. Ur telliv, keçç, d awkil nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 463,
            "ruku": 399,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4100,
            "text": "Öebbi Ippaddam leôwaê mara mmten, akked wid ur nemmut, deg ives nnsen. Iâatteq wid ief Iseyya tameppant, Ippara d wiyav, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ih, deg wayagi, ard issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 463,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4101,
            "text": "Ne ad ddmen, war Öebbi, imcafâan? Ini: 'i ma ur sâin acemma, ur fhimen'?",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 463,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4102,
            "text": "Ini: 'akw ccafuâa n Öebbi. IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Sinna, uôeS ara tualem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 463,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4103,
            "text": "Mara d Ipwadder Öebbi Yiwen, ad zemven wulawen n wid ur numin ara s laxeôt. Ma pwadren d wid, war Neppa, imiren nitni ad ceôêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 463,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4104,
            "text": "Ini: 'a Öebbi! Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan, Amusnaw n wayen iffren d wayen ivehôen, d Keçç ara Iêudden ger imdanen iK, ef wayen llan mgarraden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 463,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4105,
            "text": "Wid idensen, lemmer nnsen ayen akw i illan di tmurt, rnu yas am neppa, ur ten id ifeddu, seg uâaqeb ucmit, ass n tnekra. Ad asen d iban, suô Öebbi, ayen ief ur bnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 463,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4106,
            "text": "Ad asen d banent tucmitin kesben, ad asen innev wayen ief ttahan.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4107,
            "text": "Ma iêuza umdan ccqa, ad a£ d inâaô. Sinna, ma Nezger tacvaî nne£ fellas, ad yini: 'tusa yi d kan si tmusni'. Xaîi! D ajeôôeb, maca aîas degsen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4108,
            "text": "Ni nnan t id imezwura nnsen. Acu i sen d ibbwi wayen keppben?",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4109,
            "text": "Iwwet iten wayen kesben n tucmitin. Wid idensen, seg wigi, a ten iwwet wayen kesben n tucmitin. Ur zmiren ad sfunngen.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4110,
            "text": "Day ur éôin ara ar Öebbi Ipiti win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen? Ih, deg waya, ard issekniyen i ugdud iumnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 400,
            "hizbQuarter": 185,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4111,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yimdanen iw i ipêawalen mgal iman nnsen! Ur ppayset aêunu n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ipsemmiê akw ibekkaven. Ih, Neppa Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4112,
            "text": "Steôoâet i Mass nnwen, anzet aS, uqbel a kwen id ias uâaqeb, da ula ikwen isellken.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4113,
            "text": "Ddut d ûûam n wayen i wen d irsen, suô Mass nnwen, uqbel a kwen id ias uâaqeb, deqzalla, kunwi ur tebnim';",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4114,
            "text": "u a d yini ôôuê: 'a ssexv iw, ef wayen stehza ar loiha n Öebbi! Lli, s tidep, seg wid ittihin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 464,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4115,
            "text": "Ne a d yini: 'lemmer iyi Inha Öebbi, yili lli seg wid ipêezziben'.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4116,
            "text": "Ne a d yini mara iwali aâaqeb: 'lemmer iyi illi wallus, ad ili si lâuûam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4117,
            "text": "Xaîi! Usan k id issekniyen iW, teskaddbev ten, tzuxxev, telliv seg ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4118,
            "text": "Ass n tnekra, a pwaliv berrikit wudmawen n wid id igren tikerkas af Öebbi. Day maççi di Loahennama, i illa uxxam imzuxiyen?",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4119,
            "text": "Ad Isellek Öebbi wid iêezzben; ar rebêen. Ur ten ikkat wugur, ur webbnen.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4120,
            "text": "Öebbi Ixleq yal cci. Neppa d Awkil n yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4121,
            "text": "IneS tsura n tmurt akked igenwan. Wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, widak d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 401,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4122,
            "text": "Ini: 'day ad yi tamôem ad âabde, war Öebbi, a wid ur nessin'?",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 402,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4123,
            "text": "Ni iusa k id uweêêi, u eô wid i k izwaren. Ma tcurkev, ad mêun igiten ik, a ppiliv seg imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 402,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4124,
            "text": "Xaîi! Aâbed Öebbi. Ili seg wid isnemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 402,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4125,
            "text": "Ur qudôen ara Öebbi, azal n lqedô iS. Akw tamurt, ass n tnekra, di tumeét iS. Igenwan ad nnefvasen deg ufus iS ayeffus. Gedha s yiS! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 465,
            "ruku": 402,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4126,
            "text": "Aûuvu di lbuq: ad ixsef i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, kkes ed i S ihwan i Öebbi. Aûuvu nniven: nitni a d kkren pmuqulen.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 466,
            "ruku": 402,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4127,
            "text": "A pfeooeo tmurt, si tafat n Mass is. A d ters Tezmamt, a d awin lambiyya akked inagan. Ad âaddin di ccôaâ, s tidep, ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 466,
            "ruku": 402,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4128,
            "text": "Yal yiwen ad iellet ayen ixdem. Neppa, Yif akw akken Issen, d acu xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 466,
            "ruku": 402,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4129,
            "text": "Ad pwanehôen wid ijehlen, d igrawen, ar Loahennama. Mi bbwven uôes, u llint tebbura s, ad asen inin iâssasen is: 'day ur kwen in usan ara imazanen, segwen, mmalen awen issekniyen n Mass nnwen, nedôen kwen af temlilit n wass nnwen agi'? A d inin: 'Ih. Maca, ad iûaô wawal uâaqeb, af ijehliyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 466,
            "ruku": 403,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4130,
            "text": "A d inin: 'kecmet si tebbura, ar Loahennama! Degs, wekkôet'. Ay d ucmit uxxam n imzuxiyen!",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 466,
            "ruku": 403,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4131,
            "text": "Wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen, ad pwanehôen ar Loennet, d igrawen. Mi bbwven uôes, u llint tebbura s, ad asen inin iâssasen is: 'tifrat fellawen, tgerzem; kecmet ep, twekkôem'!",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 466,
            "ruku": 403,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4132,
            "text": "Ad inin: 'ccekôan i Öebbi i  Issawven lemâahda S. Ifka ya tamurt d lweôt; a nili, di Loennet, anda i  ihwa. A yarraz asaâdi n wid ixeddmen lxiô!",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 466,
            "ruku": 403,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4133,
            "text": "A pwaliv lmalayek zzint ed i usgeld, sbuccuâent s ccekôan Mass nnsent. Iâadda ccôaâ garasen, s tidep. Ad inin: 'a neckeô Öebbi, Mass imavalen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 403,
            "hizbQuarter": 186,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 40,
        "name": "سُورَةُ غَافِرٍ",
        "englishName": "Ghafir",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Forgiver",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4134,
            "text": "Ëm.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4135,
            "text": "Tarusi n Tezmamt, suô Öebbi, Uzmir, Amusnaw;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4136,
            "text": "Ipsemmiêen tuccva, Iqeblen nndama, Ipâaqaben s teqseê, Bab n terkunt. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. £uôeS taggara.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4137,
            "text": "Siwa wid ijehlen i ipnamaren ef issekniyen n Öebbi. Ur k ipuôôu ucali nnsen, di tmurt.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4138,
            "text": "Uqbel nitni, agdud n Nuê, akked ikabaren deffir sen, skaddben. Yal lois iclaâ ad ixvef amazan is. Ipnamar s tkerkas, iwakken, s yissent, ad iveggeô tidep. Ëekme ten. A tiyta W imiren!",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4139,
            "text": "Akka iûaô wawal n Mass ik, af wid ijehlen. Nitni, war ccekk, d at tmes.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4140,
            "text": "Tid irefden asgeld, akked tid i s izzin, sbuccuâen s ccekôan Mass nnsent, umnent yiS. Ssuturent ad pwasemmêen wid iumnen: 'a Mass nne! Terriv yal cci d aêunu, u d tamusni. Semmeê i wid isteôoâen u ddan d ubrid iK; Sellek iten seg uâaqeb n wuud.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 467,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4141,
            "text": "A Mass nne! Ssekcem iten ar leonanat n Âaden, i Tâahdev, i nitni, u i iâaôviyen seg ibabaten nnsen, tilawin nnsen, tarwa nnsen. Keçç, ih, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4142,
            "text": "Aâteq iten si tucmitin. Win Tâatqev, assen, si tucmitin, ni Têunev fellas. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 404,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4143,
            "text": "Ad pwanecden wid ijehlen: 'taâdawt n Öebbi teleb taâdawt bbwaygarawen. Mi tepwanecdem ar liman, tugim'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4144,
            "text": "A d inin: 'a Mass nne! Teniv a berdayen, Tessidrev a berdayen. Nqaôô s ibekkaven nne. Day illa ubrid n tuffa'?",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4145,
            "text": "Akka, imi mara ipwanâaô Öebbi Yiwen, kunwi tjehlem. Mara S pcaraken, kunwi tumnem. Aêuddu ar Öebbi Aâlayen, Ameqwôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4146,
            "text": "D Neppa i wen Issnaâtan issekniyen iS. Issadar awen d lit, seg igenni. Siwa win isteôoiâen, id ismektayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4147,
            "text": "Nujet uô Öebbi, s laâqida i Neppa, xas ugin ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4148,
            "text": "Aâlayen nnig idurra, Bab n usgeld, Ippak ôôuê s lameô iS, i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, iwakken ad indeô af wass umlili,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4149,
            "text": "ass ideg ara d awven, ur illi wayen iffren, degsen, i Öebbi. W ip ilan tgelda, assen? D Öebbi, Yiwen, Aqehhaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 468,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4150,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ippuqeîîi yal iman ef wayen ikseb; ur ippili ddens assen. Ih, Öebbi Ipawal deg uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4151,
            "text": "Nabi ten af ass aqôib, ideg ulawen ad rewlen s igerjumen, ad qebôen. Ur ippilli i imednas, uêbib ne amcafaâ, iwumi ara ssemêessen.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4152,
            "text": "Issen nncub n yiéôi, akked wayen teffren idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4153,
            "text": "Öebbi Iferru s tidep. Wid ipnujun ar war Neppa, ur qeîîun acemma. Ih, Öebbi d Win Isellen, Ipwalin.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 405,
            "hizbQuarter": 187,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4154,
            "text": "Day ur nudan ara tamurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren. Llan ifen ten tazmert, akked lateô, di tmurt. Issemêelleq asen Öebbi, ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Ur asen illi umêareb, mgal Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 406,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4155,
            "text": "Akka, acku ppasen uôsen, imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen, u nitni jehlen. Issemêelleq asen Öebbi. Ih, Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab uâaqeb uqsiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 406,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4156,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed Musa s issekniyen nne£, s udabu iberrzen,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 406,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4157,
            "text": "ar Ferâun, Haman, akked Qaôun. Nnan: 'd aseêêar, d akeddab'.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 406,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4158,
            "text": "Mi sen d iusa, s tidep s uône£, nnan: 'enet arrac n wid iumnen yides, ssidret tilawin nnsen'. Tandit ijehliyen siwa di ttelfan.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 469,
            "ruku": 406,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4159,
            "text": "Inna Ferâun: 'anfet iyi ad ne Musa, xas ad inuj ar Mass is. Ugade, nek, ad ibeddel ddin nnwen, ne a d issekcem lefsad di tmurt'.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 406,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4160,
            "text": "Inna Musa: 'nek, ad iyi Iûûeô Mass iw u Mass nnwen, si yal amzuxi, ur numin s wass uqeîîi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 406,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4161,
            "text": "Inna urgaz lmumen, i iffren liman is, si twacult n Ferâun: 'day a ppenem argaz, imi d iqqaô: Mass iw d Öebbi, u irna ibbwi yawen d abeggen, suô Mass nnwen? Ma iskaddeb, lkedb is fellas. Ma issawel tidep, a kwen iêaz kra seg wayen ikwen issagwad. Öebbi ur Inehhu amaâfun iskiddiben.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4162,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Assa, nnwen tagelda, tufrarem di tmurt. W ad a isellken si tiyta n Öebbi, ma tusa ya d'? Inna d Ferâun: 'i wen ssekne ayen kan wala; s anda i kwen nehhu, siwa ar ubrid imaânen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4163,
            "text": "Inna d win iumnen: 'a yagdud iw! Nek, ugade fellak tin n wass ikabaren,",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4164,
            "text": "akken tevôa d ugdud n Nuê, Âad, Tamud, akked wid i ten id ivefôen. Öebbi ur Iba ara ddens i imdanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4165,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Nek ugade, ay kwen ippaen, ass umnamar,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4166,
            "text": "ass ideg ara trewlem ar deffir. Ur awen illi umêareb mgal Öebbi. Ur illi nnahi i win Itlef Öebbi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 470,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4167,
            "text": "Ni iusa kwen id Yusef, zik, s ubeggen. Tezgam di ccekk, ef wayen i wen d ibbwi. Armi immut, tennam: 'ur d Ippazen ara Öebbi amazan, deffir es, d awezi'. Akka i Itellif Öebbi amaâfun amcekki.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 471,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4168,
            "text": "Wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten id iusi udabu, nezzeh ara ten iunfu Öebbi, akked wid iumnen. Akka ara Icemmaâ Öebbi, yal ul amzuxi, aâfrit.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 471,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4169,
            "text": "Inna Ferâun: 'a Haman, bnu yi lbeôo, amar ad awve ar iberdan,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 471,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4170,
            "text": "iberdan igenwan. Ad ali ar Öebbi n Musa. Nek êesbe t d akeddab'. Akka i s ippucebbeê i Ferâun, igi s ucmit. Ippuveôôef seg ubrid. Tandit n Ferâun, siwa taxeûûart.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 471,
            "ruku": 407,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4171,
            "text": "Inna d win iumnen: 'a yagdud iw! Ddu yidi, a k nhu s abrid umâin.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 471,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4172,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Tameddurt agi, di ddunit, d zzhu kan; wanag laxeôt d axxam n leqôaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 471,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4173,
            "text": "Win ixedmen tucmip, ad ippuqeîîi, kan, s tin i p icban. Wid ixedmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne d nnta, u nitni umnen, widak ad kecmen Loennet; din, ad aten iten, war aktili.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 471,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 188,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4174,
            "text": "A yagdud iw! Acu iyi bbwin, a kwen neccde ar leslak; kunwi, a yi tneccdem ar tmessi?",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4175,
            "text": "A yi tneccdem ad aâûu Öebbi, ad aS carke ayen ur ssine. Nek, neccde kwen ar Uzmir Ipsemmiêen",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4176,
            "text": "War ccekk, ayen uuô a yi tneccdem, ur as iwata unuju di ddunit, u di laxeôt. Ih, tualin nne ar Öebbi. Imaâfan ard at tmes.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4177,
            "text": "A d tesmektim ayen i wen qqaôe. Öôay iw fki t i Öebbi. Ni Öebbi Ipwali imdanen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4178,
            "text": "Isellek it Öebbi si tucmitin i undin. Iwellef lois n Ferâun, s uâaqeb iugaren wiyav:",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4179,
            "text": "times. Ad pwafessren degs, ûûbeê, tameddit. Ass ideg ara d ias yimir: 'ekcem, a lois n Ferâun, aâaqeb uwâiô mavi'!",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4180,
            "text": "Mara ppemqellaâen di tmes, ad inin uôhifen i imzuxiyen: 'ni nella nedda yidwen. Ma tzemrem, kunwi, ad a tesneqsem cwiî, si tmes'?",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4181,
            "text": "A d inin imzuxiyen: 'aql a, akw, degs. S tidep, Öebbi Iêudd ger imdanen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4182,
            "text": "Ad inin wid illan di tmes, i iâessasen n Loahennama: 'naâôet Mass nnwen, ad a Issifes ibwass uâaqeb'.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 472,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4183,
            "text": "Ad inin: 'day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen nnwen, s ubeggen'? Ad inin: 'ih'. Ad inin: 'naâret'! Ar ttelfan, kan, tanaârit ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 408,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4184,
            "text": "War ccekk, a Nsellek imazanen nne£, akked wid iumnen, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u deg wass ideg ara d bedden inagan,",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4185,
            "text": "ass ideg ur infaâ ustefeô imednas. Ad pwaxzun, ad zeden deg uxxam ucmit mavi.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4186,
            "text": "Ni Nefka, i Musa, nnhaya. Nefka, i At Isôail, Tazmamt d lweôt.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4187,
            "text": "D nnhaya, u d asmekti i uâqilen.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4188,
            "text": "Eûbeô. Ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep. Ssuter ssmaê ubekkav ik. Sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, tameddit, taûebêit.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4189,
            "text": "Ih, wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten id iusi udabu, d temweô kan i illan deg idmaren nnsen; ur as ssawven. Ggani Öebbi, Neppa, s tidep, Isell, Ipwali.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4190,
            "text": "Ih, lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan iugar lxelq n imdanen, maca aîas n imdanen ur éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4191,
            "text": "Ur iaâdil ara uderal akked win ipwalin, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, akked bu tucmitin. Cwiî id tesmektayem.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 473,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4192,
            "text": "Ihi, imir a d ias, ur illi ccekk fellas, maca tegwti n imdanen ur uminen.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4193,
            "text": "Inna Mass nnwen: 'naâret iyI, ad awen d Jawbe. Wanag wid igelzen aâbed iW, ad kecmen Loahennama, d imedlulen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 409,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4194,
            "text": "Öebbi i wen Irran iv, i ureyyeê degs, ass i tmuli. Öebbi, ih, d Bab n lfevl i imdanen, maca tegwti n imdanen, ur snemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4195,
            "text": "D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ixleq yal cci, ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa. Ihi, acimi tezzim akin?",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4196,
            "text": "Akka ay wexxôen wid iugin issekniyen n Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 63,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4197,
            "text": "Öebbi i wen Irran tamurt d leqôaô, igenni d ssqef; ikwen Imeslen. Iûeggem udem nnwen. Iat ikwen s wayen ilhan. D wagi ay d Öebbi, Mass nnwen. D Asaâdi Öebbi, Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 64,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4198,
            "text": "Neppa d Amuddir, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, naâôet eP, s lâaqida i Neppa. Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 65,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 189,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4199,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek, ipwakkes iyi uâbad n wid tnaârem war Öebbi, mi yi d iusa ubeggen, suô Mass iw. Pwamôe d, ad anze i Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 66,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 474,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4200,
            "text": "Neppa, ikwen Ixelqen seg wakal; sinna, si tiqqit; sinna, seg urgen; sinna, Issuffe ikwen id d igwerdan; sinna, a ppimuôem; sinna, a ppualem d imaôen. Kra segwen, pmeppaten uqbel. Iwakken a ppawvem ar lajel ipwassnen. Amendeô ma a pfehmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 67,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4201,
            "text": "D Neppa i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. Ma Iseyya d lameô, ad as Yini kan: 'ili'! Ad yili.",
            "numberInSurah": 68,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 410,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4202,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara amek ssuffen i ubrid, wid ipnamaren issekniyen n Öebbi?",
            "numberInSurah": 69,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4203,
            "text": "Wid iskaddben Tazmamt, akked wayen ief id Nuzen imazanen nne£, deqqal ad éôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 70,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4204,
            "text": "Mara pwazuôen, s teqlavin d slasel,",
            "numberInSurah": 71,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4205,
            "text": "ar waman ippayzagen; sinna, ar tmes, ad pwaveggôen;",
            "numberInSurah": 72,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4206,
            "text": "sinna, ad asen inin: 'anda t wayen tepcarakem",
            "numberInSurah": 73,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4207,
            "text": "war Öebbi'? A d inin: 'dergen fella. Xaîi! Ur illi wayen uuô nepnuju, zik'. Akka i Itellif Öebbi ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 74,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4208,
            "text": "Akka, ef wayen tzehhum di tmurt, ur teklalem, akked wayen tqebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 75,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4209,
            "text": "Kecmet Loahennama, si tebbura; degs twekkôem. Ay dir tanezdut imzuxiyen!",
            "numberInSurah": 76,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4210,
            "text": "Eûbeô, war ccekk, lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Ad ak Nessken kra n wayen i sen Nâahed, ne a Neddem ôôuê ik. £uône£ ara d ualen.",
            "numberInSurah": 77,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 475,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4211,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed imazanen uqbel ik. £ef kra segsen, Neêka yak d. £ef kra nniven, ur ak d Neêka ara. Ur iwata ara i umazan, a d iawi assekni, siwa ma s tsriê n Öebbi. Ma iusa d lameô n Öebbi, aseyyi s tidep. Ad xesôen, imiren, laâôuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 78,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 411,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4212,
            "text": "Öebbi i wen Ifkan lmal i rekba nnwen. Segsen teppeppem.",
            "numberInSurah": 79,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 412,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4213,
            "text": "Degsen, i kunwi, abauô akked agwav ar wayen id ssuturen idmaren nnwen. Fellasen, akw f ssfinat, teppâabbim.",
            "numberInSurah": 80,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 412,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4214,
            "text": "Issenâat awen d issekniyen iS. Anwi issekniyen n Öebbi ara tnekôem?",
            "numberInSurah": 81,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 412,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4215,
            "text": "Day ur nudan ara tamurt ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren. Llan ifen ten akken îîuqten, ifen ten tazmert akked lateô di tmurt. Ulay sen d ibbwi wayen la keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 82,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 412,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4216,
            "text": "Mi ten id usan imazanen nnsen s ubeggen, feôêen s tmusni i illan uôsen. Izzi fellasen wayen ief ppemsexxiôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 83,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 412,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4217,
            "text": "Mi walan tamnirt nne£, nnan: 'numen s Öebbi Yiwen, nveggeô ayen i nella ncurek aS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 84,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 412,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4218,
            "text": "Ur izmir ara a ten infaâ liman nnsen, mi walan tamnirt nne£. D tannumi n Öebbi, si zik, i imdanen iS. Akka ay xesôen ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 85,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 476,
            "ruku": 412,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 41,
        "name": "سُورَةُ فُصِّلَتۡ",
        "englishName": "Fussilat",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Explained in detail",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4219,
            "text": "Ëm.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4220,
            "text": "Tarusi suô Uênin Ipêunun,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4221,
            "text": "Tazmamt, feûûlen issekniyen is; Leqwôan s taâôabt, i ugdud issnen,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4222,
            "text": "ipbecciôen, ineddôen. Tegwti degsen numren, da ur sellen.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4223,
            "text": "Nnan: 'ulawen nne ddurin i wayen ieô la  tneccdev; di tmejjin nne: tiâéegt; garane yidek: sîeô. Ihi, exdem, nekwni la nxeddem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4224,
            "text": "Ini: 'nek d amdan kan, am kunwi. Weêêan iyi d kan ar Öebbi nnwen, d Öebbi Yiwen. Sweqmet uôeS, ssutret aS ssmaê'. A tawait n imcurak,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4225,
            "text": "wid ur nepzekki, u nitni nekôen laxeôt!",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4226,
            "text": "Ih, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan: arraz ur nepnegzay.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 413,
            "hizbQuarter": 190,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4227,
            "text": "Ini: 'kunwi aql akwen la tnekôem Win Ixelqen tamurt, di sin wussan. La S tepparam nned. Wagi d Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4228,
            "text": "Irra degs idurar sufella. Iôqa p, Iwzen degs tagwella s, di kué wussan. Akka i wid isteqsayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4229,
            "text": "Sinna, Izzi ar igenni i illan d abbu. Inna yas, u i tmurt: 'aset ed, tebam ne tugim'! Nnan: 'a n nas, d imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 477,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4230,
            "text": "Iseyya ten d ûa igenwan, di sin wussan. Iweêêa lameô is, i yal igenni. Ncebbeê igenni aqôib mavi, s teftilin, u d laânaya. D aya ay d Iqeddeô n Uzmir, Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4231,
            "text": "Ma numren, ini: 'ssagwde kwen s ssiâqa, am ssiâqa n Âad u Tamud'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4232,
            "text": "Mi ten id usan imazanen, zdat sen, u deffir sen: 'ur âabdet, siwa Öebbi'! Nnan: 'lemmer i S ihwi i Mass nne, a d Issers lmalayek. Nekwni, ihi, nenkeô ayen i s id teppuceggâam'.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4233,
            "text": "Wanag Âad, smewôen iman nnsen di tmurt, ur klalen. Nnan: 'anwa i  ielben di tezmert'? Day ur walan ara, Öebbi, iten id Ixelqen, Ielb iten di tezmert? Llan la nekôen issekniyen nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4234,
            "text": "Nuzen asen aûeôûaô, deg ussan imevyaôen, iwakken a Nessukk fellasen, aâaqeb imdelli di tmeddurt n ddunit. Aâaqeb n laxeôt, war ccekk, isdullu kteô. Ur asen ippili umâiwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4235,
            "text": "Wanag Tamud, Nebbwi ten d ubrid. Smenyafen tiderelt i nnhaya. Tewwet iten ssiâqa n uâaqeb issrusun, ilmend n wayen keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4236,
            "text": "Nsellek wid iumnen, i illan pêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 414,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4237,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ssemlilen ar tmessi, icenga n Öebbi, nitni ad pwajemmlen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 415,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4238,
            "text": "Alamma, mara awven uôes, ad cehhden fellasen, ef wayen xeddmen, imeééuen nnsen, allen nnsen, d igwelman nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 478,
            "ruku": 415,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4239,
            "text": "Ad inin i igwelman nnsen: 'acimi id tcuhhdem fella'? A d inin: 'Issenîeq a d Öebbi, id Issentaqen yal cci. Neppa, Ixelq ikwen tikelt tamezwarut, u uôeS ara tualem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 415,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4240,
            "text": "Ur tezmirem ara a ppeffrem, ur cehhden fellawen imeééuen nnwen, allen nnwen, akked igwelman nnwen. Maca, tilem ur Iéeô ara Öebbi, aîas n wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 415,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4241,
            "text": "Akka ameyyez nnwen ef Mass nnwen. Isqucc ikwen, tegwram d d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 415,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4242,
            "text": "Xas ûebôen, di tmes ara zeden. Ma ssutren ssmaê, ur llin d wid ara ipwaqeblen.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 415,
            "hizbQuarter": 191,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4243,
            "text": "Nefka yasen imeddukwal i sen icebbêen ayen illan zdat sen, akked wayen illan deffir sen. Iûaô fellasen wawal ger leoyus n yimdanen akw n leonun, i iaben, uqbel nnsen. Ih, nitni d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 415,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4244,
            "text": "Nnan wid ijehlen: 'ur ssemêaset i Leqwôan agi. Ssekret fellas, tawegwa, ahat a prebêem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 416,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4245,
            "text": "A Nessukk ef wid ijehlen, aâaqeb uqsiê. A ten Nqeîîi sennig wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 416,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4246,
            "text": "D wagi ay d aqeîîi icenga n Öebbi: times; i nitni degs axxam n lebda; d aqeîîi, imi la nekôen issekniyen nne£.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 416,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4247,
            "text": "Ad inin, wid ijehlen: 'a Mass nne! Essken a wid i  ielîen, d loenn ne d amdan; a ten neôkev, ad ualen seg wid indellen mavi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 479,
            "ruku": 416,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4248,
            "text": "Ih, wid innan: 'Mass nne d Öebbi', sinna, nudan lewqama, a d rsent uôsen lmalayek: 'ur ppagwadet, ur webblet; ppubeccôet s Loennet i wen ippuwaââden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 416,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4249,
            "text": "Nekwni d imawlan nnwen di tmeddurt n ddunit u di laxeôt. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen i cedhant teôwiêin nnwen. Dinna, i kunwi, ayen tessutrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 416,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4250,
            "text": "D tarusi suô Win Ipsemmiêen, Ipêunun.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 416,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4251,
            "text": "Anwa yifen awal umâin n win inaâôen Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, id innan: 'nek, ih, seg imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4252,
            "text": "Ur iaâdil ise akked tucmip. Err ip akin, s wayen ip yifen. Ma tella cceêna, garak d yiwen, ad iual d aêbib i k iêemmlen.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4253,
            "text": "Ur teppunefk siwa i wid iûebbôen. Ur teppunefk, siwa i bu sser abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4254,
            "text": "Ma iccacev ak Cciîan tuccva, ssuter laânaya n Öebbi. Ih, Neppa d win Isellen, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4255,
            "text": "Seg issekniyen iS, ass akked yiv, iîij akked waggur. Ur kennut ara i yiîij, ne i waggur. Knut i Öebbi, iten id Ixelqen, ma d Neppa ay tâabbdem.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4256,
            "text": "Ma zuxxen, ihi, wid illan ar Mass ik, sbuccuâen T iv akked wass, ur âaggun.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 480,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 12,
              "recommended": false,
              "obligatory": true
            }
          },
          {
            "number": 4257,
            "text": "Seg issekniyen iS: a pwaliv, keçç, akal iqquô; lemmer ad as Nesseli aman, a d iakwi, ad icuff. Win it id Issadren, d Win ara d Issidren lmeggtin. Ih, Neppa, Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4258,
            "text": "Ih, wid issexûaôen issekniyen nne£, ur drigen fellane£. Menyif win ara ipwaveggôen ar tmes, ne win ara iasen di laman, ass n tnekra? Xedmet ayen i wen ihwan. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4259,
            "text": "Akka, wid inekôen asmekti, mi ten id iusa, u neppat ard Tazmamt tuzmirt.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4260,
            "text": "Ur d iusi lewlav zdat es, ne deffir es. D tarusi suô Bab n ûûwab, Amaâzuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4261,
            "text": "Awal i k id iusan, d win kan id iusan imazanen, uqbel ik. Mass ik, ih, ard Bab n ssmaê, d Bab uâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4262,
            "text": "Lemmer Nerri Leqwôan s tmeslayt tabeôôanit, a d inin: 'lemmer feûûlen issekniyen iS s wawal abeôôani, u s taâôabt'? Ini: 'neppa, i wid iumnen, d nnhaya u d ccafuâa. Wid ur numin ara, âaégent tmejjin nnsen. Neppa, i nitni, d tiderelt. Widak pwanecden seg umkan ibaâden'.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 417,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4263,
            "text": "Ni Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal suô Mass ik, yili tefra garasen. Nitni, fellas, di ccekk imcebbwel.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4264,
            "text": "Win ixedmen ayen ilhan, i iman is; win iccven, mgal iman is. Mass ik ur Idennis ara imdanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 24,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 481,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 192,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4265,
            "text": "£uôeS ay tella tmusni n yimir. Ur d iteffe uzway si txeddact is, ur treffed nnta tadist, ur tepparew, siwa ma Iéôa. Ass ideg ar asen Isiwel: 'anda ten icriken iW'? A d inin: 'ad aK nini, ur illi garane unagi'.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 25,
