            "page": 482,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4266,
            "text": "Iooa ten wayen uuô pnujun zik. Fehmen, ur asen illi ssôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 482,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4267,
            "text": "Ur ifeccel ara umdan di tuppra n lxiô. Ma inul it lqeôê, ad iayes, ad innuben.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 482,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4268,
            "text": "Ma Nseêess as aêunu nne£, deffir ccqa i t iêuzan, war ccekk, ad yini: 'ayagi inu. Ur cukke ara imir a d ias. Ma bbwve s afus n Mass iw, ad afe uôeS ûûam'. Ih, a Nbeggen ayen xedmen, i wid ijehlen, u, ih, ad Nsâaddi fellasen aâaqeb iwaâôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 482,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4269,
            "text": "Ma Nat amdan ad iwexxeô, izzi akin. Ma iêuza t lêif, ad ipnuju, irennu.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 482,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4270,
            "text": "Ini: 'tmeyyzem ma iusa d suô Öebbi, u kunwi tnekôem t'? Anwa innetlafen sennig win illan di ticuîna tumiqt?",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 482,
            "ruku": 418,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4271,
            "text": "Ad asen Nessken issekniyen nne£ di tmurt akked igenwan, u deg iman nnsen, alamma pputebbten ar neppa d tidep. Day ur Iqadd ara Mass ik mi Neppa, war ccekk, d Anagi n yal cci?",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
