            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4276,
            "text": "IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Neppa, d Aâlayen, d Ameqwôahan.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 483,
            "ruku": 419,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4277,
            "text": "Qôib ad ccergen igenwan seg ixfawen nnsen, mara d lhint lmalayek deg usbuccaâ s ccekôan n Mass nnsent, u ssuturent ad pwassemêen kra illan di tmurt. War ccekk, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 483,
            "ruku": 419,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4278,
            "text": "Wid irran imawlan, war Neppa, Iquôaâ ten Öebbi. Ur telliv, keçç, d awkil nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 483,
            "ruku": 419,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4279,
            "text": "Akka ay k n Nweêêa Leqwôan, s taâôabt, iwakken a pnedôev tayimmap n temdinin, akked wayen i s d izzin; a pnedôev af ass n temlilit, ur degs ccekk; arbaâ di Loennet, arbaâ deg ujajiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 483,
            "ruku": 419,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4280,
            "text": "Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili Izdukkel iten d yiwen n lois. Maca, ad Issekcem win i S ihwan ar uêunu S. Imednas, ur sâin bab ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 483,
            "ruku": 419,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4281,
            "text": "Ne rran imawlan, war Neppa. Öebbi d Neppa ay d Bab, d Neppa i Issidiren lmeggtin, d Neppa i Izemren i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 483,
            "ruku": 419,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4282,
            "text": "Ayen akw ief temgarradem, aêuddu s ar Öebbi. Akka Öebbi, Mass iw; fellaS ppekle, eô Neppa ay steôoiâe.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 483,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4283,
            "text": "Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan. Seg iman nnwen Irra yawen tiyugiwin; si lmal nnwen, tiyugiwin. Isfukti kwen yisent. Ur illi wayen i T icban. Neppa Issel, Ipwali.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 484,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4284,
            "text": "IneS tisura n tmurt akked igenwan. Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, Iwezzen. Ih, Neppa Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 484,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 193,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4285,
            "text": "Issers awen d, di ddin, ayen ief Iweûûa Nuê. Ayen i k Nweêêa, d ayen ief Nweûûa Ibôahim, Musa, akked Âisa: 'sbeddet ddin, ur ppemgarradet fellas'. èÈÈéay, i imcurak, wayen uuô la ten tneccdev. Öebbi Ippawi uôeS, win i S ihwan; Inehhu uôeS, win isteôoiâen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 484,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4286,
            "text": "Ur mfaôaqen armi ten id tusa tussna. Ppemvuddun. Lemmer ur d izwar wawal suô Mass ik ef lmijal ipwassnen, yili myefran. Ih, wid iweôten Tazmamt deffir sen, haaten, fellas, di ccekk imcebbwel.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 484,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4287,
            "text": "Ilmend n waya, enced, ssewqem akken i tepwamôev, ur teddu d cchawi nnsen. Ini: 'umne s wayen id Issader Öebbi n Tira. Pwamôe d ad wezne garawen. Öebbi d Mass nne, u d Mass nnwen. I nekwni igiten nne, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Ur teppili nnmara garane. Öebbi ad a Issemlil. Tualin uôeS'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 484,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4288,
            "text": "Wid ipnamaren af Öebbi, deffir wagwav n loawab uôsen, ur teswi nnmara nnsen, ar Mass nnsen. Fellasen zzâaf, fellasen aâaqeb uqsiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 485,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4289,
            "text": "Öebbi id Issadren Tazmamt, s tidep, akked lmizan. W ad ak imlen, ahat imir iqeôb ed?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 485,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4290,
            "text": "Ëaren uôes wid ur numin ara yis. Ma d wid iumnen, ugaden t; éôan ar neppa d tidep. Ih, wid icukken deg imir, haaten, war ccekk, di ttelfan umiq.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 485,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4291,
            "text": "Öebbi d Laîif i imdanen iS. Ipiti win i S ihwan. Neppa d Uohid, d Uzmir.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 485,
            "ruku": 420,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4292,
            "text": "Win iban tayerza n laxeôt, ad as Nernu di tyerza ines. Win iban tayerza n ddunit, ad as Nefk segs. Ur as illi umur di laxeôt.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 485,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4293,
            "text": "Ne sâan icriken, sseôen ten di ddin ur Iqbil Öebbi? Lemmer ur d izwir ara wawal n ufraz, a p fru garasen. I imednas, war ccekk, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 485,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4294,
            "text": "A pwaliv imednas feqâen ilmend n wayen kesben, u neppa iddehm ed fellasen. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad ilin di tebêirin n leonanat. Nnsen i sen ihwan uô Mass nnsen. D wagi ay d lfevl ameqwôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 485,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4295,
            "text": "D wagi is Ipbecciô Öebbi imdanen iS, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ini: 'ur awen ssutre taqdiât, af waya, siwa lmaênana i llezm nnwen'. Win ixedmen ise, ad as Nernu degs lehhu. Öebbi, ih, Ipsemmiê, Ippara tajmilt.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4296,
            "text": "Ne a d inin: 'isnulfa d tikerkas af Öebbi'. Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, ad Icemmaâ ul ik. S wawal iS, ad Isqucc Öebbi tikerkas, ad Iêeqqeq tidep. Ih, Neppa Iéôa tababnit n idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4297,
            "text": "D Neppa i Iqeblen nndama n yimdanen iS. Ipsemmiê tucmitin. Issen ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4298,
            "text": "Issemêas i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb uqsiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 194,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4299,
            "text": "Ma Issuget Öebbi lit i imdanen iS, ad bewven di tmurt. Maca, Issrusu d, s lmizan, ayen i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa Ippuxebbeô ef imdanen iS, Ipwali ten.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4300,
            "text": "D Neppa id Isselayen ageffur mara aysen. Iweppaâ aêunu S. Neppa d Bab, d Amaâzuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4301,
            "text": "Seg issekniyen iS, lxelq n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan n lewêuc, degsen. Izmer Neppa, ma ihwa yaS, a ten id Issemlil.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 421,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4302,
            "text": "Kra n tiyta ikwen iwwten, siwa ayen d bbwin ifassen nnwen. Aîas i Ipsemmiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4303,
            "text": "Ur tezmirem a ppesfunngem di tmurt. Ur awen illi, war Öebbi, bab ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 486,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4304,
            "text": "Seg issekniyen iS, ssfinat di yill, amzun d idurar.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4305,
            "text": "Ma ihwa yaS ad Issens avu, ad êebsent, d tusbivin sufella s. War ccekk, ayagi d issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4306,
            "text": "Ne a ten Issenger ilmend n wayen kesben. Aîas i Ipsemmiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4307,
            "text": "Ad éôen wid ipnamaren ef issekniyen nne£, ar ur asen illi ssôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4308,
            "text": "Ayen akw i wen ippunefken n wayla, d zzhu n tmeddurt di ddunit. Ayen illan ar Öebbi, yif it; ad idum kteô, i wid iumnen, ippeklen ef Mass nnsen;",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4309,
            "text": "wid ijunben ibekkaven ibararen, akked lâaô, u ssurufen i wid i ten isserfan;",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4310,
            "text": "wid id ipjawaben i Mass nnsen, péallan, ppemcawaôen ef lameô nnsen, pseddiqen seg wayen iten Nat;",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4311,
            "text": "wid, ma iusa ten lbewv, ad qablen.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4312,
            "text": "Aqeîîi n tucmip, d tucmip i p icban. Win isemmêen, issweqmen, arraz is ar Öebbi. Neppa, ih, ur Iêemmel ara imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4313,
            "text": "Ma d wid id irran ppaô mi pwadensen, ur telli tiyta degsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4314,
            "text": "Tiyta, kan, deg wid ivuôôen imdanen, iqehôen di tmurt, war ssebba. I wigi, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4315,
            "text": "Ma d win iûebôen, isemmêen, ayagi, s tidep, d aseyyi n lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 422,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4316,
            "text": "Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi bab, deffir eS. A pwaliv imednas, mara éôen aâaqeb, ad inin: 'ma illa ubrid n tualin'?",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 487,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4317,
            "text": "A ten twaliv pwafessren fellas, ndellen, ggaren tiî s tugwdi. Ad inin wid iumnen: 'imexsuôen, s tidep, d wid i sxesôen iman nnsen, akked twacult nnsen, ass n tnekra'. War ccekk, deg uâaqeb imezgi, ara yilin imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 488,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4318,
            "text": "Ur asen llin imawlan, ara ten isellken, war Öebbi. Win Itlef Öebbi, ur isâi abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 488,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4319,
            "text": "Jawbet i Mass nnwen, uqbel a d ias, suô Öebbi, ass ur nepwexxiô. Ur awen ippili ssôan assen, ur tezmirem a pnekôem.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 488,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4320,
            "text": "Ma numren, ur k id Nuzen ara d amêareb nnsen. Ay fellak, siwa timenna. Ih, mara Nesêess i umdan aêunu suône£, ad ifôeê yis. Mara t tsami tucmip, id bbwin ifassen is, s tidep, amdan ad ikaraâ.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 488,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4321,
            "text": "N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Ippak nnta i win i S ihwan, Ippak ddkeô i win i S ihwan.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 488,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4322,
            "text": "Ne Ipcarak ddkeô d nnta. Isaâqaô win i S ihwan. Ih, Neppa Issen, Izmer.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 488,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 195,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4323,
            "text": "Ur ippunefk ara i umdan, ad as Immeslay Öebbi, siwa aweêêi, ne deffir ucembir, ne a d iazen amazan iwumi ara Iweêêi, s tsriê iS, ayen Iba. Ih, Neppa d Aâlayen, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 488,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 196,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4324,
            "text": "Akka ik d Nweêêa ôôuê, si lameô nne£; ur telliv d win issnen d acu p Tezmamt, ne liman. Maca, nerra p d tafat. Yis Nenehhu win i £ ihwan, seg imdanen nne£. Ih, d Keçç i ippawin d ubrid uwqim;",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 489,
            "ruku": 423,
            "hizbQuarter": 196,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4325,
            "text": "abrid n Öebbi, i Isâan i illan di tmurt, i illan deg igenwan. War ccekk, ar Öebbi ay teddun lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 25,
