            "hizbQuarter": 196,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4338,
            "text": "A pâanncem ef iârar nnsen; sinna, a d tesmektim lit n Mass nnwen, mara pâanncem fellasen. A ppinim: 'gedha s Win i d Inuben fella s waya, ur t nemlik!",
