            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 490,
            "ruku": 425,
            "hizbQuarter": 196,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4342,
            "text": "Ma ibbwev ed usali yiwen segsen, ef wayen id ifka d amedya i Uênin, ad yibrik wudem is, ad ikkufer:",
