            "page": 491,
            "ruku": 425,
            "hizbQuarter": 197,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4351,
            "text": "Mi inna Ibôahim i baba s, akked ugdud is: 'nek, ur pkka deg wayen la tâabdem,",
