            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 491,
            "ruku": 426,
            "hizbQuarter": 197,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4357,
            "text": "Day d nitni i ifeôôqen aêunu n Mass ik? D Nekwni i sen Ifeôôqen tamâict nnsen, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u Nessuli kra segsen, tidekkaôin sennig wiyav, iwakken kra, ad sxedmen wiyav. Aêunu n Mass ik yif ayen jemâan.",
