            "page": 492,
            "ruku": 427,
            "hizbQuarter": 197,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4363,
            "text": "Alamma ma iusa d uône£, inna d: 'ah, awufan gari yidek, amecwaô illan ger ugmuv d wayev'. A yir amsaâef!",
