            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 498,
            "ruku": 433,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4470,
            "text": "Ur pjeôôiben, dinna, tameppant, siwa tameppant tamezwarut. Isellek iten seg uâaqeb ujajiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 498,
            "ruku": 433,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4471,
            "text": "D lfevl n Mass ik, d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 498,
            "ruku": 433,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4472,
            "text": "Nsehhel it kan, s tmeslayt ik, amendeô ma a d mmektin.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 498,
            "ruku": 433,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4473,
            "text": "Ggani, ula d nitni la pganin.",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 498,
            "ruku": 433,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 45,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الجَاثِيَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Jaathiya",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Crouching",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4474,
            "text": "Ëm.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4475,
            "text": "Tarusi n Tezmamt suô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4476,
            "text": "Di tmurt akked igenwan, s tidep, llan issekniyen i lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4477,
            "text": "Di lxelq nnwen, akked wayen id Issefôuôex n lewêuc, d issekniyen i ugdud ipputebbten.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4478,
            "text": "Di lemgarda n yiv akked wass, akked wayen id Issrusu Öebbi n ôôeéq, seg igenni - Issidir yis tamurt, deffir tmeppant is -, deg udewwel n wavu, issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4479,
            "text": "D wigi ay d issekniyen n Öebbi; Nemmal ak ten, s tidep. Anwa ameslay ara amnen, deffir Öebbi akked issekniyen iS?",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4480,
            "text": "A ssxev n yal akeddab amednub!",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4481,
            "text": "Issemêas i issekniyen n Öebbi, qqaôen as ten, sinna, iggernen di temweô, amzun ur asen isli. Ihi, becceô it s uâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4482,
            "text": "Ma illa wayen iwumi isla, seg issekniyen nne£, ad ittihi fellas. I widak, aâaqeb isdullun.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4483,
            "text": "Deffir sen Loahennama. Ur ten iennu s wacemma wayen kesben akked wayen rran d imawlan, war Öebbi. I nitni, aâaqeb abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4484,
            "text": "Tagi d nnhaya. Wid iugin issekniyen n Mass nnsen, fellasen aâaqeb n daâwessu taqeôêant.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 434,
            "hizbQuarter": 199,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4485,
            "text": "Öebbi i Inuben fellawen s yill; ipcali, fellas, lbabuô, s lameô iS; a pnadim lit iS. Amar a ppesnemrem!",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4486,
            "text": "Inub fellawen s wayen akw illan deg igenwan, akked wayen illan di tmurt. Akw suôeS. S tidep, deg waya, d issekniyen i ugdud ismektayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 499,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4487,
            "text": "Ini i wid iumnen ad semmêen i wid ur negguni ara ussan n Öebbi, iwakken ad Ikafi agdud ef wayen keppben.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4488,
            "text": "Win ixedmen ayen ilhan, i iman is; win ifalîan, mgal is. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen tualin nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4489,
            "text": "Ni Nefka, i At Isôail, Tazmamt, ûûwab, lambiyya. Nôeéq iten s wayen ilhan. Nesmenyaf iten i imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4490,
            "text": "Nefka yasen abeggen si Lameô. Ur mgarraden, armi i ten id tusa tmusni, wa iqheô wa. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, ef wayen ief mgarraden.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4491,
            "text": "Sinna, Nebbwi k deg ubrid n Lameô. Ddu degs, ur teddu akked chawi n wid ur nessin.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4492,
            "text": "Ih, nitni ur ak d ppawin acemma suô Öebbi. Imednas, ih, d imawlan wa n wa. Öebbi d Bab n wid ipêezziben.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4493,
            "text": "Ayagi d assekni i laci, d nnhaya u d aêunu i ugdud ipputebbten.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4494,
            "text": "Ne ilen wid imôôeôen iman nnsen s tucmitin, a ten Neêseb am wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d imuddiren ne d lmeggtin. Dir it uêuddu nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 435,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4495,
            "text": "Öebbi Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep, iwakken yal amdan ad ippuqeîîi af wayen ikseb. Nitni ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 500,
            "ruku": 436,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4496,
            "text": "Twalav win irran lhawiyya s d ôebbi is? Itelf it Öebbi, asali uôeS. Iskweô as ul, timejjin, Irra yas aâbôuq af allen is. Anwa ara t inhun, deffir Öebbi? Day u la tesmektayem ara?",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 436,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4497,
            "text": "Nnan: 'i illan kan, d tudert nne, di ddunit. A nemmet, a nidir. Ad a inen kan d akud'. £ef ayagi, ur sâin kra n tmusni. Nitni ilen kan.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 436,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4498,
            "text": "Ma mlan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, anamer nnsen, siwa mara d inin: 'erret ed imezwura nne, ma tessawalem tidep'!",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 436,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4499,
            "text": "Ini: 'Öebbi Issidir ikwen, sinna, Ineqq ikwen. Sinna a kwen Issemlil ass n tnekra, ur illi degs ccekk'. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 436,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4500,
            "text": "N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ass ideg ara d ias yimir, ass nni, ad xesôen ucmiten.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4501,
            "text": "A pwaliv yal lois ef tgwecrar, yal lois ipwanced ar tezmamt is. Assa, a peltem ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4502,
            "text": "Tagi d tazmamt nne£, tessawal tidep fellawen. Nella Nepjerrid ayen akw txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4503,
            "text": "Ihi, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Issekcem, Mass nnsen, s aêunu S. Wagi d rrbeê n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4504,
            "text": "Wanag wid ijehlen: 'day ur awen ôan ara issekniyen iW? Tesmewôem iman nnwen, tellam d agdud ibewviyen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4505,
            "text": "Mi nnan: 'ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep; imir, ur degs ccekk', tennam: 'ur neéôi d acu ay d imir; uône d nnwaya kan, ur nepputebbet'.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 501,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4506,
            "text": "Ad asen d vehôent tucmitin xedmen, ad asen izzi wayen ief ttihin.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4507,
            "text": "Ad asen Inin: 'assa, a kwen Neppu, akken teppum timlilit n wass nnwen agi. Axxam nnwen d times, ur awen illi useîîaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4508,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku kunwi la tettihim ef issekniyen n Öebbi. Tuôô ikwen tudert n ddunit. Assa, ur d teffen segs'. Ur istifiô êedd fellasen.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4509,
            "text": "I Öebbi annuz, Mass igenwan, Mass n tmurt, Mass imavalen.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4510,
            "text": "I Neppa akw ayen iufraren, di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 25,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 437,
            "hizbQuarter": 200,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 46,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الأَحۡقَافِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Ahqaf",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Dunes",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4511,
            "text": "Ëm.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4512,
            "text": "Tarusi n Tezmamt suô Öebbi, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4513,
            "text": "Ur Nexliq tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep, ar lajel ipwassnen. Wid ijehlen numren ayen uuô pwanedôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4514,
            "text": "Ini: 'day ur twalam ara wigi uuô la tepnujum, war Öebbi? Sseknet iyi d, d acu xelqen si tmurt, ne ma sâan amur deg igenwan? Awit iyi d tazmamt id izwaren tagi, ne lateô n tmusni, ma tessawalem tidep'.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4515,
            "text": "Anwa innetlafen sennig wid ipnujun, war Öebbi, eô wayen ur asen d nepparra, ar ass n tnekra, u nitni stehzan deg unuju nnsen?",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 502,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4516,
            "text": "Mara twafesrem imdanen, ad ilin d icenga nnsen, ad skiddben aâbad nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4517,
            "text": "Ma ôan asen issekniyen nne£ iberrzen, wid iugin tidep, mi ten id tusa, ad inin: 'wagi d ssêur n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4518,
            "text": "Ne ad inin: 'isnulfa t id'. Ini: 'lemmer it id snulfa, ur tezmirem ad iyi tsellkem, s wacemma, si Öebbi. Neppa, Yif akw akken Issen, acu têekkum fellas. Iqadd Neppa d Anagi gari yidwen. Neppa, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4519,
            "text": "Ini: 'ur lli, ger imazanen, d win id isnulfuyen. Ur éôi acu ara ivôun yidi, ne yidwen. La îîafaôe, kan, ayen iyi d ippuweêêan. Aql i, kan, nek, d aneddaô ipbegginen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4520,
            "text": "Ini: 'meyyzet ma, ayagi, suô Öebbi, u tnekôem t? Icehhed unagi n At Isôail, ef lmetl is, da iumen. Tesmewrem iman nnwen'. Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 438,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4521,
            "text": "Nnan wid ijehlen, i wid iumnen: 'lemmer d ayen ilhan, ur a zeggwiren uôes'. Imi ur pwanhan ara syis, qqaôen: 'ayagi d tikerkas n zik'.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4522,
            "text": "Uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Tagi d Tazmamt itebbiten, s wawalen n taâôabt, a ppendeô wid idensen, a ppessefôeê lâuûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4523,
            "text": "Ih, wid iqqaôen: 'Mass nne d Öebbi, da îfen degs, ur ppagaden, ur weblen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4524,
            "text": "Widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen, d arraz n wayen xeddmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 503,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4525,
            "text": "Nweûûa amdan ar lewqama s imawlan is. Imma s temêen s tadist, temêen di tinnufra. Ger tadist akked ujumi, caret wagguren. Armi ibbwev d anqaqôi, issawev kuéet isegwasen, inna: 'a Mass iw! Eoo iyi a K snemmre af lit i  Tatev, nek akked lwaldin iw; ad xedme ayen ilhan ara K iôavin. Efk iyi d tarwa ilhan. Aql i utube K, aql i seg imvuâen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 504,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4526,
            "text": "£uô wigi, Nqebbel lmefruz igiten nnsen, a Nessuref i tucmitin nnsen, ger at Loennet; d lemâahda n tidep, i sen ippuwaââden.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 504,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4527,
            "text": "Win innan i imawlan is: 'tfuh nnwen! Day yi tâahdem a d kkre? Ni âaddan isuta uqbel i'. Nitni teppren tacvaî n Öebbi: 'a ssexv ik, amen! Ih, lmâahda n Öebbi, d tidep'. A d yini: 'ayagi, siwa tiêkayin imezwura'.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 504,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4528,
            "text": "D wigi ief iûaô wawal iaânan leoyus n leonun akked yimdanen, i ten id izwaren. Ih, nitni d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 504,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4529,
            "text": "I akw tiseddarin n wayen xedmen, iwakken ad yili warraz igiten nnsen. Nitni ur pwadensen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 504,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4530,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara kecmen ar tmes, wid ijehlen: 'tvegâam tiéidanin i s tezham, di tmeddurt nnwen di ddunit. Assa, a ppeppuqeîîim s uâaqeb isdullun, imi tessemwaôem iman nnwen di tmurt, ur teklalem; imi tellam tbewlem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 504,
            "ruku": 439,
            "hizbQuarter": 201,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4531,
            "text": "Mmekti d agmat n Âad, mi indeô agdud is deg igidan, u, s tidep, âaddan d ineddaôen zdat es, u zdeffir es: 'siwa Öebbi ara tâabdem. Nek ugade, fellawen, aâaqeb n wass abarar'.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 440,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4532,
            "text": "Nnan d: 'day a d tusiv, ad a tfaôqev akked iôebbiten nne? Awi a d ayen ief la  tessagwadev, ma tessawalev tidep'!",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 440,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4533,
            "text": "Inna: 'tamusni ar Öebbi kan. Ssawve awen ayen ief id ppuceggâa. Maca, wala kwen d agdud ur nessin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 440,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4534,
            "text": "Mi t walan d asigna id ileêêun ar twezza nnsen, nnan: 'wagi d asigna ar a d iawin ageffur'. Xaîi! D ayen ief têarem, d avu, degs aâaqeb aqeôêan;",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 440,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4535,
            "text": "ad isqucc yal cci, s lameô n Mass is. Gwran d ur tepwaliv siwa ixxamen nnsen. Akka i Nepqeîîi igduden ibewviyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 440,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4536,
            "text": "Ni Nessakrer asen ayen ur awen Nessakrer. Nefka yasen imeééuen, allen, akked wulawen. Ula i sen d bbwin deg wacemma imeééuen, allen, akked wulawen, mi skaddben issekniyen n Öebbi. Ayen ief ttihin, izzi d fellasen.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 440,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4537,
            "text": "Ni nessenger akw timdinin i wen d izzin, u Nenewwel asent issekniyen, amar a d ualent s abrid.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4538,
            "text": "Acimi ur ten sellken ara wid rran d iôebbiten iééaéan, war Öebbi? Xaîi! Ooan ten. D ayagi ay d tikerkas nnsen, u d wayen id snulfuyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 505,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4539,
            "text": "Mi k ed Nebbwi agraw n leonun, ad ssemêessen i Leqwôan; mi s êedôen, nnan: 'êesset'! Mi ifukk, ualen s agdud nnsen d ineddaôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 506,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4540,
            "text": "Nnan: 'a yagdud nne, aql a nesla i Tezmamt id irsen, deffir Musa, id itebbten ayen ip id izwaren, i inehhun ar tidep akked ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 506,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4541,
            "text": "A yagdud nne, erret awal i uberraê n Öebbi, amnet yiS, ad awen Isemmeê seg ibekkaven nnwen, a kwen Isellek seg uâaqeb aqeôêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 506,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4542,
            "text": "Win isâaweégen i uberraê n Öebbi, ur ipsellik di tmurt, ur ippaf imawlan, war Neppa. Widak di ttelfan n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 506,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4543,
            "text": "Day ur walan ara ar Öebbi d Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, ur Ifcil seg uxlaq nnsen? Izmer a d Issider lmeggtin. Ih, Neppa Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 506,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4544,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara d rsen, ar tmes, wid ijehlen: 'maççi s tidep ayagi'? A d inin: 'ih, s Mass nne'! A d Yini: 'jeôôbet aâaqeb ef wayen la tnekôem'!",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 506,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4545,
            "text": "Eûbeô akken ûebôen wid iôeûmen seg imazanen. I nitni, ur pawal. Ass ideg ara walin acu i sen ippuwaââden, amzun ur kminen siwa saâa n wass. D aberreê: 'anwa ara ipwakksen, siwa agdud icemten'?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 506,
            "ruku": 441,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 47,
        "name": "سُورَةُ مُحَمَّدٍ",
        "englishName": "Muhammad",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Muhammad",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4546,
            "text": "Wid ijehlen, u ssefôaen abrid n Öebbi, Itlef igiten nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4547,
            "text": "Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, umnen s wayen id irsen ar Muêemmed, u neppa d tidep suô Mass nnsen; Issemsa yasen tucmitin nnsen, Iûeggem asen lêala nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4548,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku wid ijehlen îîafaôen tikerkas; ma d wid iumnen, îîafaôen tidep n Mass nnsen. Akka id Ippak Öebbi imedyaten nnsen i imdanen.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4549,
            "text": "Mara d temlilem akked wid ijehlen, ewwtet ar tmegrav ar ten telbem. Arzet pen nezzeh. Sinna, d aserreê ne d feddu, alamma isers îôad tiâekkwmin is. Akka, lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, yili Ileb iten, maca a kwen Ijeôôeb, kra s kra. Wid ipwanan deg ubrid n Öebbi, ur pôuêun igiten nnsen, d awezi.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4550,
            "text": "A ten Inhu, ad Iûeggem lêala nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4551,
            "text": "A ten Issekcem di Loennet i sen Imla.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4552,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma tefkam afus i Öebbi, ad awen Ifk afus, ad awen itebbet isurifen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4553,
            "text": "Wid ijehlen, ay amxix nnsen, ad weddôen igiten nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4554,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku ugwin ayen id Issers Öebbi; ihi, Imêa igiten nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 202,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4555,
            "text": "Aâni ur nudan ara tamurt, ad walin amek tevôa d imezwura nnsen? Issexv iten Öebbi. Am akka i ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4556,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku Öebbi d bab n wid iumnen. Ijehliyen, ur asen illi bab.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 507,
            "ruku": 442,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4557,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi ad Issekcem wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Wid ijehlen zehhun, teppen akken itepp lmal. D times ay d leqôaô nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4558,
            "text": "Acêal n at temdinin i yifen, di tezmert, tamdint i k id iéâan! Nesqucc iten, ur asen illi useîîaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4559,
            "text": "Day win illan ar ubeggen n Mass is, am win, iwumi ppucebbêen yir igiten is, u iîîafaôen chawi nnsen?",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4560,
            "text": "Amek tga Loennet i ippuwaââden i wid ipêezziben: degs isaffen n waman ur nxeppeô, isaffen n yii ur tfessed lbenna s, isaffen n ccôab aéidan i wid itessen, isaffen n tament ippuneqqan. Degs, i nitni, yal ppemôa, akked ssmaê n Mass nnsen. Day am wid iwekkôen di tmes; sswan ten s waman ippayzagen, ara icergen afwad nnsen?",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4561,
            "text": "Llan garasen wid i k issemêasen. Sifat ffen d suôek, ad inin i wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni: 'd acu id inna kan, llinna'? Wigi d wid iwumi Isle Öebbi ulawen, teddun kan d chawi nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4562,
            "text": "Wid ipwanhan, Irna asen nnhaya, Ifka yasen aêezzeb nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4563,
            "text": "Day la pôaoun kan imir, a ten id ias, deqzalla? Ni usant ed licaôat is. Ma iusa d uôsen, iwumi t usmekti nnsen?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4564,
            "text": "Cfu ar, s tidep, ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi; ssuter ssmaê ubekkav ik, akked wid n lmumnin, argaz tameîîut. Öebbi Iéôa anda têebkem, akked wanda tberrkem.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 508,
            "ruku": 443,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4565,
            "text": "La qqaôen wid iumnen: 'a lemmer a d ters tsuôep'! Maca, mi d ters tsuôep tuêkimt, ideg id ipwader umennu, a pwaliv at wul iblan, la k id pmuqulen s tiî n win tessexcawat tmeppant. Yif it i nitni",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4566,
            "text": "wannuz, akked wawal uwqim. Mi ipwagzem ôôay, ma ssawlen tidep ar Öebbi yif it i nitni.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4567,
            "text": "Day maççi, ma twexxôem, ahat a ppesfesdem tamurt, a pfaôqem alag nnwen?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4568,
            "text": "Wigi d wid i Ixza Öebbi; Isgugem iten, Isderel iéôi nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4569,
            "text": "Day ur pmeyyizen ara Leqwôan, ne ualent tsergal ef wulawen?",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4570,
            "text": "Ih, wid ixedâan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya uôsen, ikellex iten Cciîan. Iooa ten tallit.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4571,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku nitni nnan i wid iugin ayen d Issader Öebbi: 'ad awen na awal di kra n lumuô'. Öebbi Iéôa lesrar nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4572,
            "text": "Amek ihi, ma ddment lmalayek leôwaê nnsen, la ten kkatent ar udmawen nnsen, iârar nnsen?",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4573,
            "text": "Akka, ihi, ddan akked wayen isserfayen Öebbi. Ugin llza S. Da Isseôxes igiten nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 444,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4574,
            "text": "Ne ilen at wul amehzul, ard awezi, ur d Issuffu ara Öebbi lebwev nnsen?",
