            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 509,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4575,
            "text": "Lemmer i £ ihwi, ad ak ten id Nessken, war ccekk, a ten tâaqlev ar udem nnsen, a ten tâaqlev ar ûûenf umeslay. Öebbi Issen igiten nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 510,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4576,
            "text": "S tidep, a kwen Njeôôeb, alamma Nessen imjuhad, akked iûebôiyen, segwen. A Njeôôeb isallen nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 510,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4577,
            "text": "Ih, wid ijehlen, issefôaen abrid n Öebbi, i inuqmen Amazan, deffir ubeggen n nnhaya uôsen, ur vuôôen Öebbi s wacemma. Ad Isseôxes igiten nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 510,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 203,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4578,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Aet awal i Öebbi, aet awal i Umazan, ur ssiôxiset igiten nnwen!",
