          },
          {
            "number": 4580,
            "text": "Ur ppiôhifet, ur ssuturet tifrat, mara tilim d inelaben! U Öebbi yidwen, ur kwen Ipêewwio, d awezi, seg igiten nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 510,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4581,
            "text": "Tameddurt di ddunit, d urar kan, akked lhawiyya. Ma tumnem u têezbem, ad awen d Ifk arrazen nnwen. Ur awen issutur ayla nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 510,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4582,
            "text": "Ma Issuter awen t, a kwen Icebbwel, a pcuêêem, a d iffe lebwev nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 510,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4583,
            "text": "D kunwi i ipwanecden a pseddqem deg ubrid n Öebbi. Llan degwen wid ipcuêêun. Win ipcuêêun, ipcuêêu kan ef yiman is. Öebbi d Asâay, kunwi d igellilen. Ma twexxôem, a kwen Ineûûef s ugdud ur nelli segwen. Da ur ppemcabin uôwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 510,
            "ruku": 445,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 48,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الفَتۡحِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Fath",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Victory",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4584,
            "text": "Ih, Nefya yak lelb iberrzen,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4585,
            "text": "iwakken ad Isemmeê Öebbi ibekkaven ik id izwaren akked wid igwran. Ad ak Itim lit iS, a k Iawi d ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4586,
            "text": "A k Iall Öebbi tallalt tuzmirt.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4587,
            "text": "D Neppa id Issersen talwit deg ulawen n lmumnin, iwakken ad yimuô liman nnsen. N Öebbi Iâsekôiwen n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izga Iééeô, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4588,
            "text": "Iwakken ad Issekcem wid akked tid iumnen, ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. Ad asen Issemsu tucmitin nnsen. D wagi, ar Öebbi, ay d rrbeê abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4589,
            "text": "Ad Iâaqeb ixabiten, tixabitin, imcurak, timcurak, wid id ipfekkiôen Öebbi yir afekkeô. Izzi yasen ddens. Irfa Öebbi fellasen, Ixza ten. Ihegga yasen d Loahennama. A tualin tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4590,
            "text": "N Öebbi iâsekôiwen n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4591,
            "text": "Ih, Nuzen ik id d anagi, d abcir, d aneddaô,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4592,
            "text": "iwakken a ppamnem s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, a T kfum, ad aS tanzem, a T tesbuccuâem taûebêit, tameddit.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 511,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4593,
            "text": "Wid iâaqden yidek âaqden kan d Öebbi. Afus n Öebbi nnig ufus nnsen. Win iêenten, d imanis kan i isseênet. Win iîîfen deg wayen ief iâuhed Öebbi, ad as Ifk arraz abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 512,
            "ruku": 446,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4594,
            "text": "Ad ak inin wid igwran, seg uâôaben n ucluê: 'i  icewlen, d ayla nne akked twaculin nne. Ssuter a neppusemmeê'. Qqaôen s yilsawen nnsen, ayen ur nelli deg ulawen nnsen. Ini: 'anwa ara kwen iselken si Öebbi, s wacemma, ma Iba yawen vveôô, ne ma Iba yawen abauô? Xaîi, Izga Öebbi Ippuxebbeô af wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 512,
            "ruku": 447,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4595,
            "text": "Xaîi, tilem Amazan akked lmumnin ur d ppualen ara, d awezi, ar twaculin nnsen. Ayagi, issefôeê ulawen nnwen. Nnwaya nnwen dir ip. Kunwi d agdud imsenger.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 512,
            "ruku": 447,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4596,
            "text": "Wid ur numin s Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, ihi, aql a£ Nhegga d ajajiê i ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 512,
            "ruku": 447,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4597,
            "text": "N Öebbi, tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ipsemmiê i win i S ihwan, Ipâuqub win i S ihwan. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 512,
            "ruku": 447,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4598,
            "text": "A d inin wid igwran: 'ma tôuêem a d teltem, ooet a a neddu yidwen'. Ban ad bedlen awalen n Öebbi. Ini: 'ur teppeddum yidne, d awezi. Akka ay d izwar wawal n Öebbi'. A d inin: 'teêsedm a'! Xaîi, cwiî kan ay fehhmen.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 512,
            "ruku": 447,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4599,
            "text": "Ini i wid igwran, seg uâôaben n ucluê: 'a ppepwanecdem s agdud amaâwaôu, uqsiê; a t tennaem, ne ad anzen. Ma tuem awal, ad awen Ifk Öebbi arraz igerzen. Ma twexxôem, akken twexxôem uqbel, a kwen Iâaqeb s lqeôê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 447,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4600,
            "text": "Ur telli tiyta deg uderal, ne deg urejdal, ne deg umuvin. Win iunzen i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, a t Issekcem di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Win iwexxôen, a t Iâaqeb s lqeôê.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 447,
            "hizbQuarter": 204,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4601,
            "text": "Ni Iôuva Öebbi lmumnin, mi âaqden yidek, seddaw ttejôa. Iéôa i illan deg ulawen nnsen, Issers d fellasen talwit, Ina ten s lelb aqôib,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4602,
            "text": "akked waîas n lerbaê, ara îîfen. Öebbi Izga d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4603,
            "text": "Iwaââed awen Öebbi a d teîîfem lerbaê aîas. Iawel awen d deg waya. Ikkes fellawen afus n medden. Akken ad yili ussekni i lmumnin, a kwen iawi d ubrid uwqim.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4604,
            "text": "Tayev, iwumi ur tezmirem, ihi, Izzi as Öebbi. Öebbi Izga Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4605,
            "text": "Lemmer i kwen nnuen wid ijehlen, ad rewlen, sinna, ur ppafen bab, ne asettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4606,
            "text": "D tannumi n Öebbi i illan si zik. Ur teppafev abeddel, d awezi, di tannumi n Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 513,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4607,
            "text": "D Neppa i Ikksen afus nnsen segwen, akked ufus nnwen segsen, di tezut n Mekka, siwev Isselb ikwen fellasen. Öebbi Izga Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 514,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4608,
            "text": "D nitni i ijehlen. Swexxôen kwen si Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ugin ad iawev usfel s amkan is. Lemmer maççi d lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, ur ten tessinem, a ten têazem ur teéôim; segsen a d tegwrim di leôuô - ni Öebbi Issekcam s aêunu S, win i S ihwan - lemmer mfaôaqen, yili, war ccekk, Nesâadda, ef wid segsen ijehlen, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 514,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4609,
            "text": "Mi rran wid ijehlen, aêernun deg ulawen nnsen, aêernun n war tussna, Issers ed Öebbi talwit iS af Umazan iS, akked lmumnin. Iqqen asen awal uêezzeb. Iwata ten, klalen t. Öebbi Izga Iéôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 514,
            "ruku": 448,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4610,
            "text": "Ni Issawev Öebbi, i Umazan iS, tamuli s tidep: war ccekk, a pkecmem Loamaâ n Lêaôam, ma Irad Öebbi, di laman, iqweôôa nnwen ûûeîlen u qeôcen, ur teppagwadem. Iéôa ayen ur teéôim. Ihegga yawen d, ugwar aya, lelb aqôib.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 514,
            "ruku": 449,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4611,
            "text": "Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS s nnhaya, akked ddin n tidep, iwakken a t Issifrer ef ddin meôôa. Iqadd Öebbi d Anagi.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 514,
            "ruku": 449,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4612,
            "text": "Muêemmed d Amazan n Öebbi. Wid illan yides, qesêen ar ijehliyen, êninit garasen. A ten twaliv îîinizen, kennun, ssuturen lfevl suô Öebbi akked llza. Ccama nnsen, deg udmawen nnsen, d lateô n lekni. Ata wayen i ten icban di Tuôa akked wayen i ten icban di Linoil: am uâaqqa, iger ed imi s, isoehd it. Ad iuzur, ad iâaooeô ef yile is. Ippaâoab ifellaêen; iwebben yissen ijehliyen. Iwaââed Öebbi ssmaê akked warraz abarar, i wid degsen iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 515,
            "ruku": 449,
            "hizbQuarter": 205,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 49,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الحُجُرَاتِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Hujuraat",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Inner Apartments",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4613,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur zeggwiret zdat Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 515,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4614,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur zzuhriyet tuac nnwen, sennig tawect n Nnbi. Ur zaââvet uôes, akken tepzaââvam garawen, mulac ad mêun igiten nnwen, kunwi ur tfaqem.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 515,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4615,
            "text": "Ih, wid issrusun ûut n tawect nnsen, ar Umazan n Öebbi, d wid iwumi Issefsi Öebbi ulawen nnsen, ar uêezzeb. Ad asen ippunefk ssmaê akked warraz abarar.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 515,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4616,
            "text": "Ih, tegwti n wid ik n issawlen, deffir texxamin, ur pmeyyizen.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 515,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4617,
            "text": "Lemmer ûbiôen ard teffev uôsen, ppif i nitni. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 516,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4618,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Aballa ma ibbwi yawen d asali, ppuêeqqeqet, mulac a pvuôôem agdud, war tamusni, a ppualem tnedmem deg wayen txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 516,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4619,
            "text": "Cfut illa garawen Umazan n Öebbi. Ma issemêes awen deg waîas n lumuô, a pjafem. Maca, Öebbi Issaâzez awen liman, Imelleê it deg ulawen nnwen, Isseôéeg awen tijehli, ddel, lmaâûegga. Widak d wid ipwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 516,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4620,
            "text": "D lfevl suô Öebbi, d lit. Öebbi Iéôa, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 516,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4621,
            "text": "Ma nnuent snat n îayfat n lmumnin, êuddet pent. Ma tebwev yiwet degsent, ef tayev, nnaet tin ibweven alamma tevfeô lameô n Öebbi. Ma tevfeô it, ssemûalêet pent, s lmizan. Wezznet. Öebbi Iêemmel wid iwezznen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 516,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4622,
            "text": "Lmumnin d atmaten kan i illan. Ssemûalêet atmaten nnwen, êezzbet i Öebbi, amar fellawen aêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 516,
            "ruku": 450,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4623,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! £uôwat ad imaâlek ugdud ef wayev, ahat d widen i ten yifen. Ne tilawin ef tiyav, ahat d tiden i tent yifen. Ur pqeôôidet iman nnwen, ur pmirgamet s tselleqwbin. Dir it isem n ddel, anda illa liman. Wid ur nutub ara, d widak ay d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 516,
            "ruku": 451,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4624,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Janbet aîas n nnwaya. Ih, nnwaya, tikwal, d abekkav. Ur ppemâassat ara. Ur kkatet wa deg wa. Day ibu yiwen, degwen, ad içç aksum n gmas lmegget? A t tagwim. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 517,
            "ruku": 451,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4625,
            "text": "A yimdanen! Ni Nxelq ikwen si ddker akked nnta. Nerra kwen d igduden, d laâôac, a ppemyussanem. Ihi, ukyis nnwen amxallef, ar Öebbi, d win degwen ipêezziben sennig wiyav. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa, Ippuxebbeô.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 517,
            "ruku": 451,
            "hizbQuarter": 206,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4626,
            "text": "Nnan uâôaben n ucluê: 'numen'. Ini: 'ur tuminem'. Maca init ed: 'nunez'; ur ikcim ara liman ar wulawen nnwen. Ma tôuvam Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur awen Isôuêu acemma seg igiten nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 517,
            "ruku": 451,
            "hizbQuarter": 207,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4627,
            "text": "Lmumnin d wid kan iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, da, ur pcukun. Pnaen s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. D widak ay d imawlan n tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 517,
            "ruku": 451,
            "hizbQuarter": 207,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4628,
            "text": "Ini: 'day ad aS temlem i Öebbi, ddin nnwen'? Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Issen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 6,
            "page": 517,
            "ruku": 451,
            "hizbQuarter": 207,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4629,
            "text": "Rran ak annuz nnsen, d tajmilt. Ini: 'ur iyi telli tejmilt deg annuz nnwen. Xaîi, d Öebbi ikwen Iaten mi kwen Inha ar liman, ma d imawlan n tidep ay tellam'.",
