            "text": "Ne, ad inin: 'd amedyaz. A naôou asali s akud'.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4766,
            "text": "Ini: 'gganit! Nek, yidwen, seg wid ipganin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4767,
            "text": "Ne d tirga nnsen i sen iumôen aya, ne nitni d agdud izegren tilas.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4768,
            "text": "Ne ad inin: 'isnulfa t id'. Xaîi! Ur uminen.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4769,
            "text": "Ihi, a d awin ameslay i t icban, ma d tidep ay ssawalen!",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4770,
            "text": "Ne pwaxelqen seg ulac, ne d nitni ay d ixellaqen?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4771,
            "text": "Ne xelqen tamurt akked igenwan? Xaîi, ur pputebbten!",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4772,
            "text": "Ne uôsen lexzayen n Mass ik, ne nitni d imvebbôen?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4773,
            "text": "Ne sâan sellum ad ssemêessen, segs. Ihi, win islan segsen, a d iawi adabu n ûûeê!",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4774,
            "text": "Ne i Neppa tullas, i kunwi arrac?",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4775,
            "text": "Ne tessutrev asen taqdiât, fellasen d îîlaba ééayen?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4776,
            "text": "Ne uôsen tabavnit, da la pparun?",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4777,
            "text": "Ne ban ad andin? D wid ijehlen ara ipwaîîfen.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4778,
            "text": "Ne sâan ôebbi, ur Nelli d Öebbi? Gedha s Öebbi, seg wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4779,
            "text": "Lemmer ad walin amur igenni ili, ad as inin: 'd asigna i izdin'.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4780,
            "text": "Ihi, eoo iten, ard mlilen d wass n ssiâqa nnsen,",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4781,
            "text": "Ass, ideg ur asen d teppawi acemma, tandit nnsen; ur asen illi usettaô.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4782,
            "text": "I wid idensen, s tidep, aâaqeb nniven, maca tegwti degsen, ur éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4783,
            "text": "Eûbeô i wayen d Iêudd Mass ik, aql ak, s tidep, ger wallen nne£. Sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, mara d tekkrev.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4784,
            "text": "Sbuccaâ iT deg iv, u mara xsin yitran.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 53,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّجۡمِ",
        "englishName": "An-Najm",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Star",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4785,
            "text": "S yitri mara ixeppi!",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4786,
            "text": "Ur innetlaf, ur iliv umeddakwel nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4787,
            "text": "Ur d iqqaô akken i s ihwan.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4788,
            "text": "D aweêêi kan, id ippuweêêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4789,
            "text": "Islemd it bab n tezmert iqwan.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4790,
            "text": "D bab n tezmert irs ed",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4791,
            "text": "u neppa di lejba aâlayen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4792,
            "text": "Sinna iqeôb ed, ippucengel,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4793,
            "text": "atan tasurift n sin ixtucen, ne ur tebbwiv.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4794,
            "text": "Da iweêêa i umdan iS, ayen iweêêa.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4795,
            "text": "Ur iskaddeb wul deg wayen iwala.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4796,
            "text": "Day a t tnaqwmem, ef wayen iwala?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4797,
            "text": "Ni iéôa t di trusi s nniven,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4798,
            "text": "ar tedxwent n talast,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4799,
            "text": "uuô illa leonan usemlili.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4800,
            "text": "Mi tesbur tedxwent tawlaft,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4801,
            "text": "ur iwweônenni yiéôi, ur izgir.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4802,
            "text": "Ni iwala kra issekniyen imeqwôaêanen, n Mass is.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4803,
            "text": "Twalam Allat akked Lâuzza?",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4804,
            "text": "Akked Manat, tis krav nniven?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4805,
            "text": "Day i kunwi ddkeô, i Neppa nnta?",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4806,
            "text": "Wagi, ihi, d beîîu aneêyaf.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4807,
            "text": "Wigi d ismawen kan i sent tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur sent d Issers Öebbi kra udabu. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya, akked wayen cehwant teôwiêin. Ni tusa ten id nnhaya suô Mass nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4808,
            "text": "Aâni, i umdan, ayen issaram?",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4809,
            "text": "Tamezwarut akked tneggarut, n Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4810,
            "text": "Acêal n lmalayek deg igenwan, ur d teppawi acemma ccafuâa nnsent, siwa deffir tsriê n Öebbi, ef win Iba u Iôuva.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4811,
            "text": "Ih, wid ur numin ara di laxeôt, ppaken i lmalayek ismawen n nnta.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4812,
            "text": "Ur sâin fellas kra n tmusni. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya. Wanag nnwaya ur tebbwi acemma si tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4813,
            "text": "Ihi, eoo win iwexxôen i usmekti nne£, i iban kan tudert n ddunit.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4814,
            "text": "D aya ay sen tefka tmusni. Mass ik, war ccekk, Iéôa sennig akw, anwa innetlafen seg ubrid iS; Iéôa sennig akw, anwa i ipwanhan.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4815,
            "text": "N Öebbi ayen akw illan deg igenwan, illan di tmurt. Ad Iqeîîi wid ifalîan ef wayen xedmen, ad Ioazi wid issweqmen, s ûûam.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4816,
            "text": "Wid ijunben ibekkaven ibararen akked tucmitin, siwa lfalîat fessusen, ihi, d uwsiâ ssmaê n Mass ik. Neppa Issen ikwen sennig akw, mi kwen id Ixleq seg wakal, mi tellam d icelleqluqen, deg iâabbav n tyimmatin nnwen. Ur staâmilet tezdeg deg iman nnwen! Neppa Iéôa sennig akw, anwa iêezzben.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4817,
            "text": "Twalav win iwexxôen,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4818,
            "text": "i ifkan cwiî, iccuêen?",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4819,
            "text": "Day isâa tamusni n tbavnit, da iwala?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4820,
            "text": "Ne ur ippuxebbeô ef tewôiqin n Musa?",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4821,
            "text": "Akked Ibôahim ineûêen?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4822,
            "text": "Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev.",
