      {
        "number": 57,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الحَدِيدِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Hadid",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Iron",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5076,
            "text": "Sbuccuâen, s ccekôan Öebbi, ayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 537,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5077,
            "text": "IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; Issidir, Ineqq; u Neppa Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 537,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5078,
            "text": "D Neppa ay d amezwaru, ay d aneggaru; d ayen d ibanen akked wayen iffren. Neppa Iéôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 537,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5079,
            "text": "D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Sinna, Iâannec af usgeld. Iéôa i ikeççmen ar tmurt, akked wayen id iteffen segs, ayen id ippadren seg igenni, akked wayen ippalin uôes. Neppa yidwen, anda ma tellam. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5080,
            "text": "IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ar Öebbi ara ualen lumuô.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5081,
            "text": "Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. Iéôa ayen illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5082,
            "text": "Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS! Efket seg wayen ief i kwen Irra, degs, d igensas. Wid iumnen segwen, iseddqen, d ameqwôan warraz nnsen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5083,
            "text": "Acu ikwen iuen, ur tuminem ara s Öebbi? Amazan ipnabi kwen a ppamnem s Mass nnwen. Ni uôes nnesba nnwen, ma tellam d lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5084,
            "text": "D Neppa id Issadren i umdan iS, issekniyen iberrzen, iwakken a kwen Issuffe si tillas ar tafat. Ih, Öebbi, fellawen, d Umâin Ipêunun.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5085,
            "text": "Acu ikwen iuen, ur tepseddiqem deg ubrid n Öebbi? N Öebbi lweôt n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur taâdilem ara: wid iseddqen uqbel lelb, u nnuen, widak, ad aâlayen, nezzeh, sennig wid iseddqen sin er da, u nnuen. Iwaââed asen akw Öebbi ûûam. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 472,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5086,
            "text": "Win iôevlen i Öebbi aôeîîal umâin, ad as d Irr s lufa, u ines warraz ukyis.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 538,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5087,
            "text": "Asmi ara twaliv lmumnin, argaz tameîîut, teddun tafat nnsen zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen: 'a lxiô nnwen, assa, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen a pwekkôem! D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan'.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 539,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5088,
            "text": "Ass ideg ixabiten, argaz tameîîut, ad inin i wid iumnen: 'arout a, a neddem si tafat nnwen'! A d inin: 'ualet ar deffir, a d tqelbem tafat'! Ad yili garasen lêiv, s tebburt. Zdaxel d aêunu, beôôa, zdat es: aâaqeb.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 539,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5089,
            "text": "Ad sen d siwlen: 'day ur nella ara yidwen'? Ad inin: 'ih! Maca, thewwlem iman nnwen, tekkukram, tcukkem, elvent kwen lemcihwat, armi d iusa lameô n Öebbi. Ielv ikwen af Öebbi, uellav'.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 539,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5090,
            "text": "Assa, ur ipwaîîaf feddu segwen, ne seg wid ijehlen. Axxam nnwen d times; d neppat ay d bab nnwen. A tualin tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 539,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 215,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5091,
            "text": "Âani maççi d lawan, i wid iumnen, ad rgagin wulawen nnsen ar usmekti n Öebbi, akked wayen id Issers n tidep? Ur ppilin am wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, zik, u tvul fellasen lmudda. Da qquôen wulawen nnsen; aîas degsen d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 539,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5092,
            "text": "Ecfut ar Öebbi Issidir tamurt, deffir tmeppant is. Ni Nbeggen awen d issekniyen, amendeô ma a pfehmem?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 539,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5093,
            "text": "Ih, wid akked tid ipseddiqen, iôeîlen i Öebbi aôeîîal umâin, ad asen d Irr s lufa, u nnsen arraz ukyis.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 539,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5094,
            "text": "Wid iumnen s Öebbi akked imazanen iS, d nitni ay d iêeqqiyen, u d inagan ar Mass nnsen. Ad awin arraz nnsen akked tafat nnsen. Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 540,
            "ruku": 473,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5095,
            "text": "Cfut ar tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan, d zzhu, d acebbeê, d zzux garawen, asuget n wayla akked derya. Am umedya ugeffur. Iman is âaoben ijehliyen; sinna, ad isliwen, a ten twaliv ppiwôien; da ad êevmen. Di laxeôt, aâaqeb uqsiê akked ssmaê suô Öebbi, akked llza. Tameddurt n ddunit d zzehwa kan ipuôôun.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 540,
            "ruku": 474,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5096,
            "text": "£iwlet ar ssmaê n Mass nnwen, akked Loennet iwesâan am tmurt akked igenni, teppuhegga d i wid iumnen s Öebbi akked imazanen iS. D wagi ay d lfevl n Öebbi. Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 540,
            "ruku": 474,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5097,
            "text": "Ur d tveôôu twait di tmurt, ne deg iman nnwen, siwa ma tura di Tezmamt, uqbel a p id Nawi. Ayagi, s tidep, d ayen isehlen i Öebbi.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 540,
            "ruku": 474,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5098,
            "text": "Iwakken ur kwen ipav wayen tzeglem, ur kwen issefôaê wayen i wen Ifka. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara yal amzuxi, imnefxi,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 540,
            "ruku": 474,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5099,
            "text": "wid ipcuêêun, iêeppmen ccêa af medden. Win i iwexxôen…ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 540,
            "ruku": 474,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5100,
            "text": "Nuzen ed imazanen nne£, s ubeggen. Nessader ed yidsen Tazmamt akked lmizan, iwakken ad ddun imdanen s lêeqq. Nessader ed uzzal, degs vveôô uqsiê, akked ubauô i medden, iwakken ad Iéeô Öebbi anwa ara ifken afus i Neppa akked imazanen iS, di tbavnit. Ih, Öebbi d Uohid, d Uzmir.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 541,
            "ruku": 474,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5101,
            "text": "Ni Nuzen ed Nuê akked Ibôahim. Nerra, si tarwa nnsen, Lambiyya, Tira. Degsen llan wid ipwanhan; aîas segsen d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 541,
            "ruku": 475,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5102,
            "text": "Sinna, Nessevfeô ed, deffir sen, imazanen nne. Nessevfeô ed Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Nefka yas Linoil. Nessekcem deg ulawen n wid iddan yides leênana akked tiéeî. Taxelwit, ur p Nuri fellasen; snulfan p id i llza n Öebbi. Ur qumen ara yis, akken iwata. Nefka arraz nnsen i wid iumnen segsen. Aîas, segsen, d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 541,
            "ruku": 475,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5103,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Amnet s Umazan iS. Ad awen Ifk sin imuren seg uêunu S, ad awen Irr tafat a ppeddum yis, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 541,
            "ruku": 475,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5104,
            "text": "Akken ad éôen At Tezmamt, ar ur zmiren acemma di lfevl n Öebbi. Ih, lfevl deg ufus n Öebbi; Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 541,
            "ruku": 475,
            "hizbQuarter": 216,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 58,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُجَادلَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mujaadila",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Pleading Woman",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5105,
            "text": "Ni Isla Öebbi i wawal n tin i k d ihedôen ef urgaz is. Tepcetkay i Öebbi. Öebbi Isla i umeslay nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Isell, Iéeô.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 542,
            "ruku": 476,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5106,
            "text": "Wid ipmettilen tilawin nnsen ar izugar n tyimmatin nnsen, ur llint d tiyimmatin nnsen - imi tiyimmatin d tid, kan, i ten id iurwen -, ihi, ar d nnan yir awal, akked tikerkas. Ih, Öebbi ard Win Ipsemmiêen, Ipqilin.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 542,
            "ruku": 476,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5107,
            "text": "Wid imetlen, akka, tilawin nnsen, sinna, wexxôen i wayen d nnan, ad brun i wakli, uqbel a tent nnalen. D ayen uuô i kwen nuban. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 542,
            "ruku": 476,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5108,
            "text": "Win ur newâa ara, ilaq ad iuéum sin wagguren, wa deffir wa, uqbel a p innal. Win, daen, ur nezmir ara, ad icceçç sdiset igellilen. Akka, iwakken a ppamnem s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. D tigi ay d tilisa n Öebbi. I ijehliyen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 542,
            "ruku": 476,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5109,
            "text": "Ih, wid ipqamaôen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ad nneqlaben, akken nneqlaben wid i ten id izwaren. Ni Nessers ed issekniyen iberrzen. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb isdullun.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 542,
            "ruku": 476,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5110,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ten id Issker Öebbi, meôôa, ad asen Issken ayen xedmen. Öebbi Iêesb iten, nitni ppun ten. Öebbi d Anagi n yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 542,
            "ruku": 476,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5111,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara ar Öebbi Iéôa i illan di tmurt, i illan deg igenwan? Ur ippili wawal ger krav, mebla ma Illa, Neppa, d wis kué; ne ger smus, u Neppa, d wis sdis. Ama seddaw, ne sennig waya, ad Yili yidsen, anda ma llan. Da, ad asen Imel acu xedmen, ass n tnekra. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 543,
            "ruku": 477,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5112,
            "text": "Ur twalav ara wid ief tepwagdel temlilit i umeslay, sinna, ualen ar wayen i sen ipwagedlen? Ppemlilin i ubekkav, i wanfal, i âaûûu i Umazan. Ma usan k id, ad sellmen fellak s wayen ur d Ipsellim fellak Öebbi. Qqaôen deg ulawen nnsen: 'awi d kan ur a Ipâuqub ara Öebbi ef wayen neqqaô'! Loahennama beôka ten. Ad ôen degs. A tualin icemten!",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 543,
            "ruku": 477,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5113,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma temlalem i wawal, ur ppemlilit ara i ubekkav, i wanfal, i âaûûu i Umazan. Ppemlilit i tezdeg akked uêezzeb. Ëezzbet i Öebbi uuô ara tepwafesrem.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 543,
            "ruku": 477,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5114,
            "text": "Timlilit i wawal si Cciîan kan, iwakken ad weblen wid iumnen. Acemma ur ten iîîuôôu, siwa ma Irad Öebbi. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 543,
            "ruku": 477,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5115,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma nnan awen: 'get amkan' di temliliyin, get amkan! Öebbi ad awen Ig amkan. Ma nnan awen: 'ooet amkan', ooet amkan! Ad Issali Öebbi tidekkaôin, wid iumnen segwen, akked wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 543,
            "ruku": 477,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5116,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma temlalem i wawal akked Umazan, seddqet uqbel timlilit. Akka i wen ilha, i wen iûfa. Ma ur tewâam ara, ihi, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 477,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5117,
            "text": "Tekukram a pseddqem uqbel timlilit nnwen? Ma ur tseddqem ara, u Issuref awen Öebbi, ééallet, zekkit, aet awal i Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txedmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 477,
            "hizbQuarter": 217,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5118,
            "text": "Day ur twalav ara wid idduklen akked ugdud ief Izzaâf Öebbi? Ur llin segwen ne segsen. Pgalan s tkerkas, u nitni éôan.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5119,
            "text": "Ihegga yasen d Öebbi aâaqeb uqsiê. Ih, ar dir it wayen xeddmen!",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5120,
            "text": "£ilen tagallit nnsen d ssôan. Swexxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb isdullun.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5121,
            "text": "Ur sen d ippawi acemma wayla nnsen, ne dderya nnsen, mgal Öebbi, d awezi. Widak d at tmes. Degs, nitni, ad wekkôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5122,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara ten id Issker Öebbi, meôôa, ad aS gallen akken i wen pgallan. Ad ilen ar ad yili wacu ideg ara îîfen. Aâni maççi, war ccekk, nitni d ikeddaben?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5123,
            "text": "Imelk iten Cciîan armi ppun asmekti n Öebbi. Widak d akabar n Cciîan. Ni akabar n Cciîan d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5124,
            "text": "Ih, wid ipqamaôen Öebbi akked Umazan iS, widak, ad ndellen sennig wiyav.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5125,
            "text": "Iura Öebbi: war ccekk, d Nek akked imazanen iW, ara irebêen. Öebbi, s tidep, d Uohid, d Uzmir.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 544,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5126,
            "text": "Ur teppafev ara agdud iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, ad iddukwel akked wid ipqamaôen Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Xas ma llan d ibabaten nnsen, ne d arraw nnsen, d atmaten nnsen, d alag nnsen. Widak, Iura yasen liman deg ulawen nnsen, Iul iten s ôôuê suôeS. A ten Issekcem di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. Öuvan Öebbi, Iôuva ten. Widak d akabar n Öebbi. Day akabar n Öebbi maççi d win ara irebêen?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 545,
            "ruku": 478,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 59,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الحَشۡرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Hashr",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Exile",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5127,
            "text": "Sbuccuâen Öebbi kra illan deg igenwan, akked kra illan di tmurt. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 545,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5128,
            "text": "D Neppa i Issuffen seg ixxamen nnsen wid ijehlen seg At Tezmamt, i ujemmal amezwaru. Ur tuminem ara ad ffen. £ilen leswaô nnsen a ten sellken si Öebbi. Ikka yasen d Öebbi seg wanda ur bnin. Issekcem tugdi deg ulawen nnsen. Hudden ixxamen nnsen, s ifassen nnsen, akked ifassen n lmumnin. Meyyzet a wid ipwalin!",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 545,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5129,
            "text": "Lemmer ur asen Iura ara Öebbi neffu, yili Iqeîîa ten di ddunit, u, di laxeôt, fellasen aâaqeb n tmes.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 545,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5130,
            "text": "Ayagi, acku numren Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Win inumren Öebbi, ihi, Öebbi, Iwâaô i uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 546,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5131,
            "text": "Ayen tgezmem n tezdayin akked wayen teooam beddent af iéuôan nnsent, s wannuf n Öebbi, iwakken a d Isdull iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 546,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5132,
            "text": "Ayen i s Ifka Öebbi, suôsen, i Umazan iS, ur tebgisem fellas s ioedâen akked lemrakeb. Maca, Öebbi Ippak adabu i Umazan iS, ef wid i S ihwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 546,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5133,
            "text": "Ayen Ifka Öebbi i Umazan iS, suô at tuddar, n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, llezm is, igujilen, imeban, akked win d ibbwi ubrid. Iwakken ur ippual ara ger ifassen imeôkantiyen nnwen. Ayen i wen ifka Umazan, ddmet ep. Ayen i wen ikkes, kkset ep. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi, Iwâaô i uqeîîi.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 546,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5134,
            "text": "I igellilen iminigen, id ssuffen seg ixxamen nnsen akked seg wayla nnsen, ssaramen lfevl n Öebbi akked llza, fkan afus i Öebbi akked Umazan iS, d widak ay d imawlan n tidep.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 546,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5135,
            "text": "Wid izeden ixxamen, iumnen uqbel nnsen, êemmlen wid id iunagen uôsen. Ur néifen idmaren nnsen af wayen i sen ippunefken, smenyafen ten i iman nnsen, xas ma gwran d xuûûen. Wid irran akin ccêa af yiman nnsen, widak d imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 546,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5136,
            "text": "Wid id iusan deffir sen, qqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Semmeê a, akked wamaten nne, i  d izwaren ar liman. Ur Ppara deg ulawen nne, aullu n wid iumnen. A Mass nne! Keçç, s tidep, d Umâin Ipêunun'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 547,
            "ruku": 479,
            "hizbQuarter": 218,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5137,
            "text": "Ur twalav ara ixabiten, la qqaôen i watmaten nnsen ijehlen, seg wAt Tezmamt: 'ma ssuffen kwen, ard a neffe yidwen, ur nessemêas i yiwen, d awezi, mgal nnwen. Ma nnuen kwen, ar ad awen nefk afus'. Ad Icehhed Öebbi, ar nitni d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 547,
            "ruku": 480,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5138,
            "text": "Ma ssuffen ten, ur teffen yidsen. Ma nnuen ten, ur asen ppaken afus. Ma âawnen ten, ad rewlen; ihi, ur ppâawanen!",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 547,
            "ruku": 480,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5139,
            "text": "D kunwi, sennig Öebbi, ay ugaden idmaren nnsen, ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nefhim.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 547,
            "ruku": 480,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5140,
            "text": "Ur kwen pnaen, ddukwlen, siwa ma di temdinin ippwaéeôben, ne deffir leswaô. Lbewv garasen qesseê. A pxilev dduklen, wanag rwin wulawen nnsen. Ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nepxemmim.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 547,
            "ruku": 480,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5141,
            "text": "Cban wid i ten id izwaren s cwiî kan, jeôôben lwexda igiten nnsen, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 547,
            "ruku": 480,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5142,
            "text": "Cban Cciîan, mi s inna i umdan: 'ejhel'! Mi ijhel, inna: 'nek mgirrde k, nek ugade Öebbi, Mass imavalen'!",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 547,
            "ruku": 480,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5143,
            "text": "D times, ih, ara yilin d taggara nnsen, ad wekkôen dinna. Ayagi d arraz imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 480,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5144,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Yal yiwen iwata ad iwali acu ihegga i uzekka. Ëezzbet i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Ippuxebbeô ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 481,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5145,
            "text": "Ur ppilit am wid ippun Öebbi. Irra ten, ppun iman nnsen. Widak d iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 481,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5146,
            "text": "Ur aâdilen ara at tmes akked at Loennet. At Loennet d imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 481,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5147,
            "text": "Lemmer id Nessader Leqwôan agi af udrar, a t twaliv iunez, ifelleq, si tugdi n Öebbi. D wigi ay d imedyaten id Neppawi i medden, amar ad meyyzen.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 481,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5148,
            "text": "Neppa d Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. Neppa, d Aênin Ipêunun.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 481,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5149,
            "text": "D Neppa, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, ay d Agellid, d Ssid, d Tifrat, d Bab n liman, d Aâssas, d Uzmir, d Ajebbaô, d Ameqwôaêan. Gedha s Öebbi, mgal wayen pcaraken!",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 481,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5150,
            "text": "Neppa d Öebbi, d Axellaq, d Bab usisi, d Amessal. I Neppa ismawen imxulaf mavi. Sbuccuâen T akw kra illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 548,
            "ruku": 481,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 60,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُمۡتَحنَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mumtahana",
        "englishNameTranslation": "She that is to be examined",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5151,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur ddukulet d icenga W akked icenga nnwen. Teram ten d iêbiben, u nitni nekôen ayen id iusan, uôwen, n tidep. Èèéaân Amazan, ééaân kwen, imi tumnem s Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ma teffem a ppennaem deg ubrid iW, u tepnadim ôôva W, day a ten terrem, s tuffra, d iêbiben? Nek, Ife akw akken èôi, ayen teffrem akked wayen tennam. Win, segwen, ixedmen akka, innetlaf seg ubrid umâin.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 549,
            "ruku": 482,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5152,
            "text": "Ma elben kwen, ad ualen d icenga nnwen, a kwen merten s ifassen nnsen akked yilsawen nnsen, ad ssirmen a pjehlem.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 549,
            "ruku": 482,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5153,
            "text": "Ass n tnekra, ur kwen infaâ walag, ne tarwa nnwen, d awezi. Ad Ifrez garawen. Öebbi Ipwali igiten nnwen.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 549,
            "ruku": 482,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5154,
            "text": "Ni illa i kunwi umedya ucbiê di Ibôahim akked wid illan yides, mi nnan i ugdud nnsen: 'nemgirred ikwen, kunwi akked wayen teppanzem, war Öebbi. Nenkeô ikwen. Taâdawt akked ddel, ersen d garane, i lebda, alamma tumnem s Öebbi Yiwen'. Kkes ed awalen i inna Ibôahim, i baba s: 'ad velbe a ppeppusemmêev, xas ur iyi Ikellef Öebbi, fellak, s wacemma'. A Mass nne! Ppkal nne fellaK; nutub iK; uôeK tualin.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 549,
            "ruku": 482,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5155,
            "text": "A Mass nne ur a Ppara d ahewwel i wid ijehlen. A Mass nne! Semmeê a. Ih, Keçç d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 549,
            "ruku": 482,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5156,
            "text": "Ni, i kunwi, amedya nnsen ucbiê, i wid iggunin Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Ma d win iwexxôen, ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz!",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 550,
            "ruku": 482,
            "hizbQuarter": 219,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5157,
            "text": "Ahat Öebbi ad Irr tadukli garawen akked wid, segsen, i illan d icenga nnwen. Öebbi d Uzmir, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 550,
            "ruku": 483,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5158,
            "text": "Ur awen Ikkis ara Öebbi, a pmaânem u tweznem, ar wid ur kwen nepna di ddin, ur kwen nessuffu seg ixxamen nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iêemmel wid iweznen.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 550,
            "ruku": 483,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5159,
            "text": "I awen Ikkes Öebbi, d tadukli akked wid i kwen ipnaen di ddin, i kwen issuffen seg ixxamen nnwen, ppaken afus mara kwen ssuffen. Wid iddan yidsen, widak d imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 550,
            "ruku": 483,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5160,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma usant ed uôwen tid iumnen, iunagen, jeôôbet pent. Öebbi Iéôa sennig akw liman nnsent. Ma tufam tent d tid iumnen, ur tent pparat ara i ijehliyen. Ur asen êellent, ur asent êellen. Efket asen ayen ûûeôfen. Ulac uilif ma tuem tent, ma tefkam asent tuççit nnsent. Ur pnasabet tijehliyin. Ssutret ayen tûeôôfem, ad ssutren ayen ûûeôfen. Akka ay d aêuddu n Öebbi. Ipêuddu garawen. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 550,
            "ruku": 483,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5161,
            "text": "Ma terwel tmeîîut, si tlawin nnwen, ar ijehliyen, sinna, tâaqbem, efket, ayen ûûeôfen, i wid iwumi ôôuêent tlawin nnsen. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, syiS ay tumnem.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 550,
            "ruku": 483,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5162,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Ma usant ed uôek tid iumnen, ad ak gallent ur pcarakent i Öebbi acemma, ur ppakwrent, ur zennunt, ur neqqent tarwa nnsent, ur teccvent s ifassen ne s ivaôen nnsent, ur k ppâuûunt di lewqama, eôêeb yisent, ssuter i Öebbi ad asent Isemmeê. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 551,
            "ruku": 483,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5163,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ur ddukulet akked agdud ief Izzâaf Öebbi. Ni uysen laxeôt, akken uysen ijehliyen wid illan di tneîlin.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 551,
            "ruku": 483,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 61,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الصَّفِّ",
        "englishName": "As-Saff",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Ranks",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5164,
            "text": "Sbuccuâen Öebbi, kra illan deg igenwan, akked kra illan di tmurt. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 551,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5165,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Acimi id teqqaôem ayen ur txeddmem?",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 551,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5166,
            "text": "D lâaô meqqwôen, ar Öebbi, ma teqqaôem ayen ur txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 551,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5167,
            "text": "Ih, Öebbi Iêemmel wid ipnaen deg ubrid iS, d ûûef, nitni, amzun d lebni, iéevêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 551,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5168,
            "text": "Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: 'a yagdud iw! Acimi la yi teîîuôum, u ni teéôam nek d amazan n Öebbi uôwen'? Mi ffen i ubrid, Öebbi Issuffe i ubrid ulawen nnsen. Öebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 551,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5169,
            "text": "Mi inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem: 'A yAt Isôail! Nek d amazan n Öebbi uôwen, ad tebbte ayen iyi d izwaren n Tuôa. U a kwen beccôe s Umazan ara d iasen, deffir i, ism is Aêmed'. Mi ten id iusa s ubeggen, nnan: 'wagi d ssêur n ûûeê'.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5170,
            "text": "Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas af Öebbi, u neppa ipwanced ar wannuz? Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5171,
            "text": "Ban ad ssexsin tafat n Öebbi, s imawen nnsen. Öebbi ad Itim tafat iS, di nneqwma ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5172,
            "text": "D Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS, s nnhaya, d ddin n tidep, iwakken a t issifrir f ddin meôôa, di nneqwma ijehliyen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 484,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5173,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma d awen Mle ssuq ara kwen isellken seg uâaqeb aqeôêan?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 485,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5174,
            "text": "Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Nnaet deg ubrid n Öebbi s wayla nnwen, u s yiman nnwen; ppif akka i kunwi, lemmer tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 485,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5175,
            "text": "Ad awen Isemmeê ibekkaven nnwen; a kwen Issekcem ar leonanat degsen isaffen ppazzalen, tinezduin igerzen, di leonanat n Âaden; d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 485,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5176,
            "text": "Ayen têemmlem nniven: afus suô Öebbi akked lelb aqôib. Ssefôeê lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 485,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5177,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Illit d iwiziwen n Öebbi, akken inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, i inmahalen is: 'anwi ay d iwiziwen iw ar Öebbi'? Nnan d inmahalen: 'nekwni d iwiziwen n Öebbi'. Tumen terbaât, tejhel terbaât, n At Isôail. Nefka afus i wid iumnen, mgal icenga nnsen, da rebêen.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 552,
            "ruku": 485,
            "hizbQuarter": 220,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 62,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الجُمُعَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Jumu'a",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Friday",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5178,
            "text": "Sbuccuâen Öebbi, kra illan deg igenwan, u kra illan di tmurt. Agellid, Ssid, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5179,
            "text": "D Neppa id Iuznen i wid ur neôi, Amazan segsen, iqqaô asen issekniyen iS. Izizdig iten, isselmad asen Tazmamt akked ûûwab, xas llan, zik, di ttelfan n ûûeê.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5180,
            "text": "U i wid nniven, mara awven uôsen. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5181,
            "text": "D wagi ay d lfevl n Öebbi. Ippak it i win Iba. Öebbi, d bab n lfevl ameqwôahan.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5182,
            "text": "Am wid iwumi ippukelfen s Tuôa, ur p ssawven. Cuban ayul ibubben tizmamin. I icmet umedya n ugdud inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi! Öebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5183,
            "text": "Ini: 'a yudayen, ma tilem d kunwi ay d iêbiben n Öebbi, war imdanen, ssutret tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep'!",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5184,
            "text": "Ur p ssuturen ara, d awezi, ilmend igiten nnsen. Öebbi Issen imednas.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5185,
            "text": "Ini: 'tameppant iwumi tregwlem, a kwen id temmager, war ccekk. Sinna, a kwen awin ar Win Iéôan ayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. Ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem'.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 553,
            "ruku": 486,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5186,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ma ssawlen d i téallit, ass unejmuâ, iwlet ar usmekti n Öebbi, êebset ttjaôa. Ppif akka i kunwi, lemmer tessinem.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 554,
            "ruku": 487,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5187,
            "text": "Mi tfukk téallit, mfaôaqet di tmurt, nadit lfevl n Öebbi, mmektit ed aîas Öebbi, amar a prebêem.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 554,
            "ruku": 487,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5188,
            "text": "Mi walan ssuq, ne anecôeê, ad azlen uôes, a k ooen tbeddev. Ini: 'ayen illan ar Öebbi yif anecôeê akked ssuq. Öebbi Yif akw iôeééaqen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 554,
            "ruku": 487,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 63,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُنَافِقُونَ",
        "englishName": "Al-Munaafiqoon",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Hypocrites",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5189,
            "text": "Ma usan d uôek ixabiten, ad ak inin: 'a ncehhed ar keçç, war ccekk, d Amazan n Öebbi'. Öebbi Iéôa ar keçç, war ccekk, d Amazan iS. Öebbi ad Icehhed ar, s tidep, ixabiten d ikeddaben.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 554,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5190,
            "text": "Ëesben tagallit nnsen d laânaya, da ssefôaen abrid n Öebbi. Ihi, a yicmet wayen xeddmen!",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 554,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5191,
            "text": "Akka, acku llan umnen, sinna, jehlen. Ppuselen wulawen nnsen, da nitni ur mêiûen.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 554,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 221,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5192,
            "text": "Mi ten twalav, a k taâoeb tiddi nnsen. Ma mmeslayen, tessemêasev i wawal nnsen. Amzun nitni d isaôen i isenden, ilen yal tiôi fellasen. Acengu, d nitni; êader iman ik segsen. A ten Ine Öebbi! Acêal wexxôen!",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 554,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5193,
            "text": "Ma nnan asen: 'yyaw, ad issuter Umazan n Öebbi a ppeppusemmêem', ad bernen iqweôôa nnsen, a ten twaliv wexxôen s temweô.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 555,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5194,
            "text": "Iâuva fellasen tessutrev, ne ur tessutrev ad ppusemmêen. Ur sen Ipsemmiê Öebbi, d awezi. Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud iballaen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 555,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5195,
            "text": "Nitni i iqqaôen: 'ur pseddiqet, i wid iddan akked Umazan n Öebbi, alamma mmebruzzâen'. N Öebbi igerrujen igenwan akked tmurt, maca ixabiten ur mêiûen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 555,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5196,
            "text": "Qqaôen: 'ma nual ar Lmadina, war ccekk, uzmir ad issuffe, segs, uôhif'. Tazmert, n Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked lmumnin, maca, ixabiten ur éôin.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 555,
            "ruku": 488,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5197,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! £uôwat a kwen ssbaâden, af usmekti n Öebbi, wayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen! Wid igan akka, ihi, widak d imexsuôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 555,
            "ruku": 489,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5198,
            "text": "Ssedqet seg wayen i wen Nefka, uqbel a d tas tmeppant ar yiwen degwen, ad yini: 'a Mass iw! Lemmer ad iyi Teswexxôev ar lajel aqôib, ad seddqe, ad ili seg wid imaânen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 555,
            "ruku": 489,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5199,
            "text": "Ur Irennu Öebbi di laâmeô, d awezi, ma iusa d lajel is. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 555,
            "ruku": 489,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 64,
        "name": "سُورَةُ التَّغَابُنِ",
        "englishName": "At-Taghaabun",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Mutual Disillusion",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5200,
            "text": "I illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, sbuccuâen Öebbi. IneS tagelda; ineS wannuz; Neppa Izmer i yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5201,
            "text": "Neppa ikwen Ixelqen; segwen ajehli, segwen lmumen. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5202,
            "text": "Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Imsel ikwen, Iûeggem amsal nnwen. £uôeS tualin.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5203,
            "text": "Iéôa i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Iéôa ayen teffrem akked wayen tennam. Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5204,
            "text": "Ma iusa kwen id usali n wid illan, zik, d ijehliyen? Jeôben lwexda n tikli nnsen. Fellasen, aâaqeb aqeôêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5205,
            "text": "Ayagi, imi sen ppasen imazanen nnsen s ubeggen. Nnan: 'aâni d amdan ara  inhun'? Da jehlen, xedâan. Ur Iclaâ Öebbi. Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5206,
            "text": "Pputebten ijehliyen ar, d awezi, ur d pnekkaren. Ini: 'xaîi! S Mass iw, ard a d tekkrem, sinna ard a ppepwaxebbôem ef wayen txeddmem'! Ayagi, i Öebbi, d ushil.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5207,
            "text": "Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, akked tafat id Nessers. Öebbi Ippuxebbeô ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5208,
            "text": "Ass ideg ara kwen Issemlil, i wass ujemmel, ass nni, d ass umuôôu. Win iumnen s Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad as Ikkes tucmitin is, a t Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad iwekkeô i lebda. D wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 556,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5209,
            "text": "Wid ijehlen u inekôen issekniyen nne£, widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen. A taggara icemten!",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 490,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5210,
            "text": "Ur d teppas twait, siwa ma Irad Öebbi. Win iumnen s Öebbi, ad Inhu ul is. Öebbi Iéôa yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5211,
            "text": "Aet awal i Öebbi, aet awal i Umazan! Ma twexxôem, i iwatan kan, i Umazan nne£, siwa anabi ipbegginen.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5212,
            "text": "Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5213,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! S tidep, kra n tlawin nnwen akked tarwa nnwen, d icenga nnwen. Ëadret iman nnwen segsen! Ma tsemmêem, teppum, tsemmêem, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5214,
            "text": "Ayla nnwen akked dderya nnwen, d ahewwel kan, wanag, ar Öebbi, illa warraz ameqwôahan.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5215,
            "text": "Ëezzbet i Öebbi ayen iwumi tzemrem. Ëesset, ôavit, seddqet! Yif it i iman nnwen. Wid ikksen ccêa i iman nnsen, widak d imerbaê.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5216,
            "text": "Ma tôevlem i Öebbi aôeîîal igerzen, ad awen d Irr sin imuren, ad awen Isemmeê. Öebbi Iceffu, Iêellem.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5217,
            "text": "Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ivehôen, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 557,
            "ruku": 491,
            "hizbQuarter": 222,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 65,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الطَّلَاقِ",
        "englishName": "At-Talaaq",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Divorce",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5218,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Mara tebrum i tlawin, brut asent mara tâaddi tallit n tarda nnsent. Ëesbet tallit. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, Mass nnwen. Ur tent ssuffuet si texxamin nnsent, ur d teffent, siwa ma, s tidep, ccvent. D tigi ay d tilisa n Öebbi. Win izegren tilisa n Öebbi, ni idens imanis. Ur teéôiv ara, ahat Öebbi a d Iazen lameô, ssyen eô da.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 558,
            "ruku": 492,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5219,
            "text": "Mi ssawvent lajel nnsent, âacôet pent s lewqama, ne mfaôaqet yidsent, s lewqama. Awit ed sin inagan iêeqqiyen segwen, a d cehhden zdat Öebbi. Ataya wayen uuô ppunedôen, wid iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru. Win ipêezziben i Öebbi, ad as Ildi tibbura,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 558,
            "ruku": 492,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5220,
            "text": "a t Iit s wanda ur iêtim. Win iîîfen di Öebbi, a t Iqennaâ. Ih, Öebbi Issâadday lameô iS. Ni Öebbi Iwzen yal cci.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 558,
            "ruku": 492,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5221,
            "text": "I tigad, n tlawin nnwen, i iuysen tarda, ma illa ccekk, tallit ugani nnsent: krav wagguren. Akken i tid ur nebdi tarda. Tid ibbwin tadist, tallit nnsent ar tinnufra nnsent. Win ipêezziben i Öebbi, s lameô iS, ad as Istiser.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 558,
            "ruku": 492,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5222,
            "text": "D wagi ay d lameô n Öebbi i wen d Issers. Win ipêezziben i Öebbi, ad as Ikkes tucmitin is, ad Issali arraz is.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 558,
            "ruku": 492,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5223,
            "text": "Ad asent tefkem tanezdut anda tzedem, akken tewâam. Ur tent îîuôôut s tririt nnsent ar lêeôs. Ma llant s tadist, ûeôôfet fellasent, alamma d tinnufra nnsent. Ma ssuîvent tarwa nnwen, efket asent taqdiât nnsent; mwafaqet s tiéeî. Ma temnamarem, a ppessuîîev tmeîîut nniven.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 559,
            "ruku": 492,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5224,
            "text": "Bu udrim ad iûeôôef segs. Win ixuû ôôeéq ad iûeôôef seg wayen i s Ifka Öebbi. Ur Ipkellif Öebbi taôwiêt, siwa ar ayen i s Ifka. Öebbi ad Issuffe laâtab ar tafat.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 559,
            "ruku": 492,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5225,
            "text": "Acêal n temdinin i inuqmen lameô n Mass nnsent akked imazanen iS! Nêuseb itent leêsab uqsiê. Nâaqeb itent s uâaqeb issexven.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 559,
            "ruku": 493,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5226,
            "text": "Jeôôbent lwexda igiten nnsent. D lexsaôa ay d iooa lameô nnsent.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 559,
            "ruku": 493,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5227,
            "text": "Öebbi Ihegga yasen aâaqeb uqsiê. Ëezzbet i Öebbi a yuâqilen iumnen! Ni Öebbi Issers awen d asmekti;",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 559,
            "ruku": 493,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5228,
            "text": "Amazan i wen immalen issekniyen n Öebbi iberrzen, iwakken ad Issuffe, si tillas ar tafat, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Wid iumnen s Öebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen i lebda. Ni Öebbi Igerrez asen ôôeéq.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 559,
            "ruku": 493,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5229,
            "text": "Öebbi i Ixelqen ûa igenwan, akked tmurt am nitni. Lameô iprusu garasen, iwakken a ppeéôem ar Öebbi Izmer i yal cci, u Öebbi Izzi i yal cci s tmusni.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 559,
            "ruku": 493,
            "hizbQuarter": 223,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 66,
        "name": "سُورَةُ التَّحۡرِيمِ",
        "englishName": "At-Tahrim",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Prohibition",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5230,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Ayeô tgedlev ayen i k Iêell Öebbi? Tqennâav tilawin ik. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 560,
            "ruku": 494,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5231,
            "text": "Öebbi Iêeppem fellawen a pêentem. Öebbi d Bab nnwen. Neppa d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 560,
            "ruku": 494,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5232,
            "text": "Mi inna Nnbi sser, i yiwet si tlawin is, u temla, Öebbi Issken it i neppa. Ixebbeô s wumur, iffer amur, segs. Mi p iaâlem s waya, tenna: 'wi k imlan aya'? Inna: 'Imla yi t Win Issnen, Ippuxebbôen'.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 560,
            "ruku": 494,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5233,
            "text": "Ma tutubemt Öebbi, ihi knan wulawen n kwent. Ma tedduklemt as, ihi, d Öebbi ay d Bab is, u, deffir waya, ad ilin di talalt is: Jebrayen, ûûam n lmumnin, u lmalayek ad fkent afud.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 560,
            "ruku": 494,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5234,
            "text": "Ma ibra yakwent, Izmer Öebbi ad as d Inûef s tlawin i kwent yifen, timvuâin, tid iumnen, ipéallan, iutuben, iâabden, ippuéumen, tid ijeôben tissulya, ne tiâazriyin.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 560,
            "ruku": 494,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5235,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Ëadret iman nnwen akked twacult nnwen, si tmes, isaôen is d imdanen akked idaen! Fellas lmalayek tuohidin, tuqsiêin, ur nepwexxiô i wayen i sent Iumeô Öebbi, i ixedmen i sent ipwamôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 560,
            "ruku": 494,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5236,
            "text": "A wid ijehlen, ulayeô testefôem assa! A ppeppuqeîîim kan ef wayen txeddmem.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 560,
            "ruku": 494,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5237,
            "text": "A wid iumnen! Utubet Öebbi, ppuba n ûûeê! Ahat Mass nnwen ad awen Ikkes tucmitin nnwen, u a kwen Issekcem ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Assen, Öebbi ur Isdullu Nnbi akked wid iumnen yides. Tafat nnsen teppeddu zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen. Ad qqaôen: 'a Mass nne! Tim ane tafat nne, Semmeê ane; ih, Keçç, Tzemrev i yal cci'.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 561,
            "ruku": 495,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5238,
            "text": "A Nnbi! Nna ijehliyen akked ixabiten! Iqsiê uôsen! Axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d tualin tucmip.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 561,
            "ruku": 495,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5239,
            "text": "Ifka d Öebbi amedya i wid ijehlen: tameîîut n Nuê akked tmeîîut n Luî. Llant ger ifassen n sin imdanen, seg wid imaânen n imdanen nne. £uüôôent pen. Ur zmiren a tent sselken s wacemma, seg ufus n Öebbi. Ancad: 'kecmemt ar tmes akked wid ikecmen'!",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 561,
            "ruku": 495,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5240,
            "text": "Ifka d Öebbi amedya i wid iumnen, tameîîut n Ferâun, mi tenna: 'a Mass iw! Ebnu yi, uôeK, taxxamt di Loennet, Sellek iyi si Ferâun akked igiten is, Sellek iyi si lqum imednas'!",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 561,
            "ruku": 495,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5241,
            "text": "U Meryem ult Âimôan i izazdgen tuzzuft is. Nenfes uôes si ôôuê nne£, tepputebbet ef wawalen akked tezmamin n Mass is. Neppat seg wid ipéallan.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 28,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 561,
            "ruku": 495,
            "hizbQuarter": 224,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 67,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُلۡكِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mulk",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Sovereignty",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5242,
            "text": "Iôqa Bu tgelda deg ufus iS, u Neppa, Izmer i yal cci;",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5243,
            "text": "i Ixelqen tameppant, tameddurt, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb: anwa degwen ara ixedmen igiten ilhan sennig wiyav. Neppa d Uzmir, Ipsemmiê;",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5244,
            "text": "i Ixelqen ûa igenwan d idurra. Deg wayen Ixleq Uênin, ur tepwaliv ayen ixuûûen. Ernu sikked ma a pwaliv iisiyen!",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5245,
            "text": "Sinna, ger tiî ik berdayen. Iéôi a d iual uôek, iêfa, u inzef.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5246,
            "text": "Ni Ncebbeê igenni aqôib s teftilin, Nôeooem yisent cwaîen, Nhegga yasen aâaqeb n tmes.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5247,
            "text": "I wid inekôen Mass nnsen, aâaqeb n Loahennama. A tualin tucmip!",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5248,
            "text": "Mi pwaveggôen uôes, ad slen la tesraâriâ, u neppat trekkem.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5249,
            "text": "Qôib a ppeftutes seg iûiv. Yal tikelt ara iwaveggeô uôes urbaâ, a ten steqsin iâssasen is: 'aâni ur kwen id iusi ara uneddaô'?",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5250,
            "text": "Ad inin: 'ih, iusa ya d uneddaô, nenkeô u nenna: ur illi ay d Issuder Öebbi, aql akwen kan di lewlav meqqwôen'!",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5251,
            "text": "U nnan: 'lemmer nelli nsell ne nfehhem, ur nelli seg wat tmes'.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5252,
            "text": "Qaôôen s ibekkaven nnsen. Asêaq i at tmes!",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5253,
            "text": "Wanag, i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, di tbavnit, ssmaê akked warraz meqqwôen.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 562,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5254,
            "text": "Hedôet s sser ne âinani, ihi, Neppa Iéôa ayen illan deg idmaren.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 563,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5255,
            "text": "Day ur Iéôi ara Win Ixelqen, Laîif Ippuxebbôen?",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 563,
            "ruku": 496,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5256,
            "text": "Neppa i wen Irran tamurt d tamvuât. Elêut deg ibraêen is, ççet si ôôeéq is. £uôeS tanekra.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 563,
            "ruku": 497,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5257,
            "text": "Ma tepputebtem ar, Win Illan deg igenni, ad Irr tamurt a ppertem yiswen? Appan la teppembwiwil.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 563,
            "ruku": 497,
            "hizbQuarter": 225,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
