            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5426,
            "text": "Nek, yal tikelt ara ten neccde iwakken a sen Tsemmêev, ad rren ivudan nnsen deg imeééuen nnsen, ad pplen deg iceîîiven nnsen. Ggernennen, zuxxen s temweô.",
