            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5444,
            "text": "Ilmend n tuccva nnsen, evûen, sinna kecmen ar tmes. War Öebbi, ur ppafen imâiwnen nnsen.",
